8,5,66499,66539,'00:46:10.811','00:46:12.478','I can\'t stay at my condo.',-1),(127549,5,66567,66602,'00:46:13.647','00:46:15.087','I thought you sold your dad\'s place.',-1),(127550,5,66603,66630,'00:46:15.148','00:46:16.273','Not yet.',-1),(127551,5,66702,66754,'00:46:19.277','00:46:21.445','I\'m not sure I want to stay at the farm.',-1),(127552,5,66759,66809,'00:46:21.655','00:46:23.735','You\'re not.\nYou\'re just gonna drive me to the airport',-1),(127553,5,66809,66848,'00:46:23.740','00:46:25.366','so I can pick up my car.',-1),(127554,5,66875,66903,'00:46:26.493','00:46:27.660','\"Veal\"?',-1),(127555,5,66918,66949,'00:46:28.286','00:46:29.578','Really.',-1),(127556,5,68750,68833,'00:47:44.613','00:47:48.073','<i>Captain Whitaker, this is Jim Court,</i>\n<i>I\'m with CNN. We\'d like...</i>',-1),(127557,5,68850,68930,'00:47:48.783','00:47:52.119','<i>This is the NBC affiliate in Athens.</i>\n<i>We\'re looking to...</i>',-1),(127558,5,73067,73149,'00:50:44.459','00:50:47.878','<i>In the wake of the deadly</i>\n<i>crash of SouthJet flight 227,</i>',-1),(127559,5,73151,73191,'00:50:47.962','00:50:49.630','<i>we have more questions than answers</i>',-1),(127560,5,73194,73236,'00:50:49.756','00:50:51.507','<i>as to what exactly happened that day.</i>',-1),(127561,5,73238,73290,'00:50:51.591','00:50:53.759','<i>And like many,</i>\n<i>we are out looking for answers.</i>',-1),(127562,5,73295,73362,'00:50:53.968','00:50:56.762','<i>Looking here at the home of pilot</i>\n<i>Captain William \"Whip\" Whitaker.</i>',-1),(127563,5,73376,73420,'00:50:57.347','00:50:59.181','<i>We still have no sighting</i>\n<i>and no comments</i>',-1),(127564,5,73422,73449,'00:50:59.265','00:51:00.391','<i>from the Captain himself.</i>',-1),(127565,5,73451,73523,'00:51:00.475','00:51:03.477','<i>This is Mark Mellon, still on the hunt,</i>\n<i>from midtown Atlanta.</i>',-1),(127566,5,73526,73584,'00:51:03.603','00:51:06.021','<i>You\'ve reached</i>\n<i>the Whitaker Crop Dusting Company,</i>',