 for coming.\nGlad you got my message.',-1),(127587,5,75408,75444,'00:52:22.015','00:52:23.515','- How\'s your eye?\n- Good, good.',-1),(127588,5,75449,75498,'00:52:23.725','00:52:25.768','This is Hugh Lang,\nhe\'s an attorney from Chicago.',-1),(127589,5,75500,75536,'00:52:25.852','00:52:27.352','- Pleasure to meet you, Captain.\n- My pleasure.',-1),(127590,5,75538,75592,'00:52:27.437','00:52:29.688','- Sit down. You want a coffee?\n- Yes, I do.',-1),(127591,5,75598,75648,'00:52:29.939','00:52:32.024','- Could we have some fresh coffee?\n- Yes, sir.',-1),(127592,5,75650,75726,'00:52:32.108','00:52:35.277','We were just talking\nabout your copilot\'s wife.',-1),(127593,5,75740,75796,'00:52:35.862','00:52:38.197','Told a newspaper that\n\"God landed that plane.\"',-1),(127594,5,75802,75854,'00:52:38.448','00:52:40.616','Yeah? Oh, God landed that plane?',-1),(127595,5,75862,75901,'00:52:40.950','00:52:42.576','Well, I do believe God landed the plane.',-1),(127596,5,75903,75941,'00:52:42.660','00:52:44.244','Same way I believe\nGod should hit the buffet,',-1),(127597,5,75943,75988,'00:52:44.329','00:52:46.205','the turkey sausage is excellent.',-1),(127598,5,75994,76034,'00:52:46.456','00:52:48.123','I\'m fine with coffee, thank you.',-1),(127599,5,76040,76097,'00:52:48.374','00:52:50.709','So, Len Caldwell\nreally wanted to get here this morning.',-1),(127600,5,76099,76129,'00:52:50.794','00:52:52.044','Len\'s the president of the pilots\' union.',-1),(127601,5,76131,76183,'00:52:52.128','00:52:54.296','He wanted to be here\nto meet with us and you,',-1),(127602,5,76185,76237,'00:52:54.380','00:52:56.548','but they need him at the crash site.',-1),(127603,5,76239,76287,'00:52:56.633','00:52:58.634','As you know, when a plane goes down,',-1),(127604,5,76289,76363,'00:52:58.718','00:53:01.804','the NTSB sends a Go Team\nto the crash site immediately.',-1),(127605,5,76365,76407,'00:53:01.888','00:53:03.639','They find the flight data recorder?',-1),(127606,5,76409,76437,'00:53:03.723','00:53:04.890','They did. It\'s perfectly intact.',-1),(127607,5,76439,76465,'00:53:04.974','00:53:06.058','Oh, great. Great, great, great.',-1),(127608,5,76467,76497,'00:53:06.142','00:53:07.392','Then that solves everything.',-1),(127609,5,76499,76579,'00:53:07.477','00:53:10.813','So why do we need\na lawyer from Chicago?',-1),(127610,5,76581,76664,'00:53:10.897','00:53:14.358','Well, Hugh specializes\nin criminal negligence.',-1),(127611,5,76671,76711,'00:53:14.651','00:53:16.318','Criminal negligence?',-1),(127612,5,76723,76768,'00:53:16.820','00:53:18.695','Death demands responsibility.',-1),(127613,5,76770,76819,'00:53:18.780','00:53:20.823','Six dead on that plane,\nsomeone has to pay.',-1),(127614,5,76825,76882,'00:53:21.074','00:53:23.450','Yeah, but that\'s a plane\nthat fell apart at...',-1),(127615,5,76884,76928,'00:53:23.535','00:53:25.369','Thank you. Fell apart at 30,000 feet.',-1),(127616,5,76931,76990,'00:53:25.495','00:53:27.955','The airline will try\nto prove equipment failure,',-1),(127617,5,76992,77032,'00:53:28.039','00:53:29.706','which is gonna make\nthe manufacturer responsible.',-1),(127618,5,77034,77079,'00:53:29.791','00:53:31.632','The manufacturer in turn\nis gonna try and prove',-1),(127619,5,77081,77133,'00:53:31.709','00:53:33.877','poor maintenance\nof the equipment by the airline.',-1),(127620,5,77135,77174,'00:53:33.962','00:53:35.587','Or pilot error.',-1),(127621,5,77216,77273,'00:53:37.340','00:53:39.716','I flew the plane inverted,\nthat means upside down, Hugh.',-1),(127622,5,77282,77381,'00:53:40.093','00:53:44.221','You get the picture? A hundred people,\nupside down, 500 feet off the ground.',-1),(127623,5,77383,77422,'00:53:44.305','00:53:45.931','Do you have any idea what that\'s like?',-1),(127624,5,77424,77492,'00:53:46.015','00:53:48.851','I do. I heard the black box\nrecordings last night.',-1),(127625,5,77494,77536,'00:53:48.935','00:53:50.686','Oh, you heard. Are you a pilot?',-1),(127626,5,77538,77561,'00:53:50.770','00:53:51.728','No, I\'m not.',-1),(127627,5,77563,77607,'00:53:51.813','00:53:53.647','You don\'t know what the fuck\nyou\'re talking about, do you?',-1),(127628,5,77609,77633,'00:53:53.731','00:53:54.731','Hugh\'s on our team, Whip.',-1),(127629,5,77634,77662,'00:53:54.774','00:53:55.941','- Is he?\n- Yeah, he is.',-1),(127630,5,77664,77697,'00:53:56.025','00:53:57.401','- He doesn\'t act like he\'s on our team.\n- Well, he is.',-1),(127631,5,77699,77736,'00:53:57.485','00:53:59.027','Asking me questions\nabout fucking pilot error.',-1),(127632,5,77738,77776,'00:53:59.112','00:54:00.696','Listen, it\'s the NTSB\'s ball game.',-1),(127633,5,77778,77812,'00:54:00.780','00:54:02.197','They run the investigation.',-1),(127634,5,77814,77866,'00:54:02.282','00:54:04.449','And they will ultimately\nrule on the cause.',-1),(127635,5,77869,77896,'00:54:04.576','00:54:05.701','And that\'s why we need him.',-1),(127636,5,77898,77956,'00:54:05.785','00:54:08.203','Well, they interview\nthe entire flight crew.',-1),(127637,5,77958,78072,'00:54:08.288','00:54:13.041','They interview the passengers.\nThey hold public hearings.',-1),(127638,5,78075,78105,'00:54:13.126','00:54:14.376','All right, let\'s cut to the chase.',-1),(127639,5,78107,78149,'00:54:14.460','00:54:16.211','Just tell me\nwhat it is I need to know, Charlie.',-1),(127640,5,78151,78272,'00:54:16.296','00:54:21.341','The NTSB Go Team also collects\nblood, hair and skin samples',-1),(127641,5,78274,78371,'00:54:21.426','00:54:25.470','from the entire flight crew for\nthe purposes of a toxicology report.',-1),(127642,5,78374,78434,'00:54:25.597','00:54:28.098','Okay. When do they want to do that?',-1),(127643,5,78443,78506,'00:54:28.474','00:54:31.101','They\'ve already done that.\nIn the hospital.',-1),(127644,5,78508,78550,'00:54:31.185','00:54:32.936','It\'s the first thing they do.',-1),(127645,5,78579,78634,'00:54:34.147','00:54:36.440','You don\'t remember having\nyour blood drawn the night