','Flew that damn thing all over the place.',-1),(127962,5,107348,107380,'01:14:32.844','01:14:34.178','He died.',-1),(127963,5,107396,107436,'01:14:34.846','01:14:36.514','I got a divorce and...',-1),(127964,5,107500,107566,'01:14:39.184','01:14:41.936','I\'ve been trying to sell\nthe place ever since.',-1),(127965,5,107619,107659,'01:14:44.147','01:14:45.815','What about your mom?',-1),(127966,5,107675,107700,'01:14:46.483','01:14:47.525','Dead.',-1),(127967,5,107768,107816,'01:14:50.362','01:14:52.363','You? What about your dad?',-1),(127968,5,107820,107892,'01:14:52.531','01:14:55.533','Well, I\'m pretty sure\nhe lives in Colorado.',-1),(127969,5,107896,107923,'01:14:55.700','01:14:56.826','Yeah?',-1),(127970,5,107954,107990,'01:14:58.120','01:14:59.620','No relationship?',-1),(127971,5,108012,108056,'01:15:00.539','01:15:02.373','It was my mom that raised me.',-1),(127972,5,108062,108100,'01:15:02.624','01:15:04.208','She was incredible.',-1),(127973,5,108135,108220,'01:15:05.627','01:15:09.171','She held it together for so long,\nI couldn\'t even tell how sick she was.',-1),(127974,5,108282,108336,'01:15:11.758','01:15:14.009','We spent those last\nseven months together',-1),(127975,5,108338,108384,'01:15:14.094','01:15:16.011','like we were teenagers.',-1),(127976,5,108418,108509,'01:15:17.430','01:15:21.225','We\'d trade stories\nabout boys and whatever.',-1),(127977,5,108598,108644,'01:15:24.938','01:15:26.856','She loved me.',-1),(127978,5,109062,109097,'01:15:44.291','01:15:45.749','My name\'s Trevor.',-1),(127979,5,109115,109155,'01:15:46.459','01:15:48.127','You saved my mom.',-1),(127980,5,109462,109504,'01:16:00.932','01:16:02.683','It\'s great to see you, Whip.',-1),(127981,5,109506,109558,'01:16:02.767','01:16:04.935','It\'s good to see you, too, Margaret.',-1),(127982,5,109687,109731,'01:16:10.317','01:16:12.151','The service was so nice.',-1),(127983,5,109734,109798,'01:16:12.277','01:16:14.945','I mean, all these people\nwho wanted to say goodbye.',-1),(127984,5,109839,109919,'01:16:16.656','01:16:19.992','Trina looked so beautiful in there.\nDidn\'t you think so?',-1),(127985,5,109931,110023,'01:16:20.493','01:16:24.330','I mean, like she was just\ngoing to wake up and smile.',-1),(127986,5,110031,110103,'01:16:24.664','01:16:27.666','I didn\'t go in. L... l just couldn\'t.',-1),(127987,5,110148,110264,'01:16:29.502','01:16:34.340','Trevor, find Daddy, baby.\nHe\'s over there by Mr. Benton.',-1),(127988,5,110436,110495,'01:16:41.514','01:16:43.974','You really should come\nto the counseling group.',-1),(127989,5,110497,110548,'01:16:44.059','01:16:46.185','The union has great people\nfor us to talk to.',-1),(127990,5,110551,110603,'01:16:46.311','01:16:48.479','I can\'t. Really. I...',-1),(127991,5,110628,110658,'01:16:49.522','01:16:50.773','I will.',-1),(127992,5,110755,110795,'01:16:54.819','01:16:56.487','Well...',-1),(127993,5,110828,110875,'01:16:57.864','01:16:59.823','- You take care, okay, Whip?\n- Okay.',-1),(127994,5,110888,110928,'01:17:00.367','01:17:02.034','Listen, Margaret.',-1),(127995,5,110996,111052,'01:17:04.871','01:17:07.206','You know I\'m in the middle of this',-1),(127996,5,111072,111151,'01:17:08.041','01:17:11.293','investigation. The NTSB\nis investigating the crash.',-1),(127997,5,111153,111195,'01:17:11.378','01:17:13.128','Yeah. I\'m gonna talk to them next week.',-1),(127998,5,111197,111272,'01:17:13.213','01:17:16.340','Yeah. Well, I\'m... I\'m a little nervous',-1),(127999,5,111274,111399,'01:17:16.424','01:17:21.637','because I was out the night\nbefore the crash, at dinner.',-1),(128000,5,111401,111430,'01:17:21.721','01:17:22.930','Yeah. With Trina.',-1),(128001,5,111432,111482,'01:17:23.014','01:17:25.099','Right. And I had two glasses of wine,',-1),(128002,5,111484,111544,'01:17:25.183','01:17:27.685','and they\'re probably going to ask you',-1),(128003,5,111549,111590,'01:17:27.894','01:17:29.603','about my condition that morning,',-1),(128004,5,111592,111666,'01:17:29.688','01:17:32.773','or whether you thought\nI had anything to drink.',-1),(128005,5,111757,111784,'01:17:36.569','01:17:37.695','What?',-1),(128006,5,111864,111911,'01:17:41.032','01:17:42.992','I\'ve known you 11 years, Whip.',-1),(128007,5,111913,111939,'01:17:43.076','01:17:44.159','Right.',-1),(128008,5,111941,111994,'01:17:44.244','01:17:46.453','You want to tell me that\nyou and Trina went to dinner',-1),(128009,5,111996,112045,'01:17:46.538','01:17:48.580','- and you had two glasses of wine?\n- No.',-1),(128010,5,112047,112100,'01:17:48.665','01:17:50.874','Sounds like a nice restaurant.\nNow, which one was it?',-1),(128011,5,112103,112174,'01:17:50.959','01:17:53.919','You have to say that it was\nan ordinary day, Margaret.',-1),(128012,5,112176,112203,'01:17:54.004','01:17:55.129','I mean, it was an ordinary day.',-1),(128013,5,112205,112264,'01:17:55.213','01:17:57.673','You know me. I was in shape to fly.',-1),(128014,5,112370,112409,'01:18:02.095','01:18:03.721','You have a problem with saying that?',-1),(128015,5,112462,112502,'01:18:05.932','01:18:07.599','It\'s a lie, Whip.',-1),(128016,5,112507,112591,'01:18:07.809','01:18:11.312','It\'s a lie. Trina told me\nyou two hadn\'t been to sleep.',-1),(128017,5,112593,112715,'01:18:11.396','01:18:16.483','Well, my lack of sleep had nothing to do\nwith that plane falling apart, Margaret.',-1),(128018,5,112717,112752,'01:18:16.568','01:18:18.027','I\'m just trying to get this thing straight.',-1),(128019,5,112754,112823,'01:18:18.111','01:18:20.988','Now you think any other pilot could have\nlanded that plane and saved more lives?',-1),(128020,5,112825,112855,'01:18:21.072','01:18:22.323','I didn\'t say that, Whip.\nI can\'t imagine another...',-1),(128021,5,112857,112881,'01:18:22.407','01:18:23.407','All right, then.',-1),(128022,5,112883,112948,'01:18:23.491','01:18:26.201','Well, imagine your son,\nTrevor, in this church,',-1),(128023,5,112950,112979,'01:18:26.286','01:18:27.494','looking at you in that box.',-1),(128024,5,112981,113029,'01:18:27.579','01:18:29.580','Or my son visiting me in prison. And...',-1),(128025,5,113031,113109,'01:18:29.664','01:18:32.875','- Please, Whip, enough. Enough, Whip.\n- And for the next 40 years...',-1),(128026,5,113111,113170,'01:18:32.959','01:18:35.419','Don\'t you think we\'ve all had enough?',-1),(128027,5,113351,113397,'01:18:42.969','01:18:44.887','I need this, Margaret.',-1),(128028,5,113577,113618,'01:18:52.395','01:18:54.104','What do you want me to say?',-1),(128029,5,113656,113695,'01:18:55.690','01:18:57.316','I just...',-1),(128030,5,113742,113788,'01:18:59.277','01:19:01.195','it was an ordinary day.',-1),(128031,5,113850,113930,'01:19:03.782','01:19:07.117','The storm, after we took off,',-1),(128032,5,113938,113978,'01:19:07.452','01:19:09.119','was very severe.',-1),(128033,5,114014,114082,'01:19:10.622','01:19:13.457','But as far as\nthe flight crew was concerned,',-1),(128034,5,114114,114170,'01:19:14.751','01:19:17.086','it was a perfectly ordinary day.',-1),(128035,5,114683,114723,'01:19:38.483','01:19:40.150','- Hey.\n- Hi.',-1),(128036,5,114791,114821,'01:19:42.987','01:19:44.238','You okay?',-1),(128037,5,114827,114859,'01:19:44.489','01:19:45.823','Yeah, yeah.',-1),(128038,5,114889,114919,'01:19:47.075','01:19:48.325','So?',-1),(128039,5,114924,114978,'01:19:48.535','01:19:50.786','Well, I got through my first day.\nThey didn\'t fire me.',-1),(128040,5,114980,115010,'01:19:50.870','01:19:52.121','- So...\n- Good. Good.',-1),(128041,5,115031,115098,'01:19:52.997','01:19:55.791','And they need someone to work\nthe night shift and they asked me.',-1),(128042,5,115101,115140,'01:19:55.875','01:19:57.501','It\'s time and a half, so...',-1),(128043,5,115199,115230,'01:19:59.963','01:20:01.255','I got a vest.',-1),(128044,5,115252,115285,'01:20:02.173','01:20:03.549','- And a little name tag.\n- Nice.',-1),(128045,5,115287,115311,'01:20:03.633','01:20:04.633','I got you something.',-1),(128046,5,115313,115341,'01:20:04.717','01:20:05.884','- Yeah?\n- Yeah.',-1),(128047,5,115455,115480,'01:20:10.640','01:20:11.682','It\'s a P-51 Mustang.',-1),(128048,5,115483,115508,'01:20:11.808','01:20:12.850','I know it\'s a P-51...',-1),(128049,5,115511,115538,'01:20:12.976','01:20:14.097','Your daddy fly one of those?',-1),(128050,5,115539,115567,'01:20:14.144','01:20:15.310','Yes, he did.',-1),(128051,5,115591,115631,'01:20:16.312','01:20:17.980','It\'s cause for celebration.',-1),(128052,5,115639,115719,'01:20:18.314','01:20:21.650','Oh, well, I promised Sheila that\nI\'d go to this AA meeting now.',-1),(128053,5,115724,115779,'01:20:21.860','01:20:24.153','She\'s my sponsor,\nthe one that\'s been helping me.',-1),(128054,5,115781,115815,'01:20:24.237','01:20:25.654','Can we celebrate tomorrow night?',-1),(128055,5,115827,115852,'01:20:26.156','01:20:27.197','Yeah.',-1),(128056,5,115871,115895,'01:20:27.991','01:20:28.991','Yeah, sure, come on.',-1),(128057,5,116003,116040,'01:20:33.496','01:20:35.038','You know, you could come with me.',-1),(128058,5,116047,116081,'01:20:35.331','01:20:36.748','To the meeting.',-1),(128059,5,116085,116152,'01:20:36.875','01:20:39.668','It\'s an open meeting,\nmeaning that anyone can come.',-1),(128060,5,116164,116200,'01:20:40.170','01:20:41.670','Even you.',-1),(128061,5,116236,116295,'01:20:43.173','01:20:45.632','<i>So the cops got a flashlight</i>\n<i>on me behind the dumpster.</i>',-1),(128062,5,116297,116334,'01:20:45.717','01:20:47.259','<i>I\'m wearing nothing</i>\n<i>but my girlfriend\'s panties,</i>',-1),(128063,5,116337,116400,'01:20:47.385','01:20:50.012','<i>I got vomit all down</i>\n<i>the front of my chest.</i>',-1),(128064,5,116405,116486,'01:20:50.221','01:20:53.599','<i>And I say to them,</i>\n<i>\"I might have had two beers.\"</i>',-1),(128065,5,116664,116732,'01:21:01.024','01:21:03.859','<i>So that\'s how</i>\n<i>I got the nickname \"Two Beer Barry.\"</i>',-1),(128066,5,116792,116855,'01:21:06.362','01:21:08.989','<i>I\'m getting the stink eye</i>\n<i>from Ed over here.</i>',-1),(128067,5,116857,116904,'01:21:09.073','01:21:11.033','<i>Have I gone off format?</i>',-1),(128068,5,116928,116980,'01:21:12.035','01:21:14.203','<i>My name is Barry and I am an alcoholic.</i>',-1),(128069,5,116988,117013,'01:21:14.537','01:21:15.579','Hi, Barry.',-1),(128070,5,117020,117088,'01:21:15.872','01:21:18.707','<i>Are there any other alcoholics present?</i>',-1),(128071,5,117221,117253,'01:21:24.214','01:21:25.547','<i>I always love a meeting where we</i>',-1),(128072,5,117255,117290,'01:21:25.632','01:21:27.090','<i>all have to identify at the top,</i>',-1),(128073,5,117293,117382,'01:21:27.217','01:21:30.928','<i>because it forces me</i>\n<i>to be honest about who I really am.</i>',-1),(128074,5,117417,117478,'01:21:32.388','01:21:34.932','<i>And I never told the truth</i>\n<i>out there, obviously.</i>',-1),(128075,5,117481,117529,'01:21:35.058','01:21:37.059','<i>I lied about everything.</i>',-1),(128076,5,117566,117615,'01:21:38.603','01:21:40.646','<i>I was taught in these rooms</i>\n<i>that I would never get sober</i>',-1),(128077,5,117618,117686,'01:21:40.772','01:21:43.607','<i>if I kept lying,</i>\n<i>but that\'s what I was best at.</i>',-1),(128078,5,117742,117792,'01:21:45.944','01:21:48.028','<i>If I knew anything</i>\n<i>in this world it was how to lie,</i>',-1),(128079,5,117794,117841,'01:21:48.112','01:21:50.072','<i>especially about my drinking.</i>',-1),(128080,5,117849,117954,'01:21:50.406','01:21:54.785','<i>But, whatever. I would lie</i>\n<i>about the name of my dog,</i>',-1),(128081,5,117957,118045,'01:21:54.911','01:21:58.580','<i>I\'d lie about the color of my own hair</i>\n<i>right to your face.</i>',-1),(128082,5,118078,118122,'01:21:59.958','01:22:01.750','<i>And my whole life just became</i>',-1),(128083,5,118140,118203,'01:22:02.502','01:22:05.128','<i>a series of lies strung together by me,</i>',-1),(128084,5,118206,118245,'01:22:05.255','01:22:06.880','<i>- one after the other.</i>\n- I\'m going to go, okay?',-1),(128085,5,118247,118281,'01:22:06.965','01:22:08.382','- Sure.\n- You got a ride home?',-1),(128086,5,118283,118351,'01:22:08.466','01:22:11.301','Yeah. Sheila, she can give\nme a ride. This is Sheila.',-1),(128087,5,118362,118398,'01:22:11.761','01:22:13.262','- How you doing?\n- I\'m Sheila.',-1),(128088,5,118418,118470,'01:22:14.097','01:22:16.265','<i>That my lies would kill me.</i>',-1),(128089,5,118486,118516,'01:22:16.933','01:22:18.183','<i>Left to their own devices,</i>',-1),(128090,5,118519,118594,'01:22:18.309','01:22:21.436','<i>my lies would walk me out that door.</i>',-1),(128091,5,118746,118826,'01:22:27.777','01:22:31.113','<i>Is it safe to say that Captain Whitaker</i>\n<i>remains a bit of a mystery?</i>',-1),(128092,5,118831,118879,'01:22:31.322','01:22:33.323','<i>Those are your words, sir, not mine.</i>',-1),(128093,5,118886,118914,'01:22:33.616','01:22:34.783','<i>I\'ve been speaking to some people</i>',-1),(128094,5,118916,118966,'01:22:34.867','01:22:36.952','<i>who are very close</i>\n<i>to the NTSB investigation.</i>',-1),(128095,5,118971,119031,'01:22:37.161','01:22:39.663','<i>They are confident they will</i>\n<i>soon be able to determine</i>',-1),(128096,5,119034,119087,'01:22:39.789','01:22:41.999','<i>exactly what brought this plane down.</i>',-1),(128097,5,119095,119128,'01:22:42.292','01:22:43.667','<i>I\'m sure they will, sir.</i>',-1),(128098,5,119152,119212,'01:22:44.669','01:22:47.170','<i>Well, Ken and Vicky Evans,</i>\n<i>thank you both very much.</i>',-1),(128099,5,119219,119267,'01:22:47.463','01:22:49.464','<i>Thank you, sir. And God bless you.</i>',-1),(128100,5,119587,119627,'01:23:02.812','01:23:04.479','How you feeling, Ken?',-1),(128101,5,119687,119719,'01:23:06.983','01:23:08.317','Happy to be alive.',-1),(128102,5,119724,119776,'01:23:08.526','01:23:10.694','Blessed to be alive.',-1),(128103,5,119835,119896,'01:23:13.156','01:23:15.699','I\'m Captain Whitaker. I was flying with...',-1),(128104,5,119899,119931,'01:23:15.825','01:23:17.159','I know who you are.',-1),(128105,5,119968,120031,'01:23:18.703','01:23:21.330','Excuse me. Could you give us\nsome privacy, please?',-1),(128106,5,120048,120077,'01:23:22.040','01:23:23.248','Thank you.',-1),(128107,5,120364,120396,'01:23:35.178','01:23:36.511','So...',-1),(128108,5,120424,120464,'01:23:37.680','01:23:39.348','How long have you been out of...',-1),(128109,5,120472,120512,'01:23:39.682','01:23:41.350','- Out of a coma?\n- Yeah.',-1),(128110,5,120536,120568,'01:23:42.352','01:23:43.685','Two days.',-1),(128111,5,120625,120653,'01:23:46.064','01:23:47.230','Good.',-1),(128112,5,120684,120772,'01:23:48.524','01:23:52.194','Well, look, I don\'t want\nto disrupt your whole day.',-1),(128113,5,120792,120904,'01:23:53.029','01:23:57.699','And God knows you\'ve been\nswamped by interviews and...',-1),(128114,5,120952,121012,'01:23:59.702','01:24:02.204','You were brilliant on CNN, by the way.',-1),(128115,5,121036,121129,'01:24:03.206','01:24:07.042','Both my legs are crushed.\nMy pelvis is snapped.',-1),(128116,5,121141,121190,'01:24:07.543','01:24:09.586','I\'ll probably never walk again,',-1),(128117,5,121193,121253,'01:24:09.712','01:24:12.214','at least not without a walker or braces.',-1),(128118,5,121273,121322,'01:24:13.049','01:24:15.092','I\'ll certainly never fly again.',-1),(128119,5,121357,121397,'01:24:16.552','01:24:18.220','I\'m very sorry, Ken.',-1),(128120,5,121409,121493,'01:24:18.721','01:24:22.224','That plane was doomed\nthe moment you sat in that cockpit.',-1),(128121,5,121513,121565,'01:24:23.059','01:24:25.227','You reeked like gin or something.',-1),(128122,5,121593,121665,'01:24:26.396','01:24:29.398','I called Vicky\nfrom the plane before we took off.',-1),(128123,5,121693,121737,'01:24:30.566','01:24:32.401','That\'s when the rain kicked up.',-1),(128124,5,121785,121885,'01:24:34.404','01:24:38.573','Well, I don\'t know\nhow much you remember,',-1),(128125,5,121897,121933,'01:24:39.075','01:24:40.575','but that plane,',-1),(128126,5,121953,121993,'01:24:41.411','01:24:43.078','it started falling apart, Ken.',-1),(128127,5,122001,122060,'01:24:43.413','01:24:45.872','I remember everything until we crashed.',-1),(128128,5,122062,122101,'01:24:45.957','01:24:47.582','I know what went on.',-1),(128129,5,122162,122202,'01:24:50.086','01:24:51.753','What are we trying to say, Ken?',-1),(128130,5,122207,122246,'01:24:51.963','01:24:53.588','What are we talking about?',-1),(128131,5,122258,122295,'01:24:54.090','01:24:55.632','I don\'t know, Captain Whitaker.',-1),(128132,5,122298,122326,'01:24:55.758','01:24:56.925','What are we talking about?',-1),(128133,5,122331,122402,'01:24:57.135','01:25:00.095','I\'m just trying to get a sense from you',-1),(128134,5,122442,122530,'01:25:01.764','01:25:05.434','about what you thought\ncaused the crash.',-1),(128135,5,122554,122646,'01:25:06.436','01:25:10.272','Was it the fact that you got on the plane\nstill drunk from the night before?',-1),(128136,5,122702,122806,'01:25:12.608','01:25:16.945','The NTSB is coming back tomorrow\nto finish taking a deposition from me.',-1),(128137,5,122826,122878,'01:25:17.780','01:25:19.948','About the events on that flight.',-1),(128138,5,122886,122982,'01:25:20.283','01:25:24.286','Do you think you\'d be alive\nif I wasn\'t flying that plane?',-1),(128139,5,123018,123042,'01:25:25.788','01:25:26.788','No.',-1),(128140,5,123054,123094,'01:25:27.290','01:25:28.957','We\'d all be dead.',-1),(128141,5,123115,123196,'01:25:29.792','01:25:33.170','But are you going to argue with me\nthat your physical state was tip-top?',-1),(128142,5,123343,123371,'01:25:39.302','01:25:40.469','Wait.',-1),(128143,5,123391,123419,'01:25:41.304','01:25:42.471','Sit.',-1),(128144,5,123439,123467,'01:25:43.306','01:25:44.473','Please.',-1),(128145,5,123603,123680,'01:25:50.146','01:25:53.356','I never shared my opinion\nabout your physical state',-1),(128146,5,123683,123719,'01:25:53.483','01:25:54.983','the morning of the flight.',-1),(128147,5,123751,123791,'01:25:56.319','01:25:57.986','I never said a word.',-1),(128148,5,123816,123840,'01:25:59.030','01:26:00.030','Okay.',-1),(128149,5,123843,123899,'01:26:00.156','01:26:02.491','That crash was preordained.',-1),(128150,5,123935,124031,'01:26:03.993','01:26:07.996','I prayed on it, Captain.\nVicky and I both prayed on it.',-1),(128151,5,124047,124085,'01:26:08.664','01:26:10.248','There is only one judge, sir.',-1),(128152,5,124087,124122,'01:26:10.333','01:26:11.750','Praise Jesus.',-1),(128153,5,124124,124180,'01:26:11.834','01:26:14.169','And he\'s got a higher plan for you.',-1),(128154,5,124200,124308,'01:26:15.004','01:26:19.508','This event,\nalthough it\'s tragic in its loss of life,',-1),(128155,5,124352,124416,'01:26:21.344','01:26:24.012','it\'s also a celebration of life.',-1),(128156,5,124428,124507,'01:26:24.514','01:26:27.808','Nothing happens in\nthe Kingdom of the Lord by mistake, sir.',-1),(128157,5,124509,124537,'01:26:27.892','01:26:29.059','Praise Jesus.',-1),(128158,5,124540,124568,'01:26:29.185','01:26:30.352','Captain.',-1),(128159,5,124597,124642,'01:26:31.562','01:26:33.438','Will you pray with us?',-1),(128160,5,124928,125016,'01:26:45.368','01:26:49.037','Jesus, our savior, we thank you\nfor blessing Captain Whitaker.',-1),(128161,5,125024,125092,'01:26:49.372','01:26:52.207','For guiding his hand\non that fateful morning.',-1),(128162,5,125152,125178,'01:26:54.669','01:26:55.752','- Bye.\n- Bye-bye.',-1),(128163,5,125181,125231,'01:26:55.878','01:26:57.963','- Thanks for the ride.\n- Okay.',-1),(128164,5,125481,125509,'01:27:08.391','01:27:09.558','Hi.',-1),(128165,5,125529,125567,'01:27:10.393','01:27:11.977','Hey, hey.',-1),(128166,5,125649,125686,'01:27:15.398','01:27:16.940','How you doing?',-1),(128167,5,125809,125841,'01:27:22.071','01:27:23.405','Oh, hey. Look.',-1),(128168,5,125865,125897,'01:27:24.407','01:27:25.740','Great, right?',-1),(128169,5,125905,125930,'01:27:26.075','01:27:27.117','It\'s kind of beautiful.',-1),(128170,5,125933,125968,'01:27:27.243','01:27:28.683','It is beautiful, isn\'t it? Like you.',-1),(128171,5,125970,125993,'01:27:28.786','01:27:29.744','Does it work?',-1),(128172,5,125995,126032,'01:27:29.829','01:27:31.371','Yes, it works.',-1),(128173,5,126034,126075,'01:27:31.455','01:27:33.164','I learned how to fly on this baby.',-1),(128174,5,126093,126174,'01:27:33.916','01:27:37.252','Me and my friend Harling,\nwe flew it to Jamaica.',-1),(128175,5,126182,126211,'01:27:37.587','01:27:38.795','Jamaica? In this?',-1),(128176,5,126213,126242,'01:27:38.880','01:27:40.088','Yeah. In this.',-1),(128177,5,126250,126349,'01:27:40.423','01:27:44.551','We went on an overnight fishing trip\nabout two hours south of here.',-1),(128178,5,126351,126415,'01:27:44.635','01:27:47.304','Next thing you know... Bethel, Jamaica.',-1),(128179,5,126442,126465,'01:27:48.431','01:27:49.389','You\'re insane.',-1),(128180,5,126467,126491,'01:27:49.473','01:27:50.473','Yes, I am.',-1),(128181,5,126495,126543,'01:27:50.641','01:27:52.642','It was beautiful. It was like a postcard,',-1),(128182,5,126546,126643,'01:27:52.768','01:27:56.813','you know, like one of those\npicture postcards.',-1),(128183,5,126645,126734,'01:27:56.898','01:28:00.609','White sand, beautiful, sky-blue seas.',-1),(128184,5,126762,126814,'01:28:01.777','01:28:03.945','It was the most\nbeautiful thing I ever saw.',-1),(128185,5,126850,126890,'01:28:05.448','01:28:07.115','Was the water warm?',-1),(128186,5,126914,126946,'01:28:08.117','01:28:09.451','Yes, it was very warm.',-1),(128187,5,126951,126994,'01:28:09.660','01:28:11.453','That\'s my kind of place.',-1),(128188,5,127022,127055,'01:28:12.622','01:28:13.997','Let\'s go.',-1),(128189,5,127074,127132,'01:28:14.790','01:28:17.167','Sure. Why not?',-1),(128190,5,127135,127179,'01:28:17.293','01:28:19.127','Yeah. Let\'s go tomorrow.',-1),(128191,5,127187,127229,'01:28:19.462','01:28:21.212','- Oh, you\'re serious.\n- I\'m dead serious.',-1),(128192,5,127232,127256,'01:28:21.339','01:28:22.339','We\'ll go in the morning.',-1),(128193,5,127259,127294,'01:28:22.465','01:28:23.945','You know, we\'ll just get out of here.',-1),(128194,5,127296,127332,'01:28:24.008','01:28:25.508','- Start over.\n- Whip, we can\'t. No.',-1),(128195,5,127335,127406,'01:28:25.635','01:28:28.595','Yes, we can. It\'ll be beautiful.',-1),(128196,5,127417,127446,'01:28:29.055','01:28:30.263','Bright sand beaches...',-1),(128197,5,127448,127484,'01:28:30.348','01:28:31.848','- I\'m worried about you.\n- It\'s...',-1),(128198,5,127487,127531,'01:28:31.974','01:28:33.808','Don\'t worry about me.\nI\'m fine. Thank you.',-1),(128199,5,127539,127594,'01:28:34.143','01:28:36.436','- You\'re not. You\'re really not.\n- Yes, I am. Yes, I am.',-1),(128200,5,127596,127639,'01:28:36.520','01:28:38.313','You need help.',-1),(128201,5,127659,127707,'01:28:39.148','01:28:41.149','You need rehab, Whip.',-1),(128202,5,127747,127815,'01:28:42.818','01:28:45.654','You think I need rehab?\nSo, you go to two AA meetings',-1),(128203,5,127817,127873,'01:28:45.738','01:28:48.073','and I need rehab? Okay.',-1),(128204,5,127875,127915,'01:28:48.157','01:28:49.824','Hey, look, who are you, Jesus Christ?',-1),(128205,5,127917,127955,'01:28:49.909','01:28:51.493','Don\'t worry about me, okay?',-1),(128206,5,127963,128027,'01:28:51.827','01:28:54.496','You just worry about yourself.\nDon\'t worry about me.',-1),(128207,5,128033,128059,'01:28:54.747','01:28:55.828','We\'re the same, you and me.',-1),(128208,5,128060,128084,'01:28:55.873','01:28:56.873','- No, we\'re not the same.\n- Yeah, we are.',-1),(128209,5,128087,128155,'01:28:56.999','01:28:59.793','We are not the same.\nI don\'t suck dick to get high, okay?',-1),(128210,5,128157,128191,'01:28:59.877','01:29:01.294','And don\'t give me that\nyour mother died...',-1),(128211,5,128193,128218,'01:29:01.379','01:29:02.420','- I never!\n- ...and your father...',-1),(128212,5,128221,128246,'01:29:02.546','01:29:03.588','I never in my life...',-1),(128213,5,128248,128298,'01:29:03.673','01:29:05.757','Bullshit, bullshit, bullshit.',-1),(128214,5,128301,128343,'01:29:05.883','01:29:07.634','- That why you shot dope?\n- That\'s not fair.',-1),(128215,5,128345,128377,'01:29:07.718','01:29:09.052','That\'s why you get high?',-1),(128216,5,128380,128423,'01:29:09.178','01:29:10.971','There\'s a whole lot of people\nout there whose mothers die',-1),(128217,5,128425,128450,'01:29:11.055','01:29:12.097','and they don\'t fucking drink.',-1),(128218,5,128452,128486,'01:29:12.181','01:29:13.598','- You\'re sick, Whip.\n- Yeah, well,',-1),(128219,5,128489,128532,'01:29:13.724','01:29:15.517','I embrace it. Shit!',-1),(128220,5,128553,128580,'01:29:16.394','01:29:17.519','I choose to drink!',-1),(128221,5,128584,128610,'01:29:17.687','01:29:18.770','- You do?\n- Yes, I do.',-1),(128222,5,128613,128667,'01:29:18.896','01:29:21.147','You choose it? Well, I don\'t see\na whole lot of choice going on here!',-1),(128223,5,128669,128734,'01:29:21.232','01:29:23.942','I choose to drink! And I blame myself!',-1),(128224,5,128736,128802,'01:29:24.026','01:29:26.778','I\'m happy to! And you know why?',-1),(128225,5,128804,128857,'01:29:26.862','01:29:29.072','Because I choose to drink!',-1),(128226,5,128868,128956,'01:29:29.532','01:29:33.201','I got an ex-wife and a son I never talk to!',-1),(128227,5,128964,129044,'01:29:33.536','01:29:36.871','And you know why?\nBecause I choose to drink!',-1),(128228,5,129052,129090,'01:29:37.206','01:29:38.790','No. I got to go.',-1),(128229,5,129092,129120,'01:29:38.874','01:29:40.041','Nicole.',-1),(128230,5,129537,129577,'01:29:57.393','01:29:59.060','Hey, listen.',-1),(128231,5,129685,129717,'01:30:03.566','01:30:04.899','All right, look.',-1),(128232,5,129781,129865,'01:30:07.570','01:30:11.072','I was loaded when the plane crashed.',-1),(128233,5,129893,129944,'01:30:12.241','01:30:14.367','With this