753','02:09:21.128','I\'m free.',-1),(128819,5,186598,186658,'02:09:34.935','02:09:37.436','Whitaker. You got a visitor.',-1),(128820,5,187563,187612,'02:10:15.142','02:10:17.184','- You got 40 minutes.\n- Okay.',-1),(128821,5,187875,187915,'02:10:28.155','02:10:29.822','Look at you, boy.',-1),(128822,5,187928,187977,'02:10:30.365','02:10:32.408','- How are you doing?\n- I\'m good.',-1),(128823,5,187979,188008,'02:10:32.492','02:10:33.701','You look good.',-1),(128824,5,188039,188079,'02:10:34.995','02:10:36.662','Come on, sit down.',-1),(128825,5,188112,188144,'02:10:38.039','02:10:39.373','This is a surprise.',-1),(128826,5,188155,188184,'02:10:39.833','02:10:41.041','You get that gift I sent you?',-1),(128827,5,188187,188216,'02:10:41.126','02:10:42.334','Yeah, yeah, I got it.',-1),(128828,5,188221,188251,'02:10:42.544','02:10:43.794','- Yeah? You like it?\n- Yeah.',-1),(128829,5,188253,188277,'02:10:43.879','02:10:44.879','Good.',-1),(128830,5,188320,188356,'02:10:46.673','02:10:48.174','How\'s your mom?',-1),(128831,5,188364,188396,'02:10:48.508','02:10:49.842','Oh. She\'s all right.',-1),(128832,5,188440,188544,'02:10:51.678','02:10:56.015','My college counselor\nwanted me to come and interview you.',-1),(128833,5,188557,188581,'02:10:56.558','02:10:57.558','Me?',-1),(128834,5,188588,188660,'02:10:57.851','02:11:00.853','Yeah. I\'m writing essays\nfor college applications.',-1),(128835,5,188664,188694,'02:11:01.021','02:11:02.271','Good.',-1),(128836,5,188700,188732,'02:11:02.522','02:11:03.856','I need your help.',-1),(128837,5,188745,188777,'02:11:04.399','02:11:05.733','You got it.',-1),(128838,5,188808,188912,'02:11:07.027','02:11:11.363','Well, this essay, the essay\nthat I have to write...',-1),(128839,5,188972,189060,'02:11:13.867','02:11:17.536','it\'s called \"The Most Fascinating Person.\"',-1),(128840,5,189081,189121,'02:11:18.413','02:11:20.080','\"That I\'ve Never Met.\"',-1),(128841,5,189290,189318,'02:11:27.088','02:11:28.255','Okay.',-1),(128842,5,189382,189414,'02:11:30.926','02:11:32.259','So...',-1),(128843,5,189533,189569,'02:11:37.224','02:11:38.724','Who are you?',-1),(128844,5,189782,189827,'02:11:47.609','02:11:49.485','That\'s a good question.',-1),(128845,42,4786,4816,'00:03:19.450','00:03:20.701','Hello.',-1),(128846,42,4839,4903,'00:03:21.660','00:03:24.330','My name\'s Forrest. Forrest Gump.',-1),(128847,42,5037,5086,'00:03:29.877','00:03:31.921','Do you want a chocolate?',-1),(128848,42,5148,5230,'00:03:34.506','00:03:37.927','I could eat about\na million and a half of these.',-1),(128849,42,5258,5383,'00:03:39.094','00:03:44.308','My mama always said\nlife was like a box of chocolates.',-1),(128850,42,5431,5500,'00:03:46.310','00:03:49.188','You never know what you\'re gonna get.',-1),(128851,42,5673,5734,'00:03:56.403','00:03:58.948','Those must be comfortable shoes.',-1),(128852,42,5767,5879,'00:04:00.324','00:04:04.995','I\'ll bet you could walk all day\nin shoes like that and not feel a thing.',-1),(128853,42,5932,5992,'00:04:07.206','00:04:09.667','I wish I had shoes like that.',-1),(128854,42,6008,6045,'00:04:10.334','00:04:11.877','My feet hurt.',-1),(128855,42,6074,6114,'00:04:13.087','00:04:14.755','Mama always said there\'s an awful lot',-1),(128856,42,6116,6193,'00:04:14.838','00:04:18.050','you could tell about a person\nby their shoes:',-1),(128857,42,6220,6291,'00:04:19.176','00:04:22.137','where they\'re going,\nwhere they\'ve been.',-1),(128858,42,6465,6514,'00:04:29.395','00:04:31.438','I\'ve worn lots of shoes.',-1),(128859,42,6589,6704,'00:04:34.566','00:04:39.363','I bet if I think about it real hard,\nI could remember my first pair of shoes.',-1),(128860,42,6774,6837,'00:04:42.283','00:04:44.910','Mama said they\'d take me anywhere.',-1),(128861,42,6856,6919,'00:04:45.703','00:04:48.330','<i>She said they was my magic shoes.</i>',-1),(128862,42,6921,6997,'00:04:48.414','00:04:51.583','All right, Forrest,\nyou can open your eyes now.',-1),(128863,42,7173,7232,'00:04:58.882','00:05:01.343','Let\'s take a little walk around.',-1),(128864,42,7395,7438,'00:05:08.142','00:05:09.935','How do those feel?',-1),(128865,42,7509,7561,'00:05:12.896','00:05:15.065','His legs are strong, Mrs. Gump,',-1),(128866,42,7563,7623,'00:05:15.149','00:05:17.651','as strong as I\'ve ever seen,',-1),(128867,42,7625,7706,'00:05:17.735','00:05:21.113','but his back is as crooked\nas a politician.',-1),(128868,42,7737,7812,'00:05:22.406','00:05:25.534','But we\'re gonna straighten him right up,\nnow, aren\'t we, Forrest?',-1),(128869,42,7813,7840,'00:05:25.576','00:05:26.702','Forrest!',-1),(128870,42,7876,7905,'00:05:28.203','00:05:29.413','<i>Now, when I was a baby,</i>',-1),(128871,42,7907,7975,'00:05:29.496','00:05:32.333','<i>Mama named me after\nthe great Civil War hero,</i>',-1),(128872,42,7977,8036,'00:05:32.416','00:05:34.835','<i>General Nathan Bedford Forrest.</i>',-1),(128873,42,8038,8091,'00:05:34.918','00:05:37.129','<i>She said we was related to him\nin some way.</i>',-1),(128874,42,8093,8126,'00:05:37.212','00:05:38.589','<i>And what he did was,</i>',-1),(128875,42,8128,8230,'00:05:38.672','00:05:42.926','<i>he started up this club called\nthe Ku Klux Klan.</i>',-1),(128876,42,8232,8312,'00:05:43.010','00:05:46.347','<i>They\'d all dress up in their robes\nand their bed sheets</i>',-1),(128877,42,8314,8418,'00:05:46.430','00:05:50.768','<i>and act like a bunch of ghosts\nor spooks or something.</i>',-1),(128878,42,8420,8513,'00:05:50.851','00:05:54.730','<i>They\'d even put bed sheets\non their horses and ride around.</i>',-1),(128879,42,8515,8588,'00:05:54.813','00:05:57.858','<i>And anyway, that\'s how I got my name,</i>',-1),(128880,42,8590,8624,'00:05:57.941','00:05:59.360','<i>Forrest Gump.</i>',-1),(128881,42,8626,8668,'00:05:59.443','00:06:01.195','<i>Mama said that the \"Forrest\" part</i>',-1),(128882,42,8670,8755,'00:06:01.278','00:06:04.823','<i>was to remind me that sometimes\nwe all do things that,</i>',-1),(128883,42,8757,8824,'00:06:04.907','00:06:07.701','<i>well, just don\'t make no sense.</i>',-1),(128884,42,8960,9045,'00:06:13.374','00:06:16.877','Okay... Get it, get it...',-1),(128885,42,9047,9118,'00:06:16.960','00:06:19.922','Wait, is it this way? Hold on.',-1),(128886,42,9140,9176,'00:06:20.839','00:06:22.341','All right...',-1),(128887,42,9190,9230,'00:06:22.925','00:06:24.593','What are you all staring at?',-1),(128888,42,9232,9339,'00:06:24.676','00:06:29.139','Haven\'t you ever seen a little boy\nwith braces on his legs before?',-1),(128889,42,9376,9465,'00:06:30.682','00:06:34.395','Don\'t ever let anybody tell you\nthey\'re better than you, Forrest.',-1),(128890,42,9467,9529,'00:06:34.478','00:06:37.064','If God intended\neverybody to be the same,',-1),(128891,42,9531,9582,'00:06:37.147','00:06:39.274','he\'d have given us all braces\non our legs.',-1),(128892,42,9584,9675,'00:06:39.358','00:06:43.153','<i>Mama always had a way of explaining\nthings so I could understand them.</i>',-1),(128893,42,9710,9794,'00:06:44.613','00:06:48.117','<i>We lived about a quarter mile\noff Route 17,</i>',-1),(128894,42,9796,9869,'00:06:48.200','00:06:51.245','<i>about a half mile from\nthe town of Greenbow, Alabama.</i>',-1),(128895,42,9871,9937,'00:06:51.328','00:06:54.081','<i>That\'s in the county of Greenbow.</i>',-1),(128896,42,9939,10046,'00:06:54.164','00:06:58.585','<i>Our house had been in Mama\'s family\nsince her grandpa\'s grandpa\'s grandpa</i>',-1),(128897,42,10048,10094,'00:06:58.669','00:07:00.587','<i>had come across the ocean\nabout 1,000 years ago,</i>',-1),(128898,42,10096,10142,'00:07:00.671','00:07:02.589','<i>something like that.</i>',-1),(128899,42,10144,10209,'00:07:02.673','00:07:05.384','<i>Since it was just me and Mama\nand we had all these empty rooms,</i>',-1),(128900,42,10211,10277,'00:07:05.467','00:07:08.220','<i>Mama decided to let those rooms out,</i>',-1),(128901,42,10279,10326,'00:07:08.303','00:07:10.264','<i>mostly to people passing through,</i>',-1),(128902,42,10328,10423,'00:07:10.347','00:07:14.309','<i>like from, oh, Mobile,\nMontgomery, places like that.</i>',-1),(128903,42,10425,10490,'00:07:14.393','00:07:17.104','<i>That\'s how me and Mama got money.</i>',-1),(128904,42,10492,10558,'00:07:17.187','00:07:19.940','<i>Mama was a real smart lady.</i>',-1),(128905,42,10560,10680,'00:07:20.023','00:07:25.028','Remember what I told you, Forrest.\nYou\'re no different than anybody else is.',-1),(128906,42,10740,10797,'00:07:27.531','00:07:29.908','Did you hear what I said, Forrest?',-1),(128907,42,10799,10899,'00:07:29.992','00:07:34.163','You\'re the same as everybody else.\nYou are no different.',-1),(128908,42,10911,11019,'00:07:34.663','00:07:39.126','Your boy\'s different, Mrs. Gump.',-1),(128909,42,11021,11074,'00:07:39.209','00:07:41.420','Now, his IQ is 75.',-1),(128910,42,11093,11168,'00:07:42.212','00:07:45.340','Well, we\'re all different, Mr. Hancock.',-1),(128911,42,11254,11303,'00:07:48.927','00:07:50.971','<i>She wanted me to have\nthe finest education,</i>',-1),(128912,42,11305,11399,'00:07:51.054','00:07:54.975','<i>so she took me to\nthe Greenbow County Central School.</i>',-1),(128913,42,11401,11455,'00:07:55.058','00:07:57.311','<i>I met the principal and all.</i>',-1),(128914,42,11467,11536,'00:07:57.811','00:08:00.689','I want to show you something,\nMrs. Gump.',-1),(128915,42,11547,11616,'00:08:01.148','00:08:04.026','Now, this is normal.',-1),(128916,42,11628,11707,'00:08:04.526','00:08:07.821','Forrest is right here.',-1),(128917,42,11727,11860,'00:08:08.655','00:08:14.203','The state requires a minimum IQ of\n80 to attend public school, Mrs. Gump.',-1),(128918,42,11872,11941,'00:08:14.703','00:08:17.581','He\'s gonna have to go\nto a special school.',-1),(128919,42,11943,11994,'00:08:17.664','00:08:19.791','Now, he\'ll be just fine.',-1),(128920,42,12014,12064,'00:08:20.584','00:08:22.669','What does \"normal\" mean, anyway?',-1),(128921,42,12066,12147,'00:08:22.753','00:08:26.131','He might be a bit on the slow side,',-1),(128922,42,12174,12217,'00:08:27.257','00:08:29.051','but my boy Forrest is gonna get',-1),(128923,42,12218,12279,'00:08:29.092','00:08:31.637','the same opportunities\nas everyone else.',-1),(128924,42,12281,12372,'00:08:31.720','00:08:35.516','He\'s not going to some special school\nto learn how to re-tread tires.',-1),(128925,42,12374,12450,'00:08:35.599','00:08:38.769','We\'re talking about\nfive little points here.',-1),(128926,42,12491,12554,'00:08:40.479','00:08:43.106','There must be something can be done.',-1),(128927,42,12592,12651,'00:08:44.691','00:08:47.152','We\'re a progressive school system.',-1),(128928,42,12671,12741,'00:08:47.986','00:08:50.906','We don\'t want to see anybody\nleft behind.',-1),(128929,42,12762,12845,'00:08:51.782','00:08:55.244','Is there a Mr. Gump, Mrs. Gump?',-1),(128930,42,12923,12968,'00:08:58.497','00:09:00.374','He\'s on vacation.',-1),(128931,42,13388,13479,'00:09:17.849','00:09:21.645','Well, your mama sure does care\nabout your schooling, son.',-1),(128932,42,13611,13670,'00:09:27.150','00:09:29.611','You don\'t say much, do you?',-1),(128933,42,13946,13993,'00:09:41.123','00:09:43.083','\"Finally, he had to try.',-1),(128934,42,13995,14043,'00:09:43.166','00:09:45.127','\"It looked easy, but,',-1),(128935,42,14072,14128,'00:09:46.336','00:09:48.672','\"oh, what happened.',-1),(128936,42,14130,14202,'00:09:48.755','00:09:51.758','- \"First, there...\"\n- Mama, what\'s \"vacation\" mean?',-1),(128937,42,14215,14277,'00:09:52.301','00:09:54.886','- Vacation?\n- Where Daddy went.',-1),(128938,42,14340,14405,'00:09:57.514','00:10:00.225','Vacation\'s when you go somewhere',-1),(128939,42,14462,14518,'00:10:02.603','00:10:04.938','and you don\'t ever come back.',-1),(128940,42,14622,14713,'00:10:09.276','00:10:13.071','<i>Anyway, I guess you could say\nme and Mama was on our own.</i>',-1),(128941,42,14742,14829,'00:10:14.281','00:10:17.909','<i>But we didn\'t mind.\nOur house was never empty.</i>',-1),(128942,42,14831,14893,'00:10:17.993','00:10:20.579','<i>There was always folks\ncoming and going.</i>',-1),(128943,42,14895,14921,'00:10:20.662','00:10:21.747','Supper.',-1),(128944,42,14923,15006,'00:10:21.830','00:10:25.250','- It\'s supper, everyone. Forrest...\n- My, my. That sure looks special.',-1),(128945,42,15008,15069,'00:10:25.334','00:10:27.878','<i>Sometimes we had\nso many people staying with us</i>',-1),(128946,42,15071,15135,'00:10:27.961','00:10:30.631','<i>that every room\nwas filled with travelers.</i>',-1),(128947,42,15137,15224,'00:10:30.714','00:10:34.343','<i>You know, folks living out\nof their suitcases</i>',-1),(128948,42,15226,15297,'00:10:34.426','00:10:37.387','<i>and hat cases and sample cases.</i>',-1),(128949,42,15299,15381,'00:10:37.471','00:10:40.891','Forrest Gump, it\'s suppertime!\nForrest...',-1),(128950,42,15383,15444,'00:10:40.974','00:10:43.518','<i>One time, a young man\nwas staying with us,</i>',-1),(128951,42,15446,15533,'00:10:43.602','00:10:47.230','<i>and he had him a guitar case.</i>',-1),(128952,42,15868,15964,'00:11:01.203','00:11:05.207','Forrest! I told you not to bother\nthis nice young man.',-1),(128953,42,15966,15999,'00:11:05.290','00:11:06.625','Oh, no, that\'s all right, ma\'am.',-1),(128954,42,16000,16069,'00:11:06.708','00:11:09.544','I was just showing him a thing or two\non the guitar here.',-1),(128955,42,16071,16142,'00:11:09.628','00:11:12.589','All right, but your supper\'s ready\nif y\'all want to eat.',-1),(128956,42,16144,16215,'00:11:12.673','00:11:15.634','Yeah, that sounds good.\nThank you, ma\'am.',-1),(128957,42,16231,16317,'00:11:16.301','00:11:19.888','Say, man, show me that crazy\nlittle walk you just did there.',-1),(128958,42,16319,16364,'00:11:19.971','00:11:21.848','Slow it down some.',-1),(128959,42,16415,16461,'00:11:23.975','00:11:25.894','<i>I liked that guitar.</i>',-1),(128960,42,16477,16519,'00:11:26.561','00:11:28.313','<i>It sounded good.</i>',-1),(128961,42,16562,16662,'00:11:30.107','00:11:34.277','<i>I started moving around to the music,</i>',-1),(128962,42,16664,16708,'00:11:34.361','00:11:36.196','<i>swinging my hips.</i>',-1),(128963,42,16770,16831,'00:11:38.782','00:11:41.326','<i>This one night,\nme and Mama was out shopping,</i>',-1),(128964,42,16833,16905,'00:11:41.410','00:11:44.413','<i>and we walked right by\nBenson\'s furniture and appliance store,</i>',-1),(128965,42,16907,16945,'00:11:44.496','00:11:46.081','<i>and guess what?</i>',-1),(128966,42,17242,17310,'00:11:58.427','00:12:01.263','This is not for children\'s eyes.',-1),(128967,42,17371,17415,'00:12:03.807','00:12:05.642','<i>Some years later,\nthat handsome young man</i>',-1),(128968,42,17416,17478,'00:12:05.684','00:12:08.270','<i>who they called \"The King,\"</i>',-1),(128969,42,17479,17535,'00:12:08.311','00:12:10.647','<i>well, he\'d sung too many songs,</i>',-1),(128970,42,17551,17612,'00:12:11.314','00:12:13.859','<i>had himself a heart attack,\nor something.</i>',-1),(128971,42,17638,17690,'00:12:14.943','00:12:17.112','Must be hard being a king.',-1),(128972,42,17793,17861,'00:12:21.408','00:12:24.244','You know, it\'s funny how you remember\nsome things, but some things you can\'t.',-1),(128973,42,17879,17972,'00:12:24.995','00:12:28.874','- You do your very best now, Forrest.\n- I sure will, Mama.',-1),(128974,42,18014,18124,'00:12:30.584','00:12:35.172','<i>I remember the bus ride\non the first day of school very well.</i>',-1),(128975,42,18209,18250,'00:12:38.717','00:12:40.427','Are you coming along?',-1),(128976,42,18252,18336,'00:12:40.510','00:12:44.014','Mama said not to be taking\nrides from strangers.',-1),(128977,42,18338,18390,'00:12:44.097','00:12:46.266','This is the bus to school.',-1),(128978,42,18461,18515,'00:12:49.227','00:12:51.480','I\'m Forrest. Forrest Gump.',-1),(128979,42,18538,18634,'00:12:52.439','00:12:56.443','- I\'m Dorothy Harris.\n- Well, now we ain\'t strangers anymore.',-1),(128980,42,18946,18989,'00:13:09.456','00:13:11.249','This seat\'s taken.',-1),(128981,42,19049,19085,'00:13:13.710','00:13:15.212','It\'s taken!',-1),(128982,42,19274,19319,'00:13:23.094','00:13:24.971','You can\'t sit here.',-1),(128983,42,19371,19453,'00:13:27.140','00:13:30.560','<i>You know, it\'s funny what\na young man recollects,</i>',-1),(128984,42,19455,19512,'00:13:30.644','00:13:33.021','<i>\'cause I don\'t remember being born.</i>',-1),(128985,42,19551,19604,'00:13:34.648','00:13:36.858','I don\'t recall what I got\nfor my first Christmas,',-1),(128986,42,19605,19679,'00:13:36.900','00:13:39.986','and I don\'t know when I went\non my first outdoor picnic.',-1),(128987,42,19681,19794,'00:13:40.070','00:13:44.783','But I do remember the first time I heard',-1),(128988,42,19796,19864,'00:13:44.866','00:13:47.702','the sweetest voice in the wide world.',-1),(128989,42,19876,19933,'00:13:48.203','00:13:50.580','You can sit here if you want.',-1),(128990,42,20004,20097,'00:13:53.500','00:13:57.379','<i>I had never seen anything\nso beautiful in my life.</i>',-1),(128991,42,20114,20164,'00:13:58.088','00:14:00.173','<i>She was like an angel.</i>',-1),(128992,42,20166,20236,'00:14:00.257','00:14:03.176','Well, are you gonna sit down,\nor aren\'t you?',-1),(128993,42,20355,20398,'00:14:08.139','00:14:09.933','What\'s wrong with your legs?',-1),(128994,42,20400,20502,'00:14:10.016','00:14:14.271','Nothing at all, thank you.\nMy legs are just fine and dandy.',-1),(128995,42,20524,20576,'00:14:15.188','00:14:17.357','<i>I just sat next to her on that bus</i>',-1),(128996,42,20578,20628,'00:14:17.440','00:14:19.526','<i>and had a conversation\nall the way to school.</i>',-1),(128997,42,20630,20695,'00:14:19.609','00:14:22.320','...my back\'s crooked like\na question mark.',-1),(128998,42,20697,20726,'00:14:22.404','00:14:23.613','These are going to make me...',-1),(128999,42,20727,20841,'00:14:23.655','00:14:28.410','<i>And next to Mama, no one ever\ntalked to me or asked me questions.</i>',-1),(129000,42,20854,20901,'00:14:28.952','00:14:30.912','Are you stupid or something?',-1),(129001,42,20903,20975,'00:14:30.996','00:14:33.999','Mama says, \"Stupid is as stupid does.\"',-1),(129002,42,21015,21103,'00:14:35.625','00:14:39.296','- I\'m Jenny.\n- I\'m Forrest. Forrest Gump.',-1),(129003,42,21119,21163,'00:14:39.963','00:14:41.798','<i>From that day on,\nwe was always together.</i>',-1),(129004,42,21165,21233,'00:14:41.882','00:14:44.718','<i>Jenny and me was like\npeas and carrots.</i>',-1),(129005,42,21319,21358,'00:14:48.305','00:14:49.931','<i>She taught me how to climb.</i>',-1),(129006,42,21360,21425,'00:14:50.015','00:14:52.726','Come on, Forrest, you can do it.',-1),(129007,42,21427,21490,'00:14:52.809','00:14:55.437','<i>I showed her how to dangle.</i>',-1),(129008,42,21492,21541,'00:14:55.520','00:14:57.564','\"...a good little monkey and...\"',-1),(129009,42,21543,21661,'00:14:57.647','00:15:02.569','<i>She helped me learn how to read,\nand I showed her how to swing.</i>',-1),(129010,42,21717,21807,'00:15:04.905','00:15:08.658','<i>Sometimes we\'d just sit out\nand wait for the stars.</i>',-1),(129011,42,21809,21927,'00:15:08.742','00:15:13.663','- Mama\'s gonna worry about me.\n- Just stay a little longer.',-1),(129012,42,21957,22048,'00:15:14.915','00:15:18.668','<i>For some reason,\nJenny didn\'t never want to go home.</i>',-1),(129013,42,22050,22100,'00:15:18.752','00:15:20.837','Okay, Jenny, I\'ll stay.',-1),(129014,42,22120,22186,'00:15:21.671','00:15:24.424','<i>She was my most special friend.</i>',-1),(129015,42,22268,22308,'00:15:27.844','00:15:29.512','My only friend.',-1),(129016,42,22399,22490,'00:15:33.308','00:15:37.103','Now, my mama always told me that\nmiracles happen every day.',-1),(129017,42,22492,22549,'00:15:37.187','00:15:39.564','Some people don\'t think so, but they do.',-1),(129018,42,22622,22660,'00:15:42.609','00:15:44.194','Hey, dummy!',-1),(129019,42,22683,22733,'00:15:45.153','00:15:47.238','Are you retarded, or just plain stupid?',-1),(129020,42,22735,22819,'00:15:47.322','00:15:50.825','- \"Look, I\'m Forrest Gimp.\"\n- Just run away, Forrest.',-1),(129021,42,22851,22925,'00:15:52.160','00:15:55.246','Run, Forrest! Run away! Hurry!',-1),(129022,42,22927,23005,'00:15:55.330','00:15:58.583','- Get the bikes!\n- Hurry up! Let\'s get him!',-1),(129023,42,23008,23069,'00:15:58.667','00:16:01.211','- Come on!\n- Look out, dummy, here we come!',-1),(129024,42,23071,23115,'00:16:01.294','00:16:03.129','We\'re gonna get you!',-1),(129025,42,23138,23228,'00:16:04.089','00:16:07.842','Run, Forrest, run! Run, Forrest!',-1),(129026,42,23269,23315,'00:16:09.552','00:16:11.471','Come back here, you!',-1),(129027,42,23642,23701,'00:16:25.110','00:16:27.570','Run, Forrest!',-1),(129028,42,23703,23737,'00:16:27.654','00:16:29.072','Run!',-1),(129029,42,24486,24555,'00:17:00.270','00:17:03.148','<i>Now, you wouldn\'t believe it\nif I told you,</i>',-1),(129030,42,24582,24642,'00:17:04.274','00:17:06.776','but I can run like the wind blows.',-1),(129031,42,24720,24794,'00:17:10.030','00:17:13.116','From that day on,\nif I was going somewhere,',-1),(129032,42,24814,24846,'00:17:13.950','00:17:15.285','I was running!',-1),(129033,42,24847,24904,'00:17:15.326','00:17:17.704','He\'s getting away! Stop him!',-1),(129034,42,25659,25731,'00:17:49.152','00:17:52.155','That boy sure is a running fool.',-1),(129035,42,25832,25865,'00:17:56.367','00:17:57.744','<i>Now, remember how I told you that</i>',-1),(129036,42,25867,25938,'00:17:57.827','00:18:00.789','<i>Jenny never seemed\nto want to go home?</i>',-1),(129037,42,25939,26014,'00:18:00.830','00:18:03.917','<i>Well, she lived in a house\nthat was as old as Alabama.</i>',-1),(129038,42,26016,26068,'00:18:04.000','00:18:06.169','<i>Her mama had gone up to heaven\nwhen she was five,</i>',-1),(129039,42,26070,26150,'00:18:06.252','00:18:09.589','<i>and her daddy was\nsome kind of a farmer.</i>',-1),(129040,42,26194,26220,'00:18:11.424','00:18:12.509','Jenny?',-1),(129041,42,26221,26273,'00:18:12.550','00:18:14.719','<i>He was a very loving man.</i>',-1),(129042,42,26284,26386,'00:18:15.178','00:18:19.432','<i>He was always kissing and touching\nher and her sisters.</i>',-1),(129043,42,26428,26534,'00:18:21.184','00:18:25.605','<i>And then this one time,\nJenny wasn\'t on the bus to go to school.</i>',-1),(129044,42,26562,26632,'00:18:26.773','00:18:29.692','Jenny, why didn\'t you come\nto school today?',-1),(129045,42,26633,26683,'00:18:29.734','00:18:31.820','Daddy\'s taking a nap.',-1),(129046,42,26684,26725,'00:18:31.861','00:18:33.571','- Jenny!\n- Come on!',-1),(129047,42,26760,26821,'00:18:35.031','00:18:37.575','Jenny, where\'d you run to?',-1),(129048,42,26853,26917,'00:18:38.910','00:18:41.579','You\'d better get back here, girl!',-1),(129049,42,26952,26992,'00:18:43.039','00:18:44.707','Where you at?',-1),(129050,42,27074,27153,'00:18:48.086','00:18:51.381','Jenny! Jenny! Where you at?',-1),(129051,42,27225,27257,'00:18:54.384','00:18:55.718','Jenny!',-1),(129052,42,27259,27330,'00:18:55.802','00:18:58.763','Pray with me, Forrest. Pray with me.',-1),(129053,42,27333,27361,'00:18:58.888','00:19:00.056','Jenny!',-1),(129054,42,27362,27439,'00:19:00.098','00:19:03.309','Dear God, make me a bird\nso I can fly far,',-1),(129055,42,27441,27483,'00:19:03.393','00:19:05.145','far, far away from here.',-1),(129056,42,27485,27573,'00:19:05.228','00:19:08.898','Dear God, make me a bird\nso I can fly far,',-1),(129057,42,27575,27602,'00:19:08.982','00:19:10.108','far, far away from here.',-1),(129058,42,27605,27678,'00:19:10.233','00:19:13.278','<i>Mama always said\nthat God is mysterious.</i>',-1),(129059,42,27681,27709,'00:19:13.403','00:19:14.571','Jenny!',-1),(129060,42,27710,27766,'00:19:14.612','00:19:16.948','<i>He didn\'t turn Jenny into a bird that day.</i>',-1),(129061,42,27769,27795,'00:19:17.073','00:19:18.158','You\'d better get back here!',-1),(129062,42,27797,27833,'00:19:18.241','00:19:19.742','<i>Instead,</i>',-1),(129063,42,27849,27958,'00:19:20.410','00:19:24.956','<i>he had the police say Jenny didn\'t\nhave to stay in that house no more.</i>',-1),(129064,42,27969,28059,'00:19:25.415','00:19:29.127','<i>She went to live with her grandma\njust over on Creekmore Avenue,</i>',-1),(129065,42,28062,28138,'00:19:29.252','00:19:32.422','<i>which made me happy,\n\'cause she was so close.</i>',-1),(129066,42,28200,28322,'00:19:35.008','00:19:40.096','<i>Some nights, Jenny would sneak out\nand come on over to my house,</i>',-1),(129067,42,28323,28398,'00:19:40.138','00:19:43.266','<i>just \'cause she said she was scared.</i>',-1),(129068,42,28400,28459,'00:19:43.349','00:19:45.810','<i>Scared of what, I don\'t know,</i>',-1),(129069,42,28462,28539,'00:19:45.935','00:19:49.147','<i>but I think it was her grandma\'s dog.</i>',-1),(129070,42,28542,28584,'00:19:49.272','00:19:51.024','<i>He was a mean dog.</i>',-1),(129071,42,28602,28667,'00:19:51.774','00:19:54.485','<i>Anyway, Jenny and me was best friends</i>',-1),(129072,42,28669,28700,'00:19:54.569','00:19:55.862','<i>all the way up through high school.</i>',-1),(129073,42,28747,28796,'00:19:57.822','00:19:59.866','- Hey, stupid!\n- Quit it!',-1),(129074,42,28823,28878,'00:20:00.992','00:20:03.286','- Run, Forrest, run!\n- Hey,',-1),(129075,42,28895,28930,'00:20:03.995','00:20:05.455','did you hear me, stupid?',-1),(129076,42,28932,28962,'00:20:05.538','00:20:06.789','- Run, Forrest!\n- Come on, get in the truck!',-1),(129077,42,28963,29014,'00:20:06.831','00:20:08.958','Get in the truck! Let\'s move it!',-1),(129078,42,29017,29083,'00:20:09.042','00:20:11.794','Come on, he\'s getting away! Move it!',-1),(129079,42,29085,29137,'00:20:11.878','00:20:14.047','Run, Forrest! Run!',-1),(129080,42,29139,29224,'00:20:14.130','00:20:17.675','- You better be running, stupid!\n- Come on, dummy!',-1),(129081,42,29271,29355,'00:20:19.636','00:20:23.139','- Haul ass, dummy!\n- Yeah, you better get running!',-1),(129082,42,29427,29467,'00:20:26.142','00:20:27.810','Jack rabbit!',-1),(129083,42,29669,29699,'00:20:36.236','00:20:37.487','Yeah!',-1),(129084,42,29719,29771,'00:20:38.321','00:20:40.490','Go! Go! Go!',-1),(129085,42,29812,29851,'00:20:42.200','00:20:43.826','Run, Forrest!',-1),(129086,42,29923,30009,'00:20:46.829','00:20:50.416','Now, it used to be,\nI ran to get where I was going,',-1),(129087,42,30048,30108,'00:20:52.001','00:20:54.504','I never thought it would\ntake me anywhere.',-1),(129088,42,30804,30904,'00:21:23.533','00:21:27.704','- Who in the hell is that?\n- That there is Forrest Gump, Coach.',-1),(129089,42,30928,30972,'00:21:28.705','00:21:30.540','Just a local idiot.',-1),(129090,42,30988,31073,'00:21:31.207','00:21:34.711','<i>And can you believe it?\nI got to go to college, too.</i>',-1),(129091,42,31231,31294,'00:21:41.301','00:21:43.928','Forrest! Forrest! Run!',-1),(129092,42,31297,31335,'00:21:44.053','00:21:45.638','- Okay!\n- Run!',-1),(129093,42,31337,31422,'00:21:45.722','00:21:49.267','Run, you stupid son of a bitch! Run!',-1),(129094,42,31697,31782,'00:22:00.737','00:22:04.282','You son of a bitch! Run! Go! Run!',-1),(129095,42,31839,31905,'00:22:06.659','00:22:09.412','No! Turn! Go!',-1),(129096,42,32175,32262,'00:22:20.631','00:22:24.260','He must be the stupidest\nson of a bitch alive,',-1),(129097,42,32264,32310,'00:22:24.344','00:22:26.262','but he sure is fast!',-1),(129098,42,32382,32502,'00:22:29.265','00:22:34.270','<i>Now, maybe it\'s just me,\nbut college was very confusing times.</i>',-1),(129099,42,32534,32580,'00:22:35.605','00:22:37.523','<i>Federal troops enforcing a court order</i>',-1),(129100,42,32582,32654,'00:22:37.607','00:22:40.610','<i>integrated the University\nof Alabama today.</i>',-1),(129101,42,32656,32686,'00:22:40.693','00:22:41.944','<i>Two negroes were admitted,</i>',-1),(129102,42,32687,32766,'00:22:41.986','00:22:45.281','<i>but only after Governor George Wallace\nhad carried out his symbolic threat</i>',-1),(129103,42,32768,32806,'00:22:45.365','00:22:46.949','<i>to stand in the school house door.</i>',-1),(129104,42,32807,32919,'00:22:46.991','00:22:51.662','<i>Governor Wallace,\nI take it from that statement, that...</i>',-1),(129105,42,32922,32970,'00:22:51.788','00:22:53.790','Earl, what\'s going on?',-1),(129106,42,32972,33053,'00:22:53.873','00:22:57.210','- Coons are trying to get into school.\n- Coons?',-1),(129107,42,33055,33095,'00:22:57.293','00:22:58.961','When raccoons try to get\non our back porch,',-1),(129108,42,33097,33140,'00:22:59.045','00:23:00.838','Mama just chase them off with a broom.',-1),(129109,42,33143,33251,'00:23:00.963','00:23:05.468','Not raccoons, you idiot, niggers,\nand they want to go to school with us.',-1),(129110,42,33263,33312,'00:23:05.968','00:23:08.012','With us? They do?',-1),(129111,42,33335,33395,'00:23:08.971','00:23:11.474','<i>Shortly after Governor Wallace\nhad carried out his promise</i>',-1),(129112,42,33397,33427,'00:23:11.557','00:23:12.809','<i>to block the doorway,</i>',-1),(129113,42,33428,33475,'00:23:12.850','00:23:14.811','<i>President Kennedy\nordered the Secretary of Defense</i>',-1),(129114,42,33477,33525,'00:23:14.894','00:23:16.896','<i>then to use military force.</i>',-1),(129115,42,33527,33592,'00:23:16.979','00:23:19.690','<i>Here, by videotape,\nis the encounter by General Graham,</i>',-1),(129116,42,33595,33673,'00:23:19.816','00:23:23.069','<i>commander of the National Guard,\nand Governor Wallace.</i>',-1),(129117,42,33675,33764,'00:23:23.152','00:23:26.864','<i>...because these National Guardsmen\nare here today</i>',-1),(129118,42,33766,33827,'00:23:26.948','00:23:29.492','<i>as federal soldiers for Alabamans.</i>',-1),(129119,42,33829,33923,'00:23:29.575','00:23:33.496','<i>They live within our borders,\nthey are all our brothers.</i>',-1),(129120,42,33925,33983,'00:23:33.579','00:23:35.998','<i>We are winning in this fight,</i>',-1),(129121,42,33985,34058,'00:23:36.082','00:23:39.085','<i>because we are awakening\nthe American people</i>',-1),(129122,42,34060,34140,'00:23:39.168','00:23:42.505','<i>to the dangers that we have spoken\nabout so many times,</i>',-1),(129123,42,34142,34293,'00:23:42.588','00:23:48.886','<i>just so evident today, the trend towards\nmilitary dictatorship in this country.</i>',-1),(129124,42,34376,34436,'00:23:52.348','00:23:54.851','<i>And so, at day\'s end,\nthe University of Alabama</i>',-1),(129125,42,34437,34492,'00:23:54.892','00:23:57.186','<i>in Tuscaloosa had been desegregated</i>',-1),(129126,42,34494,34566,'00:23:57.270','00:24:00.273','<i>and students Jimmy Hood\nand Vivian Malone</i>',-1),(129127,42,34568,34642,'00:24:00.356','00:24:03.443','<i>had been signed up\nfor summer classes.</i>',-1),(129128,42,34704,34772,'00:24:06.028','00:24:08.865','<i>Ma\'am, you dropped your book.\nMa\'am...</i>',-1),(129129,42,34785,34832,'00:24:09.407','00:24:11.367','<i>Governor Wallace did what\nhe promised to do.</i>',-1),(129130,42,34834,34920,'00:24:11.451','00:24:15.037','<i>By being on the Tuscaloosa campus,\nhe kept the mob from gathering...</i>',-1),(129131,42,34921,34972,'00:24:15.079','00:24:17.206','Say, wasn\'t that Gump?',-1),(129132,42,34974,35073,'00:24:17.290','00:24:21.377','- Nah, that couldn\'t be.\n- It sure as hell was.',-1),(129133,42,35187,35231,'00:24:26.132','00:24:27.967','<i>A few years later, that angry little man</i>',-1),(129134,42,35233,35293,'00:24:28.050','00:24:30.553','<i>at the school house door\nthought it would be a good idea</i>',-1),(129135,42,35295,35347,'00:24:30.636','00:24:32.805','<i>and ran for president.</i>',-1),(129136,42,35421,35485,'00:24:35.892','00:24:38.561','<i>But somebody thought that it wasn\'t.</i>',-1),(129137,42,35526,35575,'00:24:40.271','00:24:42.315','But he didn\'t die.',-1),(129138,42,35685,35725,'00:24:46.903','00:24:48.571','My bus is here.',-1),(129139,42,35742,35817,'00:24:49.280','00:24:52.408','- Is it the number nine?\n- No, it\'s the number four.',-1),(129140,42,35841,35893,'00:24:53.409','00:24:55.578','It was nice talking to you.',-1),(129141,42,35963,36062,'00:24:58.498','00:25:02.585','I remember when that happened,\nwhen Wallace got shot.',-1),(129142,42,36083,36118,'00:25:03.461','00:25:04.921','I was in college.',-1),(129143,42,36120,36150,'00:25:05.004','00:25:06.255','Did you go to a girls\' college,',-1),(129144,42,36151,36195,'00:25:06.297','00:25:08.132','or to a girls-and-boys-together college?',-1),(129145,42,36198,36222,'00:25:08.257','00:25:09.258','It was co-ed.',-1),(129146,42,36224,36290,'00:25:09.342','00:25:12.094','\'Cause Jenny went to a college\nI couldn\'t go to.',-1),(129147,42,36291,36347,'00:25:12.136','00:25:14.472','It was a college just for girls.',-1),(129148,42,36350,36426,'00:25:14.597','00:25:17.767','<i>But I\'d go and visit her\nevery chance I got.</i>',-1),(129149,42,37163,37197,'00:25:48.464','00:25:49.882','That hurts.',-1),(129150,42,37461,37513,'00:26:00.893','00:26:03.062','Forrest! Forrest!',-1),(129151,42,37567,37638,'00:26:05.314','00:26:08.276','- Forrest, stop it! Stop it!\n- Jesus!',-1),(129152,42,37639,37667,'00:26:08.317','00:26:09.485','What are you doing?',-1),(129153,42,37668,37708,'00:26:09.527','00:26:11.195','- He was hurting you.\n- What the hell is going on here?',-1),(129154,42,37711,37799,'00:26:11.320','00:26:14.991','- No, he\'s not! Get over there!\n- Who is that? Who is that?',-1),(129155,42,37801,37827,'00:26:15.074','00:26:16.158','- Billy, I\'m sorry.\n- What the hell?',-1),(129156,42,37829,37891,'00:26:16.242','00:26:18.828','- Just get away from me!\n- Don\'t...',-1),(129157,42,37893,37964,'00:26:18.911','00:26:21.872','- Don\'t go! Billy, wait a second!\n- Get away from me.',-1),(129158,42,37967,38019,'00:26:21.998','00:26:24.166','He doesn\'t know any better!',-1),(129159,42,38062,38126,'00:26:25.918','00:26:28.588','Forrest, why did you do that?',-1),(129160,42,38197,38268,'00:26:31.549','00:26:34.510','I brought you some chocolate.',-1),(129161,42,38277,38318,'00:26:34.885','00:26:36.596','I\'m sorry.',-1),(129162,42,38370,38449,'00:26:38.764','00:26:42.059','- I\'ll go back to my college now.\n- Forrest...',-1),(129163,42,38538,38576,'00:26:45.771','00:26:47.356','Look at you.',-1),(129164,42,38626,38676,'00:26:49.442','00:26:51.527','Come on. Come on.',-1),(129165,42,38856,38901,'00:26:59.035','00:27:00.911','Is this your room?',-1),(129166,42,39008,39063,'00:27:05.374','00:27:07.627','Do you ever dream, Forrest,',-1),(129167,42,39095,39163,'00:27:08.961','00:27:11.797','about who you\'re gonna be?',-1),(129168,42,39165,39209,'00:27:11.881','00:27:13.716','- Who I\'m gonna be?\n- Yeah.',-1),(129169,42,39210,39255,'00:27:13.758','00:27:15.635','Aren\'t I going to be me?',-1),(129170,42,39257,39345,'00:27:15.718','00:27:19.388','Well, you\'ll always be you,\njust another kind of you.',-1),(129171,42,39367,39445,'00:27:20.306','00:27:23.559','You know? I want to be famous.',-1),(129172,42,39486,39553,'00:27:25.269','00:27:28.064','I want to be a singer like Joan Baez.',-1),(129173,42,39582,39657,'00:27:29.273','00:27:32.401','I just want to be on an empty stage',-1),(129174,42,39659,39714,'00:27:32.485','00:27:34.779','with my guitar, my voice.',-1),(129175,42,39758,39793,'00:27:36.614','00:27:38.074','Just me.',-1),(129176,42,39829,39909,'00:27:39.575','00:27:42.912','And I want to reach people\non the personal level.',-1),(129177,42,39973,40054,'00:27:45.581','00:27:48.918','I want to be able to say things,\njust one-to-one.',-1),(129178,42,40234,40303,'00:27:56.425','00:27:59.303','Have you ever been with a girl, Forrest?',-1),(129179,42,40338,40430,'00:28:00.763','00:28:04.600','I sit next to them in my Home\nEconomics class all the time.',-1),(129180,42,41125,41183,'00:28:33.546','00:28:35.965','- I\'m... Sorry.\n- It\'s okay.',-1),(129181,42,41388,41429,'00:28:44.515','00:28:46.225','It\'s all right.',-1),(129182,42,41497,41549,'00:28:49.061','00:28:51.230','- It\'s okay.\n- Oh, I\'m dizzy.',-1),(129183,42,41757,41823,'00:28:59.905','00:29:02.658','I bet that never happened in Home Ec.',-1),(129184,42,41939,41967,'00:29:07.496','00:29:08.664','No.',-1),(129185,42,42117,42192,'00:29:14.879','00:29:18.007','I think I ruined\nyour roommate\'s bathrobe.',-1),(129186,42,42194,42244,'00:29:18.090','00:29:20.176','I don\'t care. I don\'t like her, anyway.',-1),(129187,42,42245,42327,'00:29:20.217','00:29:23.637','Run! Run! Run!',-1),(129188,42,42328,42436,'00:29:23.679','00:29:28.184','- Run! Run! Run!\n- Run! Run! Run!',-1),(129189,42,42626,42728,'00:29:36.108','00:29:40.362','<i>College ran by real fast,\n\'cause I played so much football.</i>',-1),(129190,42,42729,42808,'00:29:40.404','00:29:43.699','<i>They even put me on a thing\ncalled the All-America Team,</i>',-1),(129191,42,42809,42900,'00:29:43.741','00:29:47.536','<i>where you get to meet\nthe President of the United States.</i>',-1),(129192,42,42902,42940,'00:29:47.620','00:29:49.205','<i>President Kennedy met\nwith the Collegiate</i>',-1),(129193,42,42942,43029,'00:29:49.288','00:29:52.875','<i>All-American Football Team\nat the Oval Office today.</i>',-1),(129194,42,43043,43091,'00:29:53.459','00:29:55.461','<i>Now, the really good thing\nabout meeting</i>',-1),(129195,42,43093,43185,'00:29:55.544','00:29:59.381','<i>the President of the United States\nis the food.</i>',-1),(129196,42,43186,43251,'00:29:59.423','00:30:02.134','<i>They put you in this little room\nwith just about anything</i>',-1),(129197,42,43253,43313,'00:30:02.218','00:30:04.720','<i>you\'d want to eat or drink.</i>',-1),(129198,42,43325,43409,'00:30:05.221','00:30:08.724','<i>And since, number one,\nI wasn\'t hungry, but thirsty,</i>',-1),(129199,42,43410,43474,'00:30:08.766','00:30:11.435','<i>and number two, they was free,</i>',-1),(129200,42,43477,43550,'00:30:11.560','00:30:14.605','<i>I must have drank me about\n15 Dr. Peppers.</i>',-1),(129201,42,43621,43673,'00:30:17.566','00:30:19.735','<i>Congratulations.\nHow does it feel to be an All-American?</i>',-1),(129202,42,43674,43717,'00:30:19.777','00:30:21.570','<i>It\'s an honor, sir.</i>',-1),(129203,42,43718,43769,'00:30:21.612','00:30:23.739','<i>Congratulations.\nHow does it feel to be an All-American?</i>',-1),(129204,42,43770,43809,'00:30:23.781','00:30:25.407','<i>Very good, sir.</i>',-1),(129205,42,43829,43887,'00:30:26.242','00:30:28.661','<i>Congratulations.\nHow does it feel to be an All-American?</i>',-1),(129206,42,43889,43931,'00:30:28.744','00:30:30.496','<i>Very good, sir.</i>',-1),(129207,42,43933,44022,'00:30:30.579','00:30:34.250','<i>- Congratulations. How do you feel?\n- I gotta pee.</i>',-1),(129208,42,44038,44093,'00:30:34.917','00:30:37.211','<i>I believe he said he had to \"go pee.\"</i>',-1),(129209,42,44458,44527,'00:30:52.434','00:30:55.312','<i>Sometime later,\nfor no particular reason,</i>',-1),(129210,42,44530,44587,'00:30:55.437','00:30:57.815','<i>somebody shot that\nnice young President,</i>',-1),(129211,42,44590,44647,'00:30:57.940','00:31:00.317','<i>when he was riding in his car.</i>',-1),(129212,42,44662,44762,'00:31:00.943','00:31:05.114','<i>And a few years after that,\nsomebody shot his little brother, too,</i>',-1),(129213,42,44763,44814,'00:31:05.155','00:31:07.283','<i>only he was in a hotel kitchen.</i>',-1),(129214,42,44849,44907,'00:31:08.742','00:31:11.161','It must be hard being brothers.',-1),(129215,42,44931,44960,'00:31:12.162','00:31:13.372','I wouldn\'t know.',-1),(129216,42,44974,45007,'00:31:13.956','00:31:15.332','<i>Forrest Gump.</i>',-1),(129217,42,45010,45042,'00:31:15.457','00:31:16.750','<i>Now can you believe it?</i>',-1),(129218,42,45043,45138,'00:31:16.792','00:31:20.754','<i>After only five years of playing football,\nI got a college degree.</i>',-1),(129219,42,45139,45187,'00:31:20.796','00:31:22.798','Congratulations, son.',-1),(129220,42,45206,45255,'00:31:23.591','00:31:25.634','<i>Mama was so proud.</i>',-1),(129221,42,45287,45379,'00:31:26.969','00:31:30.806','Forrest, I\'m so proud of you.\nHere, I\'ll hold this for you.',-1),(129222,42,45382,45432,'00:31:30.931','00:31:33.017','Congratulations, son.',-1),(129223,42,45435,45507,'00:31:33.142','00:31:36.145','Have you given any thought\nto your future?',-1),(129224,42,45551,45583,'00:31:37.980','00:31:39.315','Thought?',-1),(129225,42,45618,45663,'00:31:40.774','00:31:42.651','Hello, I\'m Forrest. Forrest Gump.',-1),(129226,42,45664,45736,'00:31:42.693','00:31:45.696','Nobody gives a hunk of shit\nwho you are, fuzzball!',-1),(129227,42,45739,45803,'00:31:45.821','00:31:48.490','You\'re not even a low-life,\nscum-sucking maggot!',-1),(129228,42,45804,45899,'00:31:48.532','00:31:52.494','Get your faggotty ass on the bus.\nYou\'re in the Army now!',-1),(129229,42,45907,45950,'00:31:52.828','00:31:54.622','This seat\'s taken.',-1),(129230,42,45995,46029,'00:31:56.498','00:31:57.875','Taken.',-1),(129231,42,46099,46167,'00:32:00.794','00:32:03.631','<i>At first, it seemed like I made a mistake,</i>',-1),(129232,42,46168,46217,'00:32:03.672','00:32:05.716','<i>seeing how it was only\nmy induction day</i>',-1),(129233,42,46220,46285,'00:32:05.841','00:32:08.552','<i>and I was already getting yelled at.</i>',-1),(129234,42,46359,46413,'00:32:11.639','00:32:13.891','You can sit down if you want to.',-1),(129235,42,46416,46508,'00:32:14.016','00:32:17.853','<i>I didn\'t know who I might meet,\nor what they might ask.</i>',-1),(129236,42,46511,46573,'00:32:17.978','00:32:20.564','You ever been on a real shrimp boat?',-1),(129237,42,46585,46672,'00:32:21.065','00:32:24.693','No, but I been on a real big boat.',-1),(129238,42,46691,46759,'00:32:25.486','00:32:28.322','I\'m talking about\na shrimp-catching boat.',-1),(129239,42,46760,46820,'00:32:28.364','00:32:30.866','I\'ve been working\non shrimp boats all my life.',-1),(129240,42,46823,46889,'00:32:30.991','00:32:33.744','I started out on my uncle\'s boat,\nthat\'s my mama\'s brother,',-1),(129241,42,46892,46941,'00:32:33.869','00:32:35.913','when I was about maybe nine.',-1),(129242,42,46944,47044,'00:32:36.038','00:32:40.167','I was just looking into buying a boat\nof my own and got drafted.',-1),(129243,42,47064,47181,'00:32:41.001','00:32:45.881','My given name is Benjamin Buford Blue.\nPeople call me Bubba.',-1),(129244,42,47197,47285,'00:32:46.548','00:32:50.219','Just like one of them old redneck boys.\nCan you believe that?',-1),(129245,42,47286,47374,'00:32:50.260','00:32:53.931','My name\'s Forrest Gump.\nPeople call me Forrest Gump.',-1),(129246,42,47397,47456,'00:32:54.890','00:32:57.351','<i>So, Bubba was from\nBayou La Batre, Alabama,</i>',-1),(129247,42,47457,47503,'00:32:57.393','00:32:59.311','<i>and his mama cooked shrimp,</i>',-1),(129248,42,47557,47626,'00:33:01.563','00:33:04.441','<i>and her mama before her\ncooked shrimp,</i>',-1),(129249,42,47629,47701,'00:33:04.566','00:33:07.569','<i>and her mama before her mama\ncooked shrimp, too.</i>',-1),(129250,42,47702,47732,'00:33:07.611','00:33:08.862','<i>Bubba\'s family knew everything</i>',-1),(129251,42,47733,47797,'00:33:08.904','00:33:11.573','<i>there was to know\nabout the shrimping business.</i>',-1),(129252,42,47798,47872,'00:33:11.615','00:33:14.702','I know everything there is to know\nabout the shrimping business.',-1),(129253,42,47873,47945,'00:33:14.743','00:33:17.746','Matter of fact, I\'m going into\nthe shrimping business for myself',-1),(129254,42,47948,48004,'00:33:17.871','00:33:20.207','after I get out the Army.',-1),(129255,42,48069,48094,'00:33:22.876','00:33:23.919','Okay.',-1),(129256,42,48099,48198,'00:33:24.128','00:33:28.257','Gump! What\'s your sole purpose\nin this Army?',-1),(129257,42,48199,48261,'00:33:28.298','00:33:30.884','To do whatever you tell me,\nDrill Sergeant!',-1),(129258,42,48262,48343,'00:33:30.926','00:33:34.304','God damn it, Gump!\nYou\'re a goddamn genius!',-1),(129259,42,48346,48402,'00:33:34.430','00:33:36.765','That\'s the most outstanding answer\nI\'ve ever heard.',-1),(129260,42,48405,48471,'00:33:36.890','00:33:39.643','You must have a goddamn IQ of 160!',-1),(129261,42,48474,48545,'00:33:39.768','00:33:42.730','You are goddamn gifted, Private Gump!',-1),(129262,42,48569,48614,'00:33:43.731','00:33:45.607','Listen up, people!',-1),(129263,42,48617,48718,'00:33:45.733','00:33:49.945','<i>Now, for some reason, I fit in the Army\nlike one of them round pegs.</i>',-1),(129264,42,48719,48750,'00:33:49.987','00:33:51.280','<i>It\'s not really hard.</i>',-1),(129265,42,48751,48838,'00:33:51.321','00:33:54.950','<i>You just make your bed real neat\nand remember to stand up straight,</i>',-1),(129266,42,48841,48937,'00:33:55.075','00:33:59.079','<i>and always answer every question\nwith, \"Yes, Drill Sergeant!\"</i>',-1),(129267,42,48938,48974,'00:33:59.121','00:34:00.622','Is that clear?',-1),(129268,42,48975,49026,'00:34:00.664','00:34:02.791','- Yes, Drill Sergeant!\n- Yes, Drill Sergeant!',-1),(129269,42,49039,49119,'00:34:03.292','00:34:06.628','What you do is, you just drag\nyour nets along the bottom.',-1),(129270,42,49120,49211,'00:34:06.670','00:34:10.466','On a good day, you can catch over\n100 pounds of shrimp.',-1),(129271,42,49212,49295,'00:34:10.507','00:34:13.969','If everything goes all right,\ntwo men shrimping 10 hours,',-1),(129272,42,49296,49362,'00:34:14.011','00:34:16.764','less what you spend on gas, you can...',-1),(129273,42,49363,49430,'00:34:16.805','00:34:19.600','- Done, Drill Sergeant!\n- Gump!',-1),(129274,42,49487,49554,'00:34:21.977','00:34:24.772','Why did you put that weapon\ntogether so quickly, Gump?',-1),(129275,42,49555,49595,'00:34:24.813','00:34:26.482','You told me to, Drill Sergeant.',-1),(129276,42,49598,49680,'00:34:26.607','00:34:30.027','Jesus H. Christ,\nthis is a new company record.',-1),(129277,42,49683,49743,'00:34:30.152','00:34:32.654','If it wouldn\'t be a waste\nof such a damn fine enlisted man,',-1),(129278,42,49744,49799,'00:34:32.696','00:34:34.990','I\'d recommend you for OCS,\nPrivate Gump.',-1),(129279,42,49802,49847,'00:34:35.115','00:34:36.992','You are gonna be\na general some day, Gump.',-1),(129280,42,49848,49922,'00:34:37.034','00:34:40.120','Now, disassemble your weapon\nand continue!',-1),(129281,42,49972,50064,'00:34:42.206','00:34:46.001','Anyway, like I was saying,\nshrimp is the fruit of the sea.',-1),(129282,42,50066,50180,'00:34:46.085','00:34:50.839','You can barbecue it,\nboil it, broil it, bake it, sautÃ© it.',-1),(129283,42,50182,50254,'00:34:50.923','00:34:53.926','There\'s shrimp kebabs, shrimp Creole...',-1),(129284,42,50261,50377,'00:34:54.218','00:34:59.056','...shrimp gumbo, pan fried,\ndeep fried, stir fried.',-1),(129285,42,50385,50470,'00:34:59.389','00:35:02.935','There\'s pineapple shrimp,\nlemon shrimp,',-1),(129286,42,50472,50528,'00:35:03.018','00:35:05.354','coconut shrimp, pepper shrimp...',-1),(129287,42,50536,50680,'00:35:05.687','00:35:11.693','...shrimp soup, shrimp stew,\nshrimp salad, shrimp and potatoes,',-1),(129288,42,50681,50754,'00:35:11.735','00:35:14.780','shrimp burger, shrimp sandwich...',-1),(129289,42,50816,50872,'00:35:17.366','00:35:19.701','That\'s... That\'s about it.',-1),(129290,42,50961,51033,'00:35:23.413','00:35:26.375','<i>Night time in the Army is a lonely time.</i>',-1),(129291,42,51054,51141,'00:35:27.251','00:35:30.879','<i>We\'d lay there in our bunks\nand I\'d miss my mama.</i>',-1),(129292,42,51155,51215,'00:35:31.463','00:35:33.966','<i>And I\'d miss Jenny.</i>',-1),(129293,42,51309,51402,'00:35:37.886','00:35:41.765','Hey, Gump, get a load of the tits on her!',-1),(129294,42,51725,51801,'00:35:55.237','00:35:58.407','<i>Turns out, Jenny had gotten into\nsome trouble over</i>',-1),(129295,42,51802,51882,'00:35:58.448','00:36:01.785','<i>some photos of her\nin her college sweater,</i>',-1),(129296,42,51885,51946,'00:36:01.910','00:36:04.454','<i>and she was thrown out of school.</i>',-1),(129297,42,52032,52086,'00:36:08.000','00:36:10.252','<i>But that wasn\'t a bad thing,</i>',-1),(129298,42,52087,52174,'00:36:10.294','00:36:13.922','<i>because a man who owns\na theater in Memphis, Tennessee,</i>',-1),(129299,42,52175,52296,'00:36:13.964','00:36:19.011','<i>saw those photos and offered Jenny\na job singing in a show.</i>',-1),(129300,42,52315,52359,'00:36:19.803','00:36:21.638','<i>The first chance I got,</i>',-1),(129301,42,52362,52450,'00:36:21.763','00:36:25.434','<i>I took the bus up to Memphis\nto see her perform in that show.</i>',-1),(129302,42,52452,52488,'00:36:25.517','00:36:27.019','<i>That was Amber, Amber Flame.</i>',-1),(129303,42,52490,52550,'00:36:27.102','00:36:29.605','<i>Give her a big hand, guys.\nGood job, Amber.</i>',-1),(129304,42,52551,52618,'00:36:29.646','00:36:32.441','<i>And now, for your listening\nand viewing pleasure,</i>',-1),(129305,42,52619,52711,'00:36:32.482','00:36:36.320','<i>direct from Hollywood, California,\nour very own beatnik beauty,</i>',-1),(129306,42,52714,52802,'00:36:36.445','00:36:40.115','<i>let\'s give a big round of applause\nto the luscious Bobbi Dylan.</i>',-1),(129307,42,52854,52918,'00:36:42.284','00:36:44.953','- All right!\n- Bobbi!',-1),(129308,42,53459,53509,'00:37:07.476','00:37:09.561','<i>Her dream had come true.</i>',-1),(129309,42,53539,53587,'00:37:10.812','00:37:12.814','<i>She was a folk singer.</i>',-1),(129310,42,53809,53863,'00:37:22.074','00:37:24.326','Come on, baby. Shake it up.\nShake it up, now.',-1),(129311,42,53865,53901,'00:37:24.409','00:37:25.911','Hey, buddy, get her a harmonica.',-1),(129312,42,53991,54040,'00:37:29.665','00:37:31.708','Hey, honey, this ain\'t <i>Captain Kangaroo.</i>',-1),(129313,42,54043,54105,'00:37:31.833','00:37:34.378','Hey, honey,\nI got something here for you.',-1),(129314,42,54130,54220,'00:37:35.420','00:37:39.174','- God damn it!\n- Hey! Hey! Stupid jerk!',-1),(129315,42,54222,54281,'00:37:39.258','00:37:41.718','I\'m singing a song here.',-1),(129316,42,54337,54396,'00:37:44.054','00:37:46.515','Polly, get out here!',-1),(129317,42,54397,54438,'00:37:46.556','00:37:48.267','- Shut up, there!\n- Don\'t be so shy, honey.',-1),(129318,42,54440,54477,'00:37:48.350','00:37:49.893','Oh, shut up!',-1),(129319,42,54541,54608,'00:37:52.562','00:37:55.357','Forrest, what are you doing here?',-1),(129320,42,54609,54650,'00:37:55.399','00:37:57.109','- What are you doing?\n- Hey!',-1),(129321,42,54652,54685,'00:37:57.192','00:37:58.568','- Come on.\n- What are you doing?',-1),(129322,42,54688,54736,'00:37:58.694','00:38:00.696','Forrest, let me down!',-1),(129323,42,54876,54922,'00:38:06.535','00:38:08.453','You can\'t keep doing this, Forrest.',-1),(129324,42,54924,54975,'00:38:08.537','00:38:10.664','You can\'t keep trying\nto rescue me all the time.',-1),(129325,42,54976,55075,'00:38:10.706','00:38:14.793','- They was trying to grab you.\n- A lot of people try to grab me.',-1),(129326,42,55097,55173,'00:38:15.711','00:38:18.880','Just... You can\'t keep\ndoing this all the time.',-1),(129327,42,55185,55255,'00:38:19.381','00:38:22.301','I can\'t help it. I love you.',-1),(129328,42,55278,55362,'00:38:23.260','00:38:26.763','Forrest, you don\'t know what love is.',-1),(129329,42,55537,55609,'00:38:34.062','00:38:37.065','You remember that time\nwe prayed, Forrest?',-1),(129330,42,55630,55738,'00:38:37.941','00:38:42.446','We prayed for God to turn me\ninto a bird so I could fly far, far away?',-1),(129331,42,55785,55818,'00:38:44.406','00:38:45.782','Yes, I do.',-1),(129332,42,55913,55981,'00:38:49.745','00:38:52.581','You think I could fly off this bridge?',-1),(129333,42,56142,56194,'00:38:59.254','00:39:01.423','What do you mean, Jenny?',-1),(129334,42,56287,56323,'00:39:05.302','00:39:06.803','Nothing.',-1),(129335,42,56394,56443,'00:39:09.765','00:39:11.808','I gotta get out of here.',-1),(129336,42,56498,56525,'00:39:14.102','00:39:15.228','Wait, Jenny...',-1),(129337,42,56526,56634,'00:39:15.270','00:39:19.775','Forrest, you stay away from me, okay?\nYou just stay away from me, please.',-1),(129338,42,56635,56666,'00:39:19.816','00:39:21.109','Can I have a ride?',-1),(129339,42,56668,56706,'00:39:21.193','00:39:22.778','- Where you going?\n- I don\'t care.',-1),(129340,42,56707,56740,'00:39:22.819','00:39:24.196','Get in the truck.',-1),(129341,42,56742,56786,'00:39:24.279','00:39:26.114','So, bye-bye, Jenny.',-1),(129342,42,56846,56902,'00:39:28.617','00:39:30.952','They sending me to Vietnam.',-1),(129343,42,56968,57026,'00:39:33.705','00:39:36.124','It\'s this whole other country.',-1),(129344,42,57087,57135,'00:39:38.627','00:39:40.629','Just hang on a minute.',-1),(129345,42,57169,57243,'00:39:42.047','00:39:45.133','Listen, you promise me\nsomething, okay?',-1),(129346,42,57244,57324,'00:39:45.175','00:39:48.512','Just, if you\'re ever in trouble,\ndon\'t try to be brave. You just run, okay?',-1),(129347,42,57327,57365,'00:39:48.637','00:39:50.222','Just run away.',-1),(129348,42,57395,57427,'00:39:51.473','00:39:52.808','Okay.',-1),(129349,42,57544,57576,'00:39:57.687','00:39:59.022','Jenny.',-1),(129350,42,57621,57676,'00:40:00.899','00:40:03.193','I\'ll write you all the time.',-1),(129351,42,57895,57967,'00:40:12.327','00:40:15.330','<i>And just like that, she was gone.</i>',-1),(129352,42,58354,58434,'00:40:31.430','00:40:34.766','You come back safe to me,\ndo you hear?',-1),(129353,42,59473,59569,'00:41:18.059','00:41:22.063','<i>Now, they told us that Vietnam\nwas gonna be very different</i>',-1),(129354,42,59570,59639,'00:41:22.105','00:41:24.983','<i>from the United States of America.</i>',-1),(129355,42,59641,59762,'00:41:25.066','00:41:30.113','<i>And except for all the beer cans\nand the barbecue, it was.</i>',-1),(129356,42,60005,60080,'00:41:40.248','00:41:43.335','Hey, I bet there\'s shrimp\nall in these waters.',-1),(129357,42,60082,60158,'00:41:43.418','00:41:46.588','They tell me these Vietnams\nis good shrimpers.',-1),(129358,42,60160,60246,'00:41:46.671','00:41:50.258','You know, after we win this war,\nand we take over everything,',-1),(129359,42