is one item of GI gear',-1),(129380,42,61659,61759,'00:42:49.150','00:42:53.321','that can be the difference between\na live grunt and a dead grunt.',-1),(129381,42,61767,61843,'00:42:53.655','00:42:56.825','Socks. Cushion sole, OD green.',-1),(129382,42,61845,61876,'00:42:56.908','00:42:58.201','Try and keep your feet dry.',-1),(129383,42,61879,61913,'00:42:58.326','00:42:59.744','When we\'re out humping,\nI want you boys to remember',-1),(129384,42,61915,61975,'00:42:59.828','00:43:02.330','to change your socks\nwhenever we stop.',-1),(129385,42,61976,62047,'00:43:02.372','00:43:05.333','The Mekong will eat a grunt\'s feet\nright off his legs.',-1),(129386,42,62050,62105,'00:43:05.417','00:43:07.711','Sergeant Sims, God damn it,',-1),(129387,42,62108,62142,'00:43:07.836','00:43:09.254','where is that sling rope\nI told you to order?',-1),(129388,42,62144,62190,'00:43:09.337','00:43:11.256','I put in the requisitions at Battalion.',-1),(129389,42,62192,62240,'00:43:11.339','00:43:13.341','Yeah, yeah, yeah, well,\nyou call those sons of bitches again...',-1),(129390,42,62242,62360,'00:43:13.425','00:43:18.346','<i>Lieutenant Dan sure knew his stuff.\nI felt real lucky he was my lieutenant.</i>',-1),(129391,42,62378,62461,'00:43:19.097','00:43:22.559','<i>He was from a long,\ngreat military tradition.</i>',-1),(129392,42,62466,62540,'00:43:22.767','00:43:25.854','<i>Somebody in his family\nhad fought and died</i>',-1),(129393,42,62564,62666,'00:43:26.855','00:43:31.109','<i>in every single American war.</i>',-1),(129394,42,62688,62736,'00:43:32.027','00:43:34.029','- God damn it, kick some ass!\n- I\'m on it, Lieutenant.',-1),(129395,42,62738,62765,'00:43:34.112','00:43:35.238','Get on it!',-1),(129396,42,62768,62848,'00:43:35.363','00:43:38.700','<i>I guess you could say he had\na lot to live up to.</i>',-1),(129397,42,62889,63005,'00:43:40.410','00:43:45.248','So, you boys are from Arkansas, huh?\nWell, I\'ve been through there.',-1),(129398,42,63008,63061,'00:43:45.373','00:43:47.542','Little Rock\'s a fine town.',-1),(129399,42,63077,63163,'00:43:48.209','00:43:51.796','Now, go shake down your gear,\nsee the platoon sergeant,',-1),(129400,42,63165,63225,'00:43:51.880','00:43:54.382','draw what you need for the field.',-1),(129401,42,63226,63321,'00:43:54.424','00:43:58.386','If you boys are hungry,\nwe got steaks burning right over here.',-1),(129402,42,63323,63393,'00:43:58.470','00:44:01.389','Two standing orders in this platoon:',-1),(129403,42,63394,63458,'00:44:01.431','00:44:04.100','one, take good care of your feet,',-1),(129404,42,63461,63582,'00:44:04.225','00:44:09.272','two, try not to do anything stupid,\nlike getting yourself killed.',-1),(129405,42,63737,63787,'00:44:15.737','00:44:17.822','I sure hope I don\'t let him down.',-1),(129406,42,64066,64184,'00:44:29.417','00:44:34.339','<i>I got to see a lot of the countryside.\nWe would take these real long walks.</i>',-1),(129407,42,64387,64486,'00:44:42.806','00:44:46.935','<i>And we were always looking\nfor this guy named Charlie.</i>',-1),(129408,42,64674,64728,'00:44:54.776','00:44:57.028','- Hold it up!\n- Hold up, boys!',-1),(129409,42,64796,64852,'00:44:59.864','00:45:02.200','<i>It wasn\'t always fun.</i>',-1),(129410,42,64854,64958,'00:45:02.283','00:45:06.621','<i>Lieutenant Dan was always getting\nthese funny feelings about a rock,</i>',-1),(129411,42,64959,65083,'00:45:06.663','00:45:11.793','<i>or a trail, or the road,\nso he\'d tell us to get down, shut up...</i>',-1),(129412,42,65084,65132,'00:45:11.835','00:45:13.837','Get down! Shut up!',-1),(129413,42,65155,65190,'00:45:14.796','00:45:16.256','<i>...so we did.</i>',-1),(129414,42,65611,65663,'00:45:33.815','00:45:35.984','<i>Now, I don\'t know much about anything,</i>',-1),(129415,42,65665,65757,'00:45:36.067','00:45:39.904','<i>but I think some of America\'s\nbest young men served in this war.</i>',-1),(129416,42,65759,65824,'00:45:39.988','00:45:42.699','<i>There was Dallas, from Phoenix,</i>',-1),(129417,42,65865,65932,'00:45:44.409','00:45:47.203','<i>Cleveland, he was from Detroit.</i>',-1),(129418,42,65935,65992,'00:45:47.328','00:45:49.706','Hey, Tex. Hey, Tex.',-1),(129419,42,65995,66048,'00:45:49.831','00:45:52.000','Man, what the hell\'s going on?',-1),(129420,42,66049,66154,'00:45:52.083','00:45:56.421','<i>And Tex was... Well, I don\'t remember\nwhere Tex come from.</i>',-1),(129421,42,66156,66193,'00:45:56.504','00:45:58.047','Nothing.',-1),(129422,42,66292,66352,'00:46:02.177','00:46:04.679','Fourth Platoon, on your feet.',-1),(129423,42,66354,66444,'00:46:04.763','00:46:08.516','Still got 10 klicks to go to that river.\nMove out.',-1),(129424,42,66445,66488,'00:46:08.558','00:46:10.351','Come on, move out.',-1),(129425,42,66537,66596,'00:46:12.395','00:46:14.856','Step it up. Look alive out there.',-1),(129426,42,66597,66701,'00:46:14.898','00:46:19.235','<i>The good thing about Vietnam\nis there was always some place to go.</i>',-1),(129427,42,66704,66737,'00:46:19.360','00:46:20.737','Fire in the hole!',-1),(129428,42,66820,66876,'00:46:24.199','00:46:26.534','Gump, check out that hole.',-1),(129429,42,66878,66950,'00:46:26.618','00:46:29.621','<i>And there was always something to do.</i>',-1),(129430,42,66952,67028,'00:46:29.704','00:46:32.874','- Mount them up.\n- Spread out! Cover his back.',-1),(129431,42,67150,67285,'00:46:37.921','00:46:43.551','<i>One day, it started raining,\nand it didn\'t quit for four months.</i>',-1),(129432,42,67309,67378,'00:46:44.552','00:46:47.430','<i>We\'d been through\nevery kind of rain there is:</i>',-1),(129433,42,67381,67442,'00:46:47.555','00:46:50.099','<i>little bitty stinging rain,</i>',-1),(129434,42,67459,67523,'00:46:50.809','00:46:53.478','<i>and big old fat rain,</i>',-1),(129435,42,67534,67599,'00:46:53.937','00:46:56.648','<i>rain that flew in sideways.</i>',-1),(129436,42,67601,67698,'00:46:56.731','00:47:00.777','<i>And sometimes, rain even seemed\nto come straight up from underneath.</i>',-1),(129437,42,67741,67798,'00:47:02.570','00:47:04.948','<i>Shoot, it even rained at night.</i>',-1),(129438,42,67823,67882,'00:47:05.990','00:47:08.451','- Hey, Forrest.\n- Hey, Bubba.',-1),(129439,42,67885,67965,'00:47:08.576','00:47:11.913','I\'m gonna lean up against you.\nYou just lean right back against me.',-1),(129440,42,67966,68059,'00:47:11.955','00:47:15.792','This way, we don\'t have to sleep\nwith our heads in the mud.',-1),(129441,42,68082,68166,'00:47:16.751','00:47:20.255','You know why we a good partnership,\nForrest?',-1),(129442,42,68167,68227,'00:47:20.296','00:47:22.799','\'Cause we be watching out\nfor one another,',-1),(129443,42,68230,68275,'00:47:22.924','00:47:24.801','like brothers and stuff.',-1),(129444,42,68322,68410,'00:47:26.761','00:47:30.431','Hey, Forrest, there\'s something\nI\'ve been thinking about.',-1),(129445,42,68412,68484,'00:47:30.515','00:47:33.518','I got a very important question\nto ask you.',-1),(129446,42,68523,68618,'00:47:35.144','00:47:39.107','How would you like to go\ninto the shrimping business with me?',-1),(129447,42,68646,68686,'00:47:40.275','00:47:41.943','Okay.',-1),(129448,42,68687,68770,'00:47:41.985','00:47:45.446','Man, I tell you what,\nI got it all figured out, too.',-1),(129449,42,68772,68839,'00:47:45.530','00:47:48.324','So many pounds of shrimp\nto pay off the boat,',-1),(129450,42,68842,68922,'00:47:48.449','00:47:51.786','so many pounds for gas,\nwe can just live right on the boat.',-1),(129451,42,68923,68978,'00:47:51.828','00:47:54.122','We ain\'t got to pay no rent.',-1),(129452,42,68980,69030,'00:47:54.205','00:47:56.291','I\'ll be the captain,\nwe can just work it together,',-1),(129453,42,69032,69135,'00:47:56.374','00:48:00.628','split everything right down the middle.\nMan, I\'m telling you, 50-50.',-1),(129454,42,69137,69223,'00:48:00.712','00:48:04.299','And, hey, Forrest,\nall the shrimp you can eat.',-1),(129455,42,69260,69303,'00:48:05.842','00:48:07.635','That\'s a fine idea.',-1),(129456,42,69329,69380,'00:48:08.720','00:48:10.847','<i>Bubba did have a fine idea.</i>',-1),(129457,42,69471,69545,'00:48:14.642','00:48:17.729','<i>I even wrote Jenny\nand told her all about it.</i>',-1),(129458,42,69564,69641,'00:48:18.521','00:48:21.733','<i>I sent her letters,\nnot every day, but almost.</i>',-1),(129459,42,69643,69763,'00:48:21.816','00:48:26.821','<i>I told her what I was doing\nand asked her what she was doing,</i>',-1),(129460,42,69765,69831,'00:48:26.905','00:48:29.657','<i>and told her\nhow I thought about her always,</i>',-1),(129461,42,69863,69935,'00:48:30.992','00:48:33.995','<i>and how I was looking forward\nto getting a letter from her</i>',-1),(129462,42,69936,69996,'00:48:34.037','00:48:36.539','<i>just as soon as she had the time.</i>',-1),(129463,42,70041,70102,'00:48:38.416','00:48:40.919','<i>I\'d always let her know that I was okay.</i>',-1),(129464,42,70133,70257,'00:48:42.211','00:48:47.383','<i>Then, I\'d sign each letter,\n\"Love, Forrest Gump.\"</i>',-1),(129465,42,70613,70704,'00:49:02.231','00:49:06.027','<i>This one day, we was out walking,\nlike always,</i>',-1),(129466,42,70705,70776,'00:49:06.069','00:49:09.030','<i>and then, just like that,</i>',-1),(129467,42,70798,70880,'00:49:09.948','00:49:13.368','<i>somebody turned off the rain\nand the sun come out.</i>',-1),(129468,42,70952,70996,'00:49:16.371','00:49:18.206','Ambush!',-1),(129469,42,71008,71041,'00:49:18.706','00:49:20.083','Take cover!',-1),(129470,42,71129,71157,'00:49:23.711','00:49:24.879','Get down!',-1),(129471,42,71159,71194,'00:49:24.963','00:49:26.422','Get the sixty!',-1),(129472,42,71270,71321,'00:49:29.592','00:49:31.719','Get that pig up here, God damn it!',-1),(129473,42,71322,71373,'00:49:31.761','00:49:33.888','Forrest, you okay?',-1),(129474,42,71450,71513,'00:49:37.100','00:49:39.727','Strongarm! Strongarm!\nBe advised, Strongarm!',-1),(129475,42,71526,71585,'00:49:40.269','00:49:42.730','Medic, we got a man down!',-1),(129476,42,71586,71657,'00:49:42.772','00:49:45.733','Strongarm, this is Leg Lima 6, over!',-1),(129477,42,71674,71754,'00:49:46.442','00:49:49.779','Roger, Strongarm, be advised\nwe have incoming from the tree line',-1),(129478,42,71757,71841,'00:49:49.904','00:49:53.408','at points blue plus two.\nAKs and rockets...',-1),(129479,42,71857,71900,'00:49:54.075','00:49:55.868','Misfire! Misfire!',-1),(129480,42,71957,72005,'00:49:58.246','00:50:00.248','God damn it! Mac!',-1),(129481,42,72028,72111,'00:50:01.207','00:50:04.627','Get that thing...\nFuck it, get it in the tree line!',-1),(129482,42,72134,72162,'00:50:05.586','00:50:06.754','Jesus!',-1),(129483,42,72165,72218,'00:50:06.879','00:50:09.090','My unit is down hard and hurting!',-1),(129484,42,72221,72306,'00:50:09.215','00:50:12.760','Six are pulling back to Blue Line,\nLeg Lima 6 out.',-1),(129485,42,72325,72373,'00:50:13.553','00:50:15.555','Pull back! Pull back!',-1),(129486,42,72374,72425,'00:50:15.596','00:50:17.724','Run! Run, Forrest!',-1),(129487,42,72427,72483,'00:50:17.807','00:50:20.143','- Pull back!\n- Forrest, Forrest!',-1),(129488,42,72486,72549,'00:50:20.268','00:50:22.895','Run, man! Run!',-1),(129489,42,72550,72593,'00:50:22.937','00:50:24.731','Pull back! Run!',-1),(129490,42,72637,72690,'00:50:26.566','00:50:28.776','Run, God damn it, run!',-1),(129491,42,73199,73310,'00:50:49.964','00:50:54.594','Medic! Can I get a medic?',-1),(129492,42,73319,73399,'00:50:54.969','00:50:58.306','<i>I ran and ran, just like Jenny told me to.</i>',-1),(129493,42,73480,73582,'00:51:01.684','00:51:05.938','<i>I ran so far and so fast\nthat pretty soon I was all by myself,</i>',-1),(129494,42,73583,73630,'00:51:05.980','00:51:07.940','<i>which was a bad thing.</i>',-1),(129495,42,73643,73680,'00:51:08.483','00:51:10.026','Bubba!',-1),(129496,42,73731,73822,'00:51:12.153','00:51:15.948','<i>Bubba was my best good friend.\nI had to make sure that he was okay.</i>',-1),(129497,42,73911,73960,'00:51:19.660','00:51:21.704','Any friendlies out there?',-1),(129498,42,73983,74035,'00:51:22.663','00:51:24.832','Yeah, I\'ve got three over here.',-1),(129499,42,74050,74099,'00:51:25.458','00:51:27.460','Where the hell are you?',-1),(129500,42,74113,74145,'00:51:28.044','00:51:29.378','Bubba?',-1),(129501,42,74171,74236,'00:51:30.463','00:51:33.174','<i>And on my way back to find Bubba,</i>',-1),(129502,42,74239,74307,'00:51:33.299','00:51:36.135','<i>well, there was this boy\nlaying on the ground.</i>',-1),(129503,42,74308,74337,'00:51:36.177','00:51:37.386','Tex!',-1),(129504,42,74387,74412,'00:51:39.472','00:51:40.515','Okay.',-1),(129505,42,74413,74508,'00:51:40.556','00:51:44.519','<i>I couldn\'t just let him lay there all alone,\nscared the way he was,</i>',-1),(129506,42,74511,74604,'00:51:44.644','00:51:48.523','<i>so I grabbed him up\nand run him out of there.</i>',-1),(129507,42,74967,75025,'00:52:03.663','00:52:06.082','<i>And every time I went back\nlooking for Bubba,</i>',-1),(129508,42,75028,75113,'00:52:06.207','00:52:09.710','<i>somebody else was saying,\n\"Help me, Forrest. Help me.\"</i>',-1),(129509,42,75297,75342,'00:52:17.385','00:52:19.262','Can\'t hear... Can\'t hear...',-1),(129510,42,75397,75429,'00:52:21.556','00:52:22.890','No sweat, man. Just lay back.',-1),(129511,42,75430,75490,'00:52:22.932','00:52:25.434','You\'ll be okay. You\'ll be okay.',-1),(129512,42,75538,75612,'00:52:27.436','00:52:30.523','<i>I started to get scared\nthat I might never find Bubba.</i>',-1),(129513,42,75613,75644,'00:52:30.565','00:52:31.858','<i>...over.</i>',-1),(129514,42,75645,75725,'00:52:31.899','00:52:35.236','Roger, Strongarm,\nI know my position is danger close.',-1),(129515,42,75726,75770,'00:52:35.278','00:52:37.113','We got Charlie all over this area.',-1),(129516,42,75773,75829,'00:52:37.238','00:52:39.574','I gotta have those fast movers\nin here now. Over.',-1),(129517,42,75830,75912,'00:52:39.615','00:52:43.035','<i>- Six, Strongarm, we want...</i>\n- Lieutenant Dan, Coleman\'s dead!',-1),(129518,42,75913,75942,'00:52:43.077','00:52:44.287','I know he\'s dead!',-1),(129519,42,75945,76013,'00:52:44.412','00:52:47.248','My whole goddamn platoon\nis wiped out!',-1),(129520,42,76016,76049,'00:52:47.373','00:52:48.749','<i>- Leg Lima 6, Leg Lima 6.</i>\n- God damn it!',-1),(129521,42,76050,76117,'00:52:48.791','00:52:51.544','<i>- Copy this transmission. Over.</i>\n- What are you doing?',-1),(129522,42,76118,76198,'00:52:51.586','00:52:54.922','Just leave me here! Get away.\nJust leave me here! Get out!',-1),(129523,42,76201,76257,'00:52:55.047','00:52:57.383','<i>Leg Lima 6, Strongarm.\nHow copy this? Over.</i>',-1),(129524,42,76258,76322,'00:52:57.425','00:53:00.094','God, I said leave me here, God damn it!',-1),(129525,42,76323,76399,'00:53:00.136','00:53:03.306','<i>Leg Lima 6, Leg Lima 6,\nthis is Strongarm, be advised</i>',-1),(129526,42,76402,76450,'00:53:03.431','00:53:05.433','<i>your fast movers\nare inbound at this time, over.</i>',-1),(129527,42,76451,76533,'00:53:05.474','00:53:08.895','<i>Then, it felt like something\njust jumped up and bit me.</i>',-1),(129528,42,76554,76594,'00:53:09.770','00:53:11.439','Something bit me!',-1),(129529,42,76759,76810,'00:53:18.321','00:53:20.448','You chink son of a bitch!',-1),(129530,42,76870,76918,'00:53:22.950','00:53:24.952','I can\'t leave the platoon.',-1),(129531,42,76921,77039,'00:53:25.077','00:53:29.999','I told you to leave me there, Gump.\nForget about me. Get yourself out!',-1),(129532,42,77042,77094,'00:53:30.124','00:53:32.251','Did you hear what I said?',-1),(129533,42,77111,77158,'00:53:32.960','00:53:34.921','God damn it, put me down!',-1),(129534,42,77175,77224,'00:53:35.630','00:53:37.673','Get your ass out of here!',-1),(129535,42,77303,77366,'00:53:40.968','00:53:43.596','I didn\'t ask you to pull me out of there,\nGod damn you!',-1),(129536,42,77367,77399,'00:53:43.638','00:53:44.972','Where the hell\ndo you think you\'re going?',-1),(129537,42,77402,77428,'00:53:45.097','00:53:46.182','To get Bubba.',-1),(129538,42,77431,77523,'00:53:46.307','00:53:50.144','I got an air strike inbound right now.\nThey\'re gonna nape the whole area.',-1),(129539,42,77526,77583,'00:53:50.269','00:53:52.647','Gump, you stay here, God damn it!\nThat\'s an order!',-1),(129540,42,77586,77644,'00:53:52.772','00:53:55.191','I gotta find Bubba!',-1),(129541,42,78027,78063,'00:54:11.165','00:54:12.625','Forrest.',-1),(129542,42,78249,78313,'00:54:20.383','00:54:23.052','- Bubba.\n- I\'m okay, Forrest.',-1),(129543,42,78332,78372,'00:54:23.844','00:54:25.513','I\'m okay.',-1),(129544,42,78560,78604,'00:54:33.354','00:54:35.189','Oh, Bubba, no...',-1),(129545,42,78607,78660,'00:54:35.314','00:54:37.525','Nah, I\'m gonna be all right.',-1),(129546,42,78856,78920,'00:54:45.700','00:54:48.369','Come on. Come on. Come on.',-1),(129547,42,79040,79077,'00:54:53.374','00:54:54.875','I\'m okay, Forrest.',-1),(129548,42,79109,79177,'00:54:56.210','00:54:59.046','I\'m okay, man. I\'m fine.',-1),(129549,42,80065,80141,'00:55:36.083','00:55:39.211','Helo\'s inbound.\nTop smoke, get it out there!',-1),(129550,42,80166,80274,'00:55:40.254','00:55:44.759','<i>If I\'d a known this was gonna be the\nlast time me and Bubba was gonna talk,</i>',-1),(129551,42,80277,80333,'00:55:44.884','00:55:47.219','<i>I\'d of thought of something better to say.</i>',-1),(129552,42,80334,80370,'00:55:47.261','00:55:48.763','Hey, Bubba.',-1),(129553,42,80397,80430,'00:55:49.889','00:55:51.265','Hey, Forrest.',-1),(129554,42,80486,80563,'00:55:53.601','00:55:56.812','Forrest, why\'d this happen?',-1),(129555,42,80595,80638,'00:55:58.147','00:55:59.940','You got shot.',-1),(129556,42,80679,80779,'00:56:01.650','00:56:05.821','<i>Then Bubba said something\nI won\'t ever forget.</i>',-1),(129557,42,80798,80838,'00:56:06.614','00:56:08.282','I wanna go home.',-1),(129558,42,80886,80935,'00:56:10.284','00:56:12.328','<i>Bubba was my best good friend.</i>',-1),(129559,42,80958,81067,'00:56:13.287','00:56:17.833','<i>And even I know that ain\'t something\nyou can find just around the corner.</i>',-1),(129560,42,81070,81146,'00:56:17.958','00:56:21.087','<i>Bubba was gonna be\na shrimping boat captain,</i>',-1),(129561,42,81147,81242,'00:56:21.128','00:56:25.091','<i>but instead he died right there\nby that river in Vietnam.</i>',-1),(129562,42,81379,81434,'00:56:30.805','00:56:33.099','That\'s all I have to say about that.',-1),(129563,42,81491,81543,'00:56:35.476','00:56:37.645','It was a bullet, wasn\'t it?',-1),(129564,42,81599,81663,'00:56:39.980','00:56:42.650','- A bullet?\n- That jumped up and bit you.',-1),(129565,42,81720,81771,'00:56:45.027','00:56:47.154','Oh, yes, sir.',-1),(129566,42,81772,81847,'00:56:47.196','00:56:50.324','Bit me directly in the buttocks.',-1),(129567,42,81850,81976,'00:56:50.449','00:56:55.704','They said it was a million-dollar wound,\nbut the Army must keep that money,',-1),(129568,42,81979,82072,'00:56:55.830','00:56:59.667','\'cause I still ain\'t seen a nickel\nof that million dollars.',-1),(129569,42,82092,82176,'00:57:00.501','00:57:04.004','The only good thing\nabout being wounded in the buttocks',-1),(129570,42,82179,82220,'00:57:04.130','00:57:05.840','<i>is the ice cream.</i>',-1),(129571,42,82223,82285,'00:57:05.965','00:57:08.551','<i>They gave me all the ice cream\nI could eat.</i>',-1),(129572,42,82288,82320,'00:57:08.676','00:57:10.010','<i>And guess what?</i>',-1),(129573,42,82321,82396,'00:57:10.052','00:57:13.180','<i>A good friend of mine\nwas in the bed right next door.</i>',-1),(129574,42,82449,82523,'00:57:15.391','00:57:18.477','Lieutenant Dan,\nI got you some ice cream.',-1),(129575,42,82580,82632,'00:57:20.855','00:57:23.023','Lieutenant Dan, ice cream.',-1),(129576,42,82913,82968,'00:57:34.743','00:57:37.037','It\'s time for your bath, Lieutenant.',-1),(129577,42,83173,83205,'00:57:45.546','00:57:46.881','Harper!',-1),(129578,42,83282,83341,'00:57:50.092','00:57:52.553','Cooper, Larson,',-1),(129579,42,83394,83426,'00:57:54.763','00:57:56.098','Webster,',-1),(129580,42,83460,83544,'00:57:57.516','00:58:01.020','- Gump. Gump.\n- I\'m Forrest Gump.',-1),(129581,42,83629,83708,'00:58:04.565','00:58:07.860','Kyle, Nichols,',-1),(129582,42,83761,83904,'00:58:10.070','00:58:16.035','McMill, Johnson, Tyler,',-1),(129583,42,83936,83969,'00:58:17.369','00:58:18.746','Holiday...',-1),(129584,42,84132,84186,'00:58:25.503','00:58:27.755','<i>Surprise, surprise, surprise!</i>',-1),(129585,42,84266,84326,'00:58:31.091','00:58:33.594','Gump, how can you watch\nthat stupid shit?',-1),(129586,42,84328,84366,'00:58:33.677','00:58:35.262','<i>- From the DMZ to the Delta...</i>\n- Turn it off!',-1),(129587,42,84368,84446,'00:58:35.346','00:58:38.599','<i>...you are tuned to the\nAmerican Forces Vietnam Network.</i>',-1),(129588,42,84449,84505,'00:58:38.724','00:58:41.060','<i>This is Channel 6, Saigon.</i>',-1),(129589,42,84570,84610,'00:58:43.771','00:58:45.439','Good catch, Gump.',-1),(129590,42,84657,84709,'00:58:47.399','00:58:49.568','You know how to play this?',-1),(129591,42,84740,84790,'00:58:50.861','00:58:52.947','Come on, let me show you. Here.',-1),(129592,42,84840,84896,'00:58:55.032','00:58:57.368','Now, the secret to this game is,',-1),(129593,42,84898,85038,'00:58:57.451','00:59:03.290','no matter what happens,\nnever ever take your eye off the ball.',-1),(129594,42,85125,85157,'00:59:06.877','00:59:08.212','All right.',-1),(129595,42,85237,85325,'00:59:11.549','00:59:15.219','<i>For some reason,\nPing-Pong came very natural to me.</i>',-1),(129596,42,85333,85403,'00:59:15.553','00:59:18.472','See? Any idiot can play.',-1),(129597,42,85415,85481,'00:59:18.973','00:59:21.725','<i>So, I started playing it all the time.</i>',-1),(129598,42,85509,85542,'00:59:22.893','00:59:24.270','<i>I played Ping-Pong</i>',-1),(129599,42,85543,85622,'00:59:24.311','00:59:27.606','<i>even when I didn\'t have anyone\nto play Ping-Pong with.</i>',-1),(129600,42,85815,85927,'00:59:35.656','00:59:40.327','<i>The hospital\'s people said\nit made me look like a duck in water,</i>',-1),(129601,42,85930,85974,'00:59:40.452','00:59:42.288','<i>whatever that means.</i>',-1),(129602,42,85985,86064,'00:59:42.746','00:59:46.000','<i>Even Lieutenant Dan would come\nand watch me play.</i>',-1),(129603,42,86196,86289,'00:59:51.505','00:59:55.384','<i>I played Ping-Pong so much,\nI even played it in my sleep.</i>',-1),(129604,42,86476,86599,'01:00:03.183','01:00:08.314','Now, you listen to me.\nWe all have a destiny.',-1),(129605,42,86600,86673,'01:00:08.355','01:00:11.400','Nothing just happens,\nit\'s all part of a plan.',-1),(129606,42,86676,86740,'01:00:11.525','01:00:14.194','I should have died out there\nwith my men,',-1),(129607,42,86743,86839,'01:00:14.320','01:00:18.324','but now I\'m nothing\nbut a goddamn cripple,',-1),(129608,42,86840,86927,'01:00:18.365','01:00:21.994','a legless freak! Look! Look! Look at me!',-1),(129609,42,86945,86972,'01:00:22.745','01:00:23.871','Do you see that?',-1),(129610,42,86973,87064,'01:00:23.912','01:00:27.708','Do you know what it\'s like\nnot to be able to use your legs?',-1),(129611,42,87145,87184,'01:00:31.045','01:00:32.671','Yes, sir, I do.',-1),(129612,42,87272,87321,'01:00:36.342','01:00:38.385','Did you hear what I said?',-1),(129613,42,87342,87385,'01:00:39.261','01:00:41.055','You cheated me.',-1),(129614,42,87386,87414,'01:00:41.096','01:00:42.264','I had a destiny.',-1),(129615,42,87416,87501,'01:00:42.348','01:00:45.893','I was supposed to die in the field,\nwith honor!',-1),(129616,42,87517,87614,'01:00:46.560','01:00:50.606','That was my destiny,\nand you cheated me out of it!',-1),(129617,42,87845,87910,'01:01:00.240','01:01:02.951','Do you understand\nwhat I\'m saying, Gump?',-1),(129618,42,87961,88042,'01:01:05.079','01:01:08.457','This wasn\'t supposed to happen,\nnot to me.',-1),(129619,42,88106,88146,'01:01:11.085','01:01:12.753','I had a destiny.',-1),(129620,42,88193,88298,'01:01:14.713','01:01:19.093','I was Lieutenant Dan Taylor.',-1),(129621,42,88446,88502,'01:01:25.265','01:01:27.601','You\'re still Lieutenant Dan.',-1),(129622,42,89059,89096,'01:01:50.833','01:01:52.334','Look at me.',-1),(129623,42,89128,89175,'01:01:53.669','01:01:55.629','What am I gonna do now?',-1),(129624,42,89263,89312,'01:01:59.299','01:02:01.343','What am I gonna do now?',-1),(129625,42,89561,89596,'01:02:11.729','01:02:13.188','PFC Gump?',-1),(129626,42,89633,89667,'01:02:14.732','01:02:16.150','Yes, sir!',-1),(129627,42,89683,89719,'01:02:16.817','01:02:18.318','As you were.',-1),(129628,42,89731,89823,'01:02:18.819','01:02:22.656','Son, you\'ve been awarded\nthe Medal of Honor.',-1),(129629,42,89848,89935,'01:02:23.699','01:02:27.327','Guess what, Lieutenant Dan,\nthey want to give me a...',-1),(129630,42,90098,90188,'01:02:34.084','01:02:37.838','Ma\'am, what\'d they do\nwith Lieutenant Dan?',-1),(129631,42,90210,90253,'01:02:38.756','01:02:40.549','They sent him home.',-1),(129632,42,90397,90463,'01:02:46.555','01:02:49.308','<i>Two weeks later, I left Vietnam.</i>',-1),(129633,42,90488,90573,'01:02:50.350','01:02:53.896','<i>The ceremony was kicked off\nwith a candid speech by the President</i>',-1),(129634,42,90575,90656,'01:02:53.979','01:02:57.357','<i>regarding the need for further escalation\nof the war in Vietnam.</i>',-1),(129635,42,90658,90709,'01:02:57.441','01:02:59.568','<i>President Johnson awarded\nfour Medals of Honor</i>',-1),(129636,42,90711,90751,'01:02:59.651','01:03:01.320','<i>to men\nfrom each of the Armed Services.</i>',-1),(129637,42,90753,90823,'01:03:01.403','01:03:04.323','<i>America owes you\na debt of gratitude, son.</i>',-1),(129638,42,90871,90962,'01:03:06.325','01:03:10.120','<i>I understand you were wounded.\nWhere were you hit?</i>',-1),(129639,42,90964,91040,'01:03:10.204','01:03:13.373','<i>- In the buttocks, sir.\n- That must be a sight.</i>',-1),(129640,42,91058,91114,'01:03:14.124','01:03:16.418','<i>I\'d kind of like to see that.</i>',-1),(129641,42,91453,91488,'01:03:30.557','01:03:32.017','<i>God damn, son.</i>',-1),(129642,42,91539,91631,'01:03:34.144','01:03:37.981','<i>After that,\nMama went to the hotel to lay down,</i>',-1),(129643,42,91633,91717,'01:03:38.065','01:03:41.568','<i>so I went out for a walk\nto see our nation\'s capital.</i>',-1),(129644,42,91719,91794,'01:03:41.652','01:03:44.780','Hilary, all right, I\'ve got the vets,\nwhat do you want me to do with them?',-1),(129645,42,91796,91838,'01:03:44.863','01:03:46.615','What are you doing here so late?',-1),(129646,42,91840,91937,'01:03:46.698','01:03:50.744','<i>It\'s a good thing Mama was resting,\n\'cause the streets was awful crowded</i>',-1),(129647,42,91939,92015,'01:03:50.828','01:03:53.997','<i>with people looking\nat all the statues and monuments,</i>',-1),(129648,42,92017,92080,'01:03:54.081','01:03:56.708','<i>and some of them people were loud\nand pushy.</i>',-1),(129649,42,92083,92154,'01:03:56.792','01:03:59.753','Okay, follow me! Come on.\nLet\'s move it out.',-1),(129650,42,92174,92245,'01:04:00.587','01:04:03.549','<i>Everywhere I went,\nI had to stand in line.</i>',-1),(129651,42,92323,92360,'01:04:06.802','01:04:08.345','Follow me, let\'s go!',-1),(129652,42,92403,92442,'01:04:10.138','01:04:11.765','Come on. Let\'s go.',-1),(129653,42,92587,92625,'01:04:17.813','01:04:19.398','Stand here.',-1),(129654,42,92684,92760,'01:04:21.859','01:04:25.028','Hey, you\'re a good man\nfor doing this. Good!',-1),(129655,42,92791,92818,'01:04:26.321','01:04:27.447','Okay.',-1),(129656,42,92837,92918,'01:04:28.240','01:04:31.618','<i>There was this man giving a little talk.</i>',-1),(129657,42,92920,93004,'01:04:31.702','01:04:35.205','<i>And for some reason, he was\nwearing an American flag for a shirt.</i>',-1),(129658,42,93006,93041,'01:04:35.289','01:04:36.748','<i>Now, I\'m gonna\nbring up some soldiers...</i>',-1),(129659,42,93043,93111,'01:04:36.832','01:04:39.626','<i>And he liked to say the \"F\" word.</i>',-1),(129660,42,93113,93194,'01:04:39.710','01:04:43.088','<i>A lot.\"F\" this and \"F\" that.</i>',-1),(129661,42,93196,93252,'01:04:43.171','01:04:45.507','<i>And every time he said the \"F\" word,</i>',-1),(129662,42,93254,93320,'01:04:45.591','01:04:48.343','<i>people, for some reason,\nwell, they\'d cheer.</i>',-1),(129663,42,93322,93396,'01:04:48.427','01:04:51.513','<i>...where to stick this fucking war! Yeah!</i>',-1),(129664,42,93421,93477,'01:04:52.556','01:04:54.892','<i>Yeah! Yeah!</i>',-1),(129665,42,93491,93551,'01:04:55.475','01:04:57.978','Come on, man, come up here, man.',-1),(129666,42,93561,93641,'01:04:58.395','01:05:01.732','Come on. Come on. Yeah, you!\nCome on. Move, move, move.',-1),(129667,42,93665,93747,'01:05:02.733','01:05:06.153','You can do it. Just get up there.\nGo on. That\'s it.',-1),(129668,42,94054,94116,'01:05:18.957','01:05:21.501','<i>Tell us a little bit about the war, man.</i>',-1),(129669,42,94118,94160,'01:05:21.585','01:05:23.337','<i>The war in Vietnam?</i>',-1),(129670,42,94162,94232,'01:05:23.420','01:05:26.340','<i>- The war in Viet-fucking-nam!</i>\n- Yeah!',-1),(129671,42,94720,94746,'01:05:46.693','01:05:47.778','Peace!',-1),(129672,42,94755,94788,'01:05:48.153','01:05:49.529','Come on, man, go!',-1),(129673,42,94795,94842,'01:05:49.821','01:05:51.782','- Come on!\n- Peace!',-1),(129674,42,94844,94869,'01:05:51.865','01:05:52.908','<i>Well...</i>',-1),(129675,42,94871,94955,'01:05:52.991','01:05:56.495','<i>There was only one thing\nI could say about the war in Vietnam.</i>',-1),(129676,42,94956,95073,'01:05:56.536','01:06:01.375','<i>...there\'s only one thing\nI can say about the war in Vietnam.</i>',-1),(129677,42,95164,95255,'01:06:05.170','01:06:08.966','<i>In Vietnam, your...</i>',-1),(129678,42,95489,95515,'01:06:18.725','01:06:19.810','Hey, what the hell are you...',-1),(129679,42,95517,95584,'01:06:19.893','01:06:22.688','I\'ll beat your head in,\nyou goddamn oinker!',-1),(129680,42,95585,95645,'01:06:22.729','01:06:25.232','Jesus Christ, what\'d they do with this?',-1),(129681,42,95679,95719,'01:06:26.650','01:06:28.318','We can\'t hear you!',-1),(129682,42,95760,95808,'01:06:30.028','01:06:32.030','We can\'t hear anything!',-1),(129683,42,95825,95885,'01:06:32.739','01:06:35.242','- This one! This one! Give me that!\n- Turn it up!',-1),(129684,42,95887,95921,'01:06:35.325','01:06:36.743','Speak up!',-1),(129685,42,95940,95975,'01:06:37.536','01:06:38.996','That\'s it!',-1),(129686,42,96001,96069,'01:06:40.080','01:06:42.916','<i>...and that\'s all I have to say about that.</i>',-1),(129687,42,96245,96316,'01:06:50.215','01:06:53.176','That\'s so right on, man. You said it all.',-1),(129688,42,96352,96413,'01:06:54.678','01:06:57.222','What\'s your name, man?',-1),(129689,42,96414,96477,'01:06:57.264','01:06:59.891','<i>My name is Forrest. Forrest Gump.</i>',-1),(129690,42,96506,96534,'01:07:01.101','01:07:02.269','<i>Forrest Gump!</i>',-1),(129691,42,96537,96570,'01:07:02.394','01:07:03.770','- Gump!\n- Gump!',-1),(129692,42,96606,96696,'01:07:05.272','01:07:09.026','Forrest! Forrest!',-1),(129693,42,96793,96850,'01:07:13.071','01:07:15.449','<i>- Jenny!</i>\n- Forrest!',-1),(129694,42,97253,97317,'01:07:32.215','01:07:34.885','Hey! Hey!',-1),(129695,42,97511,97586,'01:07:42.976','01:07:46.104','<i>It was the happiest moment of my life.</i>',-1),(129696,42,97642,97723,'01:07:48.440','01:07:51.818','<i>Jenny and me were just like\npeas and carrots again.</i>',-1),(129697,42,97755,97793,'01:07:53.153','01:07:54.738','<i>She showed me around,</i>',-1),(129698,42,97795,97857,'01:07:54.821','01:07:57.407','<i>and even introduced me\nto some of her new friends.</i>',-1),(129699,42,97859,97891,'01:07:57.491','01:07:58.825','Shut that blind, man.',-1),(129700,42,97894,97947,'01:07:58.950','01:08:01.161','And get your white ass\naway from that window.',-1),(129701,42,97949,97999,'01:08:01.244','01:08:03.330','Don\'t you know we in a war here?',-1),(129702,42,98019,98053,'01:0