54.172','as they sleep in their beds at night.',-1),(129721,42,99221,99249,'01:08:54.214','01:08:55.382','You are a fucking asshole!',-1),(129722,42,99251,99332,'01:08:55.465','01:08:58.844','Yes, we are against all these racist\nand imperial dog acts.',-1),(129723,42,99555,99632,'01:09:08.145','01:09:11.356','Forrest! Quit it! Quit it!',-1),(129724,42,99679,99709,'01:09:13.316','01:09:14.568','Forrest!',-1),(129725,42,99723,99765,'01:09:15.152','01:09:16.903','Stop it! Stop it!',-1),(129726,42,99924,99957,'01:09:23.535','01:09:24.911','Oh, God...',-1),(129727,42,99977,100035,'01:09:25.745','01:09:28.165','I shouldn\'t have brought you here.',-1),(129728,42,100037,100125,'01:09:28.248','01:09:31.877','I should have known it was just\ngonna be some bullshit hassle.',-1),(129729,42,100153,100216,'01:09:33.044','01:09:35.672','He should not be hitting you, Jenny.',-1),(129730,42,100334,100376,'01:09:40.594','01:09:42.345','Come on, Forrest.',-1),(129731,42,100513,100609,'01:09:48.059','01:09:52.063','Sorry I had a fight in the middle\nof your Black Panther party.',-1),(129732,42,100678,100734,'01:09:54.941','01:09:57.277','He doesn\'t mean it when\nhe does things like this. He doesn\'t.',-1),(129733,42,100736,100792,'01:09:57.360','01:09:59.696','I would never hurt you, Jenny.',-1),(129734,42,100836,100890,'01:10:01.531','01:10:03.783','I know you wouldn\'t, Forrest.',-1),(129735,42,100936,100998,'01:10:05.702','01:10:08.288','I wanted to be your boyfriend.',-1),(129736,42,101251,101309,'01:10:18.798','01:10:21.218','That uniform is a trip, Forrest.',-1),(129737,42,101342,101419,'01:10:22.594','01:10:25.805','You look handsome in it. You do.',-1),(129738,42,101517,101563,'01:10:29.893','01:10:31.811','- You know what?\n- What?',-1),(129739,42,101650,101737,'01:10:35.440','01:10:39.069','I\'m glad we were here together\nin our nation\'s capital.',-1),(129740,42,101775,101818,'01:10:40.654','01:10:42.447','Me, too, Forrest.',-1),(129741,42,101819,101931,'01:10:42.489','01:10:47.160','<i>We walked around all night,\nJenny and me, just talking.</i>',-1),(129742,42,101981,102057,'01:10:49.246','01:10:52.415','<i>She told me about\nall the traveling she\'d done.</i>',-1),(129743,42,102059,102171,'01:10:52.499','01:10:57.128','<i>And how she\'d discovered ways\nto expand her mind</i>',-1),(129744,42,102172,102246,'01:10:57.170','01:11:00.257','<i>and learn how to live in harmony,</i>',-1),(129745,42,102248,102304,'01:11:00.340','01:11:02.676','<i>which must be out west somewhere,</i>',-1),(129746,42,102306,102362,'01:11:02.759','01:11:05.095','<i>\'cause she made it\nall the way to California.</i>',-1),(129747,42,102364,102418,'01:11:05.178','01:11:07.430','<i>Try to love one another right now</i>',-1),(129748,42,102420,102448,'01:11:07.514','01:11:08.682','Hey!',-1),(129749,42,102471,102532,'01:11:09.641','01:11:12.185','Anybody want to go to San Francisco?',-1),(129750,42,102534,102579,'01:11:12.269','01:11:14.145','- I\'ll go.\n- Far out.',-1),(129751,42,102614,102690,'01:11:15.605','01:11:18.775','<i>It was a very special night\nfor the two of us.</i>',-1),(129752,42,102728,102778,'01:11:20.360','01:11:22.445','<i>I didn\'t want it to end.</i>',-1),(129753,42,102795,102855,'01:11:23.154','01:11:25.657','I wish you wouldn\'t go, Jenny.',-1),(129754,42,102879,102922,'01:11:26.658','01:11:28.451','I have to, Forrest.',-1),(129755,42,102946,102976,'01:11:29.452','01:11:30.704','Jenny?',-1),(129756,42,103028,103092,'01:11:32.872','01:11:35.500','Things got a little out of hand.',-1),(129757,42,103093,103185,'01:11:35.542','01:11:39.379','It\'s just this war\nand that lying son of a bitch, Johnson!',-1),(129758,42,103225,103292,'01:11:41.047','01:11:43.842','I would never hurt you, you know that.',-1),(129759,42,103367,103415,'01:11:46.970','01:11:48.972','You know what I think?',-1),(129760,42,103451,103577,'01:11:50.473','01:11:55.729','I think you should go home\nto Greenbow, Alabama!',-1),(129761,42,103829,103951,'01:12:06.239','01:12:11.328','Forrest, we have very different lives,\nyou know.',-1),(129762,42,104178,104254,'01:12:20.754','01:12:23.923','I want you to have this.',-1),(129763,42,104366,104418,'01:12:28.595','01:12:30.764','Forrest, I can\'t keep this.',-1),(129764,42,104458,104560,'01:12:32.432','01:12:36.686','I got it just by doing\nwhat you told me to do.',-1),(129765,42,104609,104661,'01:12:38.730','01:12:40.899','Why are you so good to me?',-1),(129766,42,104697,104734,'01:12:42.400','01:12:43.943','You\'re my girl.',-1),(129767,42,104782,104833,'01:12:45.945','01:12:48.073','I\'ll always be your girl.',-1),(129768,42,105803,105919,'01:13:28.488','01:13:33.326','<i>And just like that, she was gone,\nout of my life again.</i>',-1),(129769,42,105955,106011,'01:13:34.828','01:13:37.163','<i>That\'s one small step for man,</i>',-1),(129770,42,106059,106128,'01:13:39.165','01:13:42.001','<i>one giant leap for mankind.</i>',-1),(129771,42,106264,106324,'01:13:47.674','01:13:50.176','<i>I thought I was going back to Vietnam,</i>',-1),(129772,42,106327,106404,'01:13:50.301','01:13:53.513','<i>but instead, they decided the best way\nfor me to fight the Communists</i>',-1),(129773,42,106406,106445,'01:13:53.596','01:13:55.223','<i>was to play Ping-Pong.</i>',-1),(129774,42,106447,106502,'01:13:55.306','01:13:57.600','<i>So, I was in the Special Services,</i>',-1),(129775,42,106504,106582,'01:13:57.684','01:14:00.937','<i>traveling around the country\ncheering up all them wounded veterans</i>',-1),(129776,42,106584,106642,'01:14:01.020','01:14:03.440','and showing them\nhow to play Ping-Pong.',-1),(129777,42,106644,106690,'01:14:03.523','01:14:05.442','I was so good that some years later',-1),(129778,42,106692,106779,'01:14:05.525','01:14:09.154','<i>the Army decided that I should be\non the All-American Ping-Pong team.</i>',-1),(129779,42,106794,106852,'01:14:09.779','01:14:12.198','<i>We were the first Americans\nto visit the land of China</i>',-1),(129780,42,106854,106912,'01:14:12.282','01:14:14.701','<i>in like a million years,\nor something like that.</i>',-1),(129781,42,106915,106997,'01:14:14.826','01:14:18.246','<i>Somebody said world peace\nwas in our hands,</i>',-1),(129782,42,106999,107067,'01:14:18.329','01:14:21.166','<i>but all I did was play Ping-Pong.</i>',-1),(129783,42,107068,107143,'01:14:21.207','01:14:24.294','When I got home,\nI was a national celebrity.',-1),(129784,42,107160,107215,'01:14:25.003','01:14:27.297','Famouser even than Captain Kangaroo.',-1),(129785,42,107217,107281,'01:14:27.380','01:14:30.049','<i>Here he is, Forrest Gump, right here.</i>',-1),(129786,42,107443,107485,'01:14:36.806','01:14:38.558','<i>Mr. Gump, have a seat.</i>',-1),(129787,42,107545,107597,'01:14:41.060','01:14:43.229','<i>Forrest Gump, John Lennon.</i>',-1),(129788,42,107613,107643,'01:14:43.897','01:14:45.148','<i>- Welcome home.\n- You had quite a trip.</i>',-1),(129789,42,107645,107725,'01:14:45.231','01:14:48.568','<i>Can you tell us, what was China like?</i>',-1),(129790,42,107803,107929,'01:14:51.821','01:14:57.076','<i>In the land of China,\npeople hardly got nothing at all.</i>',-1),(129791,42,107931,107969,'01:14:57.160','01:14:58.745','<i>No possessions?</i>',-1),(129792,42,108032,108110,'01:15:01.372','01:15:04.584','<i>And in China, they never go to church.</i>',-1),(129793,42,108141,108182,'01:15:05.877','01:15:07.587','<i>No religion, too?</i>',-1),(129794,42,108228,108307,'01:15:09.506','01:15:12.800','<i>- Hard to imagine.\n- Well, it\'s easy if you try, Dick.</i>',-1),(129795,42,108350,108407,'01:15:14.594','01:15:16.971','<i>Some years later,\nthat nice young man from England</i>',-1),(129796,42,108409,108473,'01:15:17.055','01:15:19.724','<i>was on his way home\nto see his little boy</i>',-1),(129797,42,108474,108546,'01:15:19.766','01:15:22.769','<i>and was signing some autographs,</i>',-1),(129798,42,108549,108644,'01:15:22.894','01:15:26.856','<i>and for no particular reason at all,\nsomebody shot him.</i>',-1),(129799,42,108717,108809,'01:15:29.901','01:15:33.738','They gave you\nthe Congressional Medal of Honor.',-1),(129800,42,108840,108890,'01:15:35.031','01:15:37.116','Now, that\'s Lieutenant Dan.',-1),(129801,42,108957,108996,'01:15:39.911','01:15:41.538','Lieutenant Dan!',-1),(129802,42,108998,109106,'01:15:41.621','01:15:46.084','They gave you\nthe Congressional Medal of Honor!',-1),(129803,42,109151,109187,'01:15:47.961','01:15:49.462','Yes, sir, they surely did.',-1),(129804,42,109189,109237,'01:15:49.546','01:15:51.548','They gave you,',-1),(129805,42,109239,109339,'01:15:51.631','01:15:55.802','an imbecile,\na moron who goes on television',-1),(129806,42,109341,109443,'01:15:55.885','01:16:00.139','and makes a fool out of himself\nin front of the whole damn country,',-1),(129807,42,109459,109519,'01:16:00.807','01:16:03.309','the Congressional Medal of Honor.',-1),(129808,42,109547,109575,'01:16:04.477','01:16:05.645','Yes, sir.',-1),(129809,42,109627,109695,'01:16:07.814','01:16:10.650','Well, then, that\'s just perfect!',-1),(129810,42,109741,109797,'01:16:12.569','01:16:14.904','Yeah, well,\nI just got one thing to say to that.',-1),(129811,42,109799,109853,'01:16:14.988','01:16:17.240','God damn bless America.',-1),(129812,42,109875,109906,'01:16:18.157','01:16:19.450','Hey!',-1),(129813,42,109949,109981,'01:16:21.244','01:16:22.579','Oh, God!',-1),(129814,42,110041,110100,'01:16:25.081','01:16:27.500','- Oh, God!\n- Lieutenant Dan!',-1),(129815,42,110127,110193,'01:16:28.626','01:16:31.379','<i>Lieutenant Dan said\nhe was living in a hotel.</i>',-1),(129816,42,110195,110242,'01:16:31.462','01:16:33.423','<i>And because he didn\'t have no legs,</i>',-1),(129817,42,110244,110320,'01:16:33.506','01:16:36.676','<i>he spent most of his time\nexercising his arms.</i>',-1),(129818,42,110389,110448,'01:16:39.554','01:16:42.015','Take a right. Take a right.',-1),(129819,42,110511,110572,'01:16:44.642','01:16:47.186','Hey! Come on, already!',-1),(129820,42,110574,110641,'01:16:47.270','01:16:50.064','What do you do here in New York,\nLieutenant Dan?',-1),(129821,42,110643,110704,'01:16:50.148','01:16:52.692','I\'m living off the government tit.',-1),(129822,42,110743,110776,'01:16:54.319','01:16:55.695','Sucking it dry!',-1),(129823,42,110778,110827,'01:16:55.778','01:16:57.822','Hey! Hey! Hey! Are you blind?',-1),(129824,42,110829,110870,'01:16:57.905','01:16:59.616','- I\'m walking here!\n- Get out of the way!',-1),(129825,42,110872,110934,'01:16:59.699','01:17:02.285','Get out! Come on, go! Go! Go!',-1),(129826,42,111104,111194,'01:17:09.334','01:17:13.087','<i>I stayed with Lieutenant Dan\nand celebrated the holidays.</i>',-1),(129827,42,111300,111382,'01:17:17.508','01:17:20.928','<i>You have a great year.\nHurry home and God bless you.</i>',-1),(129828,42,111454,111521,'01:17:23.931','01:17:26.726','Have you found Jesus yet, Gump?',-1),(129829,42,111559,111647,'01:17:28.311','01:17:31.981','I didn\'t know I was supposed to be\nlooking for him, sir.',-1),(129830,42,111805,111886,'01:17:38.571','01:17:41.949','That\'s all these cripples,\ndown at the VA,',-1),(129831,42,111888,111946,'01:17:42.033','01:17:44.452','that\'s all they ever talk about.',-1),(129832,42,111974,112045,'01:17:45.620','01:17:48.581','Jesus this and Jesus that.',-1),(129833,42,112080,112136,'01:17:50.041','01:17:52.335','Have I found Jesus?',-1),(129834,42,112151,112223,'01:17:52.960','01:17:55.963','They even had a priest come\nand talk to me.',-1),(129835,42,112244,112356,'01:17:56.839','01:18:01.511','He said God is listening,\nbut I have to help myself.',-1),(129836,42,112389,112444,'01:18:02.887','01:18:05.181','How if I accept Jesus into my heart,',-1),(129837,42,112468,112559,'01:18:06.182','01:18:09.977','I\'ll get to walk beside him\nin the kingdom of heaven.',-1),(129838,42,112561,112613,'01:18:10.061','01:18:12.230','Did you hear what I said?',-1),(129839,42,112638,112734,'01:18:13.272','01:18:17.276','Walk beside him\nin the kingdom of heaven.',-1),(129840,42,112736,112807,'01:18:17.360','01:18:20.321','Well, kiss my crippled ass.',-1),(129841,42,112809,112890,'01:18:20.405','01:18:23.783','God is listening? What a crock of shit.',-1),(129842,42,112978,113041,'01:18:27.453','01:18:30.081','I\'m going to heaven, Lieutenant Dan.',-1),(129843,42,113087,113113,'01:18:31.999','01:18:33.042','Oh?',-1),(129844,42,113229,113262,'01:18:37.880','01:18:39.257','Well,',-1),(129845,42,113333,113414,'01:18:42.218','01:18:45.596','before you go, why don\'t you get\nyour ass down to the corner',-1),(129846,42,113416,113476,'01:18:45.680','01:18:48.182','- and get us another bottle of Ripple.\n- Yes, sir.',-1),(129847,42,113478,113601,'01:18:48.266','01:18:53.396','<i>We are at approximately 45th Street\nin New York City at One Astor Plaza.</i>',-1),(129848,42,113603,113647,'01:18:53.479','01:18:55.314','<i>This is the site of the old Astor Hotel.</i>',-1),(129849,42,113649,113702,'01:18:55.398','01:18:57.608','What the hell is in Bayou La Batre?',-1),(129850,42,113704,113760,'01:18:57.692','01:19:00.027','- Shrimping boats.\n- Shrimping boats?',-1),(129851,42,113762,113820,'01:19:00.111','01:19:02.530','Who gives a shit\nabout shrimping boats?',-1),(129852,42,113822,113857,'01:19:02.613','01:19:04.073','I gotta buy me\none of them shrimping boats,',-1),(129853,42,113859,113896,'01:19:04.157','01:19:05.700','soon as I have some money.',-1),(129854,42,113898,113966,'01:19:05.783','01:19:08.619','I made me a promise to Bubba\nin Vietnam',-1),(129855,42,113968,114033,'01:19:08.703','01:19:11.414','that as soon as the war was over,\nwe\'d go in partners.',-1),(129856,42,114035,114118,'01:19:11.497','01:19:14.917','He\'d be the captain of the\nshrimping boat and I\'d be his first mate.',-1),(129857,42,114120,114203,'01:19:15.001','01:19:18.463','But now that he\'s dead,\nthat means I gotta be the captain.',-1),(129858,42,114205,114270,'01:19:18.546','01:19:21.257','- A shrimp boat captain.\n- Yes, sir.',-1),(129859,42,114272,114338,'01:19:21.340','01:19:24.093','A promise is a promise, Lieutenant Dan.',-1),(129860,42,114374,114433,'01:19:25.595','01:19:28.055','Now hear this!',-1),(129861,42,114451,114543,'01:19:28.806','01:19:32.643','Private Gump here\nis gonna be a shrimp boat captain.',-1),(129862,42,114561,114595,'01:19:33.394','01:19:34.812','Well, I tell you what, Gilligan,',-1),(129863,42,114597,114656,'01:19:34.896','01:19:37.356','the day that you are\na shrimp boat captain,',-1),(129864,42,114658,114743,'01:19:37.440','01:19:40.985','- I will come and be your first mate.\n- Okay.',-1),(129865,42,114745,114849,'01:19:41.068','01:19:45.406','If you\'re ever a shrimp boat captain,\nthat\'s the day I\'m an astronaut.',-1),(129866,42,114851,114923,'01:19:45.490','01:19:48.493','Danny, what are\nyou complaining about?',-1),(129867,42,114925,114987,'01:19:48.576','01:19:51.162','- What are you doing, hon?\n- Mr. Hot Wheels.',-1),(129868,42,114989,115076,'01:19:51.245','01:19:54.874','- Who\'s your friend?\n- My name is Forrest, Forrest Gump.',-1),(129869,42,115096,115198,'01:19:55.708','01:19:59.921','This is Cunning Carla\nand Long-Limbs Lenore.',-1),(129870,42,115224,115301,'01:20:01.005','01:20:04.217','So, where you been, baby cakes, huh?\nHaven\'t seen you around lately.',-1),(129871,42,115303,115338,'01:20:04.300','01:20:05.760','You know, you should have\nbeen here for Christmas,',-1),(129872,42,115340,115372,'01:20:05.843','01:20:07.178','\'cause Tommy bought a round\non the house',-1),(129873,42,115374,115410,'01:20:07.261','01:20:08.763','and gave everybody a turkey sandwich.',-1),(129874,42,115412,115485,'01:20:08.846','01:20:11.891','Well, well, I had company.',-1),(129875,42,115506,115594,'01:20:12.767','01:20:16.437','Hey, hey! We was just there.\nThat\'s at Times Square.',-1),(129876,42,115609,115708,'01:20:17.063','01:20:21.192','Don\'t you just love New Year\'s?\nYou get to start all over.',-1),(129877,42,115710,115789,'01:20:21.275','01:20:24.570','- Hey, Lenore...\n- Everybody gets a second chance.',-1),(129878,42,115791,115852,'01:20:24.654','01:20:27.198','<i>It\'s funny,\nbut in the middle of all that fun,</i>',-1),(129879,42,115854,115909,'01:20:27.281','01:20:29.575','<i>I began to think about Jenny,</i>',-1),(129880,42,115931,116038,'01:20:30.493','01:20:34.956','<i>wondering how she was spending\nher New Year\'s night out in California.</i>',-1),(129881,42,116581,116665,'01:20:57.562','01:21:01.065','<i>...eight, seven, six, five,</i>',-1),(129882,42,116668,116751,'01:21:01.190','01:21:04.652','four, three, two, one!',-1),(129883,42,116754,116818,'01:21:04.777','01:21:07.446','Happy New Year!',-1),(129884,42,117214,117279,'01:21:23.921','01:21:26.632','Happy New Year, Lieutenant Dan!',-1),(129885,42,118126,118214,'01:22:01.918','01:22:05.588','What are you, stupid or something?\nWhat\'s your problem?',-1),(129886,42,118230,118264,'01:22:06.255','01:22:07.673','What\'s his problem?',-1),(129887,42,118266,118320,'01:22:07.757','01:22:10.009','Did you lose your pecker in the war\nor something?',-1),(129888,42,118322,118372,'01:22:10.092','01:22:12.178','What, is your friend stupid\nor something?',-1),(129889,42,118373,118400,'01:22:12.219','01:22:13.346','What did you say?',-1),(129890,42,118401,118436,'01:22:13.387','01:22:14.847','I said, is your friend stupid\nor something?',-1),(129891,42,118437,118489,'01:22:14.889','01:22:17.058','Hey! Don\'t call him stupid!',-1),(129892,42,118491,118538,'01:22:17.141','01:22:19.101','- Hey, don\'t you push her!\n- You shut up!',-1),(129893,42,118540,118589,'01:22:19.185','01:22:21.228','- Don\'t you ever call him stupid!\n- What\'s the matter, baby?',-1),(129894,42,118591,118632,'01:22:21.312','01:22:23.022','- Why are you so upset?\n- Just get the hell out of here.',-1),(129895,42,118634,118660,'01:22:23.105','01:22:24.190','- Stupid damn...\n- Get your goddamn clothes...',-1),(129896,42,118662,118698,'01:22:24.273','01:22:25.775','You belong in <i>Ripley\'s Believe It Or Not!</i>',-1),(129897,42,118700,118745,'01:22:25.858','01:22:27.735','- Get the hell out of here!\n- You should be in a sideshow!',-1),(129898,42,118747,118772,'01:22:27.818','01:22:28.861','Go on! Get out of here!',-1),(129899,42,118774,118805,'01:22:28.945','01:22:30.237','Come on, Lenore.\nWe don\'t need this shit!',-1),(129900,42,118807,118840,'01:22:30.321','01:22:31.697','Get out of here!',-1),(129901,42,118879,118940,'01:22:33.324','01:22:35.868','- You retard.\n- Loser. You freak.',-1),(129902,42,119069,119098,'01:22:41.248','01:22:42.458','No, no.',-1),(129903,42,119702,119797,'01:23:07.608','01:23:11.570','I\'m sorry I ruined your\nNew Year\'s Eve party, Lieutenant Dan.',-1),(129904,42,119811,119866,'01:23:12.154','01:23:14.448','She tasted like cigarettes.',-1),(129905,42,120255,120363,'01:23:30.631','01:23:35.136','<i>I guess Lieutenant Dan figured there\'s\nsome things you just can\'t change.</i>',-1),(129906,42,120365,120488,'01:23:35.219','01:23:40.349','<i>He didn\'t want to be called crippled,\njust like I didn\'t want to be called stupid.</i>',-1),(129907,42,120620,120665,'01:23:45.855','01:23:47.732','Happy New Year, Gump.',-1),(129908,42,120780,120814,'01:23:52.528','01:23:53.946','<i>The US Ping-Pong team</i>',-1),(129909,42,120815,120870,'01:23:53.988','01:23:56.282','<i>met with President Nixon today\nat an Oval Office ceremony...</i>',-1),(129910,42,120872,120938,'01:23:56.365','01:23:59.118','And wouldn\'t you know it?\nA few months later,',-1),(129911,42,120940,121035,'01:23:59.201','01:24:03.164','they invited me and the Ping-Pong team\nto visit the White House.',-1),(129912,42,121037,121091,'01:24:03.247','01:24:05.499','So, I went, again.',-1),(129913,42,121111,121195,'01:24:06.333','01:24:09.795','And I met the President\nof the United States, again.',-1),(129914,42,121213,121284,'01:24:10.546','01:24:13.507','<i>Only, this time, they didn\'t get us rooms\nin a real fancy hotel.</i>',-1),(129915,42,121286,121367,'01:24:13.591','01:24:16.969','<i>So, are you enjoying yourself\nin our nation\'s capital, young man?</i>',-1),(129916,42,121369,121441,'01:24:17.053','01:24:20.056','<i>- Yes, sir.\n- Well, where are you staying?</i>',-1),(129917,42,121443,121506,'01:24:20.139','01:24:22.767','<i>- It\'s called the Hotel Ebbott.\n- Oh, no, no, no, no.</i>',-1),(129918,42,121508,121583,'01:24:22.850','01:24:25.978','<i>I know of a much nicer hotel.\nIt\'s brand-new, very modern.</i>',-1),(129919,42,121585,121633,'01:24:26.062','01:24:28.064','<i>I\'ll have my people\ntake care of it for you.</i>',-1),(129920,42,121648,121675,'01:24:28.689','01:24:29.815','<i>Security, Frank Wills.</i>',-1),(129921,42,121677,121763,'01:24:29.899','01:24:33.486','Yeah, sir, you might want\nto send a maintenance man',-1),(129922,42,121765,121830,'01:24:33.569','01:24:36.280','over to that office across the way.',-1),(129923,42,121831,121900,'01:24:36.322','01:24:39.200','The lights are off, and they must be\nlooking for a fuse box or something,',-1),(129924,42,121902,121967,'01:24:39.283','01:24:41.994','\'cause them flashlights,\nthey\'re keeping me awake.',-1),(129925,42,121969,122008,'01:24:42.078','01:24:43.704','<i>Okay, sir. I\'ll check it out.</i>',-1),(129926,42,122010,122051,'01:24:43.788','01:24:45.498','- Thank you.\n<i>- No problem.</i>',-1),(129927,42,122053,122100,'01:24:45.581','01:24:47.500','- Good night.\n<i>- Good night.</i>',-1),(129928,42,122187,122316,'01:24:51.128','01:24:56.509','<i>Therefore, I shall resign the presidency\neffective at noon tomorrow.</i>',-1),(129929,42,122318,122367,'01:24:56.592','01:24:58.636','<i>Vice President Ford</i>',-1),(129930,42,122369,122477,'01:24:58.719','01:25:03.224','<i>will be sworn in as president\nat that hour in this office.</i>',-1),(129931,42,122510,122625,'01:25:04.600','01:25:09.396','<i>As I recall the high hopes for America\nwith which we began this second term...</i>',-1),(129932,42,122751,122788,'01:25:14.652','01:25:16.195','Sergeant Gump.',-1),(129933,42,122800,122853,'01:25:16.695','01:25:18.906','- Yes, sir!\n- As you were.',-1),(129934,42,122855,122930,'01:25:18.989','01:25:22.118','I have your discharge papers.\nYour service is up, son.',-1),(129935,42,123012,123078,'01:25:25.538','01:25:28.290','Does this mean\nI can\'t play Ping-Pong no more?',-1),(129936,42,123080,123128,'01:25:28.374','01:25:30.334','For the Army it does.',-1),(129937,42,123191,123308,'01:25:32.962','01:25:37.842','<i>And just like that, my service\nin the United States Army was over.</i>',-1),(129938,42,123435,123478,'01:25:43.139','01:25:44.932','<i>So, I went home.</i>',-1),(129939,42,123993,124075,'01:26:06.412','01:26:09.832','- I\'m home, Mama.\n- I know, I know.',-1),(129940,42,124114,124152,'01:26:11.458','01:26:13.002','- Louise, he\'s here.\n<i>- Now, when I got home,</i>',-1),(129941,42,124154,124251,'01:26:13.085','01:26:17.131','<i>I had no idea,\nbut Mama had had all sorts of visitors.</i>',-1),(129942,42,124254,124310,'01:26:17.256','01:26:19.592','We\'ve had all sorts of visitors, Forrest.',-1),(129943,42,124311,124386,'01:26:19.633','01:26:22.761','Everybody wants you\nto use their Ping-Pong stuff.',-1),(129944,42,124387,124478,'01:26:22.803','01:26:26.599','One man even left a check for $25,000',-1),(129945,42,124480,124563,'01:26:26.682','01:26:30.144','if you\'d be agreeable to saying\nyou liked using their paddle.',-1),(129946,42,124566,124630,'01:26:30.269','01:26:32.938','Oh, but, Mama,\nI only like using my own paddle.',-1),(129947,42,124632,124680,'01:26:33.022','01:26:35.024','- Hi, Miss Louise.\n- Hey, Forrest.',-1),(129948,42,124682,124752,'01:26:35.107','01:26:38.027','I know that. I know that.',-1),(129949,42,124754,124818,'01:26:38.110','01:26:40.779','But it\'s $25,000, Forrest.',-1),(129950,42,124820,124933,'01:26:40.863','01:26:45.576','I thought maybe you could hold it\nfor a while, see if it grows on you.',-1),(129951,42,124934,124986,'01:26:45.618','01:26:47.786','- Oh, you look good, Forrest.\n<i>- That Mama, she sure was right.</i>',-1),(129952,42,124987,125047,'01:26:47.828','01:26:50.331','- You look real good.\n<i>- It\'s funny how things work out.</i>',-1),(129953,42,125050,125127,'01:26:50.456','01:26:53.626','<i>I didn\'t stay home for long,\nbecause I\'d made a promise to Bubba,</i>',-1),(129954,42,125128,125183,'01:26:53.667','01:26:55.961','<i>and I always try to keep my promise.</i>',-1),(129955,42,125184,125221,'01:26:56.003','01:26:57.546','<i>So, I went on down to Bayou La Batre</i>',-1),(129956,42,125223,125313,'01:26:57.630','01:27:01.383','<i>to meet Bubba\'s family\nand make their introduction.</i>',-1),(129957,42,125315,125403,'01:27:01.467','01:27:05.137','Are you crazy, or just plain stupid?',-1),(129958,42,125420,125475,'01:27:05.846','01:27:08.140','Stupid is as stupid does, Mrs. Blue.',-1),(129959,42,125476,125509,'01:27:08.182','01:27:09.558','I guess.',-1),(129960,42,125533,125619,'01:27:10.559','01:27:14.146','<i>And, of course,\nI paid my respect to Bubba himself.</i>',-1),(129961,42,125667,125728,'01:27:16.148','01:27:18.692','Hey, Bubba, it\'s me, Forrest Gump.',-1),(129962,42,125803,125900,'01:27:21.820','01:27:25.866','I remember everything you said,\nand I got it all figured out.',-1),(129963,42,125967,126131,'01:27:28.661','01:27:35.459','I\'m taking the $24,562\nand 47 cents that I got...',-1),(129964,42,126157,126244,'01:27:36.543','01:27:40.172','<i>Or, that\'s left after a new hair cut\nand a new suit,</i>',-1),(129965,42,126245,126292,'01:27:40.214','01:27:42.174','<i>and I took Mama out\nto a real fancy dinner,</i>',-1),(129966,42,126294,126372,'01:27:42.258','01:27:45.511','<i>and I bought a bus ticket\nand three Dr. Peppers.</i>',-1),(129967,42,126385,126428,'01:27:46.053','01:27:47.846','Tell me something.',-1),(129968,42,126453,126504,'01:27:48.889','01:27:51.016','Are you stupid or something?',-1),(129969,42,126506,126556,'01:27:51.100','01:27:53.185','Stupid is as stupid does, sir.',-1),(129970,42,126557,126628,'01:27:53.227','01:27:56.188','Well, that\'s what\'s left after me saying,',-1),(129971,42,126650,126701,'01:27:57.106','01:27:59.233','\"When I was in China\non the All-America Ping-Pong team,',-1),(129972,42,126704,126796,'01:27:59.358','01:28:03.195','\"I just loved playing Ping-Pong with\nmy Flex-O-Light Ping-Pong paddle,\"',-1),(129973,42,126797,126828,'01:28:03.237','01:28:04.530','which everybody knows isn\'t true,',-1),(129974,42,126829,126862,'01:28:04.571','01:28:05.948','but Mama says it\'s just a little white lie',-1),(129975,42,126864,126916,'01:28:06.031','01:28:08.200','so it wouldn\'t hurt nobody.',-1),(129976,42,126950,127092,'01:28:09.618','01:28:15.541','So, anyway, I\'m putting all that on gas,\nropes and new nets',-1),(129977,42,127111,127153,'01:28:16.292','01:28:18.043','and a brand-new shrimping boat.',-1),(129978,42,127673,127751,'01:28:39.732','01:28:42.985','<i>Now, Bubba had told me everything\nhe knew about shrimping,</i>',-1),(129979,42,127753,127809,'01:28:43.068','01:28:45.404','<i>but you know what I found out?</i>',-1),(129980,42,127849,127905,'01:28:47.072','01:28:49.408','<i>Shrimping is tough.</i>',-1),(129981,42,127958,128002,'01:28:51.618','01:28:53.454','I only caught five.',-1),(129982,42,128005,128085,'01:28:53.579','01:28:56.915','A couple more,\nyou could have yourself a cocktail.',-1),(129983,42,128166,128208,'01:29:00.252','01:29:02.004','Hey, you ever think\nabout naming this old boat?',-1),(129984,42,128210,128274,'01:29:02.087','01:29:04.757','It\'s bad luck\nto have a boat without a name.',-1),(129985,42,128331,128447,'01:29:07.134','01:29:11.972','<i>I\'d never named a boat before,\nbut there was only one I could think of,</i>',-1),(129986,42,128475,128552,'01:29:13.140','01:29:16.352','<i>the most beautiful name\nin the wide world.</i>',-1),(129987,42,129056,129125,'01:29:37.373','01:29:40.209','<i>Now, I hadn\'t heard from Jenny\nin a long while,</i>',-1),(129988,42,129127,129188,'01:29:40.292','01:29:42.836','<i>but I thought about her a lot,</i>',-1),(129989,42,129191,129274,'01:29:42.961','01:29:46.423','<i>and I hoped that whatever\nshe was doing made her happy.</i>',-1),(129990,42,131824,131885,'01:31:32.696','01:31:35.240','<i>I thought about Jenny all the time.</i>',-1),(129991,42,132477,132505,'01:31:59.890','01:32:01.058','Hey!',-1),(129992,42,133077,133190,'01:32:24.915','01:32:29.586','Lieutenant Dan,\nwhat are you doing here?',-1),(129993,42,133192,133287,'01:32:29.670','01:32:33.632','Well, thought I\'d try out my sea legs.',-1),(129994,42,133288,133379,'01:32:33.674','01:32:37.469','But you ain\'t got no legs,\nLieutenant Dan.',-1),(129995,42,133380,133435,'01:32:37.511','01:32:39.805','Yes, I know that.',-1),(129996,42,133443,133492,'01:32:40.138','01:32:42.182','You wrote me a letter, you idiot.',-1),(129997,42,133495,133604,'01:32:42.307','01:32:46.853','Well, well. Captain Forrest Gump.\nI had to see this for myself.',-1),(129998,42,133643,133808,'01:32:48.480','01:32:55.362','And I told you if you were ever\na shrimp boat captain',-1),(129999,42,133811,133874,'01:32:55.487','01:32:58.115','that I\'d be your first mate.\nWell, here I am.',-1),(130000,42,133875,133951,'01:32:58.156','01:33:01.326','- I am a man of my word.\n- Okay.',-1),(130001,42,133952,134048,'01:33:01.368','01:33:05.372','Yeah, but don\'t you be thinking that\nI\'m going to be calling you \"sir.\"',-1),(130002,42,134051,134083,'01:33:05.497','01:33:06.832','No, sir.',-1),(130003,42,134297,134352,'01:33:15.716','01:33:18.010','That\'s my boat.',-1),(130004,42,134414,134545,'01:33:20.596','01:33:26.059','I have a feeling if we head due east,\nwe\'ll find some shrimp,',-1),(130005,42,134548,134586,'01:33:26.184','01:33:27.769','so take a left.',-1),(130006,42,134620,134690,'01:33:29.187','01:33:32.107','- Take a left!\n- Which way?',-1),(130007,42,134692,134756,'01:33:32.190','01:33:34.860','Over there! They\'re over there!',-1),(130008,42,134772,134864,'01:33:35.527','01:33:39.364','- Get on the wheel and take a left!\n- Okay.',-1),(130009,42,134893,134992,'01:33:40.574','01:33:44.703','Gump, what are you doing?\nTake a left! Left!',-1),(130010,42,135049,135137,'01:33:47.080','01:33:50.709','That\'s where we\'re going\nto find those shrimp, my boy!',-1),(130011,42,135175,135213,'01:33:52.294','01:33:53.879','That\'s where we\'ll find them.',-1),(130012,42,135517,135616,'01:34:06.558','01:34:10.687','- Still no shrimp, Lieutenant Dan.\n- Okay, so I was wrong.',-1),(130013,42,135633,135710,'01:34:11.396','01:34:14.608','How are we going to find them?',-1),(130014,42,135713,135773,'01:34:14.733','01:34:17.235','Well, maybe you should\njust pray for shrimp.',-1),(130015,42,135932,135996,'01:34:23.867','01:34:26.536','<i>So, I went to church every Sunday.</i>',-1),(130016,42,136026,136074,'01:34:27.788','01:34:29.790','<i>Sometimes Lieutenant Dan came, too,</i>',-1),(130017,42,136077,136150,'01:34:29.915','01:34:32.918','<i>though I think\nhe left the praying up to me.</i>',-1),(130018,42,136521,136626,'01:34:48.392','01:34:52.771','- No shrimp.\n- Where the hell\'s this God of yours?',-1),(130019,42,136646,136783,'01:34:53.605','01:34:59.319','<i>It\'s funny Lieutenant Dan said that,\n\'cause right then, God showed up.</i>',-1),(130020,42,137188,137304,'01:35:16.169','01:35:21.007','- You\'ll never sink this boat!\n<i>- Now, me, I was scared,</i>',-1),(130021,42,137307,137380,'01:35:21.133','01:35:24.177','<i>but Lieutenant Dan, he was mad.</i>',-1),(130022,42,137383,137415,'01:35:24.302','01:35:25.637','Come on!',-1),(130023,42,137490,137615,'01:35:28.765','01:35:33.979','You call this a storm?\nCome on, you son of a bitch!',-1),(130024,42,137666,137771,'01:35:36.106','01:35:40.485','It\'s time for a showdown! You and me!',-1),(130025,42,137774,137867,'01:35:40.610','01:35:44.489','I\'m right here! Come and get me!',-1),(130026,42,137910,138003,'01:35:46.283','01:35:50.162','You\'ll never sink this boat!',-1),(130027,42,138052,138104,'01:35:52.205','01:35:54.374','<i>Hurricane Carmen\ncame through here yesterday,</i>',-1),(130028,42,138107,138169,'01:35:54.499','01:35:57.043','<i>destroying nearly everything in its path.</i>',-1),(130029,42,138172,138232,'01:35:57.169','01:35:59.671','<i>And as in other towns\nup and down the coast,</i>',-1),(130030,42,138236,138293,'01:35:59.838','01:36:02.215','<i>Bayou La Batre\'s\nentire shrimping industry</i>',-1),(130031,42,138295,138388,'01:36:02.299','01:36:06.178','<i>has fallen victim to Carmen\nand has been left in utter ruin.</i>',-1),(130032,42,138391,138467,'01:36:06.303','01:36:09.473','<i>Speaking with local officials,\nthis reporter has learned,</i>',-1),(130033,42,138468,138551,'01:36:09.514','01:36:12.976','<i>in fact, only one shrimping boat\nactually survived the storm.</i>',-1),(130034,42,138560,138623,'01:36:13.351','01:36:15.979','Louise. Louise, there\'s Forrest.',-1),(130035,42,138640,138688,'01:36:16.688','01:36:18.690','<i>After that, shrimping was easy.</i>',-1),(130036,42,138824,138900,'01:36:24.362','01:36:27.532','<i>Since people still needed\nthem shrimps for shrimp cocktails</i>',-1),(130037,42,138901,139000,'01:36:27.574','01:36:31.703','and barbecues and all,\nand we were the only boat left standing,',-1),(130038,42,139004,139083,'01:36:31.870','01:36:35.165','Bubba-Gump Shrimp\'s what they got.',-1),(130039,42,139084,139196,'01:36:35.207','01:36:39.836','We got a whole bunch of boats,\n12 <i>Jennys,</i>',-1),(130040,42,139197,139281,'01:36:39.878','01:36:43.381','a big old warehouse. We even have\nhats that say \"Bubba-Gump\" on them.',-1),(130041,42,139289,139368,'01:36:43.715','01:36:47.010','Bubba-Gump Shrimp.\nIt\'s a household name.',-1),(130042,42,139373,139414,'01:36:47.219','01:36:48.929','Hold on there, boy.',-1),(130043,42,139417,139526,'01:36:49.054','01:36:53.600','Are you telling me you\'re the owner of\nthe Bubba-Gump Shrimp Corporation?',-1),(130044,42,139529,139601,'01:36:53.725','01:36:56.728','Yes, sir. We got more money\nthan Davy Crockett.',-1),(130045,42,139640,139737,'01:36:58.355','01:37:02.400','Boy, I heard some whoppers in my time,\nbut that tops them all.',-1),(130046,42,139802,139869,'01:37:05.111','01:37:07.906','We was sitting next to a millionaire.',-1),(130047,42,139953,140064,'01:37:11.409','01:37:16.039','Well, I thought it was a very lovely story,',-1),(130048,42,140074,140186,'01:37:16.456','01:37:21.086','and you tell it so well,\nwith such enthusiasm.',-1),(130049,42,140227,140291,'01:37:22.796','01:37:25.465','Would you like to see\nwhat Lieutenant Dan looks like?',-1),(130050,42,140294,140330,'01:37:25.590','01:37:27.092','Well, yes, I would.',-1),(130051,42,140455,140504,'01:37:32.305','01:37:34.349','That\'s him right there.',-1),(130052,42,140555,140609,'01:37:36.476','01:37:38.728','And let me tell you something\nabout Lieutenant Dan...',-1),(130053,42,140637,140662,'01:37:39.896','01:37:40.939','Forrest,',-1),(130054,42,140795,140862,'01:37:46.486','01:37:49.281','I never thanked you for saving my life.',-1),(130055,42,141487,141638,'01:38:15.307','01:38:21.605','<i>He never actually said so,\nbut I think he made his peace with God.</i>',-1),(130056,42,141822,141875,'01:38:29.279','01:38:31.489','<i>For the second time in 17 days,</i>',-1),(130057,42,141878,141961,'01:38:31.615','01:38:35.076','<i>President Ford escaped\npossible assassination today.</i>',-1),(130058,42,141963,141995,'01:38:35.160','01:38:36.494','<i>Base to</i> Jenny 1.',-1),(130059,42,141996,142080,'01:38:36.536','01:38:40.040','<i>- Base to</i> Jenny 1.\n<i>- Jenny 1</i>. Go, Margo.',-1),(130060,42,142082,142119,'01:38:40.123','01:38:41.666','<i>Forrest has a phone call.</i>',-1),(130061,42,142120,142181,'01:38:41.708','01:38:44.210','Yeah, well, you\'ll have to tell them\nto call him back.',-1),(130062,42,142183,142264,'01:38:44.294','01:38:47.672','- He is indisposed at the moment.\n<i>- His mama\'s sick.</i>',-1),(130063,42,142760,142817,'01:39:08.360','01:39:10.737','- Where\'s Mama?\n- She\'s upstairs.',-1),(130064,42,142885,142932,'01:39:13.573','01:39:15.533','Hi, Forrest.',-1),(130065,42,142955,143016,'01:39:16.493','01:39:19.037','- I\'ll see you tomorrow.\n- All right.',-1),(130066,42,143177,143253,'01:39:25.710','01:39:28.880','We sure got you straightened out,\ndidn\'t we, boy?',-1),(130067,42,143525,143620,'01:39:40.225','01:39:44.187','- What\'s the matter, Mama?\n- I\'m dying, Forrest.',-1),(130068,42,143700,143757,'01:39:47.524','01:39:49.901','Come on in, sit down over here.',-1),(130069,42,144101,144186,'01:40:04.249','01:40:07.752','- Why are you dying, Mama?\n- It\'s my time.',-1),(130070,42,144210,144255,'01:40:08.753','01:40:10.630','It\'s just my time.',-1),(130071,42,144290,144390,'01:40:12.090','01:40:16.261','Now, don\'t you be afraid, sweetheart.',-1),(130072,42,144429,144486,'01:40:17.887','01:40:20.265','Death is just a part of life,',-1),(130073,42,144510,144573,'01:40:21.266','01:40:23.893','something we\'re all destined to do.',-1),(130074,42,144617,144722,'01:40:25.729','01:40:30.108','I didn\'t know it,\nbut I was destined to be your mama.',-1),(130075,42,144742,144828,'01:40:30.942','01:40:34.529','- I did the best I could.\n- You did good, Mama.',-1),(130076,42,144847,144971,'01:40:35.321','01:40:40.493','Well, I happen to believe\nyou make your own destiny.',-1),(130077,42,145007,145085,'01:40:41.995','01:40:45.248','You have to do the best\nwith what God gave you.',-1),(130078,42,145179,145230,'01:40:49.127','01:40:51.254','What\'s my destiny, Mama?',-1),(130079,42,145282,145359,'01:40:53.423','01:40:56.634','You\'re going to have\nto figure that out for yourself.',-1),(130080,42,145390,145462,'01:40:57.927','01:41:00.930','Life is a box of chocolates, Forrest.',-1),(130081,42,145463,145515,'01:41:00.972','01:41:03.141','You never know\nwhat you\'re going to get.',-1),(130082,42,145518,145623,'01:41:03.266','01:41:07.645','<i>Mama always had a way of explaining\nthings so I could understand them.</i>',-1),(130083,42,145625,145678,'01:41:07.729','01:41:09.939','I will miss you, Forrest.',-1),(130084,42,145722,145819,'01:41:11.775','01:41:15.820','<i>She had got the cancer\nand died on a Tuesday.</i>',-1),(130085,42,145855,145935,'01:41:17.322','01:41:20.658','<i>I bought her a new hat\nwith little flowers on it.</i>',-1),(130086,42,146008,146087,'01:41:23.703','01:41:26.998','And that\'s all I have to say about that.',-1),(130087,42,146252,146308,'01:41:33.838','01:41:36.174','Didn\'t you say you were waiting\nfor the number seven bus?',-1),(130088,42,146309,146376,'01:41:36.216','01:41:39.010','There\'ll be another one along shortly.',-1),(130089,42,146468,146555,'01:41:42.847','01:41:46.476','Now, because I had been a football star,\nand a war hero,',-1),(130090,42,146556,146631,'01:41:46.518','01:41:49.646','and a national celebrity,\nand a shrimping boat captain,',-1),(130091,42,146643,146720,'01:41:50.146','01:41:53.358','and a college graduate,\nthe city fathers of Greenbow, Alabama',-1),(130092,42,146723,146800,'01:41:53.483','01:41:56.694','decided to get together\nand offered me a fine job.',-1),(130093,42,146833,146921,'01:41:58.071','01:42:01.741','<i>So, I never went back to work\nfor Lieutenant Dan,</i>',-1),(130094,42,146924,146989,'01:42:01.866','01:42:04.577','<i>though he did take care\nof my Bubba-Gump money.</i>',-1),(130095,42,146992,147103,'01:42:04.702','01:42:09.332','<i>He got me invested\nin some kind of fruit company.</i>',-1),(130096,42,147104,147143,'01:42:09.374','01:42:10.959','<i>And so then, I got a call from him saying</i>',-1),(130097,42,147145,147229,'01:42:11.042','01:42:14.546','we don\'t have to worry about money\nno more, and I said,',-1),(130098,42,147230,147285,'01:42:14.587','01:42:16.881','\"That\'s good. One less thing.\"',-1),(130099,42,147358,147439,'01:42:19.926','01:42:23.304','<i>Now, Mama said there\'s only\nso much fortune a man really needs,</i>',-1),(130100,42,147469,147538,'01:42:24.556','01:42:27.433','<i>and the rest is just for showing off.</i>',-1),(130101,42,147540,147633,'01:42:27.517','01:42:31.396','<i>So, I gave a whole bunch of it\nto the Foursquare gospel church,</i>',-1),(130102,42,147697,147805,'01:42:34.065','01:42:38.570','<i>and I gave a whole bunch to the\nBayou La Batre fishing hospital.</i>',-1),(130103,42,147861,147970,'01:42:40.905','01:42:45.451','<i>And even though Bubba was dead\nand Lieutenant Dan said I was nuts,</i>',-1),(130104,42,147973,148036,'01:42:45.577','01:42:48.204','<i>I gave Bubba\'s mama Bubba\'s share.</i>',-1),(130105,42,148138,148179,'01:42:52.417','01:42:54.127','You know what?',-1),(130106,42,148209,148282,'01:42:55.378','01:42:58.423','<i>She didn\'t have to work\nin nobody\'s kitchen no more.</i>',-1),(130107,42,148283,148322,'01:42:58.464','01:43:00.091','That smells wonderful.',-1),(130108,42,148342,148437,'01:43:00.925','01:43:04.888','<i>And \'cause I was a gazillionaire\nand I liked doing it so much,</i>',-1),(130109,42,148438,148494,'01:43:04.929','01:43:07.265','<i>I cut that grass for free.</i>',-1),(130110,42,148585,148654,'01:43:11.060','01:43:13.938','<i>But at night time\nwhen there was nothing to do</i>',-1),(130111,42,148656,148713,'01:43:14.022','01:43:16.399','<i>and the house was all empty,</i>',-1),(130112,42,148737,148794,'01:43:17.400','01:43:19.777','<i>I\'d always think of Jenny.</i>',-1),(130113,42,150323,150399,'01:44:23.466','01:44:26.636','<i>And then, she was there.</i>',-1),(130114,42,151191,151267,'01:44:59.627','01:45:02.797','- Hello, Forrest.\n- Hello, Jenny.',-1),(130115,42,151544,151607,'01:45:14.350','01:45:16.978','<i>Jenny came back and stayed with me.</i>',-1),(130116,42,151645,151733,'01:45:18.563','01:45:22.233','<i>Maybe it was because\nshe had nowhere else to go,</i>',-1),(130117,42,151736,151825,'01:45:22.358','01:45:26.070','<i>or maybe it was because she was\nso tired, \'cause she went to bed</i>',-1),(130118,42,151828,151923,'01:45:26.195','01:45:30.158','<i>and slept and slept,\nlike she hadn\'t slept in years.</i>',-1),(130119,42,151953,152008,'01:45:31.409','01:45:33.703','<i>It was wonderful having her home.</i>',-1),(130120,42,152040,152165,'01:45:35.038','01:45:40.209','<i>Every day we\'d take a walk and\nI\'d jabber on like a monkey in a tree,</i>',-1),(130121,42,152166,152227,'01:45:40.251','01:45:42.795','<i>and she\'d listen about Ping-Ponging,\nand shrimping,</i>',-1),(130122,42,152229,152333,'01:45:42.879','01:45:47.216','<i>and Mama making a trip up to heaven.\nI did all the talking.</i>',-1),(130123,42,152334,152414,'01:45:47.258','01:45:50.595','<i>Jenny most of the time was real quiet.</i>',-1),(130124,42,153378,153455,'01:46:30.760','01:46:33.971','How could you do this?',-1),(130125,42,154342,154422,'01:47:10.925','01:47:14.262','<i>Sometimes I guess there\njust aren\'t enough rocks.</i>',-1),(130126,42,154475,154583,'01:47:16.472','01:47:20.977','<i>I never really knew why she came back,\nbut I didn\'t care.</i>',-1),(130127,42,154587,154690,'01:47:21.144','01:47:25.440','<i>It was like olden times.\nWe was like peas and carrots again.</i>',-1),(130128,42,154740,154844,'01:47:27.525','01:47:31.863','<i>Every day, I\'d pick pretty flowers\nand put them in her room for her,</i>',-1),(130129,42,154880,154967,'01:47:33.364','01:47:36.993','<i>and she gave me the best gift anyone\ncould ever get in the wide world.</i>',-1),(130130,42,154968,155036,'01:47:37.034','01:47:39.871','- New shoes.\n- They make them just for running.',-1),(130131,42,155157,155236,'01:47:44.876','01:47:48.171','<i>And she even showed me\nhow to dance.</i>',-1),(130132,42,155432,155533,'01:47:56.345','01:48:00.558','<i>And, well, we was like family,\nJenny and me.</i>',-1),(130133,42,155623,155693,'01:48:04.312','01:48:07.231','<i>And it was the happiest time in my life.</i>',-1),(130134,42,156165,156208,'01:48:26.876','01:48:28.669','<i>...and this Fourth is witnessing\none of the</i>',-1),(130135,42,156210,156282,'01:48:28.753','01:48:31.756','<i>largest fireworks displays\nin the nation\'s...</i>',-1),(130136,42,156284,156354,'01:48:31.839','01:48:34.759','- You done watching it?\n<i>- ...here in New York Harbor...</i>',-1),(130137,42,156357,156400,'01:48:34.884','01:48:36.677','- I\'m going to bed.\n<i>- ...with a spectacular display</i>',-1),(130138,42,156402,156475,'01:48:36.761','01:48:39.805','<i>of tall ships earlier.\nThe Statue of Liberty...</i>',-1),(130139,42,156644,156692,'01:48:46.854','01:48:48.856','Will you marry me?',-1),(130140,42,156810,156881,'01:48:53.778','01:48:56.739','I\'d make a good husband, Jenny.',-1),(130141,42,156945,156994,'01:48:59.408','01:49:01.452','You would, Forrest.',-1),(130142,42,157038,157094,'01:49:03.287','01:49:05.623','But you won\'t marry me.',-1),(130143,42,157150,157203,'01:49:07.917','01:49:10.127','You don\'t want to marry me.',-1),(130144,42,157289,157347,'01:49:13.714','01:49:16.133','Why don\'t you love me, Jenny?',-1),(130145,42,157467,157518,'01:49:21.138','01:49:23.266','I\'m not a smart man,',-1),(130146,42,157559,157617,'01:49:24.976','01:49:27.395','but I know what love is.',-1),(130147,42,158506,158536,'01:50:04.432','01:50:05.683','Jenny.',-1),(130148,42,158582,158642,'01:50:07.602','01:50:10.104','Forrest, I do love you.',-1),(130149,42,159917,160005,'01:51:03.240','01:51:06.911','- Where are you running off to?\n- I\'m not running.',-1),(130150,42,162204,162332,'01:52:38.502','01:52:43.841','<i>That day, for no particular reason,\nI decided to go for a little run.</i>',-1),(130151,42,162360,162466,'01:52:45.009','01:52:49.430','<i>So, I ran to the end of the road,\nand when I got there,</i>',-1),(130152,42,162468,162510,'01:52:49.513','01:52:51.265','<i>I thought maybe I\'d run\nto the end of town.</i>',-1),(130153,42,162512,162590,'01:52:51.348','01:52:54.602','<i>President Carter, suffering from heat\nexhaustion, fell into the arms of...</i>',-1),(130154,42,162592,162632,'01:52:54.685','01:52:56.353','<i>And when I got there,</i>',-1),(130155,42,162634,162734,'01:52:56.437','01:53:00.608','<i>I thought maybe I\'d just\nrun across Greenbow County.</i>',-1),(130156,42,162736,162794,'01:53:00.691','01:53:03.110','<i>And I figured since I\'d run this far,</i>',-1),(130157,42,162796,162875,'01:53:03.194','01:53:06.489','<i>maybe I\'d just run across\nthe great state of Alabama.</i>',-1),(130158,42,162876,162905,'01:53:06.530','01:53:07.740','<i>And that\'s what I did.</i>',-1),(130159,42,162920,162963,'01:53:08.365','01:53:10.159','I ran clear across Alabama.',-1),(130160,42,162988,163064,'01:53:11.202','01:53:14.371','For no particular reason,\nI just kept on going.',-1),(130161,42,163096,163134,'01:53:15.706','01:53:17.291','I ran clear to the ocean.',-1),(130162,42,163276,163352,'01:53:23.172','01:53:26.342','<i>And when I got there,\nI figured since I\'d gone this far,</i>',-1),(130163,42,163365,163433,'01:53:26.884','01:53:29.720','<i>might as well turn around\nand just keep on going.</i>',-1),(130164,42,163523,163633,'01:53:33.474','01:53:38.062','<i>And when I got to another ocean,\nI figured since I\'d gone this far,</i>',-1),(130165,42,163676,163765,'01:53:39.855','01:53:43.567','<i>I might as well just turn back\nand keep right on going.</i>',-1),(130166,42,163793,163909,'01:53:44.735','01:53:49.573','<i>When I got tired, I slept.\nWhen I got hungry, I ate.</i>',-1),(130167,42,163911,163984,'01:53:49.657','01:53:52.701','When I had to go, you know...',-1),(130168,42,164023,164052,'01:53:54.328','01:53:55.538','I went.',-1),(130169,42,164053,164125,'01:53:55.579','01:53:58.582','And so, you just ran.',-1),(130170,42,164168,164194,'01:54:00.334','01:54:01.418','Yeah.',-1),(130171,42,165040,165167,'01:54:36.704','01:54:41.959','<i>I\'d think a lot about Mama\nand Bubba and Lieutenant Dan.</i>',-1),(130172,42,165191,165275,'01:54:42.960','01:54:46.463','<i>But most of all, I thought about Jenny.</i>',-1),(130173,42,165301,165353,'01:54:47.548','01:54:49.717','<i>I thought about her a lot.</i>',-1),(130174,42,165371,165446,'01:54:50.467','01:54:53.596','<i>For more than two years now,\na man named Forrest Gump,</i>',-1),(130175,42,165447,165529,'01:54:53.637','01:54:57.057','<i>a gardener from Greenbow, Alabama,\nstopping only to sleep,</i>',-1),(130176,42,165531,165583,'01:54:57.141','01:54:59.310','<i>has been running across America.</i>',-1),(130177,42,165585,165633,'01:54:59.393','01:55:01.395','<i>Charles Cooper brings us this report.</i>',-1),(130178,42,165655,165713,'01:55:02.313','01:55:04.732','<i>For the fourth time\non his journey across America,</i>',-1),(130179,42,165715,165783,'01:55:04.815','01:55:07.651','<i>Forrest Gump,\nthe gardener from Greenbow, Alabama,</i>',-1),(130180,42,165786,165855,'01:55:07.776','01:55:10.654','<i>is about to cross\nthe Mississippi River again today.</i>',-1),(130181,42,165870,165919,'01:55:11.280','01:55:13.324','- I\'ll be damned. Forrest?\n<i>- Sir, why are you running?</i>',-1),(130182,42,165921,165947,'01:55:13.407','01:55:14.491','Why are you running?',-1),(130183,42,165949,165987,'01:55:14.575','01:55:16.160','Are you doing this for world peace?',-1),(130184,42,165989,166021,'01:55:16.243','01:55:17.578','Are you doing this for the homeless?',-1),(130185,42,166023,166095,'01:55:17.661','01:55:20.664','- Are you running for women\'s rights?\n- Or for the environment?',-1),(130186,42,166097,166122,'01:55:20.748','01:55:21.790','Or for animals?',-1),(130187,42,166123,166194,'01:55:21.832','01:55:24.752','<i>They just couldn\'t believe that\nsomebody would do all that running</i>',-1),(130188,42,166196,166229,'01:55:24.835','01:55:26.211','<i>for no particular reason.</i>',-1),(130189,42,166231,166279,'01:55:26.295','01:55:28.297','Why are you doing this?',-1),(130190,42,166280,166340,'01:55:28.339','01:55:30.841','I just felt like running.',-1),(130191,42,166343,166400,'01:55:30.966','01:55:33.344','I just felt like running.',-1),(130192,42,166403,166480,'01:55:33.469','01:55:36.680','It\'s you. I can\'t believe it\'s really you.',-1),(130193,42,166500,166623,'01:55:37.514','01:55:42.645','Now, for some reason, what I was doing\nseemed to make sense to people.',-1),(130194,42,166627,166678,'01:55:42.811','01:55:44.939','I mean, it was like an alarm\nwent off in my head, you know?',-1),(130195,42,166680,166724,'01:55:45.022','01:55:46.857','I said,\n\"Here\'s a guy that\'s got his act together.',-1),(130196,42,166727,166775,'01:55:46.982','01:55:48.984','\"Here\'s somebody\nwho\'s got it all figured out.',-1),(130197,42,166776,166875,'01:55:49.026','01:55:53.155','\"Here\'s somebody who has the answer.\"\nI\'ll follow you anywhere, Mr. Gump.',-1),(130198,42,166876,166920,'01:55:53.197','01:55:55.032','<i>So, I got company.</i>',-1),(130199,42,166964,167104,'01:55:56.867','01:56:02.706','<i>And after that, I got more company.\nAnd then, even more people joined in.</i>',-1),(130200,42,167164,167241,'01:56:05.167','01:56:08.379','Somebody later told me\nit gave people hope.',-1),(130201,42,167284,167365,'01:56:10.172','01:56:13.550','Now... Now, I don\'t know\nanything about that,',-1),(130202,42,167385,167447,'01:56:14.385','01:56:16.971','<i>but some of those people\nasked me if I could help them out.</i>',-1),(130203,42,167452,167530,'01:56:17.179','01:56:20.432','Hey, man, hey, listen, I was wondering\nif you might help me, huh?',-1),(130204,42,167532,167574,'01:56:20.516','01:56:22.267','Listen, I\'m in the\nbumper sticker business',-1),(130205,42,167576,167618,'01:56:22.351','01:56:24.103','and I\'ve been trying\nto think up a good slogan.',-1),(130206,42,167620,167695,'01:56:24.186','01:56:27.314','And since you have been such a big\ninspiration to the people around here,',-1),(130207,42,167697,167743,'01:56:27.398','01:56:29.316','I thought you might\nbe able to help me jump into...',-1),(130208,42,167745,167832,'01:56:29.400','01:56:33.028','Whoa, man! You just ran through\na big pile of dog shit!',-1),(130209,42,167869,167933,'01:56:34.571','01:56:37.241','- It happens.\n- What, shit?',-1),(130210,42,167969,168016,'01:56:38.742','01:56:40.703','Sometimes.',-1),(130211,42,168061,168125,'01:56:42.579','01:56:45.249','<i>And some years later,\nI heard that that fellow</i>',-1),(130212,42,168127,168167,'01:56:45.332','01:56:46.959','<i>did come up with\na bumper sticker slogan,</i>',-1),(130213,42,168169,168246,'01:56:47.042','01:56:50.254','<i>and he made a lot of money off of it.</i>',-1),(130214,42,168281,168334,'01:56:51.714','01:56:53.924','<i>Another time, I was running along,</i>',-1),(130215,42,168337,168417,'01:56:54.049','01:56:57.386','<i>somebody who had lost all his money\nin the T-shirt business,</i>',-1),(130216,42,168418,168467,'01:56:57.428','01:56:59.471','<i>he wanted to put my face on a T-shirt,</i>',-1),(130217,42,168469,168541,'01:56:59.555','01:57:02.558','<i>but he couldn\'t draw that well,\nand he didn\'t have a camera.</i>',-1),(130218,42,168542,168626,'01:57:02.599','01:57:06.103','Here, use this one.\nNobody likes that color anyway.',-1),(130219,42,168742,168782,'01:57:10.941','01:57:12.609','Have a nice day.',-1),(130220,42,168821,168848,'01:57:14.236','01:57:15.362','<i>Well, some years later,</i>',-1),(130221,42,168850,168944,'01:57:15.446','01:57:19.366','<i>I found out that that man\ndid come up with an idea for a T-shirt.</i>',-1),(130222,42,168946,169003,'01:57:19.450','01:57:21.827','<i>He made a lot of money off of it.</i>',-1),(130223,42,169070,169177,'01:57:24.621','01:57:29.043','<i>Anyway, like I was saying,\nI had a lot of company.</i>',-1),(130224,42,169207,169235,'01:57:30.294','01:57:31.462','<i>My mama always said,</i>',-1),(130225,42,169237,169343,'01:57:31.545','01:57:35.966','<i>\"You got to put the past behind you\nbefore you can move on.\"</i>',-1),(130226,42,169383,169463,'01:57:37.634','01:57:40.971','<i>And I think that\'s what\nmy running was all about.</i>',-1),(130227,42,169483,169579,'01:57:41.805','01:57:45.809','<i>I had run for three years, two months,</i>',-1),(130228,42,169585,169641,'01:57:46.060','01:57:48.395','<i>14 days and 16 hours.</i>',-1),(130229,42,170017,170073,'01:58:04.078','01:58:06.413','Quiet. Quiet.\nHe\'s going to say something.',-1),(130230,42,170348,170390,'01:58:17.841','01:58:19.593','I\'m pretty tired.',-1),(130231,42,170458,170507,'01:58:22.429','01:58:24.473','Think I\'ll go home now.',-1),(130232,42,170952,171011,'01:58:43.033','01:58:45.494','Now what are we supposed to do?',-1),(130233,42,171034,171136,'01:58:46.453','01:58:50.707','<i>And just like that,\nmy running days was over.</i>',-1),(130234,42,171184,171226,'01:58:52.668','01:58:54.419','<i>So, I went home to Alabama.</i>',-1),(130235,42,171245,171345,'01:58:55.212','01:58:59.383','<i>Moments ago, at 2:25 p.m.,\nas President Reagan was leaving the...</i>',-1),(130236,42,171387,171487,'01:59:01.135','01:59:05.305','<i>...five or six gunshots were fired\nby an unknown would-be assassin.</i>',-1),(130237,42,171499,171556,'01:59:05.806','01:59:08.183','<i>The President was shot in the chest,\nand the assailant...</i>',-1),(130238,42,171557,171604,'01:59:08.225','01:59:10.185','I picked up the mail.',-1),(130239,42,171623,171716,'01:59:10.978','01:59:14.857','And one day, out of the blue clear sky,\nI got a letter from Jenny,',-1),(130240,42,171717,171820,'01:59:14.898','01:59:19.194','wondering if I could come down\nto Savannah and see her,',-1),(130241,42,171821,171883,'01:59:19.236','01:59:21.822','and that\'s what I\'m doing here.',-1),(130242,42,171885,171948,'01:59:21.905','01:59:24.533','She saw me on TV, running.',-1),(130243,42,171949,172051,'01:59:24.575','01:59:28.829','I\'m supposed to go on the\nnumber nine bus to Richmond Street',-1),(130244,42,172053,172220,'01:59:28.912','01:59:35.836','and get off and go one block left\nto 1947 Henry Street, Apartment 4.',-1),(130245,42,172222,172310,'01:59:35.919','01:59:39.590','Why, you don\'t need to take a bus.',-1),(130246,42,172313,172422,'01:59:39.715','01:59:44.261','Henry Street is just five\nor six blocks down that way.',-1),(130247,42,172466,172522,'01:59:46.096','01:59:48.432','- Down that way?\n- Down that way.',-1),(130248,42,172594,172640,'01:59:51.435','01:59:53.353','It was nice talking to you.',-1),(130249,42,172665,172728,'01:59:54.396','01:59:57.024','I hope everything works out for you!',-1),(130250,42,172914,172954,'02:00:04.781','02:00:06.450','Hey!',-1),(130251,42,172964,173004,'02:00:06.867','02:00:08.535','Forrest!',-1),(130252,42,173010,173088,'02:00:08.785','02:00:12.039','How you doing? Come in, come in!',-1),(130253,42,173090,173119,'02:00:12.122','02:00:13.332','I got your letter.',-1),(130254,42,173121,173185,'02:00:13.415','02:00:16.043','I was wondering about that.',-1),(130255,42,173222,173266,'02:00:17.586','02:00:19.421','Is this your house?',-1),(130256,42,173267,173341,'02:00:19.463','02:00:22.549','Yeah. It\'s messy right now.\nI just got off work.',-1),(130257,42,173343,173432,'02:00:22.633','02:00:26.345','It\'s nice. You got air conditioning.',-1),(130258,42,173597,173646,'02:00:33.227','02:00:35.270','- Thank you.\n- I ate some.',-1),(130259,42,173713,173843,'02:00:38.065','02:00:43.487','Hey, I kept a scrapbook\nof your clippings and everything.',-1),(130260,42,173846,173885,'02:00:43.612','02:00:45.239','There you are.',-1),(130261,42,173927,173953,'02:00:46.990','02:00:48.075','And this, I got you running.',-1),(130262,42,174027,174079,'02:00:51.161','02:00:53.330','I ran a long way,',-1),(130263,42,174091,174135,'02:00:53.830','02:00:55.666','for a long time.',-1),(130264,42,174189,174225,'02:00:57.876','02:00:59.378','And there...',-1),(130265,42,174381,174464,'02:01:05.884','02:01:09.346','Listen, Forrest,\nI don\'t know how to say this.',-1),(130266,42,174524,174628,'02:01:11.848','02:01:16.186','I just I want to apologize\nfor anything that I ever did to you,',-1),(130267,42,174631,174757,'02:01:16.311','02:01:21.566','\'cause I was messed up\nfor a long time, and...',-1),(130268,42,174824,174863,'02:01:24.361','02:01:25.988','- Hey.\n- Hi.',-1),(130269,42,174868,174892,'02:01:26.196','02:01:27.197','Hey, you.',-1),(130270,42,174920,174992,'02:01:28.365','02:01:31.368','- This is an old friend from Alabama.\n- How do you do?',-1),(130271,42,174993,175068,'02:01:31.410','02:01:34.538','Listen, next week my schedule changes,\nso I\'ll be able to... But thanks...',-1),(130272,42,175069,175118,'02:01:34.579','02:01:36.623','No problem. Got to go, Jen,\nI\'m double-parked.',-1),(130273,42,175120,175165,'02:01:36.707','02:01:38.583','- Okay. Thanks.\n- Bye.',-1),(130274,42,175249,175316,'02:01:42.045','02:01:44.840','This is my very good friend, Mr. Gump.\nCan you say hi to him?',-1),(130275,42,175317,175392,'02:01:44.881','02:01:48.010','- Hello, Mr. Gump.\n- Hello.',-1),(130276,42,175393,175465,'02:01:48.051','02:01:51.054','- Can I go watch TV now?\n- Yes, you can. Just keep it low.',-1),(130277,42,175533,175613,'02:01:53.890','02:01:57.227','- You\'re a mama, Jenny.\n- I\'m a mama.',-1),(130278,42,175682,175726,'02:02:00.105','02:02:01.940','His name\'s Forrest.',-1),(130279,42,175753,175785,'02:02:03.066','02:02:04.401','Like me.',-1),(130280,42,175824,175875,'02:02:06.028','02:02:08.155','I named him after his daddy.',-1),(130281,42,175898,175957,'02:02:09.114','02:02:11.575','He got a daddy named Forrest, too?',-1),(130282,42,175988,176037,'02:02:12.868','02:02:14.911','You\'re his daddy, Forrest.',-1),(130283,42,176385,176414,'02:02:29.384','02:02:30.594','Hey.',-1),(130284,42,176442,176511,'02:02:31.762','02:02:34.639','Forrest, look at me.\nLook at me, Forrest.',-1),(130285,42,176573,176672,'02:02:37.225','02:02:41.355','There\'s nothing you need to do, okay?\nYou didn\'t do anything wrong.',-1),(130286,42,176685,176718,'02:02:41.897','02:02:43.273','Okay?',-1),(130287,42,176822,176867,'02:02:47.611','02:02:49.488','Isn\'t he beautiful?',-1),(130288,42,176891,176962,'02:02:50.489','02:02:53.450','He\'s the most beautiful thing\nI\'ve ever seen.',-1),(130289,42,177053,177079,'02:02:57.245','02:02:58.330','But...',-1),(130290,42,177168,177238,'02:03:02.000','02:03:04.920','Is he smart, or...',-1),(130291,42,177239,177335,'02:03:04.961','02:03:08.965','He\'s very smart.\nHe\'s one of the smartest in his class.',-1),(130292,42,177559,177618,'02:03:18.308','02:03:20.769','Yeah, it\'s okay. Go talk to him.',-1),(130293,42,177842,177910,'02:03:30.112','02:03:32.948','- What are you watching?\n- Bert and Ernie.',-1),(130294,42,178465,178508,'02:03:56.054','02:03:57.848','Forrest,',-1),(130295,42,178543,178580,'02:03:59.307','02:04:00.851','I\'m sick.',-1),(130296,42,178644,178732,'02:04:03.520','02:04:07.190','What, do you have\na cough due to a cold?',-1),(130297,42,178733,178791,'02:04:07.232','02:04:09.651','I have some kind of virus,',-1),(130298,42,178792,178857,'02:04:09.693','02:04:12.404','and the doctors don\'t...\nThey don\'t know what it is,',-1),(130299,42,178860,178932,'02:04:12.529','02:04:15.532','and there isn\'t anything\nthey can do about it.',-1),(130300,42,179037,179092,'02:04:19.911','02:04:22.205','You could come home with me.',-1),(130301,42,179132,179269,'02:04:23.874','02:04:29.546','Jenny, you and little Forrest could\ncome stay at my house in Greenbow.',-1),(130302,42,179373,179440,'02:04:33.884','02:04:36.678','I\'ll take care of you if you\'re sick.',-1),(130303,42,179497,179552,'02:04:39.055','02:04:41.349','Would you marry me, Forrest?',-1),(130304,42,179678,179708,'02:04:46.605','02:04:47.856','Okay.',-1),(130305,42,179733,179773,'02:04:48.899','02:04:50.567','Please take your seats.',-1),(130306,42,179865,179921,'02:04:54.404','02:04:56.740','Forrest? It\'s time to start.',-1),(130307,42,180387,180425,'02:05:16.134','02:05:17.719','Hi.',-1),(130308,42,180446,180482,'02:05:18.595','02:05:20.096','Your tie.',-1),(130309,42,180783,180822,'02:05:32.651','02:05:34.277','Lieutenant Dan.',-1),(130310,42,181191,181238,'02:05:49.626','02:05:51.586','Lieutenant Dan.',-1),(130311,42,181258,181298,'02:05:52.420','02:05:54.089','Hello, Forrest.',-1),(1303