28','00:43:58.153','We\'re caught in the middle\nof something sinister here.',-1),(135333,48,63317,63380,'00:43:58.231','00:44:00.859','My guess is Dad found out\nmore than he was looking for.',-1),(135334,48,63382,63404,'00:44:00.933','00:44:01.865','And until I\'m sure,',-1),(135335,48,63406,63443,'00:44:01.934','00:44:03.492','I\'m going to\ncontinue to do things',-1),(135336,48,63445,63488,'00:44:03.569','00:44:05.366','the way I think\nthey should be done.',-1),(135337,48,63571,63648,'00:44:08.808','00:44:12.005','How dare you kiss me!',-1),(135338,48,63777,63857,'00:44:17.383','00:44:20.716','Leave me alone.\nI don\'t like fast women.',-1),(135339,48,63858,63894,'00:44:20.786','00:44:22.253','And I hate...',-1),(135340,48,63895,63977,'00:44:22.321','00:44:25.722','arrogant men.',-1),(135341,48,64204,64240,'00:44:35.167','00:44:36.691','Ah, Venice.',-1),(135342,48,65010,65066,'00:45:08.768','00:45:11.100','What do you know\nabout this place?',-1),(135343,48,65068,65150,'00:45:11.203','00:45:14.604','I know the Brunwalds\nare famous art collectors.',-1),(135344,48,65191,65230,'00:45:16.309','00:45:17.936','What are you going to do?',-1),(135345,48,65232,65258,'00:45:18.010','00:45:19.102','Don\'t know.',-1),(135346,48,65260,65291,'00:45:19.178','00:45:20.475','I\'ll think of something.',-1),(135347,48,65481,65513,'00:45:28.387','00:45:29.718','Yes?',-1),(135348,48,65514,65554,'00:45:29.789','00:45:31.450','And not before time!',-1),(135349,48,65556,65581,'00:45:31.524','00:45:32.582','Did you intend to leave us',-1),(135350,48,65583,65615,'00:45:32.658','00:45:33.989','standing on\nthe doorstep all day?',-1),(135351,48,65617,65640,'00:45:34.060','00:45:35.027','We\'re drenched!',-1),(135352,48,65682,65733,'00:45:36.762','00:45:38.889','Now look, I\'ve gone\nand caught a sniffle.',-1),(135353,48,65735,65761,'00:45:38.965','00:45:40.057','Are you expected?',-1),(135354,48,65763,65819,'00:45:40.132','00:45:42.464','Do not take that tone\nwith me, my good man.',-1),