at are you\ndoing here?',-1),(135379,48,69285,69324,'00:48:06.912','00:48:08.539','I came to get you.\nWhat do you thi...?',-1),(135380,48,69570,69643,'00:48:18.791','00:48:21.817','Late 14th century,\nMing dynasty.',-1),(135381,48,69645,69702,'00:48:21.894','00:48:24.260','Oh, it breaks the heart.',-1),(135382,48,69703,69766,'00:48:24.330','00:48:26.924','And the head.\nYou hit me, Dad.',-1),(135383,48,69767,69823,'00:48:26.999','00:48:29.297','I\'ll never forgive myself.',-1),(135384,48,69824,69882,'00:48:29.368','00:48:31.768','Don\'t worry, I\'m fine.',-1),(135385,48,69884,69936,'00:48:31.837','00:48:34.032','Thank God.',-1),(135386,48,70008,70080,'00:48:37.009','00:48:40.001','It\'s fake.',-1),(135387,48,70081,70185,'00:48:40.079','00:48:44.413','See, you can tell\nby the cross section.',-1),(135388,48,70196,70213,'00:48:44.850','00:48:45.578','No!',-1),(135389,48,70215,70242,'00:48:45.651','00:48:46.777','Dad, get your stuff.',-1),(135390,48,70244,70283,'00:48:46.852','00:48:48.479','We\'ve got to get\nout of here.',-1),(135391,48,70285,70340,'00:48:48.554','00:48:50.852','Well, I\'m sorry about\nyour head, though,',-1),(135392,48,70342,70390,'00:48:50.923','00:48:52.948','but I thought you\nwere one of them.',-1),(135393,48,70392,70452,'00:48:53.025','00:48:55.516','Dad, they come in\nthrough the doors.',-1),(135394,48,70477,70502,'00:48:56.562','00:48:57.586','Good point.',-1),(135395,48,70503,70561,'00:48:57.663','00:49:00.063','But better safe\nthan sorry.',-1),(135396,48,70563,70607,'00:49:00.132','00:49:01.997','Hmm, so I was wrong this time.',-1),(135397,48,70609,70692,'00:49:02.067','00:49:05.503','But, by God, I wasn\'t wrong\nwhen I mailed you my diary.',-1),(135398,48,70693,70724,'00:49:05.571','00:49:06.868','You obviously got it.',-1),(135399,48,70771,70832,'00:49:08.807','00:49:11.367','I got it, and I used it.',-1),(135400,48,70834,70917,'00:49:11.443','00:49:14.879','We found the entrance\nto the catacombs.',-1),(135401,48,70918,70953,'00:49:14.947','00:49:16.414','Through the library?',-1),(135402,48,70955,71001,'00:49:16.482','00:49:18.382','Right.',-1),(135403,48,71074,71122,'00:49:21.420','00:49:23.445','I knew it.',-1),(135404,48,71124,71161,'00:49:23.522','00:49:25.080','And the tomb of Sir Richard?',-1),(135405,48,71163,71226,'00:49:25.157','00:49:27.785','Found it.',-1),(135406,48,71228,71307,'00:49:27.860','00:49:31.125','He was actually there?',-1),(135407,48,71351,71390,'00:49:32.998','00:49:34.590','You saw him?',-1),(135408,48,71392,71463,'00:49:34.667','00:49:37.636','Well, what was\nleft of him.',-1),(135409,48,71464,71509,'00:49:37.703','00:49:39.568','And his shield...',-1),(135410,48,71511,71617,'00:49:39.638','00:49:44.075','the inscription on\nSir Richard\'s shield?',-1),(135411,48,71619,71666,'00:49:44.143','00:49:46.111','\"Alexandretta.\"',-1),(135412,48,71669,71723,'00:49:46.212','00:49:48.476','Alexandretta! Of course!',-1),(135413,48,71725,71826,'00:49:48.547','00:49:52.779','On the pilgrim trail\nfrom the Eastern Empire.',-1),(135414,48,71828,71851,'00:49:52.851','00:49:53.818','Oh...',-1),(135415,48,71853,71946,'00:49:53.886','00:49:57.788','Junior, you did it.',-1),(135416,48,71948,72002,'00:49:57.856','00:50:00.120','No, Dad. You did.',-1),(135417,48,72004,72043,'00:50:00.192','00:50:01.819','Forty years.',-1),(135418,48,72045,72120,'00:50:01.894','00:50:05.022','Oh, if only I could have been\nwith you.',-1),(135419,48,72122,72166,'00:50:05.097','00:50:06.928','There were rats,\nDad.',-1),(135420,48,72167,72199,'00:50:06.999','00:50:08.296','Rats?',-1),(135421,48,72200,72231,'00:50:08.367','00:50:09.629','Yeah, big ones.',-1),(135422,48,72232,72295,'00:50:09.702','00:50:12.296','What do the Nazis\nwant with you, Dad?',-1),(135423,48,72296,72324,'00:50:12.371','00:50:13.531','They wanted my diary.',-1),(135424,48,72326,72358,'00:50:13.606','00:50:14.937','Yeah?',-1),(135425,48,72360,72441,'00:50:15.007','00:50:18.408','I knew I had to get that book\nas far away from me',-1),(135426,48,72443,72477,'00:50:18.477','00:50:19.910','as I possibly could.',-1),(135427,48,72522,72572,'00:50:21.780','00:50:23.839','Yeah.',-1),(135428,48,72674,72713,'00:50:28.087','00:50:29.748','Dr.Jones.',-1),(135429,48,72715,72746,'00:50:29.822','00:50:31.119','Yes?',-1),(135430,48,72807,72862,'00:50:33.626','00:50:35.924','I will take the book now.',-1),(135431,48,72863,72946,'00:50:35.995','00:50:39.453','What book?',-1),(135432,48,72948,73006,'00:50:39.531','00:50:41.931','You have the diary\nin your pocket.',-1),(135433,48,73008,73094,'00:50:42.001','00:50:45.596','You dolt!',-1),(135434,48,73096,73142,'00:50:45.671','00:50:47.605','Do you think my son\nwould be that stupid',-1),(135435,48,73144,73191,'00:50:47.673','00:50:49.641','that he would\nbring my diary',-1),(135436,48,73192,73231,'00:50:49.708','00:50:51.300','all the way back here?',-1),(135437,48,73257,73296,'00:50:52.378','00:50:54.005','You didn\'t, did you?',-1),(135438,48,73297,73354,'00:50:54.079','00:50:56.445','You didn\'t bring it,\ndid you?',-1),(135439,48,73356,73378,'00:50:56.515','00:50:57.447','Well, uh...',-1),(135440,48,73380,73424,'00:50:57.516','00:50:59.347','You did.',-1),(135441,48,73426,73473,'00:50:59.418','00:51:01.386','Look, can we\ndiscuss this later?',-1),(135442,48,73474,73522,'00:51:01.453','00:51:03.444','I should have mailed it\nto the Marx Brothers.',-1),(135443,48,73524,73570,'00:51:03.522','00:51:05.456','Will you take it easy?',-1),(135444,48,73572,73603,'00:51:05.524','00:51:06.821','Take it easy?!',-1),(135445,48,73605,73629,'00:51:06.892','00:51:07.881','Why do you think\nI sent it home',-1),(135446,48,73631,73653,'00:51:07.960','00:51:08.892','in the first place?',-1),(135447,48,73655,73689,'00:51:08.961','00:51:10.394','So it wouldn\'t fall\ninto their hands!',-1),(135448,48,73691,73741,'00:51:10.462','00:51:12.555','I came here\nto save you!',-1),(135449,48,73743,73765,'00:51:12.631','00:51:13.563','Oh, yeah?',-1),(135450,48,73767,73831,'00:51:13.632','00:51:16.328','And who\'s gonna come\nto save you, Junior?',-1),(135451,48,73833,73859,'00:51:16.402','00:51:17.460','I told you...',-1),(135452,48,74026,74085,'00:51:24.443','00:51:26.877','...don\'t call me Junior!',-1),(135453,48,74125,74187,'00:51:28.580','00:51:31.140','Look what you did!',-1),(135454,48,74234,74285,'00:51:33.118','00:51:35.211','I can\'t believe what you did...',-1),(135455,48,74321,74391,'00:51:36.722','00:51:39.657','Elsa? Elsa?',-1),(135456,48,74393,74455,'00:51:39.725','00:51:42.319','That\'s far enough.\nPut down the gun, Dr.Jones.',-1),(135457,48,74457,74487,'00:51:42.394','00:51:43.656','Put down the gun,\nor the fraulein dies.',-1),(135458,48,74489,74511,'00:51:43.729','00:51:44.661','But she\'s one of them.',-1),(135459,48,74513,74544,'00:51:44.730','00:51:46.027','Indy, please!',-1),(135460,48,74546,74568,'00:51:46.098','00:51:47.030','She\'s a Nazi.',-1),(135461,48,74570,74592,'00:51:47.099','00:51:48.031','What?!',-1),(135462,48,74594,74609,'00:51:48.100','00:51:48.725','Trust me.',-1),(135463,48,74611,74651,'00:51:48.801','00:51:50.496','- Indy, no!\n- I will kill her!',-1),(135464,48,74653,74685,'00:51:50.569','00:51:51.900','Yeah? Go ahead!',-1),(135465,48,74687,74715,'00:51:51.970','00:51:53.164','No! Don\'t shoot!',-1),(135466,48,74717,74769,'00:51:53.238','00:51:55.399','Don\'t worry. He won\'t.',-1),(135467,48,74771,74819,'00:51:55.474','00:51:57.499','Indy, please! Do what he says!',-1),(135468,48,74821,74881,'00:51:57.576','00:52:00.067','And don\'t listen to her.',-1),(135469,48,74883,74928,'00:52:00.145','00:52:02.010','Enough! She dies!',-1),(135470,48,74929,75010,'00:52:02.081','00:52:05.448','Wait! Wait...',-1),(135471,48,75138,75185,'00:52:10.789','00:52:12.723','I\'m sorry.',-1),(135472,48,75186,75284,'00:52:12.791','00:52:16.852','No, don\'t be.',-1),(135473,48,75564,75653,'00:52:28.540','00:52:32.237','But... you should have\nlistened to your father.',-1),(135474,48,76068,76114,'00:52:49.528','00:52:51.428','She ransacked her own room,',-1),(135475,48,76115,76159,'00:52:51.497','00:52:53.294','and I fell for it.',-1),(135476,48,76160,76237,'00:52:53.365','00:52:56.562','How did you know\nshe was a Nazi?',-1),(135477,48,76239,76261,'00:52:56.635','00:52:57.567','Hmm?',-1),(135478,48,76263,76335,'00:52:57.636','00:53:00.628','How did you know\nshe was a Nazi?',-1),(135479,48,76336,76400,'00:53:00.706','00:53:03.334','She talks in her sleep.',-1),(135480,48,76627,76693,'00:53:12.818','00:53:15.582','I didn\'t trust her.\nWhy did you?',-1),(135481,48,76695,76757,'00:53:15.654','00:53:18.248','Because he didn\'t\ntake my advice.',-1),(135482,48,76909,76967,'00:53:24.563','00:53:26.997','Donovan.',-1),(135483,48,76969,77000,'00:53:27.065','00:53:28.362','Didn\'t I warn you',-1),(135484,48,77002,77060,'00:53:28.434','00:53:30.868','not to trust anybody,\nDr.Jones?',-1),(135485,48,77062,77108,'00:53:30.936','00:53:32.870','I misjudged you, Walter.',-1),(135486,48,77110,77193,'00:53:32.938','00:53:36.396','I knew you would sell your\nmother for an Etruscan vase,',-1),(135487,48,77195,77243,'00:53:36.475','00:53:38.466','but I didn\'t know\nyou would sell',-1),(135488,48,77245,77283,'00:53:38.544','00:53:40.136','your country\nand your soul',-1),(135489,48,77285,77331,'00:53:40.212','00:53:42.146','to the slime\nof humanity.',-1),(135490,48,77333,77419,'00:53:42.247','00:53:45.808','Dr.Schneider...',-1),(135491,48,77421,77473,'00:53:45.884','00:53:48.079','there are pages\ntorn out of this.',-1),(135492,48,77675,77746,'00:53:56.462','00:53:59.431','This book contained a map,\na map with no names,',-1),(135493,48,77747,77808,'00:53:59.498','00:54:02.023','precise directions\nfrom the unknown city',-1),(135494,48,77810,77874,'00:54:02.100','00:54:04.762','to the secret Canyon\nof the Crescent Moon.',-1),(135495,48,77876,77906,'00:54:04.837','00:54:06.099','So it did.',-1),(135496,48,77908,77952,'00:54:06.171','00:54:08.036','Where are these missing pages,\nthis map?',-1),(135497,48,77954,78000,'00:54:08.106','00:54:10.040','We must have\nthese pages back.',-1),(135498,48,78002,78032,'00:54:10.108','00:54:11.370','You\'re wasting\nyour breath.',-1),(135499,48,78034,78063,'00:54:11.443','00:54:12.637','He won\'t tell us,',-1),(135500,48,78065,78120,'00:54:12.711','00:54:15.009','and he doesn\'t have to.',-1),(135501,48,78121,78216,'00:54:15.080','00:54:19.016','It\'s perfectly obvious\nwhere the pages are.',-1),(135502,48,78218,78266,'00:54:19.084','00:54:21.109','He\'s given them\nto Marcus Brody.',-1),(135503,48,78269,78290,'00:54:21.220','00:54:22.118','Marcus?',-1),(135504,48,78294,78349,'00:54:22.254','00:54:24.552','You didn\'t drag poor\nMarcus along, did you?',-1),(135505,48,78350,78386,'00:54:24.623','00:54:26.113','He\'s not up\nto the challenge.',-1),(135506,48,78389,78435,'00:54:26.225','00:54:28.125','He sticks out\nlike a sore thumb.',-1),(135507,48,78438,78467,'00:54:28.260','00:54:29.488','We\'ll find him.',-1),(135508,48,78469,78497,'00:54:29.561','00:54:30.721','The hell you will.',-1),(135509,48,78499,78539,'00:54:30.796','00:54:32.491','He\'s got a two-day\nhead start on you,',-1),(135510,48,78541,78572,'00:54:32.564','00:54:33.861','which is more\nthan he needs.',-1),(135511,48,78574,78630,'00:54:33.932','00:54:36.264','Brody\'s got friends\nin every town and village',-1),(135512,48,78632,78661,'00:54:36.335','00:54:37.563','from here to the Sudan.',-1),(135513,48,78663,78732,'00:54:37.636','00:54:40.503','He speaks a dozen languages,\nknows every local custom.',-1),(135514,48,78733,78769,'00:54:40.572','00:54:42.062','He\'ll blend in, disappear.',-1),(135515,48,78771,78808,'00:54:42.140','00:54:43.698','You\'ll never see him again.',-1),(135516,48,78810,78904,'00:54:43.775','00:54:47.677','With any luck,\nhe\'s got the Grail already.',-1),(135517,48,78907,78956,'00:54:47.813','00:54:49.838','Does anyone here\nspeak English?',-1),(135518,48,78957,78981,'00:54:49.915','00:54:50.904','Or even ancient Greek?',-1),(135519,48,78983,79017,'00:54:50.983','00:54:52.416','Uh, water?\nNo, thank you, sir.',-1),(135520,48,79019,79052,'00:54:52.484','00:54:53.849','No. Fish make love in it.',-1),(135521,48,79054,79082,'00:54:53.919','00:54:55.113','Goodness me.',-1),(135522,48,79084,79106,'00:54:55.187','00:54:56.119','Thank you so much.',-1),(135523,48,79108,79131,'00:54:56.188','00:54:57.155','No, I don\'t like that.',-1),(135524,48,79134,79159,'00:54:57.256','00:54:58.314','No, I really don\'t want...',-1),(135525,48,79161,79199,'00:54:58.390','00:54:59.982','No, no, thank you very much.',-1),(135526,48,79201,79266,'00:55:00.058','00:55:02.754','No, thank you, madam.\nI\'m a vegetarian.',-1),(135527,48,79267,79346,'00:55:02.828','00:55:06.093','Does anyone understand\na word I\'m saying here?',-1),(135528,48,79347,79375,'00:55:06.164','00:55:07.324','Mr.Brody!',-1),(135529,48,79377,79414,'00:55:07.399','00:55:08.923','Oh, Sallah.\nWhat a relief.',-1),(135530,48,79416,79466,'00:55:09.001','00:55:11.094','Marcus Brody, sir.',-1),(135531,48,79469,79492,'00:55:11.236','00:55:12.203','But where is Indy?',-1),(135532,48,79494,79517,'00:55:12.271','00:55:13.238','Oh, he\'s in Austria.',-1),(135533,48,79519,79542,'00:55:13.305','00:55:14.272','A slight detour.',-1),(135534,48,79544,79576,'00:55:14.339','00:55:15.670','You are on your own?',-1),(135535,48,79577,79604,'00:55:15.741','00:55:16.867','Yes, but don\'t panic.',-1),(135536,48,79606,79643,'00:55:16.942','00:55:18.466','Everything\'s under control.',-1),(135537,48,79645,79695,'00:55:18.544','00:55:20.637','Have you, have you\narranged our supplies?',-1),(135538,48,79697,79719,'00:55:20.712','00:55:21.644','Oh, yes,\nof course.',-1),(135539,48,79721,79748,'00:55:21.713','00:55:22.839','But where\nare we going?',-1),(135540,48,79749,79778,'00:55:22.915','00:55:24.109','Oh, this map will show you.',-1),(135541,48,79781,79824,'00:55:24.249','00:55:26.012','It was drawn by, uh...',-1),(135542,48,79826,79873,'00:55:26.084','00:55:28.052','Mr.Brody.',-1),(135543,48,79874,79922,'00:55:28.120','00:55:30.111','Welcome to Iskenderun.',-1),(135544,48,79924,79970,'00:55:30.188','00:55:32.122','The director\nof the Museum of Antiquities',-1),(135545,48,79974,80002,'00:55:32.257','00:55:33.417','has sent a car for you.',-1),(135546,48,80003,80058,'00:55:33.492','00:55:35.756','Oh, well...\nyour servant, sir.',-1),(135547,48,80059,80090,'00:55:35.827','00:55:37.124','And I am his.',-1),(135548,48,80093,80142,'00:55:37.229','00:55:39.254','Follow me, please.',-1),(135549,48,80143,80191,'00:55:39.331','00:55:41.322','My reputation precedes me.',-1),(135550,48,80193,80235,'00:55:41.400','00:55:43.129','There is no museum\nin Iskenderun.',-1),(135551,48,80238,80273,'00:55:43.268','00:55:44.735','Papers, please.',-1),(135552,48,80275,80298,'00:55:44.803','00:55:45.770','Papers?',-1),(135553,48,80300,80324,'00:55:45.837','00:55:46.861','Of course.',-1),(135554,48,80326,80351,'00:55:46.939','00:55:47.997','Run.',-1),(135555,48,80353,80376,'00:55:48.073','00:55:49.005','Yes.',-1),(135556,48,80377,80412,'00:55:49.074','00:55:50.507','Papers. Got it here.',-1),(135557,48,80413,80451,'00:55:50.576','00:55:52.134','Just finished\nreading it myself.',-1),(135558,48,80454,80477,'00:55:52.277','00:55:53.244','Run.',-1),(135559,48,80479,80501,'00:55:53.312','00:55:54.244','Yes.',-1),(135560,48,80503,80543,'00:55:54.313','00:55:55.974','\"Egyptian Mail,\"\nmorning edition.',-1),(135561,48,80545,80568,'00:55:56.048','00:55:57.015','Run.',-1),(135562,48,80569,80592,'00:55:57.082','00:55:58.014','Did you say, uh...',-1),(135563,48,80593,80608,'00:55:58.083','00:55:58.708','Run!',-1),(135564,48,80987,81024,'00:56:14.466','00:56:16.024','Okay, okay,\nquick, quick, quick!',-1),(135565,48,81026,81070,'00:56:16.101','00:56:17.932','Find the back door!\nFind the back door!',-1),(135566,48,81424,81457,'00:56:32.684','00:56:34.049','Intolerable.',-1),(135567,48,81530,81574,'00:56:37.089','00:56:38.920','Dr.Schneider.\nMessage from Berlin.',-1),(135568,48,81575,81613,'00:56:38.991','00:56:40.549','You must return immediately.',-1),(135569,48,81615,81664,'00:56:40.626','00:56:42.685','A rally at the Institute\nof Aryan Culture.',-1),(135570,48,81666,81690,'00:56:42.761','00:56:43.750','So?',-1),(135571,48,81691,81722,'00:56:43.829','00:56:45.091','Your presence\non the platform',-1),(135572,48,81723,81779,'00:56:45.163','00:56:47.495','is requested\nat the highest level.',-1),(135573,48,81781,81818,'00:56:47.566','00:56:49.124','Thank you, Herr Oberst.',-1),(135574,48,81822,81858,'00:56:49.267','00:56:50.757','I will meet you\nat Iskenderun.',-1),(135575,48,81860,81882,'00:56:50.836','00:56:51.768','Take this diary',-1),(135576,48,81884,81912,'00:56:51.837','00:56:53.031','to the Reichmuseum\nin Berlin.',-1),(135577,48,81914,81945,'00:56:53.105','00:56:54.402','It will show them\nour progress,',-1),(135578,48,81947,81969,'00:56:54.473','00:56:55.405','ahead of schedule.',-1),(135579,48,81971,81994,'00:56:55.474','00:56:56.441','Without the map,',-1),(135580,48,81996,82033,'00:56:56.508','00:56:58.066','I\'m afraid it\'s no\nbetter than a souvenir.',-1),(135581,48,82035,82063,'00:56:58.143','00:56:59.303','Let me kill them now.',-1),(135582,48,82065,82088,'00:56:59.378','00:57:00.345','No.',-1),(135583,48,82089,82144,'00:57:00.412','00:57:02.676','If we fail to recover\nthe pages from Brody,',-1),(135584,48,82145,82174,'00:57:02.748','00:57:03.942','we\'ll need them alive.',-1),(135585,48,82176,82233,'00:57:04.016','00:57:06.382','Always do what\nthe doctor orders.',-1),(135586,48,82428,82465,'00:57:14.526','00:57:16.050','Don\'t look at me like that.',-1),(135587,48,82467,82517,'00:57:16.128','00:57:18.221','We both wanted the Grail.',-1),(135588,48,82519,82590,'00:57:18.296','00:57:21.288','I would have done\nanything to get it.',-1),(135589,48,82592,82622,'00:57:21.366','00:57:22.594','You would have\ndone the same.',-1),(135590,48,82624,82683,'00:57:22.668','00:57:25.159','I\'m sorry you think so.',-1),(135591,48,8293