en\nfor 20 years.',-1),(135779,48,107912,107966,'01:14:56.346','01:14:58.610','You left just when you\nwere becoming interesting.',-1),(135780,48,107968,108003,'01:14:58.682','01:15:00.149','Unbelievable.',-1),(135781,48,108005,108030,'01:15:00.217','01:15:01.275','Dad, how can you...?',-1),(135782,48,108033,108057,'01:15:01.385','01:15:02.409','Very well.',-1),(135783,48,108059,108118,'01:15:02.486','01:15:04.920','I\'m here now.',-1),(135784,48,108119,108168,'01:15:04.988','01:15:07.013','What do you want\nto talk about?',-1),(135785,48,108170,108197,'01:15:07.090','01:15:08.216','Hmm?',-1),(135786,48,108200,108258,'01:15:08.358','01:15:10.758','Well, I...',-1),(135787,48,108305,108346,'01:15:12.729','01:15:14.424','Uh...',-1),(135788,48,108436,108491,'01:15:18.201','01:15:20.465','I can\'t think of anything.',-1),(135789,48,108492,108542,'01:15:20.537','01:15:22.596','Then what are\nyou complaining about?',-1),(135790,48,108581,108629,'01:15:24.241','01:15:26.209','Look, we have work to do.',-1),(135791,48,108669,108715,'01:15:27.878','01:15:29.812','When we get to\nAlexandretta,',-1),(135792,48,108717,108772,'01:15:29.880','01:15:32.178','we will face\nthree challenges.',-1),(135793,48,108773,108820,'01:15:32.249','01:15:34.183','The first,',-1),(135794,48,108822,108858,'01:15:34.251','01:15:35.775','\"The Breath of God.',-1),(135795,48,108860,108914,'01:15:35.852','01:15:38.116','Only the penitent\nman will pass.\"',-1),(135796,48,108916,108946,'01:15:38.188','01:15:39.450','Second,',-1),(135797,48,108948,108978,'01:15:39.523','01:15:40.785','\"The Word of God.',-1),(135798,48,108980,109066,'01:15:40.857','01:15:44.418','Only in the footsteps\nof God will he proceed.\"',-1),(135799,48,109067,109094,'01:15:44.494','01:15:45.586','Third,',-1),(135800,48,109095,109131,'01:15:45.662','01:15:47.152','\"The Path of God.',-1),(135801,48,109133,109182,'01:15:47.230','01:15:49.255','\"Only in the leap\nfrom the lion\'s head',-1),(135802,48,109183,109245,'01:15:49.333','