,48,112521,112545,'01:18:08.405','01:18:09.394','Hang on, Dad.',-1),(135827,48,112547,112577,'01:18:09.473','01:18:10.735','We\'re going in!',-1),(135828,48,112882,112909,'01:18:23.420','01:18:24.546','Nice landing.',-1),(135829,48,112910,112959,'01:18:24.621','01:18:26.646','Thanks.',-1),(135830,48,113305,113341,'01:18:41.071','01:18:42.561','Those people are\ntrying to kill us!',-1),(135831,48,113343,113369,'01:18:42.639','01:18:43.731','I know, Dad!',-1),(135832,48,113371,113404,'01:18:43.807','01:18:45.172','Well.',-1),(135833,48,113405,113453,'01:18:45.242','01:18:47.233','It\'s a new\nexperience for me.',-1),(135834,48,113455,113516,'01:18:47.310','01:18:49.870','It happens to me all the time.',-1),(135835,48,114248,114295,'01:19:20.343','01:19:22.311','This is intolerable!',-1),(135836,48,114328,114361,'01:19:23.680','01:19:25.045','This could be close.',-1),(135837,48,114560,114621,'01:19:33.356','01:19:35.916','Faster, boy! Faster!',-1),(135838,48,114997,115054,'01:19:51.575','01:19:53.941','Well, they don\'t come\nany closer than that!',-1),(135839,48,115434,115502,'01:20:09.759','01:20:12.592','Dad, he\'s coming back!',-1),(135840,48,116619,116680,'01:20:59.142','01:21:01.702','I suddenly\nremembered my Charlemagne.',-1),(135841,48,116682,116752,'01:21:01.778','01:21:04.679','\"Let my armies be the rocks\nand the trees',-1),(135842,48,116753,116805,'01:21:04.748','01:21:06.909','and the birds in the sky.\"',-1),(135843,48,117226,117255,'01:21:24.434','01:21:25.628','These pages are taken',-1),(135844,48,117256,117316,'01:21:25.702','01:21:28.193','from Professor Jones\'\ndiary, Your Highness,',-1),(135845,48,117318,117349,'01:21:28.271','01:21:29.568','and they include a map',-1),(135846,48,117351,117417,'01:21:29.639','01:21:32.403','that pinpoints the exact\nlocation of the Grail.',-1),(135847,48,117419,117481,'01:21:32.475','01:21:35.069','As you can see, the Grail\nis all but in our hands.',-1),(135848,48,117483,117510,'01:21:35.145','01:21:36.271','H