,(135871,48,119471,119506,'01:22:57.994','01:22:59.427','We have no time to lose.',-1),(135872,48,119507,119570,'01:22:59.496','01:23:02.124','Indiana Jones\nand his father have escaped.',-1),(135873,48,119636,119682,'01:23:04.868','01:23:06.768','We go this way.',-1),(135874,48,119684,119721,'01:23:06.836','01:23:08.394','Get that camel\nout of the way.',-1),(135875,48,119780,119822,'01:23:10.874','01:23:12.603','What happened\nto Marcus, Sallah?',-1),(135876,48,119824,119893,'01:23:12.675','01:23:15.542','Ah, they set out across\nthe desert this afternoon.',-1),(135877,48,119894,119962,'01:23:15.612','01:23:18.445','I believe they took\nMr.Brody with them.',-1),(135878,48,119997,120063,'01:23:19.883','01:23:22.647','Now they have the map.',-1),(135879,48,120065,120128,'01:23:22.719','01:23:25.347','And in this sort of race,',-1),(135880,48,120130,120208,'01:23:25.422','01:23:28.687','there\'s no silver medal\nfor finishing second.',-1),(135881,48,120732,120797,'01:23:50.513','01:23:53.243','Care to wet your\nwhistle, Marcus?',-1),(135882,48,120799,120846,'01:23:53.316','01:23:55.284','I\'d rather spit\nin your face.',-1),(135883,48,120850,120900,'01:23:55.418','01:23:57.511','But as I haven\'t\ngot any spit...',-1),(135884,48,120964,121019,'01:24:00.190','01:24:02.488','Must be within\nthree or four miles.',-1),(135885,48,121021,121086,'01:24:02.559','01:24:05.289','Otherwise we are\noff the map.',-1),(135886,48,121129,121195,'01:24:07.063','01:24:09.793','Well, Marcus,\nwe are on the brink',-1),(135887,48,121196,121247,'01:24:09.866','01:24:11.993','of the recovery\nof the greatest artifact',-1),(135888,48,121249,121283,'01:24:12.068','01:24:13.467','in the history\nof mankind.',-1),(135889,48,121284,121344,'01:24:13.536','01:24:16.027','You\'re meddling with powers',-1),(135890,48,121346,121415,'01:24:16.105','01:24:18.972','you cannot\npossibly comprehend.',-1),(135891,48,121543,121606,'01:24:24.314','01:24:26.942','Ah, I see Brody.',-1),(135892,48,121608,121667,'01:24:27.016','01:24:29.484','He seems okay.',-1),(135893,48,121737,121775,'01:24:32.388','01:24:33.980','They\'ve got a tank.',-1),(135894,48,121919,121958,'01:24:39.996','01:24:41.588','Six-pound gun.',-1),(135895,48,121959,122001,'01:24:41.664','01:24:43.393','What do you think\nyou\'re doing there?',-1),(135896,48,122003,122025,'01:24:43.466','01:24:44.398','Get down!',-1),(135897,48,122027,122089,'01:24:44.467','01:24:47.061','Dad, we\'re well out of range.',-1),(135898,48,122332,122378,'01:24:57.180','01:24:59.114','That car belonged\nto my brother-in-law.',-1),(135899,48,122380,122410,'01:24:59.182','01:25:00.444','Come on, come on!',-1),(135900,48,122412,122458,'01:25:00.517','01:25:02.417','I can\'t see anyone up there.',-1),(135901,48,122459,122501,'01:25:02.485','01:25:04.214','Maybe it wasn\'t\neven Jones.',-1),(135902,48,122502,122540,'01:25:04.287','01:25:05.845','No, it is him,\nall right.',-1),(135903,48,122542,122582,'01:25:05.922','01:25:07.617','He\'s here somewhere.',-1),(135904,48,122584,122650,'01:25:07.690','01:25:10.420','Put Brody in the tank.',-1),(135905,48,122835,122896,'01:25:18.134','01:25:20.694','Well, in this sun,',-1),(135906,48,122898,122953,'01:25:20.770','01:25:23.068','without transportation,\nthey\'re as good as dead.',-1),(135907,48,123185,123225,'01:25:32.715','01:25:34.376','It\'s Jones, all right.',-1),(135908,48,123325,123361,'01:25:38.555','01:25:40.045','Now, who are\nall these people?',-1),(135909,48,123362,123385,'01:25:40.123','01:25:41.055','Who cares?',-1),(135910,48,123386,123433,'01:25:41.124','01:25:43.058','As long as they\'re\nkeeping Donovan busy.',-1),(135911,48,123435,123478,'01:25:43.126','01:25:44.923','Dad, you stay here\nwhile Sallah and I',-1),(135912,48,123479,123529,'01:25:44.994','01:25:47.053','organize some transportation.',-1),(135913,48,124118,124157,'01:26:11.588','01:26:13.215','I\'m going after those horses.',-1),(135914,48,124158,124181,'01:26:13.289','01:26:14.221','I\'ll take the camels.