8,'01:07:41.793','01:07:44.523','<i>All right, buddy, looks like</i>\n<i>we\'re going to the farm again.</i>',-1),(138534,16,97550,97622,'01:07:44.596','01:07:47.622','I\'m serious. I\'m not kidding. I want-\nI can\'t take this anymore.',-1),(138535,16,97624,97678,'01:07:47.699','01:07:49.929','- What did he do?\n- Everything! What hasn\'t he done?',-1),(138536,16,97680,97735,'01:07:50.001','01:07:52.299','He\'s just a horrible,\nhorrible animal.',-1),(138537,16,97736,97811,'01:07:52.370','01:07:55.498','- Well, that\'s a little unfair.\n<i>- No, what\'s unfair...</i>',-1),(138538,16,97813,97892,'01:07:55.573','01:07:58.872','is that Conor hasn\'t slept in two weeks\nbecause of that dog\'s barking...',-1),(138539,16,97894,97952,'01:07:58.943','01:08:01.343','that Patrick gets\nknocked down twice a day...',-1),(138540,16,97953,98000,'01:08:01.413','01:08:03.347','<i>that I can\'t even think straight.</i>',-1),(138541,16,98001,98049,'01:08:03.415','01:08:05.406','God forbid there\'s\na hint of thunder.',-1),(138542,16,98051,98098,'01:08:05.483','01:08:07.417','- Just don\'t!\n- Just calm down for a second.',-1),(138543,16,98099,98172,'01:08:07.485','01:08:10.511','I know that it\'s been a rough couple of\nmonths with the new baby and everything.',-1),(138544,16,98174,98250,'01:08:10.588','01:08:13.785','I understand that.\nBut I was talking with Arnie.',-1),(138545,16,98252,98299,'01:08:13.858','01:08:15.792','- And postpartum dep-\n- Don\'t you dare.',-1),(138546,16,98300,98392,'01:08:15.860','01:08:19.694','I am not depressed.\nI am exhausted.',-1),(138547,16,98394,98454,'01:08:19.764','01:08:22.289','<i>I\'m not angry because of some condition.</i>',-1),(138548,16,98456,98519,'01:08:22.367','01:08:24.961','I can\'t even go out\nfor an hour without the kids...',-1),(138549,16,98520,98592,'01:08:25.036','01:08:28.005','because every babysitter in this\nneighborhood is terrified of Marley.',-1),(138550,16,98593,98672,'01:08:28.072','01:08:31.371','I know that, but you were the one that\nsaid you didn\'t wanna work anymore.',-1),(138551,16,98674,98721,'01:08:31.443','01:08:33.411','<i>- We can get help-</i>\n- I don\'t need any help!',-1),(138552,16,98723,98769,'01:08:33.478','01:08:35.412','- That makes it hard.\n- Just get rid of the dog!',-1),(138553,16,98771,98824,'01:08:35.480','01:08:37.675','- That\'s not gonna happen obviously.\n- Please keep your voice down.',-1),(138554,16,98825,98898,'01:08:37.749','01:08:40.775','- Me keep my voice down?\n- Just do it. Just get rid of the dog!',-1),(138555,16,98900,98947,'01:08:40.852','01:08:42.820','Everybody gets rid of their dogs.\nIt\'s just a dog.',-1),(138556,16,98949,99025,'01:08:42.887','01:08:46.050','And I\'m just a husband. You gonna\nget rid of me when I misbehave?',-1),(138557,16,99026,99073,'01:08:46.124','01:08:48.058','- I\'ve thought about it.\n- Well, that makes two of us.',-1),(138558,16,99075,99132,'01:08:48.126','01:08:50.526','- What do you have to complain about?\n- What do I-',-1),(138559,16,99134,99206,'01:08:50.595','01:08:53.621','- Because you\'re such a joy to be around?\n- You\'re such a jerk.',-1),(138560,16,99208,99277,'01:08:53.698','01:08:56.565','So nice to walk in the door,\nfeel like you\'re joining a chain gang.',-1),(138561,16,99279,99314,'01:08:56.634','01:08:58.124','<i>Just a jerk!</i>',-1),(138562,16,99399,99477,'01:09:01.639','01:09:04.904','Stop it! It\'s your fault.',-1),(138563,16,99479,99554,'01:09:04.976','01:09:08.104','- You gotta be kidding me?\n- Nope.',-1),(138564,16,99556,99636,'01:09:08.179','01:09:11.512','<i>Just for a couple of days\ntill things cool down at home.</i>',-1),(138565,16,99694,99742,'01:09:13.952','01:09:15.920','A couple days will be all right.',-1),(138566,16,99743,99802,'01:09:15.987','01:09:18.421','You guys know each other.\nYou\'ll be comfortable.',-1),(138567,16,99803,99905,'01:09:18.490','01:09:22.722','- Want a beer?\n- No, I\'m fine. Thanks. Are you moving?',-1),(138568,16,99907,99970,'01:09:22.794','01:09:25.456','- Yeah.\n<i>- Where?</i>',-1),(138569,16,99972,100020,'01:09:25.530','01:09:27.521','New York.',-1),(138570,16,100022,100114,'01:09:27.599','01:09:31.433','<i>The Gray Lady came a-courtin\'.</i>',-1),(138571,16,100116,100185,'01:09:31.503','01:09:34.404','The <i>Times</i> offered you\na permanent job?',-1),(138572,16,100187,100252,'01:09:34.472','01:09:37.202','I gave Arnie my notice last week.',-1),(138573,16,100254,100329,'01:09:37.275','01:09:40.403','- You didn\'t say anything.\n<i>- I know. I\'m sorry.</i>',-1),(138574,16,100331,100465,'01:09:40.478','01:09:46.075','I just- It all happened so fast,\nI\'m not even used to the idea yet.',-1),(138575,16,100467,100557,'01:09:46.150','01:09:49.916','That\'s great. The <i>New York Times.</i>',-1),(138576,16,100559,100625,'01:09:49.988','01:09:52.718','It\'s what we always dreamed of.',-1),(138577,16,100707,100802,'01:09:56.160','01:10:00.096','Well, congratulations.\nI mean, you deserve it.',-1),(138578,16,100803,100886,'01:10:00.164','01:10:03.622','- Yeah.\n- Thanks for looking after Marley.',-1),(138579,16,100888,100945,'01:10:03.701','01:10:06.067','- Yeah.\n- He\'s eating your briefcase right now.',-1),(138580,16,100947,101011,'01:10:06.137','01:10:08.799','- Shit!\n<i>- Marley. Marley, no.</i>',-1),(138581,16,101012,101104,'01:10:08.873','01:10:12.707','- Two days, John. I\'m serious.\n- Sorry.',-1),(138582,16,101193,101261,'01:10:16.381','01:10:19.214','Sorry. I didn\'t mean to wake you.',-1),(138583,16,101262,101307,'01:10:19.284','01:10:21.149','I wasn\'t, uh, sleeping.',-1),(138584,16,101373,101467,'01:10:23.888','01:10:27.824','<i>- Where\'s Marley?</i>\n- Sebastian\'s gonna watch him for a few days.',-1),(138585,16,101469,101535,'01:10:27.892','01:10:30.656','Mm-hmm. I\'d love to see that.',-1),(138586,16,101537,101662,'01:10:30.728','01:10:35.927','<i>Just until I can find\na more permanent home.</i>',-1),(138587,16,101700,101785,'01:10:37.502','01:10:41.063','- This is his permanent home, John.\n- Mmm.',-1),(138588,16,101787,101835,'01:10:41.139','01:10:43.130','<i>Marley\'s not going anywhere.</i>\n<i>Honey, I\'m sorry.</i>',-1),(138589,16,101836,101901,'01:10:43.207','01:10:45.903','I just got overwhelmed.',-1),(138590,16,101903,102020,'01:10:45.977','01:10:50.846','<i>- No one tells you how hard this is all gonna be.</i>\n- Which part?',-1),(138591,16,102021,102096,'01:10:50.915','01:10:54.009','All of it:',-1),(138592,16,102098,102173,'01:10:54.085','01:10:57.248','Marriage, being a parent.',-1),(138593,16,102175,102266,'01:10:57.322','01:11:01.122','<i>It\'s the hardest job in the world</i>\n<i>and nobody prepares you for that.</i>',-1),(138594,16,102268,102339,'01:11:01.192','01:11:04.161','Nobody tells you how much\nyou have to give up.',-1),(138595,16,102341,102452,'01:11:04.228','01:11:08.858','I feel like they do tell you,\nbut you don\'t listen...',-1),(138596,16,102454,102530,'01:11:08.933','01:11:12.096','or you think, \"Ah, they\'re just miserable.\"',-1),(138597,16,102642,102728,'01:11:16.774','01:11:20.335','I\'ve given up so much\nof what made me who I am.',-1),(138598,16,102761,102808,'01:11:21.713','01:11:23.681','But I can\'t say that because...',-1),(138599,16,102809,102877,'01:11:23.748','01:11:26.581','I\'m a very bad person if I say that.',-1),(138600,16,102925,102985,'01:11:28.553','01:11:31.044','But I feel it. I really do.',-1),(138601,16,102986,103093,'01:11:31.122','01:11:35.582','I feel it sometimes. I just-',-1),(138602,16,103095,103148,'01:11:35.660','01:11:37.855','I just want you to know that.',-1),(138603,16,103150,103243,'01:11:37.929','01:11:41.797','I do know that.\nAnd you can say it. I say it.',-1),(138604,16,103244,103319,'01:11:41.866','01:11:44.994','But I did make a choice.',-1),(138605,16,103321,103436,'01:11:45.069','01:11:49.870','I made a choice, and even\nif it\'s harder than I thought...',-1),(138606,16,103438,103487,'01:11:49.941','01:11:51.966','I don\'t regret it.',-1),(138607,16,103489,103540,'01:1