11736,11801,'00:08:09.000','00:08:11.731','The judgment will just\nabout empty his savings.',-1),(145836,7,11806,11833,'00:08:11.920','00:08:13.046','Moment.',-1),(145837,7,11853,11912,'00:08:13.880','00:08:16.360','Your report is light\nin another area.',-1),(145838,7,11916,11957,'00:08:16.520','00:08:18.249','His personal life.',-1),(145839,7,11961,12005,'00:08:18.400','00:08:20.243','Anything you chose\nnot to disclose?',-1),(145840,7,12036,12073,'00:08:21.520','00:08:23.045','Nothing that\nwarranted inclusion.',-1),(145841,7,12076,12118,'00:08:23.200','00:08:24.929','Does that mean yes or no?',-1),(145842,7,12121,12221,'00:08:25.080','00:08:29.210','I think what Miss Salander means, and\nI agree, is that everyone has a right',-1),(145843,7,12225,12301,'00:08:29.400','00:08:32.563','to a certain amount of privacy,\neven if they\'re being investigated.',-1),(145844,7,12305,12369,'00:08:32.720','00:08:35.405','Not in this case.\nI need to know anything about him',-1),(145845,7,12373,12460,'00:08:35.560','00:08:39.167','I might find unsavory,\neven if she doesn\'t.',-1),(145846,7,12548,12600,'00:08:42.840','00:08:45.002','He\'s had a longstanding\nsexual relationship',-1),(145847,7,12603,12701,'00:08:45.160','00:08:49.245','with his co-editor of the magazine.\nIt wrecked his marriage but not hers.',-1),(145848,7,12705,12759,'00:08:49.400','00:08:51.641','Sometimes he performs\ncunnilingus.',-1),(145849,7,12764,12819,'00:08:51.840','00:08:54.161','Not often enough, in my opinion.',-1),(145850,7,12840,12887,'00:08:55.000','00:08:56.968','No, you\'re right not\nto include that.',-1),(145851,7,12890,12923,'00:08:57.120','00:08:58.485','I know.',-1),(145852,7,14268,14340,'00:09:54.520','00:09:57.524','You needed a better attorney.\nYou needed your sister.',-1),(145853,7,14344,14375,'00:09:57.680','00:09:58.966','She offered. He declined.',-1),(145854,7,14379,14416,'00:09:59.160','00:10:00.685','As she hoped. Never a good idea.',-1),(145855,7,14420,14479,'00:10:00.840','00:10:03.320','Mixing family and business.\nI would\'ve lost anyway.',-1),(145856,7,14483,14568,'00:10:03.480','00:10:07.007','It wasn\'t about Mikael.\nIt was about WennerstrÃ¶m sending a message',-1),(145857,7,14571,14647,'00:10:07.160','00:10:10.323','to the press and the FSA,\nsaying, \"Don\'t ask questions.\"',-1),(145858,7,14653,14678,'00:10:10.560','00:10:11.607','Cheer up.',-1),(145859,7,14780,14804,'00:10:15.840','00:10:16.841','Dad.',-1),(145860,7,14808,14868,'00:10:17.000','00:10:19.526','Nilla, you don\'t have\nto worry about me.',-1),(145861,7,14873,14915,'00:10:19.720','00:10:21.484','Mom\'s worried. About me?',-1),(145862,7,14937,14968,'00:10:22.400','00:10:23.686','About the money.',-1),(145863,7,16547,16577,'00:11:29.480','00:11:30.720','Good evening.',-1),(145864,7,16651,16709,'00:11:33.800','00:11:36.246','Nilla? What are you doing?',-1),(145865,7,16713,16740,'00:11:36.400','00:11:37.526','Nothing.',-1),(145866,7,16744,16773,'00:11:37.680','00:11:38.886','Are you serious?',-1),(145867,7,16776,16862,'00:11:39.040','00:11:42.601','I don\'t wanna talk about it\nsince I know you won\'t approve.',-1),(145868,7,16867,16893,'00:11:42.800','00:11:43.881','Of, um...?',-1),(145869,7,16905,16937,'00:11:44.400','00:11:45.731','Nilla. Light of Life.',-1),(145870,7,16941,16973,'00:11:45.880','00:11:47.245','Light of what?',-1),(145871,7,17193,17224,'00:11:56.400','00:11:57.686','<i>Herr Blomkvist.</i>',-1),(145872,7,17228,17260,'00:11:57.840','00:11:59.171','<i>Yea h. Forgive me for intruding</i>',-1),(145873,7,17264,17315,'00:11:59.360','00:12:01.488','<i>on Christmas.\nMy name is Dirch Frode.</i>',-1),(145874,7,17319,17414,'00:12:01.640','00:12:05.611','I\'m an attorney. I represent Henrik Vanger.\nPerhaps you\'ve heard of him?',-1),(145875,7,17418,17445,'00:12:05.760','00:12:06.886','Yeah, of course I have.',-1),(145876,7,17449,17507,'00:12:07.080','00:12:09.481','<i>He\'d love to talk to you\nabout a private matter.</i>',-1),(145877,7,17511,17584,'00:12:09.640','00:12:12.689','This is an awkward moment.',-1),(145878,7,17588,17663,'00:12:12.840','00:12:15.969','<i>Oh, I\'m sorry. I\'m about to sit\ndown to a Christmas dinner myself.</i>',-1),(145879,7,17666,17716,'00:12:16.120','00:12:18.202','No, that\'s not exactly\nwhat I meant.',-1),(145880,7,17720,17778,'00:12:18.360','00:12:20.761','You\'re referring to your\nrecent legal problems.',-1),(145881,7,17782,17827,'00:12:20.920','00:12:22.809','That has provided us\nwith much amusement.',-1),(145882,7,17831,17855,'00:12:22.960','00:12:23.961','I\'m sorry?',-1),(145883,7,17858,17921,'00:12:24.120','00:12:26.726','<i>Herr Vanger has little love\nfor Herr WennerstrÃ¶m either.</i>',-1),(145884,7,17925,17986,'00:12:26.880','00:12:29.451','Have him call me.\nBut he would love to speak to you',-1),(145885,7,17991,18053,'00:12:29.640','00:12:32.211','in person, if possible.\nUp north.',-1),(145886,7,18056,18104,'00:12:32.360','00:12:34.362','<i>In Hedestad.\nThat\'s not gonna be possible.</i>',-1),(145887,7,18109,18177,'00:12:34.560','00:12:37.404','<i>Herr Blomkvist, he\'s far too old\nto go to Stockholm. Please.</i>',-1),(145888,7,18181,18234,'00:12:37.560','00:12:39.767','Be so kind as to consider.',-1),(145889,7,18238,18305,'00:12:39.920','00:12:42.730','<i>Hedestad is lovely\nin the winter.</i>',-1),(145890,7,18309,18406,'00:12:42.880','00:12:46.930','I\'ll call you back on this number.\nOkay?',-1),(145891,7,18726,18791,'00:13:00.280','00:13:02.965','Usually when I wake up in\na cold bed it\'s at home.',-1),(145892,7,18794,18837,'00:13:03.120','00:13:04.884','I\'m sorry. What are you doing?',-1),(145893,7,18840,18913,'00:13:05.040','00:13:08.044','I\'m writing a press release.\nSaying?',-1),(145894,7,18990,19049,'00:13:11.280','00:13:13.726','You\'re taking over as\npublisher, you\'re very sorry',-1),(145895,7,19053,19108,'00:13:13.880','00:13:16.167','for any nuisance Mr\n. WennerstrÃ¶m was caused,',-1),(145896,7,19111,19184,'00:13:16.320','00:13:19.369','and I can\'t be reached for comment.\nAre you giving up?',-1),(145897,7,19188,19219,'00:13:19.520','00:13:20.806','Stepping aside.',-1),(145898,7,19227,19269,'00:13:21.160','00:13:22.889','This makes me sick.',-1),(145899,7,20137,20196,'00:13:59.080','00:14:01.526','- First time in Hedestad?\n- And the last.',-1),(145900,7,20200,20257,'00:14:01.680','00:14:04.047','Oh, don\'t say that.\nIt\'s lovely in the spring.',-1),(145901,7,20260,20327,'00:14:04.200','00:14:06.965','You said it would be\nlovely in the winter.',-1),(145902,7,20330,20378,'00:14:07.120','00:14:09.088','Well, this is unseasonable.',-1),(145903,7,20382,20443,'00:14:09.280','00:14:11.806','Well, I\'ll be on the 4:30\ntrain back to Stockholm.',-1),(145904,7,20447,20477,'00:14:11.960','00:14:13.246','Unless we get snowed in.',-1),(145905,7,20499,20526,'00:14:14.160','00:14:15.286','I\'m joking...',-1),(145906,7,20530,20599,'00:14:15.440','00:14:18.330','You\'ll be home tonight,\nif that\'s what you wish.',-1),(145907,7,21556,21582,'00:14:58.200','00:14:59.281','Welcome.',-1),(145908,7,21587,21612,'00:14:59.480','00:15:00.527','Come inside.',-1),(145909,7,21635,21675,'00:15:01.480','00:15:03.130','It\'s warm.',-1),(145910,7,21680,21713,'00:15:03.360','00:15:04.725','How do you do?',-1),(145911,7,21867,21904,'00:15:11.160','00:15:12.685','So,',-1),(145912,7,21935,21968,'00:15:13.960','00:15:15.371','what do you know about me?',-1),(145913,7,21983,22057,'00:15:15.960','00:15:19.043','You used to run one of the largest\nindustrial firms in the country.',-1),(145914,7,22060,22119,'00:15:19.200','00:15:21.646','\"Used to.\" That\'s correct.\nOh, I didn\'t mean that.',-1),(145915,7,22123,22166,'00:15:21.800','00:15:23.609','Should I stay? No.',-1),(145916,7,22178,22256,'00:15:24.120','00:15:27.363','My grandfather forged the tracks',-1),(145917,7,22260,22312,'00:15:27.520','00:15:29.682','that the 4:30 train\nwill take you home on.',-1),(145918,7,22326,22374,'00:15:30.280','00:15:32.282','We stitched this\ncountry together.'