ies N</i>',-1),(145938,7,24237,24269,'00:16:49.880','00:16:51.211','No, thank you.',-1),(145939,7,24344,24374,'00:16:54.360','00:16:55.600','This <i>is</i> Harriet.',-1),(145940,7,24412,24480,'00:16:57.200','00:17:00.010','The granddaughter of\nmy brother Richard.',-1),(145941,7,24493,24565,'00:17:00.560','00:17:03.564','Richard was a Nazi\nof the first order,',-1),(145942,7,24573,24700,'00:17:03.880','00:17:09.205','joining the Nationalist Socialist\nFreedom League when he was 17.',-1),(145943,7,24704,24815,'00:17:09.360','00:17:13.968','Isn\'t it interesting how fascists always\nsteal the word \"freedom\"? Heh, heh.',-1),(145944,7,24865,24956,'00:17:16.080','00:17:19.846','Oh, the 4:30. Yes, I know. Okay.',-1),(145945,7,24960,25076,'00:17:20.000','00:17:24.847','Anyway, Richard died a martyr\nto the Nazi cause in 1940.',-1),(145946,7,25080,25143,'00:17:25.000','00:17:27.651','Missed all the real excitement.',-1),(145947,7,25152,25251,'00:17:28.000','00:17:32.130','But not the opportunity to regularly\nbeat his wife, Margareta,',-1),(145948,7,25255,25297,'00:17:32.320','00:17:34.049','and their son, Gottfried.',-1),(145949,7,25301,25342,'00:17:34.240','00:17:35.924','Now, Gottfried,\nHarriet\'s father,',-1),(145950,7,25345,25411,'00:17:36.080','00:17:38.811','was what they used to\ncall a good-time Charlie.',-1),(145951,7,25415,25478,'00:17:38.960','00:17:41.611','They still call them that.\nDo they? Okay.',-1),(145952,7,25482,25539,'00:17:41.760','00:17:44.161','He was a charmer, a\nladies\' man and a drunk.',-1),(145953,7,25543,25614,'00:17:44.320','00:17:47.290','In other words, a born salesman.\nWhich he did for the company,',-1),(145954,7,25618,25684,'00:17:47.440','00:17:50.171','traveling around and taking\nclients out to dinner.',-1),(145955,7,25687,25743,'00:17:50.320','00:17:52.641','Well, somebody\'s gotta do it.\nThat\'s right.',-1),(145956,7,25748,25820,'00:17:52.840','00:17:55.844','Anyway, ahem, he died in 1965.',-1),(145957,7,25824,25872,'00:17:56.000','00:17:58.002','Drowned, drunk,\nhere on the island.',-1),(145958,7,25875,25982,'00:17:58.160','00:18:02.609','His wife, Isabella, who had been pretty\nmuch useless as a parent before,',-1),(145959,7,25986,26043,'00:18:02.760','00:18:05.127','became even more so\nafter his death,',-1),(145960,7,26046,26111,'00:18:05.280','00:18:07.965','which is when I began\nlooking after the children.',-1),(145961,7,26114,26186,'00:18:08.120','00:18:11.124','Martin, who runs Vanger\nIndustries, now that I\'m retired.',-1),(145962,7,26190,26230,'00:18:11.280','00:18:12.930','That\'s right, I Googled him.',-1),(145963,7,26233,26262,'00:18:13.080','00:18:14.286','And Harriet.',-1),(145964,7,26289,26386,'00:18:15.400','00:18:19.450','Ah. She was bright, curious,',-1),(145965,7,26399,26469,'00:18:19.960','00:18:22.884','a winning combination\nin any person.',-1),(145966,7,26483,26555,'00:18:23.480','00:18:26.484','And beautiful. Yeah.',-1),(145967,7,26588,26632,'00:18:27.840','00:18:29.683','Something happened to her?',-1),(145968,7,26636,26689,'00:18:29.840','00:18:32.081','Someone in the family\nmurdered Harriet,',-1),(145969,7,26706,26753,'00:18:32.760','00:18:34.728','and for the past 40 years,',-1),(145970,7,26758,26812,'00:18:34.920','00:18:37.207','has been trying to\ndrive me insane.',-1),(145971,7,26864,26938,'00:18:39.360','00:18:42.443','<i>It was\nSeptember 24th, 1966.</i>',-1),(145972,7,26943,26985,'00:18:42.640','00:18:44.404','A Saturday.',-1),(145973,7,26990,27030,'00:18:44.600','00:18:46.284','Harriet was 16.',-1),(145974,7,27036,27062,'00:18:46.520','00:18:47.601','My brothers',-1),(145975,7,27066,27165,'00:18:47.760','00:18:51.890','<i>and their wives and their children and\ngrandchildren were all gathered here</i>',-1),(145976,7,27168,27242,'00:18:52.040','00:18:55.089','<i>for our loathsome annual\nboard meeting and dinner.</i>',-1),(145977,7,27245,27343,'00:18:55.240','00:18:59.325','<i>It was also the day the yacht\nclub held their autumn parade.</i>',-1),(145978,7,27347,27423,'00:18:59.480','00:19:02.643','<i>Harriet, with one or two school\nfriends, went into town to see it.</i>',-1),(145979,7,27427,27501,'00:19:02.800','00:19:05.883','She returned a\nlittle after 2:00.',-1),(145980,7,27505,27599,'00:19:06.080','00:19:09.971','<i>She came into the parlor.\nShe asked if she could talk to me.</i>',-1),(145981,7,27602,27656,'00:19:10.120','00:19:12.361','I honestly don\'t remember\nwhat I was doing',-1),(145982,7,27660,27705,'00:19:12.520','00:19:14.409','that I thought was\nmore important,',-1),(145983,7,27709,27768,'00:19:14.560','00:19:17.040','<i>but I told her to give\nme a few minutes.</i>',-1),(145984,7,27810,27925,'00:19:18.760','00:19:23.561','It was during those few minutes\nthat something else occurred.',-1),(145985,7,27992,28075,'00:19:26.360','00:19:29.807','<i>The accident had nothing\nto do with Harriet,</i>',-1),(145986,7,28079,28106,'00:19:29.960','00:19:31.086','and yet everything.',-1),(145987,7,28129,28206,'00:19:32.080','00:19:35.289','<i>Heh. It was chaos as everybody\nput down what they were doing.</i>',-1),(145988,7,28211,28267,'00:19:35.480','00:19:37.801','<i>Police, ambulance, fire brigade,</i>',-1),(145989,7,28271,28365,'00:19:37.960','00:19:41.885','<i>reporters, photographers, onlookers\nall quickly arrived from town</i>',-1),(145990,7,28368,28477,'00:19:42.040','00:19:46.568','<i>just as we on the island, the family,\nhurried to the bridge from our side.</i>',-1),(145991,7,28481,28515,'00:19:46.720','00:19:48.165','<i>The driver of the car,</i>',-1),(145992,7,28519,28557,'00:19:48.320','00:19:49.890','a man named Aronsson,',-1),(145993,7,28561,28617,'00:19:50.080','00:19:52.401','<i>was pinned and severely injured.</i>',-1),(145994,7,28621,28691,'00:19:52.560','00:19:55.484','<i>We tried desperately to pry\nhim loose with our hands</i>',-1),(145995,7,28695,28752,'00:19:55.640','00:19:58.041','<i>since metal tools might spark.</i>',-1),(145996,7,28785,28875,'00:19:59.400','00:20:03.166','<i>It was an hour after the crash\nthat Harriet was in the kitchen.</i>',-1),(145997,7,28879,28930,'00:20:03.320','00:20:05.448','Anna herself saw her.',-1),(145998,7,29030,29147,'00:20:09.600','00:20:14.481','<i>Well, we finally got poor Aronsson out\nof his car and off to the hospital.</i>',-1),(145999,7,29160,29235,'00:20:15.000','00:20:18.163','<i>Just as we from our side</i>',-1),(146000,7,29240,29312,'00:20:18.360','00:20:21.364','<i>slowly drifted back\nto the house.</i>',-1),(146001,7,29359,29413,'00:20:23.320','00:20:25.561','<i>The sun was down, the\nexcitement over.</i>',-1),(146002,7,29422,29473,'00:20:25.920','00:20:28.082','<i>We sat down to dinner.</i>',-1),(146003,7,29477,29516,'00:20:28.240','00:20:29.844','<i>It was then that I noticed.</i>',-1),(146004,7,29528,29563,'00:20:30.360','00:20:31.805','<i>Harriet wasn\'t there.</i>',-1),(146005,7,29592,29640,'00:20:33.040','00:20:35.008','<i>And she wasn\'t there\nthe next morning.</i>',-1),(146006,7,29662,29687,'00:20:35.920','00:20:36.967','<i>Or the next.</i>',-1),(146007,7,29704,29738,'00:20:37.680','00:20:39.091','Or the next 40 years.',-1),(146008,7,29827,29868,'00:20:42.800','00:20:44.529','<i>What was she going to tell me?</i>',-1),(146009,7,29873,29951,'00:20:44.720','00:20:47.963','Why didn\'t I make time for her?\nWhy didn\'t I listen?',-1),(146010,7,29954,30036,'00:20:48.120','00:20:51.522','And she couldn\'t have just run away?\nNo. Not without being seen.',-1),(146011,7,30040,30079,'00:20:51.680','00:20:53.330','The firemen stayed out all night',-1),(146012,7,30084,30131,'00:20:53.520','00:20:55.488','<i>on the bridge pumping\nup gasoline.</i>',-1),(146013,7,30135,30203,'00:20:55.640','00:20:58.484','<i>No one swam across\nor took a boat.</i>',-1),(146014,7,30207,30272,'00:20:58.640','00:21:01.371','All the boats were still\ntied up on this side Sunday.',-1),(146015,7,30276,30339,'00:21:01.520','00:21:04.126','Believe me, I checked.',-1),(146016,7,30388,30434,'00:21:06.200','00:21:08.123','She couldn\'t have\njust fallen and drowned?',-1),(146017,7,30438,30553,'00:21:08.280','00:21:13.047','No. The currents aren\'t strong here.\nAnything that falls in the water turns up.',-1),(146018,7,30556,30587,'00:21:13.200','00:21:14.486','Like her father.',-1),(146019,7,30591,30648,'00:21:14.640','00:21:17.041','His body didn\'t drift\nmore than 10 meters',-1),(146020,7,30652,30710,'00:21:17.200','00:21:19.601','when he drowned the year before.',-1),(146021,7,30714,30790,'00:21:19.760','00:21:22.923','Oh, no. Someone killed her.',-1),(146022,7,30793,30857,'00:21:23.080','00:21:25.731','Someone on the island that day.',-1),(146023,7,30861,30909,'00:21:25.880','00:21:27.882','Someone close enough to know',-1),(146024,7,30912,31018,'00:21:28.040','00:21:32.443','what she used to give me\neach year on my birthday.',-1),(146025,7,31065,31117,'00:21:34.400','00:21:36.562','Those are from her.',-1),(146026,7,31128,31212,'00:21:37.040','00:21:40.522','And the rest, from her killer.',-1),(146027,7,31521,31552,'00:21:53.400','00:21:54.686','Who knows about these?',-1),(146028,7,31556,31640,'00:21:54.840','00:21:58.367','There\'s me, the\npolice, the killer,',-1),(146029,7,31649,31674,'00:21:58.720','00:21:59.767','and now you.',-1),(146030,7,31891,31949,'00:22:08.800','00:22:11.246','<i>After the police\ninvestigation evaporated,</i>',-1),(146031,7,31953,32021,'00:22:11.400','00:22:14.210','<i>I kept at it, studying all\nthe information there was.</i>',-1),(146032,7,32033,32126,'00:22:14.720','00:22:18.611','I have spent half my life examining\nthe events of a single day.',-1),(146033,7,32130,32182,'00:22:18.760','00:22:20.922','I understand your frustration,',-1),(146034,7,32185,32254,'00:22:21.080','00:22:23.924','but what you\'re asking me to\ndo, it\'s a waste of money.',-1),(146035,7,32257,32333,'00:22:24.080','00:22:27.243','But we haven\'t discussed your fee.\nWe don\'t need to.',-1),(146036,7,32337,32372,'00:22:27.400','00:22:28.845','Thank you.',-1),(146037,7,32376,32463,'00:22:29.000','00:22:32.641','I can\'t find something you\'ve\nbeen unable to find in 40 years.',-1),(146038,7,32467,32559,'00:22:32.800','00:22:36.646','You don\'t know that.\nYou have a very keen investigative mind.',-1),(146039,7,32575,32609,'00:22:37.320','00:22:38.731','Here\'s what I propose:',-1),(146040,7,32613,32655,'00:22:38.880','00:22:40.644','You come stay on the island.',-1),(146041,7,32659,32737,'00:22:40.800','00:22:44.043','I have a nice little cottage\nby the water you can use.',-1),(146042,7,32740,32786,'00:22:44.200','00:22:46.123','You study the\nmaterial I send you.',-1),(146043,7,32790,32844,'00:22:46.280','00:22:48.521','You find something I\'ve\nmissed or you don\'t.',-1),(146044,7,32849,32923,'00:22:48.720','00:22:51.803','What you\'re asking me to do is set\naside my life and career for...',-1),(146045,7,32927,32976,'00:22:51.960','00:22:54.008','Think of this as a\nwell-deserved holiday.',-1),(146046,7,32979,33089,'00:22:54.160','00:22:58.722','A way of avoiding all those people that\nyou might want to avoid right now.',-1),(146047,7,33093,33154,'00:22:58.880','00:23:01.451','As for compensation, I\'ll\npay you double your salary',-1),(146048,7,33158,33198,'00:23:01.600','00:23:03.284','for as many months as it takes.',-1),(146049,7,33203,33270,'00:23:03.480','00:23:06.290','Quadruple it if you solve the mystery.\nHerr Vanger...',-1),(146050,7,33274,33326,'00:23:06.440','00:23:08.602','I\'m not done.\nI will throw in one more thing,',-1),(146051,7,33330,33382,'00:23:08.760','00:23:10.922','even though you\'re a\nterrible negotiator.',-1),(146052,7,33385,33448,'00:23:11.080','00:23:13.686','It\'s something you want\nmore than anything else,',-1),(146053,7,33452,33535,'00:23:13.840','00:23:17.322','and it can\'t be bought at any price.\nSo let me give it to you.',-1),(146054,7,33552,33622,'00:23:18.040','00:23:20.930','Hans-Erik WennerstrÃ¶m.',-1),(146055,7,33643,33698,'00:23:21.800','00:23:24.121','He began his career\nworking for me,',-1),(146056,7,33702,33791,'00:23:24.280','00:23:27.966','and I have followed it with\ninterest, shall we say, ever since.',-1),(146057,7,33863,33896,'00:23:30.960','00:23:32.371','You were right about him.',-1),(146058,7,33917,33968,'00:23:33.240','00:23:35.368','You just couldn\'t prove it.',-1),(146059,7,34703,34784,'00:24:05.960','00:24:09.362','We\'re in the middle of the worst crisis\never, and you\'re writing a memoir.',-1),(146060,7,34788,34876,'00:24:09.520','00:24:13.206','You fired me. I need something to do.\nYou fired you.',-1),(146061,7,34927,34977,'00:24:15.320','00:24:17.402','I need you here, not\nthe North Pole.',-1),(146062,7,34982,35040,'00:24:17.600','00:24:20.001','Mikael, you know what this\nis going to look like.',-1),(146063,7,35043,35093,'00:24:20.160','00:24:22.242','Like I\'ve been gutted.\nI\'m running away. I am.',-1),(146064,7,35097,35166,'00:24:22.400','00:24:25.290','WennerstrÃ¶m wants to see me wave\na white flag, not a red flag.',-1),(146065,7,35171,35247,'00:24:25.480','00:24:28.643','If it looks like there\'s a problem\nbetween us, it\'ll satisfy him.',-1),(146066,7,35251,35283,'00:24:28.800','00:24:30.165','There is a problem between us.',-1),(146067,7,35288,35350,'00:24:30.360','00:24:32.931','He won\'t be satisfied\nuntil he shuts us down.',-1),(146068,7,35365,35459,'00:24:33.560','00:24:37.485','You\'re leaving me to fight him alone.\nIt\'s four hours by train.',-1),(146069,7,35585,35639,'00:24:42.720','00:24:44.961','It\'s not the North Pole.',-1),(146070,7,36637,36675,'00:25:26.560','00:25:28.164','Hey, hey...',-1),(146071,7,38057,38132,'00:26:25.720','00:26:28.849','<i>Network busy.\nPlease try again later.</i>',-1),(146072,7,38384,38467,'00:26:39.360','00:26:42.807','<i>Network busy.\nPlease try again later.</i>',-1),(146073,7,38615,38651,'00:26:48.960','00:26:50.485','What?',-1),(146074,7,38663,38691,'00:26:50.960','00:26:52.166','Some milk?',-1),(146075,7,39147,39229,'00:27:11.160','00:27:14.562','<i>Network busy.\nPlease try again later.</i>',-1),(146076,7,39276,39338,'00:27:16.520','00:27:19.091','Oh, yeah. These as well.',-1),(146077,7,40242,40275,'00:27:56.760','00:27:58.125','You\'re Mr. Palmgren\'s daughter?',-1),(146078,7,40279,40321,'00:27:58.320','00:28:00.049','His ward.\nHe doesn\'t have a daughter.',-1),(146079,7,40367,40402,'00:28:01.960','00:28:03.450','Please.',-1),(146080,7,40436,40500,'00:28:04.840','00:28:07.525','He\'s had severe\ncerebral hemorrhaging,',-1),(146081,7,40504,40589,'00:28:07.680','00:28:11.241','<i>either from the fall itself or from\na stroke that led to the fall.</i>',-1),(146082,7,40594,40639,'00:28:11.440','00:28:13.329','<i>His blood pressure\nis still high.</i>',-1),(146083,7,40643,40715,'00:28:13.480','00:28:16.484','<i>I\'m hopeful he\'ll regain consciousness,\nbut that\'s not assured.</i>',-1),(146084,7,40719,40775,'00:28:16.640','00:28:18.961','<i>And it\'s possible,\neven if he does,</i>',-1),(146085,7,40778,40846,'00:28:19.120','00:28:21.930','<i>that there will be\nneurological damage.</i>',-1),(146086,7,41361,41405,'00:28:43.400','00:28:45.209','Oh, jeez.',-1),(146087,7,41532,41574,'00:28:50.520','00:28:52.284','Hi. I\'m Gunnar.',-1),(146088,7,41601,41626,'00:28:53.400','00:28:54.447','The caretaker.',-1),(146089,7,41630,41687,'00:28:54.600','00:28:56.967','Oh, hey, Gunnar. Come in. Okay.',-1),(146090,7,41796,41860,'00:29:01.520','00:29:04.171','You want to put it in there?\nOkay.',-1),(146091,7,42053,42095,'00:29:12.240','00:29:13.969','You\'re an author.',-1),(146092,7,42098,42196,'00:29:14.120','00:29:18.205','Well, I\'m doing a\nbiography of Herr Vanger.',-1),(146093,7,42206,42238,'00:29:18.600','00:29:19.931','Oh.',-1),(146094,7,42241,42319,'00:29:20.080','00:29:23.323','I saw you on television.\nThat\'s unfortunate.',-1),(146095,7,42323,42366,'00:29:23.480','00:29:25.289','Bit of trouble, I guess.',-1),(146096,7,42388,42450,'00:29:26.200','00:29:28.771','No jail time though.\nThat\'s good. No.',-1),(146097,7,42467,42526,'00:29:29.480','00:29:31.926','Cost you a lot of\nmoney though, yeah?',-1),(146098,7,42573,42606,'00:29:33.880','00:29:35.291','There.',-1),(146099,7,42682,42792,'00:29:38.440','00:29:43.002','The entire island\nis owned by my family.',-1),(146100,7,42829,42953,'00:29:44.560','00:29:49.726','Your closest neighbor\nis my brother Harald,',-1),(146101,7,42974,43030,'00:29:50.600','00:29:52.921','another Nazi, if\nyou can believe.',-1),(146102,7,43033,43071,'00:29:53.080','00:29:54.650','Two in the family.',-1),(146103,7,43075,43175,'00:29:54.800','00:29:58.964','Oh, yes, he\'s quite\ndetestable, to put it nicely.',-1),(146104,7,43178,43261,'00:29:59.120','00:30:02.567','But you\'ll probably never see him.\nHe\'s a recluse.',-1),(146105,7,43265,43332,'00:30:02.720','00:30:05.530','He was there that day?\nIndeed, he was.',-1),(146106,7,43336,43419,'00:30:05.680','00:30:09.162','His daughter, Cecilia,\nlives over there.',-1),(146107,7,43432,43464,'00:30:09.680','00:30:11.011','They don\'t speak.',-1),(146108,7,43468,43517,'00:30:11.200','00:30:13.248','Does anybody speak to\nanybody on this island?',-1),(146109,7,43521,43598,'00:30:13.400','00:30:16.609','Ha, ha. Actually, Isabella,\nHarriet\'s mother, who lives there,',-1),(146110,7,43602,43695,'00:30:16.760','00:30:20.651','she speaks to Harald, which is one\nof the reasons I don\'t speak to her.',-1),(146111,7,43699,43726,'00:30:20.800','00:30:21.926','Right.',-1),(146112,7,43729,43806,'00:30:22.080','00:30:25.289','Cecilia\'s brother, Birger,\nlives over there.',-1),(146113,7,43810,43850,'00:30:25.440','00:30:27.090','Who doesn\'t he speak to?',-1),(146114,7,43853,43880,'00:30:27.240','00:30:28.366','You, probably.',-1),(146115,7,43884,43969,'00:30:28.520','00:30:32.047','But you wouldn\'t want him to.\nHe can be just as unpleasant as Harald.',-1),(146116,7,43972,44016,'00:30:32.200','00:30:34.009','Quickly losing track\nof who\'s who here.',-1),(146117,7,44019,44091,'00:30:34.160','00:30:37.164','Ho-ho-ho.\nHow you\'ll wish it were always so.',-1),(146118,7,44095,44190,'00:30:37.320','00:30:41.291','Soon you will know us all only\ntoo well, with my apologies.',-1),(146119,7,44197,44319,'00:30:41.560','00:30:46.646','Now, out there, my grandnephew\nMartin\'s house, Harriet\'s brother.',-1),(146120,7,44323,44357,'00:30:46.800','00:30:48.211','Who speaks to him?',-1),(146121,7,44360,44441,'00:30:48.360','00:30:51.728','I speak to him. He runs the company\nnow, as I think I told you.',-1),(146122,7,44494,44582,'00:30:53.920','00:30:57.606','Oh. Someone\'s shooting his dinner.\nGunnar, probably.',-1),(146123,7,44586,44619,'00:30:57.760','00:30:59.125','Oh, yes, I met him earlier.',-1),(146124,7,44622,44709,'00:30:59.280','00:31:02.887','He was 19 when\nHarriet disappeared.',-1),(146125,7,44723,44765,'00:31:03.480','00:31:05.209','Well, he lives over there.',-1),(146126,7,44814,44853,'00:31:07.280','00:31:08.884','And you live there. Sorry?',-1),(146127,7,44856,44893,'00:31:09.040','00:31:10.565','Your house.',-1),(146128,7,44931,45000,'00:31:12.160','00:31:15.004','Oh. Ha. Oh, yes.',-1),(146129,7,45013,45053,'00:31:15.560','00:31:17.244','Yes, you\'re right.',-1),(146130,7,45057,45098,'00:31:17.400','00:31:19.084','The man who hires the detective',-1),(146131,7,45101,45181,'00:31:19.240','00:31:22.562','should always be kept\non the suspects list.',-1),(146132,7,46443,46483,'00:32:15.160','00:32:16.810','Her mother.',-1),(146133,7,47176,47231,'00:32:45.680','00:32:47.967','But what about the search?\nPlease.',-1),(146134,7,47258,47328,'00:32:49.120','00:32:52.010','Please. I beg you.',-1),(146135,7,48078,48163,'00:33:23.280','00:33:26.807','<i>The fact that I never\nfound a body was not surprising.</i>',-1),(146136,7,48167,48237,'00:33:26.960','00:33:29.884','<i>You can\'t dig up\nan entire island.</i>',-1),(146137,7,48266,48320,'00:33:31.120','00:33:33.361','But neither could I\nfind the motive.',-1),(146138,7,48324,48388,'00:33:33.520','00:33:36.205','Was it spontaneous?\nWas it calculated?',-1),(146139,7,48392,48449,'00:33:36.360','00:33:38.727','Did she know something\nsomeone wished she didn\'t?',-1),(146140,7,48453,48538,'00:33:38.880','00:33:42.441','Was it about business?\nBusiness? Well, she was 16.',-1),(146141,7,48542,48584,'00:33:42.600','00:33:44.364','And very bright.',-1),(146142,7,48588,48654,'00:33:44.520','00:33:47.251','Henrik told me and many others\nhe could easily see her',-1),(146143,7,48657,48698,'00:33:47.400','00:33:49.084','running the company one day.',-1),(146144,7,48711,48775,'00:33:49.640','00:33:52.325','She was with some friends\nthat day at a parade.',-1),(146145,7,48779,48868,'00:33:52.480','00:33:56.201','She told them she was feeling unwell.\nShe left early.',-1),(146146,7,48872,48957,'00:33:56.360','00:33:59.887','But they also told me she\nkept secrets from them too.',-1),(146147,7,48964,49047,'00:34:00.200','00:34:03.647','The main thing I learned was that\nteenage girls are complicated.',-1),(146148,7,49051,49106,'00:34:03.800','00:34:06.087','I have one. Oh, then you know.',-1),(146149,7,49112,49187,'00:34:06.360','00:34:09.489','I wanted to, uh, ahem,',-1),(146150,7,49191,49234,'00:34:09.640','00:34:11.449','ask you about this.',-1),(146151,7,49298,49361,'00:34:14.120','00:34:16.726','She received that from\nHenrik the Christmas before.',-1),(146152,7,49420,49492,'00:34:19.200','00:34:22.170','I\'ve studied it more\ntimes than I can say.',-1),(146153,7,49524,49557,'00:34:23.520','00:34:24.885','I know every page of it.',-1),(146154,7,49561,49617,'00:34:25.080','00:34:27.401','It\'s the last page I was curious about.\nAs was I.',-1),(146155,7,49621,49715,'00:34:27.560','00:34:31.485','It\'s a list of names, numbers and\nit must have some significance.',-1),(146156,7,49719,49755,'00:34:31.640','00:34:33.130','All local phone numbers.',-1),(146157,7,49758,49813,'00:34:33.280','00:34:35.567','The first belonged\nto a woman, Margot,',-1),(146158,7,49818,49888,'00:34:35.760','00:34:38.684','whose mother was Magda, who\ndenied knowing Harriet.',-1),(146159,7,49892,49965,'00:34:38.840','00:34:41.889','The fourth, R.L., belonged\nto Rosmarie Larsson,',-1),(146160,7,49968,50062,'00:34:42.040','00:34:45.931','an elderly woman who\ndied some years before.',-1),(146161,7,50065,50171,'00:34:46.080','00:34:50.483','The other three were not connected\nin any way that I could find.',-1),(146162,7,50185,50263,'00:34:51.080','00:34:54.323','I reminded you of things you\'d\nrather forget, and I\'m sorry.',-1),(146163,7,50268,50316,'00:34:54.520','00:34:56.522','I can\'t forget.',-1),(146164,7,50349,50391,'00:34:57.880','00:34:59.644','It\'s my Rebecka case.',-1),(146165,7,50411,50445,'00:35:00.480','00:35:01.891','Uh, I don\'t know what that is.',-1),(146166,7,50461,50574,'00:35:02.560','00:35:07.282','Every policeman has at least one\nunsolved case to obsess over.',-1),(146167,7,50592,50651,'00:35:08.040','00:35:10.486','Back then we had an\nOfficer Torstensson.',-1),(146168,7,50655,50724,'00:35:10.640','00:35:13.530','Year after year, he kept going\nback to this Rebecka case.',-1),(146169,7,50728,50807,'00:35:13.680','00:35:16.968','Taking out the files,\nstudying them over and over.',-1),(146170,7,50810,50860,'00:35:17.120','00:35:19.168','We were young.\nWe laughed at him.',-1),(146171,7,50863,50910,'00:35:19.320','00:35:21.288','And that was also a\nmissing-girl case?',-1),(146172,7,50914,50980,'00:35:21.440','00:35:24.205','No, no, no, that\'s not\nwhy I mention it.',-1),(146173,7,50984,51054,'00:35:24.360','00:35:27.284','I\'m talking about the\nsoul of a policeman.',-1),(146174,7,51068,51137,'00:35:27.840','00:35:30.730','<i>Poor old Torstensson\nnever solved it.</i>',-1),(146175,7,51141,51197,'00:35:30.880','00:35:33.247','<i>And he never let it go.</i>',-1),(146176,7,51369,51416,'00:35:40.400','00:35:42.368','So how\'s Mr.\nPalmgren doing?',-1),(146177,7,51428,51496,'00:35:42.840','00:35:45.684','I heard he had a stroke\nof some kind? Huh?',-1),(146178,7,51500,51525,'00:35:45.840','00:35:46.887','It\'s terrible.',-1),(146179,7,51556,51626,'00:35:48.200','00:35:51.124','Now, what exactly do you do\nat this security company?',-1),(146180,7,51630,51673,'00:35:51.280','00:35:53.044','Make coffee, sort mail.',-1),(146181,7,51676,51717,'00:35:53.200','00:35:54.884','But not full-time.',-1),(146182,7,51729,51770,'00:35:55.400','00:35:57.084','Not even part-time consistently.',-1),(146183,7,51773,51892,'00:35:57.240','00:36:02.201','They somehow got along without\ncoffee or mail in July and August?',-1),(146184,7,52005,52057,'00:36:06.880','00:36:09.042','How much do you make there?\nEnough.',-1),(146185,7,52099,52125,'00:36:10.800','00:36:11.881','How much is your rent?',-1),(146186,7,52128,52165,'00:36:12.040','00:36:13.565','<i>I Pay my rent.</i>',-1),(146187,7,52252,52297,'00:36:17.200','00:36:19.043','And when was the last\ntime you were late?',-1),(146188,7,52300,52325,'00:36:19.200','00:36:20.247','Never.',-1),(146189,7,52356,52439,'00:36:21.520','00:36:24.967','You think that thing through your\neyebrow makes you attractive?',-1),(146190,7,52495,52521,'00:36:27.320','00:36:28.401','Here\'s the problem.',-1),(146191,7,52562,52634,'00:36:30.120','00:36:33.090','There\'s a discrepancy\nbetween the obligation',-1),(146192,7,52637,52736,'00:36:33.240','00:36:37.370','of Mr. Palmgren\'s guardianship and\nthe management of your finances.',-1),(146193,7,52740,52818,'00:36:37.520','00:36:40.763','There\'s no discrepancy.\nIt was clear I could manage my own finances.',-1),(146194,7,52822,52849,'00:36:40.920','00:36:42.046','That is not clear to me.',-1),(146195,7,52852,52905,'00:36:42.200','00:36:44.407','I\'m not a child.\nYou are not. But you were.',-1),(146196,7,52909,52962,'00:36:44.560','00:36:46.767','And between then and now,\nyou were committed',-1),(146197,7,52966,53034,'00:36:46.920','00:36:49.764','to the locked ward of St.\nStefan\'s where you continued',-1),(146198,7,53038,53089,'00:36:49.920','00:36:52.048','to display violent aggression.',-1),(146199,7,53106,53170,'00:36:52.760','00:36:55.445','And you failed to adapt\nto four foster homes,',-1),(146200,7,53174,53254,'00:36:55.600','00:36:58.922','arrested twice for intoxication,\ntwice for narcotics,',-1),(146201,7,53257,53355,'00:36:59.080','00:37:03.130','again for assault, smashing\na bottle into a man\'s face.',-1),(146202,7,53359,53414,'00:37:03.320','00:37:05.607','And it\'s not even that long ago.',-1),(146203,7,53418,53523,'00:37:05.760','00:37:10.129','You may have conned Mr. Palmgren\ninto thinking that you have changed,',-1),(146204,7,53526,53570,'00:37:10.280','00:37:12.123','but when I\'m looking at this,',-1),(146205,7,53574,53670,'00:37:12.280','00:37:16.251','not to mention the way\nyou\'re looking at me now,',-1),(146206,7,53673,53717,'00:37:16.400','00:37:18.209','I don\'t think you have.',-1),(146207,7,53727,53791,'00:37:18.640','00:37:21.325','So the good old Mr\n. Palmgren days are over.',-1),(146208,7,53795,53867,'00:37:21.480','00:37:24.484','Starting now, you will be\ngiven a monthly allowance.',-1),(146209,7,53871,53927,'00:37:24.640','00:37:26.961','You\'ll provide me with\nreceipts for your expenses.',-1),(146210,7,53930,54007,'00:37:27.120','00:37:30.329','If the numbers don\'t balance, I assume\nthe difference is going to drugs.',-1),(146211,7,54011,54056,'00:37:30.480','00:37:32.369','I\'ve taken care of\nmyself since I was 10.',-1),(146212,7,54061,54096,'00:37:32.560','00:37:34.005','The state has taken care of you.',-1),(146213,7,54099,54165,'00:37:34.160','00:37:36.891','Miss Salander, please, look\nat me, this is important.',-1),(146214,7,54168,54249,'00:37:37.040','00:37:40.408','Since your behavior is\nelaborately documented in here,',-1),(146215,7,54254,54315,'00:37:40.600','00:37:43.126','it will shock no one if\nI chose an alternative',-1),(146216,7,54319,54400,'00:37:43.320','00:37:46.688','to the very lenient arrangement\nI have just outlined.',-1),(146217,7,54459,54559,'00:37:49.160','00:37:53.324','Would you prefer\ninstitutionalization?',-1),(146218,7,55061,55087,'00:38:14.240','00:38:15.321','Yes.',-1),(146219,7,55092,55130,'00:38:15.520','00:38:17.090','I\'m Liv. Oh, hi.',-1),(146220,7,55133,55173,'00:38:17.240','00:38:18.890','We\'re going to the same place.\nHop in.',-1),(146221,7,55176,55210,'00:38:19.040','00:38:20.451','Oh, good, thank you.',-1),(146222,7,55409,55485,'00:38:28.720','00:38:31.883','I found him at death\'s\ndoor, halfway up the hill.',-1),(146223,7,55491,55561,'00:38:32.160','00:38:35.050','I\'m afraid I\'m a little out of shape.\nIt\'s a climb for anyone.',-1),(146224,7,55564,55622,'00:38:35.200','00:38:37.601','- I should\'ve warned you. Come in.\n- Thank you, Martin.',-1),(146225,7,55626,55664,'00:38:37.760','00:38:39.364','Henrik says\ngreat things about you.',-1),(146226,7,55668,55775,'00:38:39.520','00:38:43.969','- Mmm. Martin? Smells wonderful.\n- No. Leave your shoes on.',-1),(146227,7,55778,55808,'00:38:44.120','00:38:45.360','What are we drinking?',-1),(146228,7,55812,55852,'00:38:45.520','00:38:47.204','What a place.\nLook at that view.',-1),(146229,7,55856,55941,'00:38:47.360','00:38:50.887','I used to work in the company\'s\npetrochemical division in GÃ¶teborg.',-1),(146230,7,55944,55982,'00:38:51.040','00:38:52.610','When it was sold,\nI went with it.',-1),(146231,7,55986,56017,'00:38:52.760','00:38:54.046','A dark day.',-1),(146232,7,56024,56103,'00:38:54.360','00:38:57.648','I live in Hong Kong, but come\nback to Stockholm for family events.',-1),(146233,7,56107,56164,'00:38:57.800','00:39:00.201','And I drive up to spend a\ncouple of days with Martin.',-1),(146234,7,56169,56251,'00:39:00.400','00:39:03.802','It\'s just the moose steak she wants.\nWho can blame her? It\'s wonderful.',-1),(146235,7,56307,56378,'00:39:06.160','00:39:09.084','Something\'s left open.\nDo you like this wine,',-1),(146236,7,56382,56473,'00:39:09.280','00:39:13.046','or you want to try something else?\nNo, no, it\'s fine.',-1),(146237,7,56579,56629,'00:39:17.480','00:39:19.562','You\'re writing a book\nnow, Martin said.',-1),(146238,7,56633,56696,'00:39:19.720','00:39:22.371','Henrik\'s biography. I love Henrik.\nHe\'s fascinating.',-1),(146239,7,56700,56732,'00:39:22.520','00:39:23.851','Martin too.',-1),(146240,7,56736,56813,'00:39:24.000','00:39:27.209','Together they are the\nold Sweden and the new.',-1),(146241,7,56816,56846,'00:39:27.360','00:39:28.600','Yes, they are.',-1),(146242,7,56889,56946,'00:39:30.400','00:39:32.767','You know about Harriet, right?',-1),(146243,7,56967,57010,'00:39:33.640','00:39:35.449','You don\'t? Yes, I do.',-1),(146244,7,57038,57130,'00:39:36.600','00:39:40.446','The family doesn\'t want to talk about it,\nbut it can\'t be swept under the rug.',-1),(146245,7,57134,57180,'00:39:40.600','00:39:42.523','What can\'t? Harriet.',-1),(146246,7,57188,57217,'00:39:42.840','00:39:44.080','We can talk about it later.',-1),(146247,7,57221,57290,'00:39:44.240','00:39:47.084','Uh... We can talk about it now.',-1),(146248,7,57298,57348,'00:39:47.440','00:39:49.522','Liv knows everything\nabout my crazy family.',-1),(146249,7,57352,57411,'00:39:49.680','00:39:52.160','That\'s why she\'ll never marry me.\nThat\'s one reason.',-1),(146250,7,57415,57463,'00:39:52.320','00:39:54.322','I don\'t want to read\nabout that in the book.',-1),(146251,7,57467,57522,'00:39:54.480','00:39:56.767','Everything else is fine.\nHarriet certainly.',-1),(146252,7,57533,57619,'00:39:57.240','00:40:00.801','You know, everything\nchanged after that.',-1),(146253,7,57624,57679,'00:40:01.000','00:40:03.321','Not just the family, but\nthe company as well.',-1),(146254,7,57683,57733,'00:40:03.480','00:40:05.562','How so?\nWe\'re not Ericsson or Nordea.',-1),(146255,7,57737,57821,'00:40:05.720','00:40:09.247','But we\'re still the largest\nfamily-owned company in the country.',-1),(146256,7,57827,57878,'00:40:09.480','00:40:11.608','At our height we had\n40,000 employees.',-1),(146257,7,57883,57912,'00:40:11.800'