ce.',-1),(147657,11,19031,19078,'00:13:12.959','00:13:14.927','Hello. Is Elizabeth in?',-1),(147658,11,19082,19141,'00:13:15.086','00:13:17.555','She having bridge club right now.\nMay I take a message?',-1),(147659,11,19145,19238,'00:13:17.714','00:13:21.594','Yes, please tell her Celia Foote\ncalled again.',-1),(147660,11,19266,19307,'00:13:22.760','00:13:24.478','I\'ll call back tomorrow.',-1),(147661,11,19311,19360,'00:13:24.637','00:13:26.685','- Yes, ma\'am.\n- Uh...',-1),(147662,11,19364,19410,'00:13:26.848','00:13:28.771','Miss?',-1),(147663,11,19414,19518,'00:13:28.933','00:13:33.279','I\'m looking for some help at my house.\nDo you know any maids looking?',-1),(147664,11,19522,19550,'00:13:33.438','00:13:34.610','No, ma\'am.',-1),(147665,11,19554,19614,'00:13:34.772','00:13:37.275','OK. It\'s Ce/ia Foote.',-1),(147666,11,19618,19706,'00:13:37.442','00:13:41.117','Emerson-684. [giggling]\nBye now.',-1),(147667,11,19797,19845,'00:13:44.907','00:13:46.909','[935Pin9, 9i99lin9]',-1),(147668,11,19849,19912,'00:13:47.076','00:13:49.704','You scared the daylights out of me!',-1),(147669,11,19932,20017,'00:13:50.538','00:13:54.042','It is lunchtime,\nand I am suddenly hungry.',-1),(147670,11,20031,20098,'00:13:54.625','00:13:57.424','[Celia giggling, indistinct chatter]',-1),(147671,11,20102,20147,'00:13:57.587','00:13:59.464','Honestly!',-1),(147672,11,20151,20203,'00:13:59.630','00:14:01.803','[snoring]',-1),(147673,11,20275,20307,'00:14:04.802','00:14:06.145','[gasping] Oh.',-1),(147674,11,20311,20353,'00:14:06.304','00:14:08.056','I\'m still working on it, Aibileen.',-1),(147675,11,20439,20471,'00:14:11.642','00:14:12.985','Who was that on the phone?',-1),(147676,11,20475,20525,'00:14:13.144','00:14:15.238','Miss Celia Foote called again.',-1),(147677,11,20557,20602,'00:14:16.564','00:14:18.441','I\'ve never called her back, Hilly.',-1),(147678,11,20641,20693,'00:14:20.068','00:14:22.241','She can\'t take a hint, can she?',-1),(147679,11,20697,20735,'00:14:22.403','00:14:23.996','Who\'s Celia Foote?',-1),(147680,11,20739,20787,'00:14:24.155','00:14:26.157','That tacky girl Johnny married.',-1),(147681,11,20791,20836,'00:14:26.324','00:14:28.167','From Sugar Ditch.',-1),(147682,11,20839,20876,'00:14:28.326','00:14:29.873','It could have been you, Hilly.',-1),(147683,11,20880,21009,'00:14:30.036','00:14:35.384','And live 30 minutes outside of town?\nNo, thank you. [chuckling]',-1),(147684,11,21012,21131,'00:14:35.541','00:14:40.468','Anyway, I ran into her at the beauty\nparlor, and she had the nerve to ask',-1),(147685,11,21135,21184,'00:14:40.630','00:14:42.678','if she could help with\nthe Children\'s Benefit Ball.',-1),(147686,11,21188,21264,'00:14:42.840','00:14:46.014','Aren\'t we taking non-members?\nThe benefit has gotten so big.',-1),(147687,11,21268,21342,'00:14:46.177','00:14:49.272','Yes, but we\'re not telling her.',-1),(147688,11,21346,21395,'00:14:49.430','00:14:51.478','[all giggling]',-1),(147689,11,21407,21445,'00:14:51.974','00:14:53.567','Thank you, Aibileen.',-1),(147690,11,21449,21501,'00:14:53.726','00:14:55.899','[groaning]',-1),(147691,11,21576,21620,'00:14:59.023','00:15:00.866','Hilly, I wish you\'d just\ngo use the bathroom.',-1),(147692,11,21624,21660,'00:15:01.025','00:15:02.527','I\'m fine.',-1),(147693,11,21664,21706,'00:15:02.693','00:15:04.445','[Missus Walters]\nOh, she\'s just upset',-1),(147694,11,21710,21776,'00:15:04.612','00:15:07.365','because the nigra uses the guest bath\nand so do we.',-1),(147695,11,21860,21911,'00:15:10.868','00:15:12.996','Aibileen, go check on Mae Mobley.',-1),(147696,11,21915,21942,'00:15:13.162','00:15:14.254','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(147697,11,21970,22011,'00:15:15.456','00:15:17.129','Just go use mine and Raleigh\'s.',-1),(147698,11,22014,22103,'00:15:17.291','00:15:20.966','If Aibileen uses the guest bath,\nI\'m sure she uses yours, too.',-1),(147699,11,22107,22139,'00:15:21.129','00:15:22.472','She does not.',-1),(147700,11,22161,22238,'00:15:23.381','00:15:26.601','Wouldn\'t you rather them\ntake their business outside?',-1),(147701,11,22280,22340,'00:15:28.344','00:15:30.847','Have you all seen the cover\nof Life this week?',-1),(147702,11,22344,22377,'00:15:31.013','00:15:32.390','Jackie\'s never looked more regal.',-1),(147703,11,22381,22448,'00:15:32.557','00:15:35.356','Tell Raleigh every penny he spends\non a colored\'s bathroom',-1),(147704,11,22452,22520,'00:15:35.518','00:15:38.362','he\'ll get back in spades\nwhen y\'all sell.',-1),(147705,11,22524,22551,'00:15:38.521','00:15:39.647','[makes disgusted noise]',-1),(147706,11,22555,22653,'00:15:39.814','00:15:43.910','it\'s just plain dangerous. They carry\ndifferent diseases than we do.',-1),(147707,11,22676,22700,'00:15:44.861','00:15:45.862','Pass.',-1),(147708,11,22704,22779,'00:15:46.028','00:15:49.157','That\'s why I\'ve drafted\nthe Home Health Sanitation Initiative.',-1),(147709,11,22783,22814,'00:15:49.323','00:15:50.620','The what?',-1),(147710,11,22818,22864,'00:15:50.783','00:15:52.706','[Hilly] A disease-preventative bill',-1),(147711,11,22868,22975,'00:15:52.869','00:15:57.295','that requires every white home to have a\nseparate bathroom for the colored help.',-1),(147712,11,22995,23052,'00:15:58.166','00:16:00.510','It\'s been endorsed\nby the White Citizens\' Council.',-1),(147713,11,23146,23220,'00:16:04.422','00:16:07.517','Maybe we should just build you\na bathroom outside, Hilly.',-1),(147714,11,23224,23308,'00:16:07.675','00:16:11.179','You ought not to joke\nabout the colored situation.',-1),(147715,11,23340,23404,'00:16:12.513','00:16:15.187','I\'ll do whatever it takes\nto protect our children.',-1),(147716,11,23449,23494,'00:16:17.059','00:16:18.936','Your lead, Elizabeth.',-1),(147717,11,23520,23582,'00:16:20.021','00:16:22.615','[sermon on radio]',-1),(147718,11,23617,23664,'00:16:24.066','00:16:26.034','[plates clinking]',-1),(147719,11,23776,23812,'00:16:30.698','00:16:32.200','- Aibileen?\n- Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(147720,11,23864,2393