25.456','00:19:26.457','Unzip me.',-1),(147765,11,28035,28060,'00:19:28.125','00:19:29.172','Come on.',-1),(147766,11,28117,28177,'00:19:31.545','00:19:34.048','Did I tell you Fanny Peatrow\ngot engaged?',-1),(147767,11,28203,28246,'00:19:35.132','00:19:36.930','After she got that teller job,',-1),(147768,11,28250,28299,'00:19:37.093','00:19:39.141','her mother said she was swimming\nin proposals.',-1),(147769,11,28303,28348,'00:19:39.303','00:19:41.180','Good for fair Fanny Peatrow.',-1),(147770,11,28352,28430,'00:19:41.347','00:19:44.601','Eugenia, your eggs are dying.\nWould it kill you to go on a date?',-1),(147771,11,28448,28546,'00:19:45.351','00:19:49.447','Just show a little gumption.\nCareful now, careful.',-1),(147772,11,28550,28605,'00:19:49.605','00:19:51.903','Oh, now look at this.',-1),(147773,11,28621,28699,'00:19:52.566','00:19:55.820','This dress is just precious on you.',-1),(147774,11,28703,28799,'00:19:55.986','00:19:59.991','Just take it in a little here.\nLittle there.',-1),(147775,11,28856,28922,'00:20:02.368','00:20:05.121','- Get your hair fixed.\n- I got a job today.',-1),(147776,11,28926,28950,'00:20:05.287','00:20:06.288','Where?',-1),(147777,11,28966,29017,'00:20:06.956','00:20:09.050','Writing for The Jackson Journal.',-1),(147778,11,29049,29104,'00:20:10.376','00:20:12.674','- [pulling up zipper]\n- Great.',-1),(147779,11,29122,29174,'00:20:13.421','00:20:15.594','You can write my obituary!',-1),(147780,11,29178,29277,'00:20:15.756','00:20:19.886','\"Charlotte Phelan, dead!\nHer daughter, still single.\"',-1),(147781,11,29281,29341,'00:20:20.052','00:20:22.555','Mother, would it really be so bad\nif I never met a husband?',-1),(147782,11,29345,29411,'00:20:22.722','00:20:25.475','Skeeter! Skeeter!',-1),(147783,11,29436,29470,'00:20:26.517','00:20:27.939','[shouting] Skeeter!',-1),(147784,11,29583,29616,'00:20:32.648','00:20:34.025','I need to ask you something.',-1),(147785,11,29732,29826,'00:20:38.863','00:20:42.788','I read the other day about how\nsome girls get unbalanced.',-1),(147786,11,29842,29875,'00:20:43.451','00:20:44.794','They start thinking these...',-1),(147787,11,29915,29963,'00:20:46.495','00:20:48.463','...unnatural thoughts.',-1),(147788,11,29966,29999,'00:20:48.622','00:20:49.965','Are you...',-1),(147789,11,30042,30157,'00:20:51.751','00:20:56.552','Do you, uh... find men attractive?',-1),(147790,11,30171,30286,'00:20:57.131','00:21:01.932','Are you having unnatural thoughts\nabout girls or women?',-1),(147791,11,30328,30354,'00:21:03.679','00:21:04.771','Oh, my God.',-1),(147792,11,30358,30470,'00:21:04.930','00:21:09.606','Because this article says there\'s\na cure. A special root tea!',-1),(147793,11,30474,30603,'00:21:09.769','00:21:15.151','Mother, I want to be with girls as much\nas you want to be with Jameso.',-1),(147794,11,30607,30659,'00:21:15.316','00:21:17.489','- Eugenia!\n- Unless, of course, you do!',-1),(147795,11,30663,30696,'00:21:17.651','00:21:19.028','Oh!',-1),(147796,11,30708,30743,'00:21:19.528','00:21:20.996','[exclaiming]',-1),(147797,11,30747,30831,'00:21:21.155','00:21:24.625','Carlton\'s bringing Rebecca to dinner.\nTry to look presentable!',-1),(147798,11,30865,30931,'00:21:26.076','00:21:28.795','[laughing]',-1),(147799,11,30934,30985,'00:21:28.954','00:21:31.082','What the hell you know\nabout cleaning a house, Skeeter?',-1),(147800,11,30989,31055,'00:21:31.248','00:21:33.967','It\'s a start, Carlton.',-1),(147801,11,31059,31142,'00:21:34.126','00:21:37.596','If you say so.\nI thought you wanted to write books.',-1),(147802,11,31146,31220,'00:21:37.755','00:21:40.850','Now, y\'all leave Sister alone.',-1),(147803,11,31224,31293,'00:21:41.008','00:21:43.887','- I\'m proud of you, sweetheart.\n- The irony of it all.',-1),(147804,11,31297,31352,'00:21:44.053','00:21:46.351','Giving advice on how to keep up a home\nwhen she doesn\'t even...',-1),(147805,11,31356,31438,'00:21:46.514','00:21:49.939','Oh, no, Pascagoula. You couldn\'t have\nknown this, but I\'m allergic to almonds.',-1),(147806,11,31442,31507,'00:21:50.100','00:21:52.819','Sorry, Miss Eugenia,\nI\'ll get you another one.',-1),(147807,11,31511,31572,'00:21:52.978','00:21:55.527','You know, last time I had an almond,\nI stopped liking men.',-1),(147808,11,31576,31613,'00:21:55.689','00:21:57.236','Oh, my Lord.',-1),(147809,11,31617,31707,'00:21:57.399','00:22:01.154','Oh, no, Rebecca, it\'s fine. There\'s\na special root tea for that now.',-1),(147810,11,31711,31743,'00:22:01.320','00:22:02.663','You have pushed it, young lady.',-1),(147811,11,31760,31835,'00:22:03.364','00:22:06.493','Daddy. What happened to Constantine?',-1),(147812,11,31839,31894,'00:22:06.659','00:22:08.957','Uh, well...',-1),(147813,11,31912,31993,'00:22:09.703','00:22:13.048','Constantine went to live in Chicago\nwith her family.',-1),(147814,11,31996,32057,'00:22:13.207','00:22:15.710','People move on, Skeeter.',-1),(147815,11,32061,32118,'00:22:15.876','00:22:18.254','But I do wish that she\'d\nstayed down here with us.',-1),(147816,11,32238,32279,'00:22:23.259','00:22:24.977','I don\'t believe you.',-1),(147817,11,32294,32318,'00:22:25.594','00:22:26.595','[sighing]',-1),(147818,11,32322,32380,'00:22:26.762','00:22:29.185','She would\'ve written and told me.',-1),(147819,11,32604,32643,'00:22:38.524','00:22:40.151','Did you fire her?',-1),(147820,11,32659,32758,'00:22:40.818','00:22:44.948','We were just a job to her, honey.\nWith them, it\'s all about money.',-1),(147821,11,32762,32846,'00:22:45.114','00:22:48.618','You\'ll understand that once you\'ve\nhired help of your own.',-1),(147822,11,32865,32934,'00:22:49.410','00:22:52.254','- She raised me.\n- She did not!',-1),(147823,11,32937,33000,'00:22:52.413','00:22:55.007','She worked here for 29 years!',-1),(147824,11,33003,33057,'00:22:55.165','00:22:57.384','It was a colored thing\nand I put it behind me!',-1),(147825,11,33075,33166,'00:22:58.127','00:23:01.927','Excuse me a moment, Rebecca. My daughter\nhas upset my cancerous ulcers.',-1),(147826,11,33284,33332,'00:23:06.844','00:23:08.846','[door slamming]',-1),(147827,11,33336,33389,'00:23:09.013','00:23:11.232','[birds calling]',-1),(147828,11,34288,34346,'00:23:48.677','00:23:51.100','What you doing hiding out here, girl?',-1),(147829,11,34386,34467,'00:23:52.765','00:23:56.144','I couldn\'t tell Mama I didn\'t\nget asked to the dance.',-1),(147830,11,34471,34498,'00:23:56.310','00:23:57.436','It\'s all right.',-1),(147831,11,34527,34611,'00:23:58.646','00:24:02.150','Some things we just got to\nkeep to ourselves, right?',-1),(147832,11,34637,34681,'00:24:03.233','00:24:05.076','All the boys say I\'m ugly.',-1),(147833,11,34726,34825,'00:24:06.946','00:24:11.042','Mama was third runner-up in\nthe Miss South Carolina pageant.',-1),(147834,11,34828,34917,'00:24:11.200','00:24:14.875','I wish you\'d quit\nfeeling sorry for yourself.',-1),(147835,11,34920,34971,'00:24:15.037','00:24:17.165','Now, that\'s ugly.',-1),(147836,11,34996,35082,'00:24:18.207','00:24:21.757','Ugly is something that\ngoes up inside you.',-1),(147837,11,35086,35169,'00:24:21.919','00:24:25.389','It\'s mean and hurtful, like them boys.',-1),(147838,11,35201,35244,'00:24:26.715','00:24:28.513','Now you\'re not one of them, is you?',-1),(147839,11,35269,35315,'00:24:29.551','00:24:31.474','I didn\'t think so, honey.',-1),(147840,11,35440,35464,'00:24:36.684','00:24:37.685','Every day...',-1),(147841,11,35512,35579,'00:24:39.687','00:24:42.486','Every day you\'re not\ndead in the ground,',-1),(147842,11,35583,35693,'00:24:42.648','00:24:47.245','when you wake up in the morning, you\'re\ngonna have to make some decisions.',-1),(147843,11,35728,35786,'00:24:48.696','00:24:51.119','Got to ask yourself this question:',-1),(147844,11,35803,35842,'00:24:51.824','00:24:53.417','\"Am I gonna believe',-1),(147845,11,35845,35958,'00:24:53.575','00:24:58.251','all them bad things them fools\nsay about me today?\"',-1),(147846,11,36004,36031,'00:25:00.207','00:25:01.299','You hear me?',-1),(147847,11,36034,36110,'00:25:01.458','00:25:04.587','\"Am I gonna believe all them bad things',-1),(147848,11,36114,36174,'00:25:04.753','00:25:07.256','them fools say about me today\'?\"',-1),(147849,11,36243,36270,'00:25:10.134','00:25:11.260','Au right?',-1),(147850,11,36346,36438,'00:25:14.430','00:25:18.276','As for your mama,\nshe didn\'t pick her life.',-1),(147851,11,36473,36505,'00:25:19.727','00:25:21.070','It picked her.',-1),(147852,11,36572,36599,'00:25:23.856','00:25:24.982','But you...',-1),(147853,11,36665,36753,'00:25:27.735','00:25:31.410','...you\'re gonna do\nsomething big with yours.',-1),(147854,11,36780,36818,'00:25:32.531','00:25:34.124','You wait and see.',-1),(147855,11,36875,36947,'00:25:36.493','00:25:39.463','Come on, go home with me\ntill the dance over. Come on.',-1),(147856,11,37119,37182,'00:25:46.628','00:25:49.256','[chuckling]',-1),(147857,11,37459,37530,'00:26:00.809','00:26:03.779','Miss Stein, you said in your letter\nto write about what disturbs me,',-1),(147858,11,37534,37565,'00:26:03.937','00:26:05.234','particularly if it bothers no one else.',-1),(147859,11,37569,37593,'00:26:05.397','00:26:06.398','Come on.',-1),(147860,11,37597,37640,'00:26:06.565','00:26:08.363','And I understand that now.',-1),(147861,11,37674,37702,'00:26:09.777','00:26:10.949','Continue.',-1),(147862,11,37728,37793,'00:26:12.029','00:26:14.748','I\'d like to write something\nfrom the point of view of the help.',-1),(147863,11,37830,37891,'00:26:16.283','00:26:18.832','These colored women\nraise white children,',-1),(147864,11,37895,37975,'00:26:18.994','00:26:22.294','and in 20 years,\nthose children become the boss.',-1),(147865,11,37978,38044,'00:26:22.456','00:26:25.175','We love them and they love us,',-1),(147866,11,38048,38103,'00:26:25.334','00:26:27.632','but they can\'t even use the toilets\nin our houses.',-1),(147867,11,38107,38145,'00:26:27.795','00:26:29.388','Don\'t you find that ironic, Miss Stein?',-1),(147868,11,38149,38173,'00:26:29.546','00:26:30.547','I\'m listening.',-1),(147869,11,38210,38272,'00:26:32.091','00:26:34.685','Margaret Mitchell glorified\nthe mammy figure,',-1),(147870,11,38276,38316,'00:26:34.843','00:26:36.516','- [sighing]\n- who dedicates her whole life',-1),(147871,11,38320,38345,'00:26:36.678','00:26:37.725','to a white family.',-1),(147872,11,38349,38430,'00:26:37.888','00:26:41.267','But nobody ever asked Mammy\nhow she felt about it.',-1),(147873,11,38434,38500,'00:26:41.433','00:26:44.186','So, a side to this never before heard?',-1),(147874,11,38504,38550,'00:26:44.353','00:26:46.276','Yes.',-1),(147875,11,38554,38622,'00:26:46.438','00:26:49.282','\'Cause nobody ever really\ntalks about it down here.',-1),(147876,11,38690,38733,'00:26:52.111','00:26:53.909','Skeeter, who are you\ntalking to in there?',-1),(147877,11,38758,38790,'00:26:54.947','00:26:56.290','Go away!',-1),(147878,11,38877,38949,'00:26:59.910','00:27:02.880','- Who was that?\n- My mother.',-1),(147879,11,38952,38990,'00:27:03.038','00:27:04.585','Look.',-1),(147880,11,38993,39077,'00:27:04.748','00:27:08.218','No maid in her right mind is ever gonna\ntell you the truth.',-1),(147881,11,39081,39166,'00:27:08.377','00:27:11.927','That\'s a hell of a risk to take in\na place like Jackson, Mississippi.',-1),(147882,11,39170,39203,'00:27:12.089','00:27:13.466','I already have a maid.',-1),(147883,11,39251,39335,'00:27:15.467','00:27:18.971','Really? A Negro maid has already agreed\nto speak with you?',-1),(147884,11,39355,39392,'00:27:19.805','00:27:21.352','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(147885,11,39484,39556,'00:27:25.185','00:27:28.189','Well... I guess I can read\nwhat you come up with.',-1),(147886,11,39560,39612,'00:27:28.355','00:27:30.528','The book biz could use\na little rattling.',-1),(147887,11,39616,39649,'00:27:30.691','00:27:32.068','Thank you, Miss Stein.',-1),(147888,11,39653,39695,'00:27:32.234','00:27:33.986','Hey, hey, hey, all I\'m saying',-1),(147889,11,39699,39770,'00:27:34.153','00:27:37.123','is that I\'ll let you know\nif it\'s even worth pursuing.',-1),(147890,11,39774,39856,'00:27:37.281','00:27:40.706','And for God\'s sake, you\'re\na 23-year-old educated woman.',-1),(147891,11,39860,39912,'00:27:40.868','00:27:43.041','Go get yourself an apartment.',-1),(147892,11,40016,40057,'00:27:47.374','00:27:49.047','[Skeeter] \"Dear Miss Myrna:',-1),(147893,11,40080,40144,'00:27:50.002','00:27:52.676','When I\'m chopping onions, how do I\nkeep tears out of my eyes?\"',-1),(147894,11,40148,40234,'00:27:52.838','00:27:56.433','[Aibileen] Shoot, that\'s easy. You tell\nher hold a matchstick between her teeth.',-1),(147895,11,40269,40306,'00:27:57.885','00:27:59.432','Is it lit?',-1),(147896,11,40310,40349,'00:27:59.595','00:28:01.222','No, ma\'am.',-1),(147897,11,40405,40478,'00:28:03.557','00:28:06.606','[Hilly] Miss Leefolt said\nyou could start right away.',-1),(147898,11,40482,40601,'00:28:06.768','00:28:11.740','Build it just like the bathroom\nat my house. Let\'s see. [gasping]',-1),(147899,11,40605,40692,'00:28:11.899','00:28:15.529','- Right there. That will be nice.\n- Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(147900,11,40696,40754,'00:28:15.694','00:28:18.117','[thunder rumbling]',-1),(147901,11,40824,40881,'00:28:21.033','00:28:23.377','My goodness, we got to run back\nto the car. Come on.',-1),(147902,11,40893,40926,'00:28:23.911','00:28:25.288','[Hilly] Bye, Skeeter!',-1),(147903,11,41012,41051,'00:28:28.874','00:28:30.467','Aibileen.',-1),(147904,11,41055,41142,'00:28:30.626','00:28:34.256','There\'s something else I want to\nwrite about. I would need your help.',-1),(147905,11,41221,41316,'00:28:37.549','00:28:41.520','I want to interview you about\nwhat it\'s like to work as a maid.',-1),(147906,11,41320,41399,'00:28:41.678','00:28:44.978','I\'d like to do a book of interviews\nabout working for white families.',-1),(147907,11,41419,41508,'00:28:45.807','00:28:49.528','And we could show what it\'s like\nto work for, say, Elizabeth?',-1),(147908,11,41512,41590,'00:28:49.686','00:28:52.940','You know what Miss Leefolt do to me if\nshe knew I was telling stories on her?',-1),(147909,11,41594,41669,'00:28:53.106','00:28:56.235','I was thinking that we wouldn\'t\nhave to tell her.',-1),(147910,11,41673,41742,'00:28:56.401','00:28:59.280','The other maids would have\nto keep it a secret, too.',-1),(147911,11,41746,41778,'00:28:59.446','00:29:00.789','Other maids?',-1),(147912,11,41813,41870,'00:29:02.241','00:29:04.619','I was hoping to get four or five.',-1),(147913,11,41874,41911,'00:29:04.785','00:29:06.332','[wind blowing]',-1),(147914,11,41915,41983,'00:29:06.495','00:29:09.294','To show what it\'s really like\nin Jackson.',-1),(147915,11,42012,42054,'00:29:10.540','00:29:12.258','[thunder rolling]',-1),(147916,11,42058,42175,'00:29:12.417','00:29:17.298','Show what y\'all get paid,\nand the babies and the bathrooms.',-1),(147917,11,42179,42208,'00:29:17.464','00:29:18.681','The good and the bad.',-1),(147918,11,42212,42232,'00:29:18.840','00:29:19.682','[door slamming]',-1),(147919,11,42236,42293,'00:29:19.841','00:29:22.219','I bought you this damn house.\nI put up with your new clothes',-1),(147920,11,42297,42358,'00:29:22.386','00:29:24.935','and trips to New Orleans,\nbut this takes the goddamn cake.',-1),(147921,11,42362,42391,'00:29:25.097','00:29:26.314','[Elizabeth]\nHilly spoke to the surgeon general,',-1),(147922,11,42395,42460,'00:29:26.473','00:29:29.192','and she also said it\'ll add value\nto our home.',-1),(147923,11,42464,42532,'00:29:29.351','00:29:32.195','I guess Mae Mobley can go to college\nin that damn bathroom!',-1),(147924,11,42536,42566,'00:29:32.354','00:29:33.606','Hilly\'s covering the cost and said',-1),(147925,11,42570,42614,'00:29:33.772','00:29:35.615','you could just do William\'s taxes\nto pay her back.',-1),(147926,11,42618,42667,'00:29:35.774','00:29:37.822','We don\'t take orders\nfrom the Holbrooks.',-1),(147927,11,42737,42782,'00:29:40.737','00:29:42.614','Skeeter, how you doing?',-1),(147928,11,42817,42841,'00:29:44.074','00:29:45.075','Fine.',-1),(147929,11,42868,42904,'00:29:46.201','00:29:47.669','[Mae Mobley crying]',-1),(147930,11,42948,42984,'00:29:49.538','00:29:51.006','Fix me a sandwich, Aibileen.',-1),(147931,11,43064,43118,'00:29:54.334','00:29:56.587','Aibileen, Mae Mobley\'s\ncrying her eyes out.',-1),(147932,11,43219,43258,'00:30:00.799','00:30:02.426','Skeeter.',-1),(147933,11,43273,43342,'00:30:03.051','00:30:05.930','I\'m sorry, but I think it\'s best\nif you leave now.',-1),(147934,11,43346,43389,'00:30:06.096','00:30:07.894','Oh, sure, sure.',-1),(147935,11,43393,43483,'00:30:08.056','00:30:11.811','And this Miss Myrna thing isn\'t going\nto work out with Aibileen.',-1),(147936,11,43512,43553,'00:30:13.020','00:30:14.738','I\'m sorry.',-1),(147937,11,43665,43693,'00:30:19.401','00:30:20.573','[thunder cracking]',-1),(147938,11,43697,43733,'00:30:20.736','00:30:22.238','[rain pouring]',-1),(147939,11,43807,43892,'00:30:25.324','00:30:28.874','You\'re making it hotter,\nflapping your arms like that, Minny.',-1),(147940,11,44116,44178,'00:30:38.170','00:30:40.764','Look how big the waves are, Minny.',-1),(147941,11,44182,44212,'00:30:40.922','00:30:42.174','[wind howling]',-1),(147942,11,44216,44294,'00:30:42.341','00:30:45.595','Let\'s go to the beach.\nRun, get Mr. Walters!',-1),(147943,11,44298,44339,'00:30:45.761','00:30:47.479','He loves riding these waves!',-1),(147944,11,44343,44398,'00:30:47.637','00:30:49.935','You know we went to Biloxi\non our honeymoon?',-1),(147945,11,44402,44437,'00:30:50.098','00:30:51.566','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(147946,11,44459,44529,'00:30:52.476','00:30:55.400','Are we in Biloxi, Minny?',-1),(147947,11,44557,44629,'00:30:56.563','00:30:59.567','No, ma\'am. We ain\'t.',-1),(147948,11,44710,44805,'00:31:02.944','00:31:06.915','Why don\'t you sit down here for a spell.',-1),(147949,11,44834,44948,'00:31:08.116','00:31:12.872','And then me and you will go on down\nto the beach in a l