00:42:41.392','That gonna be hard.',-1),(148102,11,61477,61517,'00:42:41.559','00:42:43.232','What about Minny?',-1),(148103,11,61521,61559,'00:42:43.394','00:42:44.987','Minny got her some stories,\nsure enough,',-1),(148104,11,61563,61655,'00:42:45.146','00:42:48.992','but she ain\'t real keen on talking\nto white peoples right now.',-1),(148105,11,61731,61793,'00:42:52.153','00:42:54.747','What does it feel like\nto raise a white child',-1),(148106,11,61797,61866,'00:42:54.906','00:42:57.785','when your own child\'s at home being\nlooked after by somebody else?',-1),(148107,11,61934,61972,'00:43:00.620','00:43:02.167','It feel...',-1),(148108,11,62269,62298,'00:43:14.550','00:43:15.767','Is that your son?',-1),(148109,11,62422,62467,'00:43:20.932','00:43:22.809','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(148110,11,62471,62523,'00:43:22.975','00:43:25.148','Can we move on to the next question?',-1),(148111,11,62527,62596,'00:43:25.311','00:43:28.190','You don\'t have to call me ma\'am.',-1),(148112,11,62610,62658,'00:43:28.773','00:43:30.775','Not here.',-1),(148113,11,62801,62826,'00:43:36.739','00:43:37.786','Uh...',-1),(148114,11,62830,62888,'00:43:37.949','00:43:40.372','Do you want to talk about the bathroom?',-1),(148115,11,62908,62980,'00:43:41.202','00:43:44.172','Or anything about Miss Leefolt?',-1),(148116,11,63003,63115,'00:43:45.164','00:43:49.795','How she pays you, or has she ever\nyelled at you in front of Mae Mobley?',-1),(148117,11,63221,63301,'00:43:54.215','00:43:57.560','I thought I might write my stories down\nand read them to you.',-1),(148118,11,63318,63368,'00:43:58.261','00:44:00.355','Ain\'t no different than writing down\nmy prayers.',-1),(148119,11,63463,63497,'00:44:04.308','00:44:05.730','OK.',-1),(148120,11,63534,63559,'00:44:07.270','00:44:08.317','Sure.',-1),(148121,11,63736,63795,'00:44:15.695','00:44:18.164','I don\'t say my prayers out loud.',-1),(148122,11,63799,63875,'00:44:18.322','00:44:21.496','I can get my point across\na lot better writing them down.',-1),(148123,11,63879,64001,'00:44:21.659','00:44:26.711','I write an hour,\nsometimes two, every night.',-1),(148124,11,64004,64117,'00:44:26.873','00:44:31.549','And after my prayers last night,\nI got some stories down, too.',-1),(148125,11,64196,64227,'00:44:34.839','00:44:36.136','Go ahead.',-1),(148126,11,64458,64532,'00:44:45.766','00:44:48.861','\"My first white baby to ever look after',-1),(148127,11,64536,64613,'00:44:49.020','00:44:52.240','was named Alton Carrington Speers.',-1),(148128,11,64617,64714,'00:44:52.398','00:44:56.448','It was 1925, and I had just turned 14.',-1),(148129,11,64730,64803,'00:44:57.111','00:45:00.160','I dropped out of school\nto help Mama with the bills.',-1),(148130,11,64807,64870,'00:45:00.323','00:45:02.917','Alton\'s mama died of lung disease.\"',-1),(148131,11,64922,64952,'00:45:05.119','00:45:06.371','[sighs]',-1),(148132,11,64956,65051,'00:45:06.537','00:45:10.462','I loved that baby. And he loved me.',-1),(148133,11,65110,65184,'00:45:12.919','00:45:16.014','That\'s when I learned I could make\nchildren feel proud of theyself_',-1),(148134,11,65249,65332,'00:45:18.716','00:45:22.186','Alton used to always be asking me\nhow come I was black.',-1),(148135,11,65336,65385,'00:45:22.345','00:45:24.393','Just ate him up.',-1),(148136,11,65389,65482,'00:45:24.555','00:45:28.435','And one time, I told him it was because\nI drank too much coffee. [chortling]',-1),(148137,11,65584,65647,'00:45:32.688','00:45:35.316','You should have seen his face.',-1),(148138,11,65944,66007,'00:45:47.703','00:45:50.297','This was just so great.',-1),(148139,11,66054,66134,'00:45:52.291','00:45:55.591','I can\'t tell you how much I appreciate\nyour doing this with me.',-1),(148140,11,66164,66205,'00:45:56.837','00:45:58.555','What changed your mind?',-1),(148141,11,66246,66273,'00:46:00.258','00:46:01.384','God.',-1),(148142,11,66325,66372,'00:46:03.552','00:46:05.520','And Miss Hilly Holbrook.',-1),(148143,11,66376,66425,'00:46:05.680','00:46:07.728','[radio on, indistinct]',-1),(148144,11,66689,66801,'00:46:18.734','00:46:23.410','Miss Hilly, I would like to ask you\nand Mr. William something.',-1),(148145,11,66884,66982,'00:46:26.867','00:46:30.917','My twin boys graduated from high school,\nboth on the honor roll.',-1),(148146,11,66997,67081,'00:46:31.580','00:46:35.050','Me and my husband, we been saving\nfor years to send them to Tougaloo.',-1),(148147,11,67129,67204,'00:46:37.044','00:46:40.173','We\'re short about $75\non one of the tuitions.',-1),(148148,11,67253,67372,'00:46:42.216','00:46:47.188','Whoo! I am late. I gotta get going.',-1),(148149,11,67443,67472,'00:46:50.141','00:46:51.358','See you tonight, honey.',-1),(148150,11,67476,67501,'00:46:51.517','00:46:52.564','OK.',-1),(148151,11,67511,67555,'00:46:52.977','00:46:54.820','[door opens, closes]',-1),(148152,11,67559,67586,'00:46:54.979','00:46:56.105','Go on.',-1),(148153,11,67670,67739,'00:46:59.608','00:47:02.487','Well, now we\'re... [clears throat]',-1),(148154,11,67743,67808,'00:47:02.653','00:47:05.372','...faced with having to choose',-1),(148155,11,67812,67875,'00:47:05.531','00:47:08.159','which son can go if we don\'t\ncome up with the money.',-1),(148156,11,67904,67967,'00:47:09.368','00:47:11.996','Would you consider giving us a Ioan?',-1),(148157,11,67985,68111,'00:47:12.747','00:47:17.969','I\'d work every day for free\ntill it was paid off.',-1),(148158,11,68115,68211,'00:47:18.127','00:47:22.132','That\'s not working for free.\nThat\'s paying off a debt.',-1),(148159,11,68271,68307,'00:47:24.633','00:47:26.135','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(148160,11,68401,68503,'00:47:30.056','00:47:34.311','As a Christian, I\'m doing you a favor.',-1),(148161,11,68545,68646,'00:47:36.062','00:47:40.283','See, God don\'t give charity to those\nwho are well and able.',-1),(148162,11,68674,68765,'00:47:41.442','00:47:45.242','You need to come up with this money\non your own. OK?',-1),(148163,11,68818,68867,'00:47:47.448','00:47:49.496','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(148164,11,68871,68907,'00:47:49.658','00:47:51.126','You\'ll thank me one day.',-1),(148165,11,68967,69048,'00:47:53.662','00:47:57.007','[Minny] You cooking white food,\nyou taste it with a different spoon.',-1),(148166,11,69066,69117,'00:47:57.750','00:47:59.878','If they see you put the tasting spoon\nback in the pot,',-1),(148167,11,69121,69153,'00:48:00.044','00:48:01.387','might as well throw it all out.',-1),(148168,11,69157,69185,'00:48:01.545','00:48:02.717','Spoon, too.',-1),(148169,11,69189,69266,'00:48:02.880','00:48:06.100','And you use the same cup, same fork,\nsame plate every day.',-1),(148170,11,69270,69308,'00:48:06.258','00:48:07.851','And you put it up in the cabinet.',-1),(148171,11,69312,69377,'00:48:08.010','00:48:10.729','You tell that white woman that\'s where\nyou\'re gonna keep it from now on out.',-1),(148172,11,69381,69424,'00:48:10.888','00:48:12.686','Don\'t do it and see what happens.',-1),(148173,11,69428,69468,'00:48:12.848','00:48:14.521','Morning, ladies.',-1),(148174,11,69472,69512,'00:48:14.683','00:48:16.356','When you\'re sewing white folks coffee,',-1),(148175,11,69516,69547,'00:48:16.519','00:48:17.816','set it down in front of them.',-1),(148176,11,69551,69615,'00:48:17.978','00:48:20.652','Don\'t hand it to them,\n\'cause your hands can\'t touch.',-1),(148177,11,69634,69699,'00:48:21.440','00:48:24.159','And don\'t hit on they children.',-1),(148178,11,69703,69764,'00:48:24.318','00:48:26.867','White folks like to do\nthey own spanking.',-1),(148179,11,69795,69855,'00:48:28.155','00:48:30.658','And last thing. Come here.',-1),(148180,11,69886,69916,'00:48:31.951','00:48:33.168','Look at me.',-1),(148181,11,69919,69976,'00:48:33.327','00:48:35.671','No Sass-mouthing.',-1),(148182,11,70026,70084,'00:48:37.790','00:48:40.168','No Sass-mouthing.',-1),(148183,11,70088,70129,'00:48:40.334','00:48:42.052','I mean it.',-1),(148184,11,70254,70286,'00:48:47.258','00:48:48.601','Give your mama a kiss.',-1),(148185,11,70350,70458,'00:48:51.262','00:48:55.768','[Aibileen] Leroy had made Sugar quit\nschool to help him with the bills.',-1),(148186,11,70551,70633,'00:48:59.645','00:49:03.070','And every day Minny\nwent without a job,',-1),(148187,11,70637,70703,'00:49:03.232','00:49:05.985','might have been a day Leroy\ntook her from our world.',-1),(148188,11,70810,70852,'00:49:10.448','00:49:12.200','Good morning, everybody.',-1),(148189,11,71017,71049,'00:49:19.081','00:49:20.378','But I knew.',-1),(148190,11,71052,71156,'00:49:20.541','00:49:24.842','I knew the only white lady Miss Hilly\nhadn\'t gotten to with her lies.',-1),(148191,11,71357,71398,'00:49:33.220','00:49:34.938','[excitedly] Hey!',-1),(148192,11,71402,71475,'00:49:35.097','00:49:38.146','[giggling] Come on!',-1),(148193,11,71479,71586,'00:49:38.309','00:49:42.780','No sass-mouthing, Minny Jackson.\nNo Sass-mouthing.',-1),(148194,11,71632,71695,'00:49:44.690','00:49:47.318','Aibileen said you\'d be on time.',-1),(148195,11,71797,71842,'00:49:51.572','00:49:53.449','I\'m Celia Rae Foote.',-1),(148196,11,71846,71886,'00:49:53.616','00:49:55.289','I\'m Minny Jackson.',-1),(148197,11,71925,71999,'00:49:56.911','00:49:59.960','You, uh... cooking something?',-1),(148198,11,72027,72110,'00:50:01.165','00:50:04.590','One of those upside-down cakes\nfrom a magazine.',-1),(148199,11,72114,72204,'00:50:04.752','00:50:08.507','It ain\'t working out too good.\nCome on, let\'s get you a cold Coca-Cola.',-1),(148200,11,72269,72293,'00:50:11.217','00:50:12.218','Come on.',-1),(148201,11,72344,72393,'00:50:14.345','00:50:16.393','This here is the kitchen.',-1),(148202,11,72423,72478,'00:50:17.640','00:50:19.938','What in the hell?',-1),(148203,11,72559,72617,'00:50:23.312','00:50:25.735','I guess I got some learning to do.',-1),(148204,11,72635,72708,'00:50:26.482','00:50:29.531','[scoffs] You sure do.',-1),(148205,11,72712,72785,'00:50:29.693','00:50:32.742','Johnny\'s grandmama left him this house\nwhen she died.',-1),(148206,11,72789,72861,'00:50:32.905','00:50:35.909','And then Johnny\'s mama\nwouldn\'t let me change a thing.',-1),(148207,11,72865,72913,'00:50:36.075','00:50:38.077','But if I had it my way,',-1),(148208,11,72917,73035,'00:50:38.244','00:50:43.125','this place would be wall-to-wall\nwhite carpet with gold trim.',-1),(148209,11,73038,73091,'00:50:43.290','00:50:45.463','None of this old stuff.',-1),(148210,11,73095,73150,'00:50:45.626','00:50:47.924','The main house has\nfive beds and baths,',-1),(148211,11,73154,73257,'00:50:48.087','00:50:52.388','and then the pool house has\ntwo more beds and baths.',-1),(148212,11,73261,73313,'00:50:52.550','00:50:54.723','When y\'all gonna start\nhaving some children,',-1),(148213,11,73317,73367,'00:50:54.885','00:50:56.979','filling up all these empty beds?',-1),(148214,11,73419,73482,'00:50:59.139','00:51:01.767','- I\'m pregnant now.\n- Oh.',-1),(148215,11,73486,73570,'00:51:01.934','00:51:05.438','Gonna be eating for two.\nThat\'s double the cooking.',-1),(148216,11,73595,73664,'00:51:06.480','00:51:09.359','I know. It\'s an awful lotto do.',-1),(148217,11,73689,73763,'00:51:10.401','00:51:13.496','Five other maids have\nalready turned me down.',-1),(148218,11,73787,73850,'00:51:14.488','00:51:17.116','Let me at least get you some bus money.',-1),(148219,11,73854,73936,'00:51:17.283','00:51:20.708','Now, uh... when did you hear me say\nI don\'t want to clean this house?',-1),(148220,11,73966,74044,'00:51:21.954','00:51:25.208','Wait. So you\'ll do it?',-1),(148221,11,74116,74141,'00:51:28.168','00:51:29.215','[shrieks]',-1),(148222,11,74145,74182,'00:51:29.378','00:51:30.925','[laughing happily]',-1),(148223,11,74202,74243,'00:51:31.755','00:51:33.473','Ooh. No hugging. No hugging.',-1),(148224,11,74271,74375,'00:51:34.633','00:51:38.979','I\'m sorry. This is the first time\nI\'ve hired a maid.',-1),(148225,11,74397,74434,'00:51:39.888','00:51:41.435','Come on.',-1),(148226,11,74438,74491,'00:51:41.599','00:51:43.818','[laughing, giggling]',-1),(148227,11,74584,74667,'00:51:47.688','00:51:51.158','- You hungry?\n- No, ma\'am. Hold on a minute.',-1),(148228,11,74671,74720,'00:51:51.317','00:51:53.365','We gots to talk about\nsome things first.',-1),(148229,11,74772,74817,'00:51:55.529','00:51:57.406','Oh.',-1),(148230,11,74821,74860,'00:51:57.573','00:51:59.200','I work Sunday through Friday.',-1),(148231,11,74864,74936,'00:51:59.366','00:52:02.370','No, you can\'t work at all\non the weekends.',-1),(148232,11,74940,75021,'00:52:02.536','00:52:05.915','OK. What time you want me here?',-1),(148233,11,75049,75142,'00:52:07.082','00:52:10.928','After 9:00, and you gotta leave\nbefore 4:00.',-1),(148234,11,75170,75198,'00:52:12.087','00:52:13.259','OK.',-1),(148235,11,75202,75243,'00:52:13.422','00:52:15.140','Now...',-1),(148236,11,75247,75285,'00:52:15.299','00:52:16.892','What your husband say you can pay?',-1),(148237,11,75325,75375,'00:52:18.552','00:52:20.646','Johnny doesn\'t know\nI\'m bringing in help.',-1),(148238,11,75379,75429,'00:52:20.804','00:52:22.898','And what Mr. Johnny gonna do\nwhen he come home',-1),(148239,11,75433,75485,'00:52:23.057','00:52:25.230','and find a colored woman in his house?',-1),(148240,11,75489,75556,'00:52:25.392','00:52:28.191','It\'s not like I\'d be fibbing.',-1),(148241,11,75560,75618,'00:52:28.354','00:52:30.777','I just want him to think I can do this\non my own.',-1),(148242,11,75668,75725,'00:52:32.858','00:52:35.236','I really need a maid.',-1),(148243,11,75773,75830,'00:52:37.237','00:52:39.615','I\'ll be here tomorrow morning\nabout 9:15.',-1),(148244,11,75834,75877,'00:52:39.782','00:52:41.580','[chuckling]',-1),(148245,11,75881,75908,'00:52:41.742','00:52:42.868','Great.',-1),(148246,11,75985,76045,'00:52:46.080','00:52:48.549','- Miss Celia?\n- Hmm?',-1),(148247,11,76058,76104,'00:52:49.124','00:52:51.001','I think you done burned up your cake.',-1),(148248,11,76178,76210,'00:52:54.088','00:52:55.431','Doggone it!',-1),(148249,11,76214,76286,'0