ut\nMiss Leefolt now.',-1),(148291,11,81405,81481,'00:56:31.889','00:56:35.063','Baby Girl still gotta wear a diaper\nwhen she sleep at night.',-1),(148292,11,81485,81539,'00:56:35.225','00:56:37.478','And it don\'t get changed till\nI get there in the morning.',-1),(148293,11,81543,81611,'00:56:37.644','00:56:40.488','That about ten hours\nshe gotta sleep in her mess.',-1),(148294,11,81643,81705,'00:56:41.815','00:56:44.409','Now Miss Leefolt pregnant\nwith her second baby.',-1),(148295,11,81725,81805,'00:56:45.235','00:56:48.580','Lord... I pray this child\nturn out good.',-1),(148296,11,81827,81894,'00:56:49.489','00:56:52.288','It\'s a lonely road if a mama\ndon\'t think their child is pretty.',-1),(148297,11,81965,82010,'00:56:55.245','00:56:57.088','That\'s very true.',-1),(148298,11,82103,82150,'00:57:00.959','00:57:02.927','Miss Leefolt should not\nbe having babies.',-1),(148299,11,82257,82284,'00:57:07.382','00:57:08.508','Write that down.',-1),(148300,11,82455,82519,'00:57:15.641','00:57:18.315','Treelore would like me doing this.',-1),(148301,11,82523,82590,'00:57:18.477','00:57:21.276','He always said we were gonna have\na writer in the family one day.',-1),(148302,11,82594,82652,'00:57:21.438','00:57:23.861','I always thought it was gonna be him.\nMaybe it\'s gonna be me.',-1),(148303,11,82678,82725,'00:57:24.942','00:57:26.910','[Minny] Aibileen, Aibileen.',-1),(148304,11,82729,82796,'00:57:27.069','00:57:29.868','They done set a bomb off\nin Medgar Evers\' carport.',-1),(148305,11,83000,83092,'00:57:38.372','00:57:42.172','Yule Mae told me what y\'all was up to.\nI didn\'t want to believe it.',-1),(148306,11,83159,83232,'00:57:44.962','00:57:48.011','And just what makes you think\ncolored people need your help?',-1),(148307,11,83259,83297,'00:57:49.132','00:57:50.725','- Why do you care?\n- Minny.',-1),(148308,11,83301,83344,'00:57:50.884','00:57:52.682','Maybe you just want\nto get Aibileen in trouble.',-1),(148309,11,83348,83386,'00:57:52.844','00:5