.',-1),(148350,11,87101,87134,'01:00:29.209','01:00:30.586','We gone and done it now.',-1),(148351,11,87138,87183,'01:00:30.752','01:00:32.629','[laughing]',-1),(148352,11,87196,87320,'01:00:33.171','01:00:38.348','Skeeter! Get down here! Something just\narrived from New York for you.',-1),(148353,11,87517,87541,'01:00:46.560','01:00:47.561','[shrieking]',-1),(148354,11,87694,87718,'01:00:53.942','01:00:54.943','What is that?',-1),(148355,11,87722,87810,'01:00:55.110','01:00:58.785','The Shinalator.\nAll the way from New York City.',-1),(148356,11,87830,87899,'01:00:59.614','01:01:02.493','I\'m a good mother.\nCome on. Sit down.',-1),(148357,11,87937,88063,'01:01:04.077','01:01:09.299','The whole system cost 11 dollars.\nEven smells expensive.',-1),(148358,11,88103,88185,'01:01:10.959','01:01:14.384','You\'re gonna look beautiful\non your date tonight.',-1),(148359,11,88189,88245,'01:01:14.546','01:01:16.890','I can feel the hope in your fingers.',-1),(148360,11,88317,88365,'01:01:19.885','01:01:21.887','Holy shit.',-1),(148361,11,88369,88431,'01:01:22.053','01:01:24.647','- You shrunk five inches.\n- Oh, my God.',-1),(148362,11,88435,88484,'01:01:24.806','01:01:26.854','You\'ll be able to wear heels tonight.',-1),(148363,11,88504,88584,'01:01:27.684','01:01:31.029','You\'re not leaving the house in those\nawful Mexican man shoes.',-1),(148364,11,88588,88614,'01:01:31.188','01:01:32.280','Can I take the Cadillac?',-1),(148365,11,88618,88676,'01:01:32.439','01:01:34.862','We promised the Cadillac\nto Carlton and Rebecca tonight,',-1),(148366,11,88680,88755,'01:01:35.025','01:01:38.154','so William\'s cousin will just\nhave to come pick you up himself.',-1),(148367,11,88759,88821,'01:01:38.320','01:01:40.914','- I\'ll take the truck.\n- it\'s hooked up to the motor grader.',-1),(148368,11,88825,88849,'01:01:41.072','01:01:42.073','I\'ll drive slow.',-1),(148369,11,88853,88919,'01:01:42.240','01:01:44.993','[mother] Skeeter! Skeeter!',-1),(148370,11,88923,89040,'01:01:45.160','01:01:50.007','Now remember, no gentleman wants\nto spend the evening with a sourpuss.',-1),(148371,11,89043,89122,'01:01:50.165','01:01:53.419','Don\'t mope! Smile!',-1),(148372,11,89126,89254,'01:01:53.585','01:01:58.933','And for heaven\'s sakes, don\'t sit like\nsome squaw Indian! Cross your ankles!',-1),(148373,11,89283,89318,'01:02:00.133','01:02:01.601','I love you!',-1),(148374,11,89545,89583,'01:02:11.061','01:02:12.654','Stuart, she\'ll be here any minute.',-1),(148375,11,89626,89651,'01:02:14.439','01:02:15.486','Hâ¬Y-',-1),(148376,11,89707,89739,'01:02:17.817','01:02:19.160','Skeeter.',-1),(148377,11,89795,89892,'01:02:21.488','01:02:25.538','Boys, we\'ll be right back. Y\'all talk\nabout quarterbacks or something.',-1),(148378,11,89896,89939,'01:02:25.700','01:02:27.498','Yule Mae, get Miss Skeeter a Coca-Cola.',-1),(148379,11,89943,89971,'01:02:27.661','01:02:28.833','Yes, ma\'am.',-1),(148380,11,90009,90110,'01:02:30.413','01:02:34.589','[swing music]',-1),(148381,11,90250,90274,'01:02:40.423','01:02:41.424','[whistling]',-1),(148382,11,90313,90337,'01:02:43.051','01:02:44.052','Want a drink?',-1),(148383,11,90341,90384,'01:02:44.219','01:02:46.017','Just water, please.',-1),(148384,11,90419,90514,'01:02:47.472','01:02:51.443','[sighing] Double Old Kentucky, straight\nwith a water back. Make that two backs.',-1),(148385,11,90518,90587,'01:02:51.601','01:02:54.480','You sure you don\'t want to just make it\nthe whole bottle and a straw?',-1),(148386,11,90606,90670,'01:02:55.272','01:02:57.946','Honey, there\'s the lieutenant governor.\nLet\'s go say hi.',-1),(148387,11,90777,90837,'01:03:02.404','01:03:04.907','Good to see you, sir.\nYou remember my wife?',-1),(148388,11,90841,90870,'01:03:05.073','01:03:06.290','Hi, how are you? Good to see you.',-1),(148389,11,90874,90914,'01:03:06.449','01:03:08.122','[burping]',-1),(148390,11,90992,91072,'01:03:11.371','01:03:14.671','So, what do you do with your time?',-1),(148391,11,91100,91125,'01:03:15.834','01:03:16.881','You work?',-1),(148392,11,91144,91178,'01:03:17.669','01:03:19.091','I write.',-1),(148393,11,91203,91263,'01:03:20.130','01:03:22.633','But right now I\'m working on\na domestic maintenance column',-1),(148394,11,91267,91293,'01:03:22.799','01:03:23.891','for The Jackson Journal.',-1),(148395,11,91344,91372,'01:03:26.011','01:03:27.183','You mean housekeeping.',-1),(148396,11,91400,91485,'01:03:28.346','01:03:31.896','Jesus, I can\'t think of anything worse\nthan reading a cleaning column,',-1),(148397,11,91489,91533,'01:03:32.058','01:03:33.901','except for maybe writing one.',-1),(148398,11,91537,91574,'01:03:34.060','01:03:35.607','Well, I can.',-1),(148399,11,91578,91676,'01:03:35.770','01:03:39.866','Working with a bunch of greasy,\nstinky men in the middle of the ocean.',-1),(148400,11,91680,91764,'01:03:40.025','01:03:43.529','It sounds like a ploy to find a husband,\nbecoming an expert in keeping house.',-1),(148401,11,91768,91855,'01:03:43.695','01:03:47.325','Well, aren\'t you a genius?\nYou figured out my whole scheme.',-1),(148402,11,91859,91937,'01:03:47.490','01:03:50.710','Isn\'t that what all you girls\nfrom Ole Miss major in...',-1),(148403,11,91940,91982,'01:03:50.869','01:03:52.587','...professional husband hunting?',-1),(148404,11,91985,92056,'01:03:52.746','01:03:55.670','Who is hungry?',-1),(148405,11,92059,92146,'01:03:55.832','01:03:59.427','I\'m sorry, but were you dropped\non your head as an infant?',-1),(148406,11,92150,92188,'01:03:59.586','01:04:01.179','Or were you just born stupid?',-1),(148407,11,92192,92222,'01:04:01.338','01:04:02.590','[coughing]',-1),(148408,11,92465,92510,'01:04:12.724','01:04:14.601','[squawking]',-1),(148409,11,92622,92665,'01:04:19.272','01:04:21.070','[chopping]',-1),(148410,11,92712,92761,'01:04:23.026','01:04:25.074','So, what can you cook?',-1),(148411,11,92792,92871,'01:04:26.363','01:04:29.663','Oh, um, I can cook cornpone.',-1),(148412,11,92899,92935,'01:04:30.825','01:04:32.327','Boil potatoes.',-1),(148413,11,92960,92987,'01:04:33.370','01:04:34.462','I can do grits.',-1),(148414,11,92990,93040,'01:04:34.621','01:04:36.669','[laughing]',-1),(148415,11,93071,93097,'01:04:37.999','01:04:39.046','Well...',-1),(148416,11,93119,93213,'01:04:39.959','01:04:43.884','...I reckon if there\'s anything you\nought to know about cooking, it\'s this.',-1),(148417,11,93217,93291,'01:04:44.047','01:04:47.142','The most important invention since\nthey put mayonnaise in a jar.',-1),(148418,11,93343,93390,'01:04:49.302','01:04:51.270','- You got gum in your hair,\n- [sizzling]',-1),(148419,11,93394,93447,'01:04:51.429','01:04:53.648','you got a squeaky door hinge...',-1),(148420,11,93451,93475,'01:04:53.807','01:04:54.808','Crisco.',-1),(148421,11,93517,93556,'01:04:56.559','01:04:58.186','How pretty.',-1),(148422,11,93602,93648,'01:05:00.105','01:05:02.028','Looks like frosting.',-1),(148423,11,93652,93721,'01:05:02.190','01:05:05.069','You got bags under your eyes.',-1),(148424,11,93725,93772,'01:05:05.235','01:05:07.203','Want to soften your husband\'s\nscaly feet.',-1),(148425,11,93799,93838,'01:05:08.321','01:05:09.948','Mm-hm. Crisco.',-1),(148426,11,93872,93945,'01:05:11.366','01:05:14.415','But it\'s best for frying chicken.',-1),(148427,11,93975,94016,'01:05:15.662','01:05:17.335','Frying chicken just...',-1),(148428,11,94043,94094,'01:05:18.498','01:05:20.592','...tend to make you\nfeel better about life.',-1),(148429,11,94179,94213,'01:05:24.129','01:05:25.551','At least me, anyway.',-1),(148430,11,94246,94310,'01:05:26.923','01:05:29.597','Mm, I love me some fried chicken.',-1),(148431,11,94348,94374,'01:05:31.177','01:05:32.269','Now...',-1),(148432,11,94423,94447,'01:05:34.305','01:05:35.306','...shake that.',-1),(148433,11,94451,94487,'01:05:35.473','01:05:36.975','Oh.',-1),(148434,11,94603,94671,'01:05:41.813','01:05:44.657','This is so much fun!',-1),(148435,11,94705,94788,'01:05:46.067','01:05:49.537','All right, all right.\nThe chicken already dead, Miss Celia.',-1),(148436,11,94793,94857,'01:05:49.737','01:05:52.411','[giggling]',-1),(148437,11,94878,94911,'01:05:53.283','01:05:54.660','Yep. He dead.',-1),(148438,11,95057,95094,'01:06:00.748','01:06:02.250','[sighing]',-1),(148439,11,95180,95212,'01:06:05.837','01:06:07.180','[Celia] There you are.',-1),(148440,11,95244,95361,'01:06:08.506','01:06:13.387','I\'m starved. Looks so good.',-1),(148441,11,95374,95415,'01:06:13.928','01:06:15.646','We done been over this, Miss Celia.',-1),(148442,11,95419,95512,'01:06:15.805','01:06:19.685','You supposed to eat in the dining room.\nThat\'s how it works.',-1),(148443,11,95516,95544,'01:06:19.851','01:06:21.023','Let me take your plate back.',-1),(148444,11,95560,95610,'01:06:21.686','01:06:23.780','I\'m fine right here, Minny.',-1),(148445,11,95894,95937,'01:06:35.617','01:06:37.415','[sighing]',-1),(148446,11,96078,96103,'01:06:43.291','01:06:44.292','What?',-1),(148447,11,96138,96191,'01:06:45.752','01:06:47.971','I just want you to know\nI\'m real grateful you\'re here.',-1),(148448,11,96195,96261,'01:06:48.129','01:06:50.882','You gots plenty more\nto be grateful for than me.',-1),(148449,11,96295,96375,'01:06:52.300','01:06:55.645','And look, now I ain\'t\nmessing around no more.',-1),(148450,11,96379,96410,'01:06:55.803','01:06:57.100','Now Mr. Johnny gonna catch me here,',-1),(148451,11,96414,96482,'01:06:57.263','01:07:00.107','and shoot me dead right here\non this no-wax floor.',-1),(148452,11,96508,96533,'01:07:01.184','01:07:02.231','You gots to tell him.',-1),(148453,11,96537,96605,'01:07:02.393','01:07:05.237','Ain\'t he wondering how\nthe cooking\'s so good?',-1),(148454,11,96609,96648,'01:07:05.396','01:07:07.023','You\'re right.',-1),(148455,11,96692,96740,'01:07:08.858','01:07:10.860','Maybe we ought to\nburn the chicken a little.',-1),(148456,11,96790,96830,'01:07:12.946','01:07:14.619','Minny don\'t burn chicken.',-1),(148457,11,96895,96982,'01:07:17.325','01:07:20.955','I like this Sarah Ross. She testifies\nwithout complaining too much.',-1),(148458,11,96986,97074,'01:07:21.120','01:07:24.750','And that Bertha,\nshe\'s got chutzpah, I\'ll give her that.',-1),(148459,11,97077,97110,'01:07:24.916','01:07:26.259','So you liked it?',-1),(148460,11,97114,97177,'01:07:26.417','01:07:29.045','Eugenia, Martin Luther King\njust invited',-1),(148461,11,97181,97252,'01:07:29.212','01:07:32.182','the entire country to march with him\nin D.C. in August.',-1),(148462,11,97256,97288,'01:07:32.340','01:07:33.683','This many Negroes and whites',-1),(148463,11,97292,97349,'01:07:33.841','01:07:36.219','have not worked together since\nGone with the Wind.',-1),(148464,11,97353,97419,'01:07:36.386','01:07:39.139','How many stories have you\nrecorded thus far?',-1),(148465,11,97423,97471,'01:07:39.305','01:07:41.307','The ones you\'ve read.',-1),(148466,11,97475,97519,'01:07:41.474','01:07:43.317','Two domestics, that\'s all?',-1),(148467,11,97523,97553,'01:07:43.476','01:07:44.728','[scoffing]',-1),(148468,11,97573,97619,'01:07:45.562','01:07:47.485','[Skeeter] I\'m real close to\ngetting more interviews.',-1),(148469,11,97623,97719,'01:07:47.647','01:07:51.652','Don\'t send me anything else\nuntil you do have more maids.',-1),(148470,11,97723,97791,'01:07:51.818','01:07:54.662','Yes, ma\'am. How... how many more?',-1),(148471,11,97795,97864,'01:07:54.821','01:07:57.700','I don\'t know. At least a dozen.',-1),(148472,11,97868,97949,'01:07:57.865','01:08:01.210','My advice to you is to write it\nand write it fast',-1),(148473,11,97952,98009,'01:08:01.369','01:08:03.713','before this whole civil rights thing\nblows over.',-1),(148474,11,98012,98053,'01:08:03.871','01:08:05.544','Now good night to you, Miss Phelan.',-1),(148475,11,98352,98401,'01:08:18.011','01:08:20.059','We need a dozen more.',-1),(148476,11,98421,98523,'01:08:20.888','01:08:25.143','Me and Aibileen done asked everybody\nwe know. Thirty-one maids.',-1),(148477,11,98545,98594,'01:08:26.060','01:08:28.108','They all too scared. Think we crazy.',-1),(148478,11,98639,98690,'01:08:29.981','01:08:32.109','If we don\'t get more,\nwe\'re not getting published.',-1),(148479,11,98694,98765,'01:08:32.275','01:08:35.245','[Minny] I gots plenty stories,\nMiss Skeeter.',-1),(148480,11,98769,98855,'01:08:35.403','01:08:38.998','Just write them down\nand invent the maid that said it.',-1),(148481,11,98859,98920,'01:08:39.157','01:08:41.706','You\'re already making up names.\nJust make up the maids, too.',-1),(148482,11,98924,99019,'01:08:41.868','01:08:45.793','We\'re not gonna do that.\nThat would be wrong.',-1),(148483,11,99022,99055,'01:08:45.955','01:08:47.298','Don\'t give up on this, Miss Skeeter.',-1),(148484,11,99058,99098,'01:08:47.457','01:08:49.084','It wouldn\'t be real.',-1),(148485,11,99135,99172,'01:08:50.627','01:08:52.174','They Killed my son.',-1),(148486,11,99359,99413,'01:08:59.969','01:09:02.222','He fell carrying two-by-fours\nat the mill.',-1),(148487,11,99451,99503,'01:09:03.806','01:09:05.979','Truck run over him, crushed his lung.',-1),(148488,11,99507,99545,'01:09:06.142','01:09:07.735','[whispering] Aibileen.',-1),(148489,11,99625,99691,'01:09:11.064','01:09:13.817','That white foreman threw his body\non back of a truck.',-1),(148490,11,99710,99779,'01:09:14.609','01:09:17.488','Drove to the colored hospital...',-1),(148491,11,99783,99830,'01:09:17.654','01:09:19.622','...dumped him there and honked the horn.',-1),(148492,11,100081,100183,'01:09:30.083','01:09:34.304','There was nothing they could do,\nso I brought my baby home.',-1),(148493,11,100297,100351,'01:09:39.050','01:09:41.303','[voice breaking]\nLaid him down on that sofa right there.',-1),(148494,11,100438,100486,'01:09:44.931','01:09:46.933','He died right in front of me.',-1),(148495,11,100548,100635,'01:09:49.519','01:09:53.149','He was just 24 years old, Miss Skeeter.\nBest part of a person\'s life.',-1),(148496,11,100674,100760,'01:09:54.774','01:09:58.369','Anniversary of his death