8902,118941,'01:22:34.283','01:22:35.876','- I\'m OK.\n- The bullet hit him in the back,',-1),(148682,11,118944,119013,'01:22:36.034','01:22:38.913','crashed through his body\nthrough a window, into the house.',-1),(148683,11,119017,119077,'01:22:39.079','01:22:41.548','He died within an hour\nat a Jackson hospital.',-1),(148684,11,119080,119137,'01:22:41.707','01:22:44.051','City detectives believe the fatal shot\nwas fired from...',-1),(148685,11,119141,119237,'01:22:44.209','01:22:48.214','KKK shot him. An hour ago.',-1),(148686,11,119279,119326,'01:22:49.965','01:22:51.933','Right in front of his children,\nAibileen.',-1),(148687,11,119364,119437,'01:22:53.510','01:22:56.559','We\'re gonna pray for the Evers.\nWe\'re gonna pray for Myrlie.',-1),(148688,11,119441,119521,'01:22:56.722','01:23:00.067','We living in hell. Trapped.',-1),(148689,11,119544,119578,'01:23:01.018','01:23:02.440','Our kids, trapped.',-1),(148690,11,119582,119624,'01:23:02.603','01:23:04.355','[coughing]',-1),(148691,11,119661,119721,'01:23:05.898','01:23:08.401','Sugar, take your brothers and sisters\nand y\'all go on to bed.',-1),(148692,11,119852,119896,'01:23:13.864','01:23:15.707','Good night.',-1),(148693,11,119900,119957,'01:23:15.866','01:23:18.210','Good night. Good night.',-1),(148694,11,119963,120010,'01:23:18.494','01:23:20.417','[coughing]',-1),(148695,11,120013,120066,'01:23:20.579','01:23:22.752','Oh. Good night, baby.',-1),(148696,11,120344,120395,'01:23:34.343','01:23:36.471','What they gonna do if they catch us\nwith Miss Skeeter?',-1),(148697,11,120419,120452,'01:23:37.471','01:23:38.848','We\'re gonna be careful.',-1),(148698,11,120483,120596,'01:23:40.140','01:23:44.862','Hitch us to a pickup? Drag us behind?\nShoot me in front of my children?',-1),(148699,11,120600,120660,'01:23:45.020','01:23:47.523','We ain\'t doing civil rights.',-1),(148700,11,120664,120734,'01:23:47.689','01:23:50.613','We\'re just telling stories\nlike they really happened.',-1),(148701,11,120779,120835,'01:23:52.486','01:23:54.830','- You\'re a fool, old woman.\n- [chuckling]',-1),(148702,11,120864,120898,'01:23:56.031','01:23:57.453','A fool.',-1),(148703,11,120931,120991,'01:23:58.825','01:24:01.328','[both laughing]',-1),(148704,11,121527,121551,'01:24:23.642','01:24:24.643','[door opening]',-1),(148705,11,121555,121590,'01:24:24.810','01:24:26.278','[phones ringing]',-1),(148706,11,121632,121751,'01:24:28.021','01:24:32.993','Miss Phelan, the presses are heating up.\nWe needed Miss Myrna 30 minutes ago.',-1),(148707,11,121766,121790,'01:24:33.610','01:24:34.611','Yes, Sir.',-1),(148708,11,121794,121831,'01:24:34.778','01:24:36.325','Chop-chop.',-1),(148709,11,121862,121895,'01:24:37.614','01:24:38.991','Good Lord.',-1),(148710,11,121899,121944,'01:24:39.157','01:24:41.000','[vacuum running]',-1),(148711,11,122148,122184,'01:24:49.501','01:24:51.003','[thudding upstairs]',-1),(148712,11,122278,122320,'01:24:54.923','01:24:56.675','[Minny] Miss Celia?',-1),(148713,11,122746,122771,'01:25:14.443','01:25:15.490','Miss Celia?',-1),(148714,11,122775,122823,'01:25:15.652','01:25:17.654','[Celia] Go home.\nI\'ll see you tomorrow.',-1),(148715,11,122827,122881,'01:25:17.821','01:25:20.074','You mess up your hair coloring again?',-1),(148716,11,122885,122969,'01:25:20.240','01:25:23.710','I helped you fix it last time.\nWe got it back to butter batch.',-1),(148717,11,122972,123011,'01:25:23.869','01:25:25.462','Was real pretty, remember?',-1),(148718,11,123107,123140,'01:25:29.499','01:25:30.842','Miss Celia.',-1),(148719,11,123167,123211,'01:25:31.960','01:25:33.803','[Celia] I told you, go home!',-1),(148720,11,123517,123554,'01:25:46.558','01:25:48.105','[loud thudding]',-1),(148721,11,123594,123631,'01:25:49.770','01:25:51.317','[shouting] I said get out!',-1),(148722,11,123635,123673,'01:25:51.480','01:25:53.073','[rattling]',-1),(148723,11,123774,123815,'01:25:57.277','01:25:58.995','[sobbing]',-1),(148724,11,124012,124074,'01:26:07.204','01:26:09.753','Why is there so much blood?',-1),(148725,11,124106,124173,'01:26:11.124','01:26:13.877','[breathing heavily]',-1),(148726,11,124208,124302,'01:26:15.337','01:26:19.262','Next one\'s gonna catch, Miss Celia.\nYou just wait and see.',-1),(148727,11,124358,124422,'01:26:21.593','01:26:24.267','We got married \'cause I was pregnant.',-1),(148728,11,124480,124536,'01:26:26.682','01:26:29.026','Then I lost it a month later.',-1),(148729,11,124597,124644,'01:26:31.561','01:26:33.529','Johnny wants kids now.',-1),(148730,11,124729,124771,'01:26:37.067','01:26:38.819','What\'s he gonna do with me?',-1),(148731,11,124844,124874,'01:26:41.863','01:26:43.115','Well...',-1),(148732,11,124908,124956,'01:26:44.533','01:26:46.535','Mr. Johnny just gonna have\nto get over it.',-1),(148733,11,124960,125014,'01:26:46.702','01:26:48.921','[exhaling]',-1),(148734,11,125017,125067,'01:26:49.079','01:26:51.127','He doesn\'t know about the baby.',-1),(148735,11,125168,125213,'01:26:55.335','01:26:57.212','Or the two before.',-1),(148736,11,125417,125468,'01:27:05.721','01:27:07.849','[sniffing]',-1),(148737,11,126284,126352,'01:27:41.840','01:27:44.684','[indistinct chattering]',-1),(148738,11,126530,126562,'01:27:52.100','01:27:53.443','[man] Yule Mae Davis?',-1),(148739,11,126632,126687,'01:27:56.354','01:27:58.652','- What do you want me to do?\n- You\'re under arrest.',-1),(148740,11,126716,126796,'01:27:59.858','01:28:03.203','Just call my husband.\nJust call my husband.',-1),(148741,11,126885,126964,'01:28:06.907','01:28:10.207','- Wait a minute. I want my purse.\n- No, you\'re under arrest.',-1),(148742,11,126968,127060,'01:28:10.368','01:28:14.168','I want to get my purse. [shouting]\nI want to get my purse! Aibee!',-1),(148743,11,127078,127131,'01:28:14.956','01:28:17.129','- Don\'t fight, Yule Mae!\n- Aibee!',-1),(148744,11,127135,127233,'01:28:17.292','01:28:21.388','Aibee, I want my purse! I want my purse!',-1),(148745,11,127269,127294,'01:28:22.881','01:28:23.928','[sobbing]',-1),(148746,11,127327,127373,'01:28:25.300','01:28:27.223','Just let me go!',-1),(148747,11,127392,127446,'01:28:28.011','01:28:30.264','Yule Mae, don\'t fight.',-1),(148748,11,127651,127726,'01:28:38.814','01:28:41.943','[Hilly] I knew she was a thief\nthe day she started.',-1),(148749,11,127746,127846,'01:28:42.776','01:28:46.952','A nigra walks into a pawn shop\nwith a ring of such size and color.',-1),(148750,11,127878,127953,'01:28:48.281','01:28:51.376','It took them all of ten minutes\nto find out where she worked.',-1),(148751,11,128001,128057,'01:28:53.411','01:28:55.709','I am desperate for\na grilled cheese sandwich.',-1),(148752,11,128060,128119,'01:28:55.872','01:28:58.295','Are you? Are you?\nDo you want a grilled cheese sandwich?',-1),(148753,11,128122,128163,'01:28:58.458','01:29:00.131','- [Billy] Oh, yes.\n- [Hilly laughing]',-1),(148754,11,128167,128209,'01:29:00.293','01:29:02.045','Just go sit down over there.',-1),(148755,11,128213,128262,'01:29:02.212','01:29:04.260','[dishes clattering]',-1),(148756,11,128369,128474,'01:29:08.718','01:29:13.098','Miss Skeeter, you best head on over\nto Miss Aibileen\'s house.',-1),(148757,11,128493,128517,'01:29:13.890','01:29:14.891','Now.',-1),(148758,11,129249,129301,'01:29:45.380','01:29:47.553','I\'m gonna help with your stories.',-1),(148759,11,129334,129390,'01:29:48.925','01:29:51.269','I\'m gonna help, too. Mm-hm.',-1),(148760,11,129435,129463,'01:29:53.138','01:29:54.310','We all are.',-1),(148761,11,129467,129538,'01:29:54.472','01:29:57.442','- [all] That\'s right.\n- I\'ll help you.',-1),(148762,11,129571,129630,'01:29:58.810','01:30:01.279','[woman] I used to take\na shortcut every day',-1),(148763,11,129634,129699,'01:30:01.438','01:30:04.157','when I went to work\nat Dr. Dixon\'s house.',-1),(148764,11,129715,129788,'01:30:04.816','01:30:07.865','Cut through that farmer\'s lower 40\nto get there.',-1),(148765,11,129792,129884,'01:30:08.028','01:30:11.874','One day this farmer\nwas waiting for me with a gun.',-1),(148766,11,129888,129975,'01:30:12.032','01:30:15.627','Said he\'d shoot me dead\nif I walked on his land again.',-1),(148767,11,129991,130129,'01:30:16.328','01:30:22.051','Dr. Dixon went and paid that farmer\ndouble for two of those acres.',-1),(148768,11,130142,130210,'01:30:22.584','01:30:25.428','Told him he was gonna\nstart farming, too.',-1),(148769,11,130233,130345,'01:30:26.379','01:30:31.055','But he bought that just for me,\nso I could get to work easy.',-1),(148770,11,130376,130405,'01:30:32.344','01:30:33.561','He did.',-1),(148771,11,130409,130482,'01:30:33.720','01:30:36.769','I worked for Miss Jolene\'s mother\ntill the day she died.',-1),(148772,11,130503,130587,'01:30:37.641','01:30:41.145','Then her daughter, Miss Nancy,\nasked me to come and work for her.',-1),(148773,11,130613,130668,'01:30:42.228','01:30:44.526','Miss Nancy is a real sweet lady.',-1),(148774,11,130692,130797,'01:30:45.523','01:30:49.903','But Miss Jolene\'s ma done put it in her\nwill I got to work for Miss Jolene.',-1),(148775,11,130822,130890,'01:30:50.946','01:30:53.790','Miss Jolene\'s a mean woman.',-1),(148776,11,130894,130931,'01:30:53.949','01:30:55.496','Mean for sport.',-1),(148777,11,130987,131052,'01:30:57.827','01:31:00.501','Lord, I tried to find another job.',-1),(148778,11,131077,131129,'01:31:01.581','01:31:03.709','But in everybody\'s mind',-1),(148779,11,131133,131214,'01:31:03.875','01:31:07.254','the French family\nand Miss Jolene owned me.',-1),(148780,11,131266,131298,'01:31:09.422','01:31:10.765','Owned me.',-1),(148781,11,131436,131479,'01:31:16.513','01:31:18.311','[Miss Stein] I leave early\nthis week for Thanksgiving.',-1),(148782,11,131483,131550,'01:31:18.473','01:31:21.272','Our last editors\' meeting\nis December 17th,',-1),(148783,11,131554,131596,'01:31:21.434','01:31:23.186','so if you want a prayer\nof this getting read,',-1),(148784,11,131600,131672,'01:31:23.353','01:31:26.357','- I\'d better have it by then.\n- That\'s in