),(149813,39,50680,50724,'00:35:11.697','00:35:13.532','The ship is nice, huh?',-1),(149814,39,50748,50772,'00:35:14.534','00:35:15.534','Yeah. It\'s an Irish ship.',-1),(149815,39,50775,50799,'00:35:15.660','00:35:16.660','Is English, no?',-1),(149816,39,50802,50826,'00:35:16.786','00:35:17.786','No, it was built\nin Ireland.',-1),(149817,39,50828,50872,'00:35:17.870','00:35:19.704','15,000 Irishmen\nbuilt this ship.',-1),(149818,39,50876,50940,'00:35:19.872','00:35:22.541','Solid as a rock.\nBig Irish hands.',-1),(149819,39,50957,50981,'00:35:23.209','00:35:24.209','That\'s typical.',-1),(149820,39,50984,51057,'00:35:24.335','00:35:27.379','First-class dogs\ncome down here to take a shite.',-1),(149821,39,51075,51124,'00:35:28.131','00:35:30.173','Lets us know where we rank\nin the scheme of things.',-1),(149822,39,51129,51169,'00:35:30.383','00:35:32.050','Like we could forget?',-1),(149823,39,51209,51237,'00:35:33.719','00:35:34.886','I\'m Tommy Ryan.',-1),(149824,39,51244,51293,'00:35:35.179','00:35:37.222','- Jack Dawson.\n- Fabrizio.',-1),(149825,39,51343,51380,'00:35:39.308','00:35:40.851','Do you make any money\nwith your drawings?',-1),(149826,39,51645,51685,'00:35:51.904','00:35:53.572','Ah, forget it, boyo.',-1),(149827,39,51687,51741,'00:35:53.656','00:35:55.907','You\'d as like have angels fly out of\nyour arse as get next to...',-1),(149828,39,51745,51781,'00:35:56.075','00:35:57.576','...the likes of her.',-1),(149829,39,52342,52438,'00:36:20.933','00:36:24.936','I saw my whole life\nas if I\'d already lived it.',-1),(149830,39,52446,52530,'00:36:25.271','00:36:28.773','An endless parade\nof parties and cotillions...',-1),(149831,39,52538,52586,'00:36:29.108','00:36:31.109','...yachts and polo matches.',-1),(149832,39,52602,52714,'00:36:31.777','00:36:36.448','Always the same narrow people,\nthe same mindless chatter.',-1),(149833,39,52726,52818,'00:36:36.949','00:36:40.785','I felt like I was standing\nat a great precipice...',-1),(149834,39,52834,5