879,39,58828,58935,'00:40:51.203','00:40:55.665','You can\'t think. Least not about\nanything but the pain.',-1),(149880,39,59009,59087,'00:40:58.711','00:41:01.963','Which is why I\'m not looking\nforward to jumping in there after you.',-1),(149881,39,59113,59137,'00:41:03.048','00:41:04.048','Like I said...',-1),(149882,39,59181,59221,'00:41:05.885','00:41:07.552','...I don\'t have a choice.',-1),(149883,39,59321,59389,'00:41:11.724','00:41:14.559','I guess I\'m kind of hoping you\'ll\ncome back over the rail and...',-1),(149884,39,59391,59425,'00:41:14.643','00:41:16.060','...and get me off\nthe hook here.',-1),(149885,39,59445,59477,'00:41:16.896','00:41:18.229','You\'re crazy.',-1),(149886,39,59509,59561,'00:41:19.565','00:41:21.733','That\'s what everybody says but...',-1),(149887,39,59597,59637,'00:41:23.235','00:41:24.903','...with all due respect, miss...',-1),(149888,39,59639,59705,'00:41:24.987','00:41:27.739','...I\'m not the one hanging off\nthe back of a ship here.',-1),(149889,39,59725,59757,'00:41:28.574','00:41:29.908','Come on.',-1),(149890,39,59773,59813,'00:41:30.576','00:41:32.243','Come on, give me your hand.',-1),(149891,39,59835,59865,'00:41:33.162','00:41:34.412','You don\'t want to do this.',-1),(149892,39,60250,60286,'00:41:50.429','00:41:51.930','I\'m Jack Dawson.',-1),(149893,39,60322,60362,'00:41:53.432','00:41:55.099','Rose DeWitt Bukater.',-1),(149894,39,60369,60410,'00:41:55.392','00:41:57.101','I\'ll have to get you to\nwrite that one down.',-1),(149895,39,60470,60498,'00:41:59.605','00:42:00.772','Come on.',-1),(149896,39,60625,60649,'00:42:06.070','00:42:07.070','I got you.',-1),(149897,39,60661,60726,'00:42:07.571','00:42:10.281','Come on.',-1),(149898,39,60833,60865,'00:42:14.745','00:42:16.079','Help, please!',-1),(149899,39,60872,60910,'00:42:16.372','00:42:17.956','Help!',-1),(149900,39,60945,60970,'00:42:19.416','00:42:20.458','- Please, help me!\n- Listen. Listen to me.',-1),(149901,39,60974,61011,'00:42:20.584','00:42:22.126','Listen. Listen to me.',-1),(149902,39,61015,61055,'00:42:22.294','00:42:23.962','I\'ve got you.\nI won\'t let go.',-1),(149903,39,61062,61110,'00:42:24.255','00:42:26.256','Now pull yourself up.\nCome on!',-1),(149904,39,61183,61207,'00:42:29.301','00:42:30.301','Come on.',-1),(149905,39,61213,61238,'00:42:30.553','00:42:31.594','That\'s right.',-1),(149906,39,61251,61277,'00:42:32.137','00:42:33.221','You can do it.',-1),(149907,39,61395,61427,'00:42:38.143','00:42:39.477','I got you.',-1),(149908,39,61563,61599,'00:42:45.150','00:42:46.651','What\'s all this?',-1),(149909,39,61739,61767,'00:42:52.491','00:42:53.658','You stand back and...',-1),(149910,39,61775,61809,'00:42:53.993','00:42:55.410','...don\'t move an inch!',-1),(149911,39,61865,61892,'00:42:57.746','00:42:58.871','Fetch the Master at Arms.',-1),(149912,39,61956,61994,'00:43:01.500','00:43:03.084','This is completely unacceptable!',-1),(149913,39,61996,62064,'00:43:03.168','00:43:06.004','What made you think that you could\nput your hands on my fiancÃ©e?!',-1),(149914,39,62104,62132,'00:43:07.673','00:43:08.840','Look at me, you filth!',-1),(149915,39,62140,62164,'00:43:09.174','00:43:10.174','Cal.',-1),(149916,39,62168,62195,'00:43:10.342','00:43:11.467','What do you think\nyou were doing?',-1),(149917,39,62200,62260,'00:43:11.677','00:43:14.178','Cal, stop.\nIt was an accident.',-1),(149918,39,62276,62316,'00:43:14.847','00:43:16.514','An accident?',-1),(149919,39,62324,62356,'00:43:16.849','00:43:18.182','It was.',-1),(149920,39,62380,62408,'00:43:19.184','00:43:20.351','Stupid, really.',-1),(149921,39,62428,62488,'00:43:21.186','00:43:23.688','I was leaning over and I slipped.',-1),(149922,39,62548,62632,'00:43:26.191','00:43:29.694','I was leaning far over\nto see the, uh...',-1),(149923,39,62640,62696,'00:43:30.029','00:43:32.363','...uh, uh, the uh...',-1),(149924,39,62716,62772,'00:43:33.198','00:43:35.533','- Propellers?\n- Propellers, and I slipped.',-1),(149925,39,62780,62844,'00:43:35.868','00:43:38.536','And I would have gone\noverboard but Mr. Dawson here...',-1),(149926,39,62852,62928,'00:43:38.871','00:43:42.040','...saved me. And almost\nwent over himself.',-1),(149927,39,62950,62977,'00:43:42.958','00:43:44.042','You wanted to see the...\nShe wanted to see the propellers.',-1),(149928,39,62985,63061,'00:43:44.376','00:43:47.545','Like I said, women and\nmachinery do not mix.',-1),(149929,39,63081,63129,'00:43:48.380','00:43:50.381','Was that the way of it?',-1),(149930,39,63189,63237,'00:43:52.885','00:43:54.886','Yeah. Yeah, that\nwas pretty much it.',-1),(149931,39,63245,63281,'00:43:55.220','00:43:56.721','Well, the boy\'s a hero then.',-1),(149932,39,63297,63327,'00:43:57.389','00:43:58.640','Good for you, son.\nWell done.',-1),(149933,39,63333,63381,'00:43:58.891','00:44:00.892','So, it\'s all\'s well and back\nto our brandy, eh?',-1),(149934,39,63445,63525,'00:44:03.562','00:44:06.898','Look at you. You must be freezing.\nLet\'s get you inside.',-1),(149935,39,63541,63597,'00:44:07.566','00:44:09.901','Perhaps a little something\nfor the boy?',-1),(149936,39,63649,63681,'00:44:12.071','00:44:13.404','Of course.',-1),(149937,39,63688,63773,'00:44:13.697','00:44:17.241','Mr. Lovejoy,\nI think a 20 should do it.',-1),(149938,39,63789,63853,'00:44:17.910','00:44:20.578','Is that the going rate\nfor saving the woman you love?',-1),(149939,39,63893,63937,'00:44:22.247','00:44:24.082','Rose is displeased.',-1),(149940,39,63949,63990,'00:44:24.583','00:44:26.250','What to do?',-1),(149941,39,64001,64025,'00:44:26.710','00:44:27.710','I know.',-1),(149942,39,64078,64166,'00:44:29.922','00:44:33.591','Perhaps you could join us for\ndinner tomorrow evening...',-1),(149943,39,64174,64210,'00:44:33.926','00:44:35.426','...to regale our group...',-1),(149944,39,64218,64270,'00:44:35.761','00:44:37.929','...with your heroic tale.',-1),(149945,39,64326,64378,'00:44:40.265','00:44:42.433','Sure.\nCount me in.',-1),(149946,39,64386,64442,'00:44:42.768','00:44:45.103','Good.\nIt\'s settled then.',-1),(149947,39,64466,64498,'00:44:46.105','00:44:47.438','This should be interesting.',-1),(149948,39,64722,64786,'00:44:56.782','00:44:59.450','Can I bum a smoke?',-1),(149949,39,64999,65027,'00:45:08.293','00:45:09.460','You\'ll want to tie those.',-1),(149950,39,65091,65117,'00:45:12.131','00:45:13.214','It\'s interesting...',-1),(149951,39,65131,65173,'00:45:13.799','00:45:15.550','...the young lady slipped\nso suddenly...',-1),(149952,39,65178,65259,'00:45:15.759','00:45:19.137','...and you still had time to remove\nyour jacket and your shoes.',-1),(149953,39,65647,65695,'00:45:35.320','00:45:37.321','I know you\'ve been melancholy.',-1),(149954,39,65719,65767,'00:45:38.323','00:45:40.324','I don\'t pretend to know why.',-1),(149955,39,65831,65883,'00:45:42.995','00:45:45.163','I intended to save this...',-1),(149956,39,65895,66008,'00:45:45.664','00:45:50.334','...until the engagement\ngala next week...',-1),(149957,39,66040,66096,'00:45:51.670','00:45:54.005','...but, I thought...',-1),(149958,39,66104,66136,'00:45:54.339','00:45:55.673','...tonight.',-1),(149959,39,66171,66200,'00:45:57.134','00:45:58.342','Good gracious.',-1),(149960,39,66222,66288,'00:45:59.261','00:46:02.013','Perhaps as a reminder\nof my feelings for you.',-1),(149961,39,66308,66339,'00:46:02.848','00:46:04.140','- Is it a...\n- Diamond. Yes.',-1),(149962,39,66400,66476,'00:46:06.685','00:46:09.854','56 carats to be exact.',-1),(149963,39,66524,66580,'00:46:11.857','00:46:14.192','It was worn by Louis XVI.',-1),(149964,39,66600,66656,'00:46:15.027','00:46:17.361','And they called\nit Le Coeur de la Mer.',-1),(149965,39,66668,66712,'00:46:17.863','00:46:19.697','- The Heart of the Ocean.\n- The Heart of the Ocean. Yes.',-1),(149966,39,66868,66908,'00:46:26.205','00:46:27.872','It\'s overwhelming.',-1),(149967,39,66919,66959,'00:46:28.332','00:46:29.999','Well, it\'s for royalty.',-1),(149968,39,66989,67041,'00:46:31.210','00:46:33.377','We are royalty, Rose.',-1),(149969,39,67137,67193,'00:46:37.382','00:46:39.717','You know, there\'s\nnothing I couldn\'t give you.',-1),(149970,39,67213,67261,'00:46:40.552','00:46:42.553','There\'s nothing I\'d deny you...',-1),(149971,39,67277,67329,'00:46:43.222','00:46:45.389','...if you would not deny me.',-1),(149972,39,67429,67485,'00:46:49.561','00:46:51.896','Open your heart to me, Rose.',-1),(149973,39,67857,67950,'00:47:07.412','00:47:11.290','Well, I\'ve been on my own since\nI was 15, since my folks died.',-1),(149974,39,67978,68074,'00:47:12.417','00:47:16.420','And I had no brothers or sisters or\nclose kin in that part of the country...',-1),(149975,39,68085,68165,'00:47:16.880','00:47:20.216','...so I lit on out of there and I\nhaven\'t been back since.',-1),(149976,39,68170,68222,'00:47:20.425','00:47:22.593','You could just call me a\ntumbleweed blowing in the wind.',-1),(149977,39,68282,68382,'00:47:25.097','00:47:29.267','Well, Rose, we\'ve walked about a mile\naround this boat deck and...',-1),(149978,39,68389,68461,'00:47:29.560','00:47:32.562','...chewed over how great the weather\'s\nbeen and how I grew up...',-1),(149979,39,68466,68554,'00:47:32.771','00:47:36.440','...but I reckon that\'s not why\nyou came to talk to me, is it?',-1),(149980,39,68602,68650,'00:47:38.443','00:47:40.444','- Mr. Dawson, I...\n- Jack.',-1),(149981,39,68684,68708,'00:47:41.864','00:47:42.864','Jack.',-1),(149982,39,68718,68796,'00:47:43.282','00:47:46.534','I want to thank you\nfor what you did.',-1),(149983,39,68798,68910,'00:47:46.618','00:47:51.289','Not just for pulling me back,\nbut for your discretion.',-1),(149984,39,68918,68950,'00:47:51.623','00:47:52.957','You\'re welcome.',-1),(149985,39,68962,68986,'00:47:53.458','00:47:54.458','Look.',-1),(149986,39,69013,69077,'00:47:55.544','00:47:58.212','I know what you\nmust be thinking.',-1),(149987,39,69083,69122,'00:47:58.463','00:48:00.089','Poor little rich girl.',-1),(149988,39,69126,69177,'00:48:00.257','00:48:02.383','What does she know about misery?',-1),(149989,39,69183,69207,'00:48:02.634','00:48:03.634','No.',-1),(149990,39,69231,69283,'00:48:04.636','00:48:06.804','No, that\'s not what I was thinking.',-1),(149991,39,69291,69321,'00:48:07.139','00:48:08.389','What I was thinking was...',-1),(149992,39,69325,69407,'00:48:08.557','00:48:11.976','...what could have happened to this girl\nto make her think she had no way out?',-1),(149993,39,69471,69495,'00:48:14.646','00:48:15.646','Well I...',-1),(149994,39,69513,69610,'00:48:16.398','00:48:20.443','It was everything.\nIt was my whole world and...',-1),(149995,39,69615,69641,'00:48:20.652','00:48:21.736','...all the people in it.',-1),(149996,39,69657,69733,'00:48:22.404','00:48:25.573','And the inertia of my life,\nplunging ahead and me...',-1),(149997,39,69738,69782,'00:48:25.782','00:48:27.617','...powerless to stop it.',-1),(149998,39,69787,69835,'00:48:27.826','00:48:29.827','God,\nlook at that thing.',-1),(149999,39,69842,69894,'00:48:30.120','00:48:32.288','You would have gone\nstraight to the bottom.',-1),(150000,39,69935,69996,'00:48:33.999','00:48:36.500','500 invitations have gone out.',-1),(150001,39,70004,70068,'00:48:36.835','00:48:39.503','All of Philadelphia society will be there.',-1),(150002,39,70075,70123,'00:48:39.796','00:48:41.797','And all the while I feel I\'m...',-1),(150003,39,70132,70178,'00:48:42.174','00:48:44.091','...standing in the middle\nof a crowded room...',-1),(150004,39,70180,70220,'00:48:44.176','00:48:45.843','...screaming at the\ntop of my lungs...',-1),(150005,39,70223,70252,'00:48:45.969','00:48:47.178','...and no one\neven looks up.',-1),(150006,39,70296,70320,'00:48:49.014','00:48:50.014','Do you love him?',-1),(150007,39,70352,70376,'00:48:51.350','00:48:52.350','Pardon me?',-1),(150008,39,70384,70419,'00:48:52.684','00:48:54.143','Do you love him?',-1),(150009,39,70432,70504,'00:48:54.686','00:48:57.688','You\'re being very rude. You\nshouldn\'t be asking me this.',-1),(150010,39,70515,70576,'00:48:58.148','00:49:00.691','Well, it\'s a simple question.\nDo you love the guy or not?',-1),(150011,39,70635,70684,'00:49:03.153','00:49:05.196','This is not a suitable conversation.',-1),(150012,39,70691,70720,'00:49:05.489','00:49:06.697','Why can\'t you just\nanswer the question?',-1),(150013,39,70784,70831,'00:49:09.368','00:49:11.327','This is absurd.',-1),(150014,39,70846,70872,'00:49:11.954','00:49:13.037','You don\'t know me\nand I don\'t know you...',-1),(150015,39,70879,70951,'00:49:13.330','00:49:16.332','...and we are not having this\nconversation at all. You are rude...',-1),(150016,39,70956,71037,'00:49:16.541','00:49:19.877','...and uncouth and presumptuous\nand I am leaving now...',-1),(150017,39,71045,71113,'00:49:20.212','00:49:23.047','...Jack. Mr. Dawson.\nIt\'s been a pleasure.',-1),(150018,39,71117,71159,'00:49:23.215','00:49:24.966','I sought you out to thank you\nand now I have thanked you.',-1),(150019,39,71164,71212,'00:49:25.175','00:49:27.176','And you\'ve insulted me.',-1),(150020,39,71217,71256,'00:49:27.386','00:49:29.011','Well, you deserved it.',-1),(150021,39,71261,71289,'00:49:29.221','00:49:30.388','- Right.\n- Right.',-1),(150022,39,71361,71400,'00:49:33.392','00:49:35.017','I thought you were leaving.',-1),(150023,39,71405,71437,'00:49:35.227','00:49:36.560','I am.',-1),(150024,39,71489,71521,'00:49:38.730','00:49:40.064','You are so annoying.',-1),(150025,39,71557,71581,'00:49:41.566','00:49:42.566','Wait.',-1),(150026,39,71587,71689,'00:49:42.818','00:49:47.071','I don\'t have to leave. This is\nmy part of the ship. You leave.',-1),(150027,39,71697,71769,'00:49:47.406','00:49:50.408','Well, well, well.\nNow who\'s being rude?',-1),(150028,39,71861,71929,'00:49:54.246','00:49:57.081','What is this stupid thing\nyou\'re carrying around?',-1),(150029,39,71958,72014,'00:49:58.250','00:50:00.584','So, what are you,\nan artist or something?',-1),(150030,39,72114,72158,'00:50:04.756','00:50:06.590','These are rather good.',-1),(150031,39,72238,72314,'00:50:09.928','00:50:13.097','They\'re very good, actually.',-1),(150032,39,72490,72530,'00:50:20.439','00:50:22.106','Jack, this is exquisite work.',-1),(150033,39,72538,72602,'00:50:22.441','00:50:25.109','Ah, they didn\'t think too\nmuch of them in old Paree.',-1),(150034,39,72606,72638,'00:50:25.277','00:50:26.610','Paris?',-1),(150035,39,72669,72733,'00:50:27.904','00:50:30.573','You do get around\nfor a p...',-1),(150036,39,72774,72865,'00:50:32.284','00:50:36.078','Well, a... a\nperson of limited means.',-1),(150037,39,72870,72918,'00:50:36.288','00:50:38.289','Go on. A poor guy. You can say it.',-1),(150038,39,72999,73039,'00:50:41.626','00:50:43.294','Well, well, well.',-1),(150039,39,73143,73182,'00:50:47.632','00:50:49.258','And these were drawn from life?',-1),(150040,39,73267,73315,'00:50:52.804','00:50:54.805','Well, that\'s one of the good things about Paris.',-1),(150041,39,73327,73361,'00:50:55.307','00:50:56.724','Lots of girls are willing\nto take their clothes off.',-1),(150042,39,73518,73551,'00:51:03.273','00:51:04.648','You liked this woman.',-1),(150043,39,73571,73623,'00:51:05.484','00:51:07.651','You used her several times.',-1),(150044,39,73651,73675,'00:51:08.820','00:51:09.820','Well.',-1),(150045,39,73693,73739,'00:51:10.572','00:51:12.490','She had beautiful\nhands, you see?',-1),(150046,39,73799,73855,'00:51:14.993','00:51:17.328','I think you must have\nhad a love affair with her.',-1),(150047,39,73867,73915,'00:51:17.829','00:51:19.830','No, no, no.\nJust with her hands.',-1),(150048,39,73923,73987,'00:51:20.165','00:51:22.833','She was a\none-legged prostitute.',-1),(150049,39,74015,74039,'00:51:23.960','00:51:24.960','See?',-1),(150050,39,74196,74244,'00:51:31.510','00:51:33.511','She had a good\nsense of humor though.',-1),(150051,39,74304,74328,'00:51:36.014','00:51:37.014','Oh, and this lady...',-1),(150052,39,74372,74444,'00:51:38.850','00:51:41.852','She used to sit at this bar every night...',-1),(150053,39,74448,74488,'00:51:42.020','00:51:43.687','...wearing every piece\nof jewelry she owned...',-1),(150054,39,74494,74550,'00:51:43.939','00:51:46.273','...just waiting for\nher long, lost love.',-1),(150055,39,74568,74624,'00:51:47.025','00:51:49.360','We called her Madame Bijoux.',-1),(150056,39,74636,74680,'00:51:49.861','00:51:51.695','See, her clothes are all moth-eaten.',-1),(150057,39,74720,74788,'00:51:53.365','00:51:56.200','Well,\nyou have a gift, Jack.',-1),(150058,39,74796,74828,'00:51:56.535','00:51:57.868','You do.',-1),(150059,39,74836,74872,'00:51:58.203','00:51:59.703','You see people.',-1),(150060,39,74879,74916,'00:51:59.996','00:52:01.539','I see you.',-1),(150061,39,74975,75007,'00:52:03.959','00:52:05.292','And?',-1),(150062,39,75040,75081,'00:52:06.670','00:52:08.379','You wouldn\'t have jumped.',-1),(150063,39,75185,75272,'00:52:12.717','00:52:16.345','But the purpose of university\nis to find a suitable husband.',-1),(150064,39,75277,75317,'00:52:16.555','00:52:18.222','Rose has already done that.',-1),(150065,39,75325,75393,'00:52:18.557','00:52:21.392','Look, here comes that\nvulgar Brown woman.',-1),(150066,39,75401,75465,'00:52:21.726','00:52:24.395','Quickly, get up before\nshe sits with us.',-1),(150067,39,75489,75552,'00:52:25.397','00:52:28.023','Hello, girls. I was hoping\nI\'d catch you at tea.',-1),(150068,39,75557,75593,'00:52:28.233','00:52:29.733','We\'re awfully sorry,\nyou missed it.',-1),(150069,39,75597,75679,'00:52:29.901','00:52:33.320','The Countess and I were just\noff to take the air on the boat deck.',-1),(150070,39,75684,75757,'00:52:33.530','00:52:36.574','What a lovely idea.\nI need to catch up on my gossip.',-1),(150071,39,75841,75869,'00:52:40.078','00:52:41.245','Countess.',-1),(150072,39,75905,75973,'00:52:42.747','00:52:45.583','So, you\'ve not yet lit the\nlast four boilers?',-1),(150073,39,75986,76021,'00:52:46.084','00:52:47.543','No, I don\'t see\nthe need.',-1),(150074,39,76041,76066,'00:52:48.378','00:52:49.420','We are making excellent time.',-1),(150075,39,76102,76206,'00:52:50.922','00:52:55.259','The press knows the size of Titanic.\nNow, I want them to marvel at her speed.',-1),(150076,39,76213,76266,'00:52:55.552','00:52:57.761','We must give them\nsomething new to print.',-1),(150077,39,76314,76362,'00:52:59.764','00:53:01.765','This maiden voyage\nof Titanic must...',-1),(150078,39,76374,76412,'00:53:02.267','00:53:03.851','...make headlines.',-1),(150079,39,76418,76514,'00:53:04.102','00:53:08.105','Mr. Ismay, I would prefer\nnot to push the engines...',-1),(150080,39,76522,76582,'00:53:08.440','00:53:10.941','...until they\'ve been properly run in.',-1),(150081,39,76614,76645,'00:53:12.277','00:53:13.569','Of course I\'m just a passenger.',-1),(150082,39,76646,76704,'00:53:13.612','00:53:16.030','I leave it to your good offices\nto decide what\'s best.',-1),(150083,39,76718,76782,'00:53:16.615','00:53:19.283','But what a glorious end to your final crossing...',-1),(150084,39,76786,76824,'00:53:19.451','00:53:21.035','...if we were to get into New York\non Tuesday night...',-1),(150085,39,76829,76890,'00:53:21.244','00:53:23.787','...and surprise them all.\nMake the morning papers.',-1),(150086,39,76909,76957,'00:53:24.581','00:53:26.582','Retire with a bang, eh, E. J?',-1),(150087,39,77047,77079,'00:53:30.295','00:53:31.629','Good man.',-1),(150088,39,77113,77173,'00:53:33.048','00:53:35.549','After that, I worked\non a squid boat in Monterey...',-1),(150089,39,77183,77243,'00:53:35.967','00:53:38.469','...then I went to Los Angeles to the...',-1),(150090,39,77249,77325,'00:53:38.720','00:53:41.889','...Santa Monica pier\nand did portraits for 10 cents each.',-1),(150091,39,77343,77387,'00:53:42.641','00:53:44.475','Why can\'t I be like you?',-1),(150092,39,77395,77479,'00:53:44.809','00:53:48.312','Just head out for the horizon\nwhenever I feel like it.',-1),(150093,39,77527,77593,'00:53:50.315','00:53:53.067','Say we\'ll go there sometime, to that pier...',-1),(150094,39,77599,77651,'00:53:53.318','00:53:55.486','...only if we just talk about it.',-1),(150095,39,77659,77727,'00:53:55.820','00:53:58.656','No, we\'ll do it. We\'ll drink cheap beer.',-1),(150096,39,77735,77799,'00:53:58.990','00:54:01.659','Ride on the roller coaster till we throw up.',-1),(150097,39,77807,77883,'00:54:01.993','00:54:05.162','We\'ll ride horses on the beach, in the surf.',-1),(150098,39,77891,77988,'00:54:05.497','00:54:09.500','But you have to do it like a real cowboy.\nNo sidesaddle stuff.',-1),(150099,39,78000,78064,'00:54:10.001','00:54:12.670','You mean with one leg on each side?',-1),(150100,39,78096,78120,'00:54:14.005','00:54:15.005','Can you show me?',-1),(150101,39,78126,78170,'00:54:15.257','00:54:17.091','Sure, if you like.',-1),(150102,39,78208,78248,'00:54:18.677','00:54:20.344','Teach me to ride like a man.',-1),(150103,39,78254,78286,'00:54:20.595','00:54:21.929','Chew tobacco like a man.',-1),(150104,39,78324,78376,'00:54:23.515','00:54:25.683','And spit like a man.',-1),(150105,39,78384,78426,'00:54:26.017','00:54:27.768','You didn\'t learn in finishing school?',-1),(150106,39,78432,78460,'00:54:28.019','00:54:29.186','No.',-1),(150107,39,78468,78512,'00:54:29.521','00:54:31.355','Come on, I\'ll show you.',-1),(150108,39,78536,78560,'00:54:32.357','00:54:33.357','I\'ll show you how.',-1),(150109,39,78566,78636,'00:54:33.608','00:54:36.527','Jack! No, Jack, no. Wait.',-1),(150110,39,78668,78716,'00:54:37.862','00:54:39.863','I couldn\'t possibly, Jack.',-1),(150111,39,78724,78764,'00:54:40.198','00:54:41.865','Watch closely.',-1),(150112,39,78804,78848,'00:54:43.535','00:54:45.369','That\'s disgusting.',-1),(150113,39,78852,78876,'00:54:45.537','00:54:46.537','Your turn.',-1),(150114,39,78932,79005,'00:54:48.873','00:54:51.875','That was pitiful.\nYou really have to hawk it back.',-1),(150115,39,79013,79085,'00:54:52.210','00:54:55.212','Get some leverage.\nUse your arms. Arc your neck.',-1),(150116,39,79117,79165,'00:54:56.548','00:54:58.549','You see the range on that thing?',-1),(150117,39,79185,79213,'00:54:59.384','00:55:00.551','Okay, go.',-1),(150118,39,79297,79417,'00:55:04.055','00:55:09.059','That was better. You have to work on it.\nReally try to hawk it up.',-1),(150119,39,79607,79639,'00:55:16.985','00:55:18.319','Mother.',-1),(150120,39,79769,79825,'00:55:23.742','00:55:26.076','May I introduce Jack Dawson?',-1),(150121,39,79853,79897,'00:55:27.245','00:55:29.079','Charmed, I\'m sure.',-1),(150122,39,80010,80122,'00:55:33.752','00:55:38.422','The others were gracious and curious\nabout the man who\'d saved my life.',-1),(150123,39,80150,80222,'00:55:39.591','00:55:42.593','But my mother looked at him like an insect.',-1),(150124,39,80234,80330,'00:55:43.094','00:55:47.097','A dangerous insect\nwhich must be squashed quickly.',-1),(150125,39,80338,80430,'00:55:47.432','00:55:51.268','Sounds like you\'re a good man\nto have around in a sticky spot.',-1),(150126,39,80502,80614,'00:55:54.272','00:55:58.942','Why do they always insist on announcing\ndinner like a damn cavalry charge?',-1),(150127,39,80622,80662,'00:55:59.277','00:56:00.944','Shall we go dress, Mother?',-1),(150128,39,80686,80730,'00:56:01.946','00:56:03.781','See you at dinner, Jack.',-1),(150129,39,80778,80802,'00:56:05.784','00:56:06.784','Uh, son?',-1),(150130,39,80814,80842,'00:56:07.285','00:56:08.452','Son!',-1),(150131,39,80854,80910,'00:56:08.953','00:56:11.288','Do you have any idea what you\'re doing?',-1),(150132,39,80934,80958,'00:56:12.290','00:56:13.290','Not really.',-1),(150133,39,80967,81027,'00:56:13.625','00:56:16.126','You\'re about to go into the snake pit.',-1),(150134,39,81085,81125,'00:56:18.546','00:56:20.214','What are you going to wear?',-1),(150135,39,81199,81247,'00:56:23.301','00:56:25.302','I figured. Come on.',-1),(150136,39,81311,81415,'00:56:27.972','00:56:32.309','I was right. You and my son\nare just about the same size.',-1),(150137,39,81423,81463,'00:56:32.644','00:56:34.311','Pretty close.',-1),(150138,39,81551,81607,'00:56:37.982','00:56:40.317','You shine up like a new penny.',-1),(150139,39,81891,81931,'00:56:52.163','00:56:53.831','Good evening, sir.',-1),(150140,39,83475,83541,'00:57:58.146','00:58:00.898','Thousands of tons of Hockley steel\nare in this ship.',-1),(150141,39,83547,83597,'00:58:01.149','00:58:03.233','- Which part?\n- All the right ones.',-1),(150142,39,83603,83679,'00:58:03.485','00:58:06.653','Then you\'re accountable\nif there\'s a problem. Where\'s Rose?',-1),(150143,39,83685,83717,'00:58:06.905','00:58:08.238','She\'ll be along.',-1),(150144,39,83725,83773,'00:58:08.573','00:58:10.574','There is the Countess.',-1),(150145,39,84466,84550,'00:58:39.437','00:58:42.940','I saw that in a nickelodeon\nand always wanted to do it.',-1),(150146,39,84896,84924,'00:58:57.372','00:58:58.539','Darling...',-1),(150147,39,84938,84990,'00:58:59.123','00:59:01.291','...surely you remember Mr. Dawson.',-1),(150148,39,85059,85145,'00:59:04.128','00:59:07.714','It\'s amazing.\nYou could almost pass for a gentleman.',-1),(150149,39,85175,85203,'00:59:08.967','00:59:10.133','Almost.',-1),(150150,39,85211,85245,'00:59:10.468','00:59:11.885','This is extraordinary.',-1),(150151,39,85595,85635,'00:59:26.484','00:59:28.151','This is a remarkable voyage.',-1),(150152,39,85641,85675,'00:59:28.403','00:59:29.820','- Mad.\n- Completely lunatic.',-1),(150153,39,85717,85765,'00:59:31.573','00:59:33.574','There\'s the Countess of Rothes.',-1),(150154,39,85815,85887,'00:59:35.660','00:59:38.662','That\'s John Jacob Astor...',-1),(150155,39,85903,85943,'00:59:39.330','00:59:40.998','...the richest man on board.',-1),(150156,39,85949,86044,'00:59:41.249','00:59:45.168','His little wifey, Madeleine,\nis my age and in a delicate condition.',-1),(150157,39,86064,86112,'00:59:46.004','00:59:48.005','See how she tries to hide it.',-1),(150158,39,86118,86152,'00:59:48.256','00:59:49.673','Quite the scandal.',-1),(150159,39,86164,86272,'00:59:50.174','00:59:54.678','Benjamin Guggenheim and his mistress,\nMadame Aubert. Mrs. Guggenheim...',-1),(150160,39,86278,86366,'00:59:54.929','00:59:58.599','...is at home with the children, of course.\nAnd over here...',-1),(150161,39,86372,86412,'00:59:58.850','01:00:00.517','...Sir Cosmo and Lucile, Lady Duff-Gordon.',-1),(150162,39,86418,86498,'01:00:00.768','01:00:04.104','She designs naughty lingerie,\namong her many talents.',-1),(150163,39,86504,86560,'01:00:04.355','01:00:06.690','Very popular with the royals.',-1),(150164,39,86584,86628,'01:00:07.692','01:00:09.526','Congratulations. She\'s splendid.',-1),(150165,39,86636,86672,'01:00:09.861','01:00:11.361','Why, thank you.',-1),(150166,39,86692,86726,'01:00:12.196','01:00:13.614','Escort a lady to dinner?',-1),(150167,39,86732,86768,'01:00:13.865','01:00:15.365','Certainly.',-1),(150168,39,86800,86848,'01:00:16.701','01:00:18.702','Sweet pea, sweet pea.',-1),(150169,39,86868,86902,'01:00:19.537','01:00:20.954','Ain\'t nothing to it.',-1),(150170,39,86920,87029,'01:00:21.706','01:00:26.209','They love money. Pretend like you own\na gold mine and you\'re in the club.',-1),(150171,39,87081,87121,'01:00:28.379','01:00:30.047','Hey, Astor.',-1),(150172,39,87141,87205,'01:00:30.882','01:00:33.550','Hello, Molly. Nice to see you.',-1),(150173,39,87211,87281,'01:00:33.801','01:00:36.720','J.J., Madeleine,\nI\'d like you to meet Jack Dawson.',-1),(150174,39,87315,87347,'01:00:38.139','01:00:39.473','Well, Jack...',-1),(150175,39,87357,87397,'01:00:39.891','01:00:41.558','...are you of the Boston Dawsons?',-1),(150176,39,87421,87483,'01:00:42.560','01:00:45.145','No, the Chippewa Falls Dawsons, actually.',-1),(150177,39,87489,87521,'01:00:45.396','01:00:46.730','Oh, yes.',-1),(150178,39,87569,87665,'01:00:48.733','01:00:52.736','He must have been nervous.\nBut he never faltered.',-1),(150179,39,87685,87737,'01:00:53.571','01:00:55.739','They assumed he was one of them.',-1),(150180,39,87745,87821,'01:00:56.074','01:00:59.242','Heir to a railroad fortune, perhaps.',-1),(150181,39,87829,87929,'01:00:59.577','01:01:03.747','New money, obviously,\nbut still a member of the club.',-1),(150182,39,87945,88028,'01:01:04.415','01:01:07.834','Mother. Of course.\nCould always be counted upon.',-1),(150183,39,88042,88160,'01:01:08.419','01:01:13.340','Tell us of the accommodations in steerage,\nMr. Dawson. I hear they\'re quite good.',-1),(150184,39,88196,88272,'01:01:14.842','01:01:18.011','The best I\'ve seen, ma\'am. Hardly any rats.',-1),(150185,39,88346,88414,'01:01:21.099','01:01:23.934','Mr. Dawson is joining us from third class.',-1),(150186,39,88420,88476,'01:01:24.185','01:01:26.520','He was of help to my fiancÃ©e last night.',-1),(150187,39,88482,88550,'01:01:26.771','01:01:29.606','It happens Mr. Dawson is quite a fine artist.',-1),(150188,39,88558,88618,'01:01:29.941','01:01:32.442','He showed me some of his work today.',-1),(150189,39,88630,88746,'01:01:32.944','01:01:37.781','Rose and I differ in our definition of fine art.\nNot to impugn your work, sir.',-1),(150190,39,89007,89031,'01:01:48.626','01:01:49.626','Are all these mine?',-1),(150191,39,89037,89087,'01:01:49.877','01:01:51.962','Start from the outside and work in.',-1),(150192,39,89093,89141,'01:01:52.213','01:01:54.214','He knows every rivet in her.',-1),(150193,39,89147,89203,'01:01:54.465','01:01:56.800','Your ship is a wonder, Mr. Andrews.',-1),(150194,39,89209,89241,'01:01:57.051','01:01:58.385','Thank you, Rose.',-1),(150195,39,89317,89355,'01:02:01.556','01:02:03.140','How do you take your caviar, sir?',-1),(150196,39,89361,89439,'01:02:03.391','01:02:06.643','No caviar for me, thanks.\nNever did like it much.',-1),(150197,39,89483,89547,'01:02:08.479','01:02:11.148','Where exactly do you live, Mr. Dawson?',-1),(150198,39,89557,89629,'01:02:11.566','01:02:14.568','Right now, my address is the RMS Titanic.',-1),(150199,39,89635,89683,'01:02:14.819','01:02:16.820','After that, I\'m on God\'s good humor.',-1),(150200,39,89695,89741,'01:02:17.321','01:02:19.239','How do you have means to travel?',-1),(150201,39,89763,89863,'01:02:20.158','01:02:24.327','I work my way from place to place.\nTramp steamers and such.',-1),(150202,39,89871,89959,'01:02:24.662','01:02:28.331','I won my ticket on Titanic\nat a lucky hand at poker.',-1),(150203,39,89965,90001,'01:02:28.583','01:02:30.083','A very lucky hand.',-1),(150204,39,90024,90072,'01:02:31.002','01:02:33.003','All life is a game of luck.',-1),(150205,39,90100,90170,'01:02:34.172','01:02:37.090','A real man makes his own luck.\nRight, Dawson?',-1),(150206,39,90210,90302,'01:02:38.760','01:02:42.596','And you find\nthat sort of rootless existence appealing?',-1),(150207,39,90376,90414,'01:02:45.683','01:02:47.267','Yes, ma\'am, I do.',-1),(150208,39,90432,90504,'01:02:48.019','01:02:51.021','I\'ve got everything I need\nright here with me.',-1),(150209,39,90510,90578,'01:02:51.272','01:02:54.107','I have air in my lungs\nand blank sheets of paper.',-1),(150210,39,90612,90718,'01:02:55.526','01:02:59.946','I love waking up, not knowing\nwhat will happen or who I\'ll meet.',-1),(150211,39,90740,90774,'01:03:00.865','01:03:02.282','Where I\'ll wind up.',-1),(150212,39,90784,90838,'01:03:02.700','01:03:04.951','One night I\'m sleeping under a bridge...',-1),(150213,39,90844,90946,'01:03:05.203','01:03:09.456','...now I\'m on the grandest ship\nin the world, with you fine people.',-1),(150214,39,90952,90976,'01:03:09.707','01:03:10.707','I\'ll take more of that.',-1),(150215,39,91009,91081,'01:03:12.043','01:03:15.045','Life\'s a gift. I don\'t intend on wasting it.',-1),(150216,39,91113,91173,'01:03:16.380','01:03:18.882','You never know what hand you\'ll get dealt.',-1),(150217,39,91181,91245,'01:03:19.217','01:03:21.885','You take life as it comes at you. Here, Cal.',-1),(150218,39,91307,91347,'01:03:24.472','01:03:26.139','Make each day count.',-1),(150219,39,91367,91391,'01:03:26.974','01:03:27.974','Well said, Jack.',-1),(150220,39,91397,91423,'01:03:28.226','01:03:29.309','Hear, hear.',-1),(150221,39,91447,91565,'01:03:30.311','01:03:35.232','To making it count.',-1),(150222,39,91577,91601,'01:03:35.733','01:03:36.733','Bravo.',-1),(150223,39,91767,91857,'01:03:43.658','01:03:47.410','But Mr. Brown didn\'t know\nI\'d hidden the money in the stove.',-1),(150224,39,91889,91985,'01:03:48.746','01:03:52.749','He comes home drunk as a pig celebrating\nand lights a fire.',-1),(150225,39,92070,92122,'01:03:56.254','01:03:58.421','Next is brandy in the smoking room.',-1),(150226,39,92174,92224,'01:04:00.591','01:04:02.676','Join me in a brandy, gentlemen?',-1),(150227,39,92270,92376,'01:04:04.595','01:04:09.015','Now they retreat to congratulate each\nother on being masters of the universe.',-1),(150228,39,92382,92430,'01:04:09.267','01:04:11.268','Ladies, thank you for your company.',-1),(150229,39,92456,92496,'01:04:12.353','01:04:14.020','May I escort you to the cabin?',-1),(150230,39,92502,92526,'01:04:14.272','01:04:15.272','No, I\'ll stay here.',-1),(150231,39,92546,92570,'01:04:16.107','01:04:17.107','Here, Molly.',-1),(150232,39,92594,92642,'01:04:18.109','01:04:20.110','Joining us, Dawson?',-1),(150233,39,92650,92706,'01:04:20.444','01:04:22.779','You don\'t want to stay with the women.',-1),(150234,39,92718,92774,'01:04:23.281','01:04:25.615','No, thanks. I have to head back.',-1),(150235,39,92782,92894,'01:04:25.950','01:04:30.620','That\'s best. It\'ll be all business and politics.\nWouldn\'t interest you.',-1),(150236,39,92920,92984,'01:04:31.706','01:04:34.374','But Dawson, good of you to come.',-1),(150237,39,93119,93151,'01:04:39.964','01:04:41.298','Must you go?',-1),(150238,39,93157,93213,'01:04:41.549','01:04:43.884','Time for me to row with the other slaves.',-1),(150239,39,93299,93331,'01:04:47.471','01:04:48.805','Good night, Rose.',-1),(150240,39,94292,94352,'01:05:28.846','01:05:31.348','Want to go to a real party?',-1),(150241,39,94602,94654,'01:05:41.776','01:05:43.944','Is okay I put my hand here?',-1),(150242,39,95125,95173,'01:06:03.547','01:06:05.548','I can\'t understand you.',-1),(150243,39,95947,96003,'01:06:37.832','01:06:40.166','I\'m going to dance with her now.',-1),(150244,39,96008,96032,'01:06:40.334','01:06:41.334','Come on.',-1),(150245,39,96046,96094,'01:06:41.919','01:06:43.920','Come on. Come with me.',-1),(150246,39,96102,96146,'01:06:44.255','01:06:46.089','Jack. Jack, wait.',-1),(150247,39,96202,96226,'01:06:48.426','01:06:49.426','I can\'t do this.',-1),(150248,39,96232,96276,'01:06:49.677','01:06:51.511','We\'ll have to get a bit closer.',-1),(150249,39,96282,96310,'01:06:51.762','01:06:52.929','Like this.',-1),(150250,39,96390,96430,'01:06:56.267','01:06:57.934','You\'re still my best girl, Cora.',-1),(150251,39,96508,96584,'01:07:01.188','01:07:04.357','- I don\'t know the steps.\n- Me, either. Just go with it.',-1),(150252,39,96594,96628,'01:07:04.775','01:07:06.192','Don\'t think.',-1),(150253,39,97087,97151,'01:07:25.296','01:07:27.964','Wait! Jack! Wait! Stop, Jack!',-1),(150254,39,97387,97423,'01:07:37.808','01:07:39.309','What? Wait!',-1),(150255,39,98412,98452,'01:08:20.518','01:08:22.185','Jack, no.',-1),(150256,39,98592,98680,'01:08:28.025','01:08:31.694','- Beyond the jurisdiction\nof the Sherman Act.',-1),(150257,39,98688,98778,'01:08:32.029','01:08:35.782','That\'s what Rockefeller said...\nSupreme Court didn\'t swallow it.',-1),(150258,39,99265,99353,'01:08:56.053','01:08:59.722','What? You think\na first-class girl can\'t drink?',-1),(150259,39,99407,99431,'01:09:01.976','01:09:02.976','Get out of here.',-1),(150260,39,99445,99477,'01:09:03.561','01:09:04.894','Are you all right?',-1),(150261,39,99525,99549,'01:09:06.897','01:09:07.897','I\'m fine.',-1),(150262,39,99555,99603,'01:09:08.149','01:09:10.150','Two out of three.',-1),(150263,39,99625,99657,'01:09:11.068','01:09:12.402','So...',-1),(150264,39,99685,99733,'01:09:13.571','01:09:15.572','...you think you\'re tough?',-1),(150265,39,99765,99801,'01:09:16.907','01:09:18.408','Let\'s see you do this.',-1),(150266,39,99857,99921,'01:09:20.744','01:09:23.413','Hold this for me, Jack. Hold it up.',-1),(150267,39,100346,100372,'01:09:41.098','01:09:42.182','Jesus!',-1),(150268,39,100378,100406,'01:09:42.433','01:09:43.600','You okay?',-1),(150269,39,100412,100450,'01:09:43.851','01:09:45.435','I haven\'t done that in years.',-1),(150270,39,100644,100710,'01:09:53.527','01:09:56.279','Come on, lads. Give it all you got. Let\'s go.',-1),(150271,39,101335,101367,'01:10:22.306','01:10:23.640','Coffee, sir?',-1),(150272,39,101605,101645,'01:10:33.567','01:10:35.235','You didn\'t come to me last night.',-1),(150273,39,101699,101735,'01:10:37.488','01:10:38.988','I was tired.',-1),(150274,39,101795,101859,'01:10:41.492','01:10:44.160','Your exertions below deck\nwere no doubt exhausting.',-1),(150275,39,101935,102019,'01:10:47.331','01:10:50.833','I see you had\nthat undertaker of a manservant follow me.',-1),(150276,39,102028,102098,'01:10:51.168','01:10:54.087','You will never behave like that again.',-1),(150277,39,102184,102256,'01:10:57.675','01:11:00.677','I\'m not one of your mill foremen\nwho you can command.',-1),(150278,39,102292,102332,'01:11:02.179','01:11:03.846','I\'m your fiancÃ©e.',-1),(150279,39,102372,102420,'01:11:05.516','01:11:07.517','My fiancÃ©e. My fiancÃ©e!',-1),(150280,39,102428,102476,'01:11:07.851','01:11:09.852','Yes, you are! And my wife!',-1),(150281,39,102508,102616,'01:11:11.188','01:11:15.692','My wife in practice,\nif not yet by law, so you will honor me!',-1),(150282,39,102624,102690,'01:11:16.026','01:11:18.778','You will honor me the way\na wife honors her husband.',-1),(150283,39,102696,102750,'01:11:19.029','01:11:21.281','Because I will not be made a fool of.',-1),(150284,39,102770,102814,'01:11:22.116','01:11:23.950','Is this in any way unclear?',-1),(150285,39,102836,102864,'01:11:24.868','01:11:26.035','No.',-1),(150286,39,102872,102928,'01:11:26.370','01:11:28.705','Good. Excuse me.',-1),(150287,39,103065,103105,'01:11:34.378','01:11:36.045','Oh, Miss Rose.',-1),(150288,39,103145,103183,'01:11:37.715','01:11:39.299','We had a little accident.',-1),(150289,39,103189,103241,'01:11:39.550','01:11:41.718','- That\'s all right.\n- I\'m sorry.',-1),(150290,39,103251,103275,'01:11:42.136','01:11:43.136','Let me help you.',-1),(150291,39,103281,103511,'01:11:43.387','01:11:52.979','It\'s all right, miss.',-1),(150292,39,103645,103677,'01:11:58.569','01:11:59.902','Tea, Trudy.',-1),(150293,39,104098,104174,'01:12:17.421','01:12:20.590','You\'re not to see that boy again.\nYou understand?',-1),(150294,39,104206,104262,'01:12:21.925','01:12:24.260','Rose, I forbid it.',-1),(150295,39,104286,104358,'01:12:25.262','01:12:28.264','Stop it, Mother.\nYou\'ll give yourself a nosebleed.',-1),(150296,39,104366,104406,'01:12:28.599','01:12:30.266','This is not a game.',-1),(150297,39,104420,104506,'01:12:30.851','01:12:34.437','Our situation is precarious.\nYou know the money\'s gone.',-1),(150298,39,104514,104618,'01:12:34.772','01:12:39.108','Of course I know.\nYou remind me every day.',-1),(150299,39,104644,104760,'01:12:40.194','01:12:45.031','Your father left us nothing but a legacy\nof bad debts hidden by a good name.',-1),(150300,39,104766,104830,'01:12:45.282','01:12:47.950','That name is the only card we have to play.',-1),(150301,39,104846,104886,'01:12:48.619','01:12:50.286','I don\'t understand you.',-1),(150302,39,104902,104998,'01:12:50.954','01:12:54.957','It is a fine match with Hockley.\nIt will ensure our survival.',-1),(150303,39,105031,105071,'01:12:56.293','01:12:57.960','How can you put this on me?',-1),(150304,39,105077,105113,'01:12:58.212','01:12:59.712','Why are you being so selfish?',-1),(150305,39,105125,105169,'01:13:00.214','01:13:02.048','I\'m being selfish?',-1),(150306,39,105253,105323,'01:13:05.552','01:13:08.471','Do you want to see me\nworking as a seamstress?',-1),(150307,39,105367,105411,'01:13:10.307','01:13:12.141','Is that what you want?',-1),(150308,39,105475,105543,'01:13:14.812','01:13:17.647','To see our fine things sold at auction?',-1),(150309,39,105583,105627,'01:13:19.316','01:13:21.150','Our memories scattered?',-1),(150310,39,105895,105935,'01:13:32.329','01:13:33.996','It\'s so unfair.',-1),(150311,39,105967,106011,'01:13:35.332','01:13:37.166','Of course it\'s unfair.',-1),(150312,39,106044,106076,'01:13:38.502','01:13:39.836','We\'re women.',-1),(150313,39,106136,106188,'01:13:42.339','01:13:44.507','Our choices are never easy.',-1),(150314,39,106712,106804,'01:14:06.363','01:14:10.199','Protect them by Thy guiding hand',-1),(150315,39,106812,106928,'01:14:10.534','01:14:15.371','From every peril on the land',-1),(150316,39,106976,107073,'01:14:17.374','01:14:21.377','O, spirit whom the Father sent',-1),(150317,39,107089,107189,'01:14:22.045','01:14:26.215','To spread abroad the firmament',-1),(150318,39,107197,107301,'01:14:26.550','01:14:30.887','O, wind of heaven, by Thy might',-1),(150319,39,107309,107425,'01:14:31.221','01:14:36.058','Save all who dare the eagle\'s flight',-1),(150320,39,107433,107525,'01:14:36.393','01:14:40.229','And keep them by Thy watchful care...',-1),(150321,39,107589,107629,'01:14:42.900','01:14:44.567','Hello, Mr. Andrews.',-1),(150322,39,107875,107909,'01:14:54.828','01:14:56.245','I need to talk to someone.',-1),(150323,39,107915,107969,'01:14:56.497','01:14:58.748','You\'re not supposed to be in here.',-1),(150324,39,108082,108120,'01:15:03.420','01:15:05.004','I was here last night, remember?',-1),(150325,39,108126,108166,'01:15:05.255','01:15:06.923','No. Now please turn around.',-1),(150326,39,108172,108240,'01:15:07.174','01:15:10.009','He\'ll tell you. I just need to talk...',-1),(150327,39,108246,108322,'01:15:10.260','01:15:13.429','Mr. Hockley and Mrs. DeWitt Bukater...',-1),(150328,39,108330,108398,'01:15:13.764','01:15:16.599','...are still appreciative of your assistance.',-1),(15