0189,110261,'01:16:31.216','01:16:34.218','Mr. Andrews... Forgive me.',-1),(150350,39,110276,110310,'01:16:34.845','01:16:36.262','I did the sum\nin my head...',-1),(150351,39,110325,110409,'01:16:36.888','01:16:40.391','...and with the number of lifeboats\ntimes the capacity you mentioned...',-1),(150352,39,110417,110501,'01:16:40.726','01:16:44.228','Forgive me, but it seems that there are\nnot enough for everyone aboard.',-1),(150353,39,110520,110561,'01:16:45.022','01:16:46.731','About half, actually.',-1),(150354,39,110581,110617,'01:16:47.566','01:16:49.066','Rose, you miss nothing,\ndo you?',-1),(150355,39,110637,110689,'01:16:49.901','01:16:52.069','In fact, I put in these new\ntype davits...',-1),(150356,39,110697,110760,'01:16:52.404','01:16:55.031','...which can take an extra row\nof boats inside this one.',-1),(150357,39,110777,110824,'01:16:55.741','01:16:57.700','But it was thought,\nby some...',-1),(150358,39,110828,110866,'01:16:57.868','01:16:59.452','...the deck would look\ntoo cluttered.',-1),(150359,39,110877,110933,'01:16:59.911','01:17:02.246','So, I was overruled.',-1),(150360,39,110945,111018,'01:17:02.748','01:17:05.750','It\'s a waste of deck space\nas it is on an unsinkable ship.',-1),(150361,39,111026,111066,'01:17:06.084','01:17:07.752','Sleep soundly, young Rose.',-1),(150362,39,111069,111131,'01:17:07.878','01:17:10.463','I have built you a good ship,\nstrong and true.',-1),(150363,39,111138,111178,'01:17:10.756','01:17:12.423','She\'s all the lifeboat\nyou need.',-1),(150364,39,111186,111258,'01:17:12.758','01:17:15.760','Just keep heading aft. The next\nstop will be the engine room.',-1),(150365,39,111386,111490,'01:17:21.099','01:17:25.436','Jack, this is impossible.\nI can\'t see you.',-1),(150366,39,111497,111566,'01:17:25.729','01:17:28.606','- I need to talk to you.\n- No, Jack. No.',-1),(150367,39,111602,111658,'01:17:30.108','01:17:32.443','Jack.\nI\'m engaged.',-1),(150368,39,111682,111726,'01:17:33.445','01:17:35.279','I\'m 