ort!',-1),(150593,39,145586,145622,'01:41:06.106','01:41:07.607','Get back!',-1),(150594,39,146329,146361,'01:41:37.054','01:41:38.387','Let\'s go!',-1),(150595,39,146367,146447,'01:41:38.639','01:41:41.974','They\'re closing the doors! Get out!',-1),(150596,39,146603,146659,'01:41:48.482','01:41:50.817','Get out the door! Go!',-1),(150597,39,146667,146739,'01:41:51.151','01:41:54.153','Go! Come on, lads! Go, lads, go!',-1),(150598,39,146971,147011,'01:42:03.831','01:42:05.498','Go! Go!',-1),(150599,39,147023,147072,'01:42:05.999','01:42:08.000','Out! Out!',-1),(150600,39,147424,147464,'01:42:22.683','01:42:24.350','Oh, my God.',-1),(150601,39,147484,147516,'01:42:25.185','01:42:26.519','That was a close shave.',-1),(150602,39,147524,147594,'01:42:26.854','01:42:29.772','Smell ice, can you? Bleedin\' Christ!',-1),(150603,39,147692,147760,'01:42:33.861','01:42:36.696','Note the time. Enter it in the log.',-1),(150604,39,147898,147938,'01:42:42.452','01:42:44.120','What was that, Mr. Murdoch?',-1),(150605,39,147960,147994,'01:42:45.038','01:42:46.455','An iceberg, sir.',-1),(150606,39,148020,148105,'01:42:47.541','01:42:51.043','I put her hard to starboard, but it was too close.',-1),(150607,39,148113,148165,'01:42:51.378','01:42:53.546','I tried to port round it, but...',-1),(150608,39,148173,148249,'01:42:53.881','01:42:57.049','- Close the watertight doors.\n- They\'re closed, sir.',-1),(150609,39,148325,148353,'01:43:00.220','01:43:01.387','All stop.',-1),(150610,39,148577,148629,'01:43:10.731','01:43:12.899','Have the carpenter sound the ship.',-1),(150611,39,148909,148989,'01:43:24.578','01:43:27.914','Come on, let\'s get the hell out of here!',-1),(150612,39,149106,149174,'01:43:32.753','01:43:35.588','Why have the engines stopped? I felt a shudder.',-1),(150613,39,149180,149244,'01:43:35.839','01:43:38.507','Not to worry. We threw a propeller blade.',-1),(150614,39,149250,149318,'01:43:38.759','01:43:41.594','That\'s the shudder you felt.\nDo you need anything?',-1),(150615,39,149338,149364,'01:43:42.429','01:43:43.512','No, thank you.',-1),(150616,39,149482,149542,'01:43:48.435','01:43:50.937','There\'s talk of an iceberg.',-1),(150617,39,149548,149590,'01:43:51.188','01:43:52.939','I don\'t see anything. Do you?',-1),(150618,39,149642,149718,'01:43:55.108','01:43:58.277','If this is where the rats are going, I am, too.',-1),(150619,39,149886,149926,'01:44:05.285','01:44:06.953','- You.\n- There is no emergency.',-1),(150620,39,149932,150000,'01:44:07.204','01:44:10.039','- There is. I\'ve been robbed.\n- Get the Master at Arms.',-1),(150621,39,150014,150054,'01:44:10.624','01:44:12.291','Now, you moron!',-1),(150622,39,150167,150199,'01:44:16.964','01:44:18.297','Did I miss the fun?',-1),(150623,39,150227,150315,'01:44:19.466','01:44:23.135','- Did you see what happened?\n- No. I guess it hit over there.',-1),(150624,39,150343,150445,'01:44:24.304','01:44:28.557','Boiler room six is flooded eight feet\nand the mail hold is worse.',-1),(150625,39,150451,150509,'01:44:28.809','01:44:31.227','- Can you shore up?\n- Not unless the pumps get ahead.',-1),(150626,39,150515,150591,'01:44:31.478','01:44:34.647','- Have you seen the mail hold?\n- It\'s already underwater.',-1),(150627,39,150605,150645,'01:44:35.232','01:44:36.899','This is bad.',-1),(150628,39,150701,150739,'01:44:39.236','01:44:40.820','We should tell Mother and Cal.',-1),(150629,39,150765,150815,'01:44:41.905','01:44:43.990','I think they\'re very good, sir.',-1),(150630,39,150883,150955,'01:44:46.827','01:44:49.829','Don\'t touch anything.\nI want the room photographed.',-1),(150631,39,151076,151128,'01:44:54.835','01:44:57.003','We\'ve been looking for you, miss.',-1),(150632,39,151244,151270,'01:45:01.842','01:45:02.925','Here we go.',-1),(150633,39,151412,151446,'01:45:08.849','01:45:10.266','Something serious has happened.',-1),(150634,39,151484,151520,'01:45:11.852','01:45:13.352','Yes, it has.',-1),(150635,39,151556,151638,'01:45:14.855','01:45:18.274','Indeed.\nTwo things dear to me have disappeared.',-1),(150636,39,151644,151744,'01:45:18.525','01:45:22.695','Now that one is back,\nI know where to find the other. Search him.',-1),(150637,39,151750,151794,'01:45:22.946','01:45:24.780','- Take your coat off.\n- Now what?',-1),(150638,39,151822,151918,'01:45:25.949','01:45:29.952','What are you doing?\nWe\'re in the middle of an emergency.',-1),(150639,39,151924,151974,'01:45:30.203','01:45:32.288','- Is this it?\n- That\'s it.',-1),(150640,39,151988,152032,'01:45:32.873','01:45:34.707','This is horseshit!',-1),(150641,39,152065,152097,'01:45:36.043','01:45:37.376','Don\'t you believe it.',-1),(150642,39,152105,152185,'01:45:37.711','01:45:41.047','- He couldn\'t have.\n- Easy enough for a professional.',-1),(150643,39,152191,152251,'01:45:41.298','01:45:43.799','I was with him the entire time.',-1),(150644,39,152257,152329,'01:45:44.051','01:45:47.053','Perhaps he did it while you were putting\nyour clothes back on, dear.',-1),(150645,39,152369,152423,'01:45:48.722','01:45:50.973','Real slick. They put it in my pocket.',-1),(150646,39,152429,152497,'01:45:51.224','01:45:54.060','- Shut up.\n- It isn\'t even your pocket.',-1),(150647,39,152503,152539,'01:45:54.311','01:45:55.811','\"Property of A.L. Ryerson.\"',-1),(150648,39,152643,152679,'01:46:00.150','01:46:01.650','That was reported stolen.',-1),(150649,39,152685,152723,'01:46:01.902','01:46:03.486','I just borrowed it.',-1),(150650,39,152729,152785,'01:46:03.737','01:46:06.072','Oh, we have an honest thief.',-1),(150651,39,152793,152845,'01:46:06.406','01:46:08.574','You know I didn\'t do this, Rose.',-1),(150652,39,152865,152913,'01:46:09.409','01:46:11.410','Don\'t believe them. You know it.',-1),(150653,39,152919,152943,'01:46:11.661','01:46:12.661','Let\'s go, son.',-1),(150654,39,152949,152993,'01:46:12.913','01:46:14.747','You know I didn\'t do it!',-1),(150655,39,153001,153074,'01:46:15.082','01:46:18.084','There\'s a good lad. Come on.',-1),(150656,39,153082,153138,'01:46:18.418','01:46:20.753','You know I didn\'t do it! You know me!',-1),(150657,39,153184,153238,'01:46:22.672','01:46:24.924','This is most unfortunate, Captain.',-1),(150658,39,153322,153404,'01:46:28.428','01:46:31.847','Water fourteen feet above the keel\nin ten minutes...',-1),(150659,39,153410,153490,'01:46:32.099','01:46:35.434','...in the forepeak,\nall three holds and boiler room six.',-1),(150660,39,153496,153520,'01:46:35.685','01:46:36.685','That\'s right.',-1),(150661,39,153526,153558,'01:46:36.937','01:46:38.270','When can we get underway?',-1),(150662,39,153564,153612,'01:46:38.522','01:46:40.523','That\'s five compartments.',-1),(150663,39,153658,153754,'01:46:42.442','01:46:46.445','She can float with four compartments breached,\nbut not five.',-1),(150664,39,153770,153858,'01:46:47.114','01:46:50.783','Not five. As she goes down,\nthe water will spill...',-1),(150665,39,153864,153964,'01:46:51.034','01:46:55.204','...over the tops of the bulkheads at E deck,\none to the next...',-1),(150666,39,153970,154034,'01:46:55.455','01:46:58.124','...back and back. There\'s no stopping it.',-1),(150667,39,154042,154072,'01:46:58.458','01:46:59.708','The pumps.',-1),(150668,39,154079,154155,'01:46:59.960','01:47:03.129','The pumps buy you time, but minutes only.',-1),(150669,39,154171,154225,'01:47:03.797','01:47:06.048','As of now, no matter what we do...',-1),(150670,39,154247,154299,'01:47:06.967','01:47:09.135','...Titanic will founder.',-1),(150671,39,154355,154387,'01:47:11.471','01:47:12.805','But this ship can\'t sink.',-1),(150672,39,154393,154461,'01:47:13.056','01:47:15.891','She\'s made of iron. I assure you, she can.',-1),(150673,39,154475,154499,'01:47:16.476','01:47:17.476','And she will.',-1),(150674,39,154519,154569,'01:47:18.311','01:47:20.396','It\'s a mathematical certainty.',-1),(150675,39,154675,154711,'01:47:24.818','01:47:26.318','How much time?',-1),(150676,39,154891,154951,'01:47:33.827','01:47:36.328','An hour. Two, at most.',-1),(150677,39,155096,155146,'01:47:42.335','01:47:44.420','How many aboard, Mr. Murdoch?',-1),(150678,39,155156,155224,'01:47:44.838','01:47:47.673','Two thousand, two hundred souls, sir.',-1),(150679,39,155384,155468,'01:47:54.347','01:47:57.850','Well, I believe you may get your headlines,\nMr. Ismay.',-1),(150680,39,155888,155940,'01:48:15.368','01:48:17.536','Oh, it is a little slut, isn\'t it?',-1),(150681,39,155960,156012,'01:48:18.371','01:48:20.539','Look at me when I\'m talking to you!',-1),(150682,39,156018,156070,'01:48:20.790','01:48:22.958','- Mr. Hockley?\n- Not now. We\'re busy.',-1),(150683,39,156077,156159,'01:48:23.210','01:48:26.629','You\'ve been asked to put on lifebelts\nand go to the boat deck.',-1),(150684,39,156165,156189,'01:48:26.880','01:48:27.880','I said, not now.',-1),(150685,39,156195,156315,'01:48:28.131','01:48:33.135','I\'m sorry, Mr. Hockley, but it\'s Captain\'s orders.\nDress warmly.',-1),(150686,39,156321,156373,'01:48:33.386','01:48:35.554','It\'s quite cold out.',-1),(150687,39,156381,156449,'01:48:35.889','01:48:38.724','May I suggest topcoats and hats?',-1),(150688,39,156457,156501,'01:48:39.059','01:48:40.893','This is ridiculous.',-1),(150689,39,156517,156605,'01:48:41.561','01:48:45.231','Not to worry, miss.\nI\'m sure it\'s just a precaution.',-1),(150690,39,156613,156661,'01:48:45.565','01:48:47.566','Everybody up! Lifebelts on!',-1),(150691,39,156701,156739,'01:48:49.236','01:48:50.819','What\'s he on about?',-1),(150692,39,156761,156805,'01:48:51.738','01:48:53.572','- Put your lifebelts on!\n- What is it?',-1),(150693,39,156811,156843,'01:48:53.823','01:48:55.157','Just put them on.',-1),(150694,39,156873,156901,'01:48:56.409','01:48:57.576','C.Q. D?',-1),(150695,39,156917,156945,'01:48:58.245','01:48:59.411','Sir?',-1),(150696,39,156985,157078,'01:49:01.081','01:49:04.917','That\'s right, C.Q.D. The distress call.\nThat\'s our position.',-1),(150697,39,157212,157314,'01:49:10.507','01:49:14.760','Tell whoever responds we\'re going down\nand need immediate assistance.',-1),(150698,39,157542,157574,'01:49:24.271','01:49:25.604','Blimey.',-1),(150699,39,157818,157918,'01:49:35.782','01:49:39.952','Keep lowering!',-1),(150700,39,158010,158103,'01:49:43.790','01:49:47.626','Steady! Make it taut! And winch out!',-1),(150701,39,158195,158291,'01:49:51.464','01:49:55.467','Uncover this boat! Uncover all the boats aft!',-1),(150702,39,158299,158339,'01:49:55.802','01:49:57.469','Release those ties!',-1),(150703,39,158347,158413,'01:49:57.804','01:50:00.556','Roll back that cover! Smartly now!',-1),(150704,39,158427,158463,'01:50:01.141','01:50:02.641','Where are the passengers?',-1),(150705,39,158469,158549,'01:50:02.892','01:50:06.228','They went inside. Too cold and noisy for them.',-1),(150706,39,158555,158659,'01:50:06.479','01:50:10.816','You there! Get down here\nand help with these lines!',-1),(150707,39,158999,159043,'01:50:24.998','01:50:26.832','Care for a drink, sir?',-1),(150708,39,159104,159222,'01:50:29.336','01:50:34.256','Sonny, what\'s doing? You get us all trussed up\nand now we\'re cooling our heels.',-1),(150709,39,159228,159288,'01:50:34.507','01:50:37.009','Sorry, ma\'am. Let me go find out.',-1),(150710,39,159304,159360,'01:50:37.677','01:50:40.012','Nobody knows what\'s going on.',-1),(150711,39,159366,159436,'01:50:40.263','01:50:43.182','Just like the damn English... everything by the book.',-1),(150712,39,159442,159508,'01:50:43.433','01:50:46.185','No need for language, Mr. Hockley.',-1),(150713,39,159512,159628,'01:50:46.353','01:50:51.190','Go back and turn on the heaters in our rooms.\nI want a cup of tea when I return.',-1),(150714,39,159888,159912,'01:51:02.035','01:51:03.035','Mr. Andrews.',-1),(150715,39,159960,160040,'01:51:05.038','01:51:08.374','I saw the iceberg. And I see it in your eyes.',-1),(150716,39,160048,160089,'01:51:08.708','01:51:10.376','Please tell me the truth.',-1),(150717,39,160285,160329,'01:51:18.551','01:51:20.386','The ship will sink.',-1),(150718,39,160371,160395,'01:51:22.138','01:51:23.138','You\'re certain?',-1),(150719,39,160421,160537,'01:51:24.224','01:51:29.061','In an hour or so, all this\nwill be at the bottom of the Atlantic.',-1),(150720,39,160601,160705,'01:51:31.731','01:51:36.068','Please, tell only who you must.\nI don\'t want to cause a panic.',-1),(150721,39,160713,160781,'01:51:36.403','01:51:39.238','And get to a boat. Quickly. Don\'t wait.',-1),(150722,39,160797,160873,'01:51:39.906','01:51:43.075','You remember what I told you about the boats?',-1),(150723,39,160929,160961,'01:51:45.412','01:51:46.745','Yes.',-1),(150724,39,161005,161041,'01:51:48.581','01:51:50.082','I understand.',-1),(150725,39,161234,161266,'01:51:58.091','01:51:59.425','Over here, son.',-1),(150726,39,161290,161366,'01:52:00.427','01:52:03.595','Sir, there\'s a big mob\nat the Second Class Purser\'s office.',-1),(150727,39,161374,161416,'01:52:03.930','01:52:05.681','Go on. I\'ll watch him.',-1),(150728,39,161434,161482,'01:52:06.433','01:52:08.434','Aye. Right.',-1),(150729,39,161810,161930,'01:52:22.115','01:52:27.119','Sir, Carpathia says they\'re making 17 knots.\nFull steam for them, sir.',-1),(150730,39,161974,162008,'01:52:28.955','01:52:30.372','She\'s the only one responding?',-1),(150731,39,162014,162101,'01:52:30.623','01:52:34.209','The only one close. They\'ll be here in four hours.',-1),(150732,39,162119,162159,'01:52:34.961','01:52:36.628','Four hours?!',-1),(150733,39,162279,162315,'01:52:41.634','01:52:43.135','Thank you, Bride.',-1),(150734,39,162419,162459,'01:52:47.474','01:52:49.141','My God.',-1),(150735,39,162687,162735,'01:52:58.651','01:53:00.652','We are swung out and ready, sir.',-1),(150736,39,162771,162865,'01:53:02.155','01:53:06.074','Hadn\'t we better get the women and children\ninto the boats?',-1),(150737,39,162911,162935,'01:53:07.994','01:53:08.994','Yes.',-1),(150738,39,163035,163112,'01:53:13.166','01:53:16.335','Women and children first, yes.'