:48.537','00:29:51.123','Facemash did exactly\nwhat he wanted it to do.',-1),(154707,12,42988,43049,'00:29:51.207','00:29:53.727','Were you aware that while Mr Zuckerberg\nwas building The Facebook,',-1),(154708,12,43050,43093,'00:29:53.751','00:29:55.551','he was also communicating\nwith the plaintiffs?',-1),(154709,12,43095,43147,'00:29:55.628','00:29:57.797','Not at the time, I wasn\'t. But...',-1),(154710,12,43193,43260,'00:29:59.715','00:30:02.510','It really didn\'t have much to do\nwith the Winklevosses\' dating site.',-1),(154711,12,43262,43288,'00:30:02.593','00:30:03.695','How would you know?\nYou weren\'t even there.',-1),(154712,12,43289,43315,'00:30:03.719','00:30:04.804','Ty.',-1),(154713,12,43323,43397,'00:30:05.137','00:30:08.224','Were you aware that while Mr Zuckerberg\nwas building The Facebook,',-1),(154714,12,43399,43482,'00:30:08.307','00:30:11.769','he was leading the plaintiffs to believe\nhe was building Harvard Connection?',-1),(154715,12,43485,43520,'00:30:11.894','00:30:13.372','You\'re offering a conclusion\nnot found in evidence.',-1),(154716,12,43521,43585,'00:30:13.396','00:30:16.065','We are about to find it in evidence.',-1),(154717,12,43598,43649,'00:30:16.607','00:30:18.734','From Mark Zuckerberg to Tyler Winklevoss.',-1),(154718,12,43657,43695,'00:30:19.068','00:30:20.653','November 30th, 2003.',-1),(154719,12,43697,43769,'00:30:20.736','00:30:23.739','\"I read over all the stuff you sent me\nre: Harvard Connection.',-1),(154720,12,43771,43835,'00:30:23.823','00:30:26.492','\"And it seems like it shouldn\'t\ntake too long to implement.',-1),(154721,12,43837,43950,'00:30:26.575','00:30:31.288','\"So we can talk about it after I get all\nthe basic functionality up tomorrow night.\"',-1),(154722,12,43953,44059,'00:30:31.414','00:30:35.793','From Mark Zuckerberg\nto Cameron Winklevoss. December 1st, 2003.',-1),(154723,12,44062,44145,'00:30:35.918','00:30:39.380','\"Sorry I was unreachable tonight. I just\ngot about three of your missed calls.',-1),(154724,12,44147,44215,'00:30:39.463','00:30:42.299','\"I was working on a problem set\nfor my systems class.\"',-1),(154725,12,44218,44272,'00:30:42.425','00:30:44.677','From Mark Zuckerberg\nto Tyler and Cameron Winklevoss.',-1),(154726,12,44274,44326,'00:30:44.760','00:30:46.929','December 10, 2003.',-1),(154727,12,44340,44404,'00:30:47.513','00:30:50.182','\"This week has been pretty busy\nthus far with classes and work,',-1),(154728,12,44406,44481,'00:30:50.266','00:30:53.394','\"so I think it\'s probably best\nto postpone the meeting.\"',-1),(154729,12,44483,44534,'00:30:53.477','00:30:55.604','\"I\'m also really busy tomorrow.\"',-1),(154730,12,44536,44617,'00:30:55.688','00:30:59.066','Okay, anybody else feel like\nthere\'s something up with this guy?',-1),(154731,12,44619,44644,'00:30:59.150','00:31:00.192','Tell him okay,',-1),(154732,12,44646,44717,'00:31:00.276','00:31:03.236','but we do have to make sure that\nwe meet up before we all go off for break.',-1),(154733,12,44726,44792,'00:31:03.612','00:31:06.365','I know, I know. Yeah, watch out.',-1),(154734,12,45535,45564,'00:31:37.313','00:31:38.522','Hey, Mark.',-1),(154735,12,45567,45636,'00:31:38.647','00:31:41.525','I need a dedicated Linux box\nrunning Apache with a MySQL back end.',-1),(154736,12,45639,45674,'00:31:41.650','00:31:43.110','It\'s gonna cost a little more money.',-1),(154737,12,45676,45733,'00:31:43.194','00:31:45.571','- How much more?\n- About 200 more.',-1),(154738,12,45737,45795,'00:31:45.738','00:31:48.157','- Do we need it?\n- Gotta handle the traffic.',-1),(154739,12,45875,45920,'00:31:51.494','00:31:53.370','- Do it.\n- I already did.',-1),(154740,12,46024,46052,'00:31:57.708','00:31:58.834','Hey, guess what?',-1),(154741,12,46093,46132,'00:32:00.544','00:32:02.171','I made the second cut.',-1),(154742,12,46149,46174,'00:32:02.880','00:32:03.923','That\'s good.',-1),(154743,12,46176,46264,'00:32:04.006','00:32:07.676','You should be proud of that right there. Don\'t\nworry if you don\'t make it any further.',-1),(154744,12,46380,46415,'00:32:12.515','00:32:13.974','I\'ll get out of here.',-1),(154745,12,46417,46473,'00:32:14.058','00:32:16.393','From Mark Zuckerberg\nto Tyler and Cameron Winklevoss',-1),(154746,12,46475,46500,'00:32:16.477','00:32:17.520','and Divya Narendra.',-1),(154747,12,46502,46554,'00:32:17.603','00:32:19.772','December 15th, 2003.',-1),(154748,12,46556,46613,'00:32:19.855','00:32:22.233','\"I have a CS problem set\nthat I\'m just getting started with',-1),(154749,12,46615,46703,'00:32:22.316','00:32:25.986','\"and it should be about 15 hours of coding,\nso I\'ll be busy tomorrow night.\"',-1),(154750,12,46705,46785,'00:32:26.070','00:32:29.406','\"I won\'t really be free to meet\nuntil next Wednesday afternoon.\"',-1),(154751,12,46787,46838,'00:32:29.490','00:32:31.617','\"I have to cancel Wednesday afternoon.',-1),(154752,12,46840,46916,'00:32:31.700','00:32:34.870','\"I\'ve basically been in the lab\nthis whole time, and also',-1),(154753,12,46919,47029,'00:32:34.995','00:32:39.583','\"won\'t be able to do Saturday,\nas I have to meet up with my parents.\"',-1),(154754,12,47129,47235,'00:32:43.712','00:32:48.134','As the plaque reads, this is John Harvard,\nfounder of Harvard University in 1638.',-1),(154755,12,47237,47293,'00:32:48.217','00:32:50.553','It\'s also called the Statue of Three Lies.',-1),(154756,12,47312,47363,'00:32:51.345','00:32:53.472','What are the three lies?',-1),(154757,12,47384,47410,'00:32:54.348','00:32:55.432','Mr Dowd.',-1),(154758,12,47413,47463,'00:32:55.558','00:32:57.643','The three lies. First...',-1),(154759,12,47467,47492,'00:32:57.810','00:32:58.853','Shit!',-1),(154760,12,47494,47538,'00:32:58.936','00:33:00.771','- Take your pants off.\n- I know.',-1),(154761,12,47566,47596,'00:33:01.939','00:33:03.190','Mr Saverin.',-1),(154762,12,47598,47683,'00:33:03.274','00:33:06.819','One, Harvard was founded in 1636, not 1638.',-1),(154763,12,47685,47741,'00:33:06.902','00:33:09.238','Two, Harvard was not founded\nby John Harvard.',-1),(154764,12,47743,47780,'00:33:09.321','00:33:10.865','And three, that is not John Harvard.',-1),(154765,12,47782,47814,'00:33:10.948','00:33:12.283','Who is it?',-1),(154766,12,47828,47915,'00:33:12.867','00:33:16.495','It\'s a friend of the\nsculptor, Daniel Chester.',-1),(154767,12,47937,47964,'00:33:17.413','00:33:18.539','Keep your jacket on.',-1),(154768,12,48060,48143,'00:33:22.501','00:33:25.963','Thirty-nine days after Mr Zuckerberg\'s\ninitial meeting with my clients,',-1),(154769,12,48145,48226,'00:33:26.046','00:33:29.425','and he still hadn\'t completed work\non Harvard Connection.',-1),(154770,12,48229,48295,'00:33:29.550','00:33:32.303','But on January 11th, 2004,',-1),(154771,12,48313,48390,'00:33:33.053','00:33:36.265','Mr Zuckerberg registered\nthe domain name The Facebook',-1),(154772,12,48392,48459,'00:33:36.348','00:33:39.143','via Network Solutions.',-1),(154773,12,48487,48582,'00:33:40.311','00:33:44.273','To the best of your knowledge, had he even\nbegun work on Harvard Connection?',-1),(154774,12,48610,48659,'00:33:45.441','00:33:47.484','Not to my knowledge. No.',-1),(154775,12,48762,48813,'00:33:51.780','00:33:53.908','What in the world is this?',-1),(154776,12,48840,48938,'00:33:55.034','00:33:59.121','\"Hey, Cameron, I\'m still a little sceptical\nthat we have enough functionality in the site',-1),(154777,12,48940,49003,'00:33:59.205','00:34:01.805','\"to really draw the attention\nand gain the critical mass necessary',-1),(154778,12,49007,49068,'00:34:01.999','00:34:04.501','\"to get a site like this to run\"?',-1),(154779,12,49081,49114,'00:34:05.044','00:34:06.420','\"We\'ll speak soon\"?',-1),(154780,12,49169,49232,'00:34:08.714','00:34:11.342','This is the first time\nhe mentioned any problem?',-1),(154781,12,49235,49260,'00:34:11.467','00:34:12.509','Yes, it was.',-1),(154782,12,49262,49370,'00:34:12.593','00:34:17.097','You sent 36 e-mails to Mr Zuckerberg\nand received 16 e-mails in return,',-1),(154783,12,49372,49434,'00:34:17.181','00:34:19.767','and this was the first time\nhe indicated he was not happy.',-1),(154784,12,49436,49461,'00:34:19.850','00:34:20.893','That\'s correct.',-1),(154785,12,49463,49527,'00:34:20.976','00:34:23.646','He had 42 days to study our system\nand get out ahead.',-1),(154786,12,49529,49580,'00:34:23.729','00:34:25.874','- Do you see any of your code on Facebook?\n- Sy, could you...',-1),(154787,12,49581,49618,'00:34:25.898','00:34:27.441','Did I use any of your code?',-1),(154788,12,49620,49664,'00:34:27.524','00:34:29.360','You stole our whole goddamn idea.',-1),(154789,12,49666,49719,'00:34:29.443','00:34:31.654','- Fellas.\n- What? Match.com for Harvard guys?',-1),(154790,12,49721,49750,'00:34:31.737','00:34:32.923','Can I continue with my deposition?',-1),(154791,12,49750,49825,'00:34:32.947','00:34:36.075','You know, you really don\'t need a forensics\nteam to get to the bottom of this.',-1),(154792,12,49827,49869,'00:34:36.158','00:34:37.878','If you guys were the inventors of Facebook,',-1),(154793,12,49899,49947,'00:34:39.161','00:34:41.163','you\'d have invented Facebook.',-1),(154794,12,49966,50030,'00:34:41.956','00:34:44.601','I can\'t wait to stand over your shoulder\nand watch you write us a cheque.',-1),(154795,12,50031,50062,'00:34:44.625','00:34:45.918','No shit.',-1),(154796,12,50104,50136,'00:34:47.670','00:34:49.004','Let\'s continue.',-1),(154797,12,50176,50235,'00:34:50.673','00:34:53.133','February 4, 2004.',-1),(154798,12,50321,50349,'00:34:56.720','00:34:57.888','Mark.',-1),(154799,12,50367,50395,'00:34:58.639','00:34:59.807','Mark.',-1),(154800,12,50397,50490,'00:34:59.890','00:35:03.769','There is a girl in your art history class.\nHer name is Stephanie Attis.',-1),(154801,12,50492,50537,'00:35:03.852','00:35:05.729','Do you happen to know\nif she has a boyfriend?',-1),(154802,12,50572,50625,'00:35:07.189','00:35:09.400','Have you ever seen her with anyone?',-1),(1548